NK070(thu)001:1: // dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i 'grel pa spar khab kyi
NK070(thu)001:2: mchan 'grel nyi ma'i 'od zer zhes bya ba nam
NK070(thu)001:3: mkha' dpal bas mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:5: rgya gar ba rnams kyi skad du /
NK070(thu)001:6: ma h+aa ga ra dza kha ta na tra ka
NK070(thu)001:7: sh+r+ai ngag+hu ya cagar+b+ha chana ma nyatri ka jabod skad
NK070(thu)001:8: du / sgra bsgyur ba la bskrugs te bsgyur ba
NK070(thu)001:9: thang logs su thod logs su bsgrur ba dang gsum
NK070(thu)001:10: las 'dir bskrugs te bsgrur ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:11: rgyud kyi ka rgyal po kha chen po ga dpal
NK070(thu)001:12: ngagsang ba'i casnying po'i cha'grel pa jazhes bya ba nyazhes
NK070(thu)001:13: bya ba de la 'bru 'grel don 'grel bsdus 'grel
NK070(thu)001:14: rgya che 'grel la sogs pa yod pa las 'di
NK070(thu)001:16: dpal gyi don la gsum rdo rje la chos lnga
NK070(thu)001:17: sems la bzhi'am lnga dpa' phrin la bzhi bdud bcom
NK070(thu)001:18: pas yul de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK070(thu)001:19: gang gis na sgegs pa rdo rjes tshul ci ltar na gsum /
NK070(thu)001:20: don yod la tshogs rdzogs sgrig pa dag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:21: rgyud kyi ston pa ni dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid che //
NK070(thu)001:22: na so 'khor 'das kun gyis byed pa po drug
NK070(thu)001:23: pa kun bzang des thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ston
NK070(thu)001:24: pa'i tshe 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa'
NK070(thu)001:26: bo mdun du gnas par byed cing dus gsum gyis
NK070(thu)001:27: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa lam dang 'bras bus tha dag
NK070(thu)001:29: rgyal ba thams cad kyis bdag nyid kun bzang yid rang byung ye shes la'ang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK070(thu)001:30: zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhi drangs de'i khyad par gyi chos la bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:32: de ltar ston pa kun tu bzang po dang rdo
NK070(thu)001:33: rje sems dpa' gnyis la mchod par brjod pa'i phyag
NK070(thu)001:34: byas nas // brjod bya'i don mngon gsum gtan la phab ste /
NK070(thu)001:36: gsal bar byed pa brjod byed lam gyi rgyud gcig gis 'byung khungs su gyur bas na gter //
NK070(thu)001:37: des na spyi don gyis rnam grangs gzhi lam 'bras
NK070(thu)001:38: bu gsum 'khrul ba'i snang ba dang bzhi'i don mtshon
NK070(thu)001:40: theg pa kun gyis mthar thug lam 'bras bus gsang sngags kyi theg pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:41: de yang rgyas par bkrol ba ma yin pas mdor
NK070(thu)001:42: bsdus pa tsam gcig bdag sgeg pa'i rdo rjes thugs
NK070(thu)001:43: kyi dgongs pa zhal du phyung nas dbye bar bya
NK070(thu)001:45: de la spyir gsang sngags phyi nang bla med kyi rgyud mtha' dag khog dbubs gzhi lam 'bras bu'i /
NK070(thu)001:46: rgyud gsum gyi dbye bas bshad de /
NK070(thu)001:48: gzhi rang bzhin gyis snang ba 'bras ba /
NK070(thu)001:49: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba lam /
NK070(thu)001:52: snang ba dang gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK070(thu)001:54: mtshon byed tshig gis rgyud kyis dbye ba rnam par bzhag /
NK070(thu)001:56: don la gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi ngo bo gcig
NK070(thu)001:57: pa yin la gsum gyi ngo bo rang byung ba
NK070(thu)001:58: de yang yang // gang gis byas na rang ngo rang gi ma shes pas /
NK070(thu)001:59: 'khrul pa'i snang bas phye bas gzhi lam 'bras gsum du 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:61: des na 'khrul ba'i snang ba dang gzhi po dag tu //
NK070(thu)001:63: rgyal ba'i lung dang bla ma dam pa'i rig pas
NK070(thu)001:64: bkod pa'i man ngag gis bstan chos kun las de
NK070(thu)001:68: gzhi don byang chub kyi sems rang rigs pa thams
NK070(thu)001:69: cad nyid 'khor 'das kyi chos du rtsal ma 'gag
NK070(thu)001:70: par yul med du rang snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:71: gzhi rang bzhin gyis snang ba'i nges tshig yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:72: gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya shes byed du 'brel la /
NK070(thu)001:73: gzhi dang 'bras bu ngo bo bdag gcig par thams
NK070(thu)001:74: cad du 'brel cing gzhi la shes bya yon tan
NK070(thu)001:75: gyi dgos pa thams cad du tshang ba'i phyir rang
NK070(thu)001:76: bzhin gyi rgyud kyis nges tshig du gsungs la gzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:77: don de nges par ston pa'ang 'i theg pa blo'i
NK070(thu)001:78: che chung gi rim pas phye bas bstan pa theg
NK070(thu)001:79: pa rim dgu bye brag tu snang ba rnams ni
NK070(thu)001:80: / gdul bya'i snang ba'i nges tshig rnams yin te /
NK070(thu)001:81: 'brel pa'i gzhi dang rjes su mthun cing de'ang lam
NK070(thu)001:82: dang gzhi gnyis shes bya shes byed du 'brel la
NK070(thu)001:83: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis thob bya thob byed du
NK070(thu)001:84: 'brel / lam la thams cad bgrod cing 'gro ba'i
NK070(thu)001:85: yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang ba'i phyir lam gyi
NK070(thu)001:86: 'brel / rgyud do // kyi nges tshig tu brjod /
NK070(thu)001:87: lam bgrod pa de mthar thug pa ni 'bras bu de yang spang bya'i sgrib pa bral dang /
NK070(thu)001:88: rtogs bya'i 'bras bu gsar du thob pa med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:89: sa ye gdod ma nas gzhi ngo bo nyid du
NK070(thu)001:91: lhun gyis grub pas na de nyid rtogs pa'i rig
NK070(thu)001:92: pa la sku dang ye shes thams cad rdzogs pa
NK070(thu)001:94: de pa'i snang 'i nges tshig yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:95: 'brel pa ni gang gis rjes su snyag pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:96: 'bras bu dang gzhi gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig
NK070(thu)001:97: par 'brel la / 'bras bu dang lam gnyis thob bya thob byed du 'brel cing /
NK070(thu)001:98: 'bras bu thob bya yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang bas 'bras bu'i rgyud te kyi nges tshig yin /
NK070(thu)001:99: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i snang ba de dag ngo bo nyid gcig pa la /
NK070(thu)001:100: gzhi lam 'bras gsum rim par snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:101: yul yul can kun tu brtag pa gzung 'dzin sna
NK070(thu)001:102: tshogs kyi rang bzhin gyis snang ba la bsgrib pa
NK070(thu)001:103: dang / de lam gyi spangs pas sangs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:104: 'bras bu'i snang ba dang gsum du phye ba gang yin pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:105: sgrib byed kyi 'khrul pa'i snang bar gsungs pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:106: na 'brel ba dgos pa dang dgos pa med pas
NK070(thu)001:107: snang ba yin yang rgyud ma yin pas gsum po'i
NK070(thu)001:108: zhar las bshad pas na snang ba bzhir phye bar
NK070(thu)001:109: 'gyur ro // de la rang gzhi bzhin gyis snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:110: log rtog 'khrul ba'i snang ba dang sbyar te bshad na rgyas pa'i gzhung nyid la /
NK070(thu)001:111: rnal ma don gyi sa kun gzhi'i rnam par 'char
NK070(thu)001:112: ba'i shes pa nyid gsal cha de phyi nang gi
NK070(thu)001:113: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ste /
NK070(thu)001:115: rang rig pa'i gnas lugs kyis dbang du 'khor 'das kyi chos cir yang snang ba de dag nyid /
NK070(thu)001:116: rang rig pa nyid kyi phyir rtsal du rang snang ba'i /
NK070(thu)001:117: gzhi'i snang ba de la lam dang 'bras bu'i yon
NK070(thu)001:118: tan tshang zhing lam dang 'bras bu'i rgyud gnyis kyang
NK070(thu)001:119: gnas skabs las shes bya shes byed dang ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:120: bdag nyid gcig par 'brel pas na rgyud de /
NK070(thu)001:121: de yang gzhi rang bzhin gyis snang ba'i zhar las
NK070(thu)001:122: bshad pa'i 'khrul pa'i nyes pa lnga'i rang bzhin gyis
NK070(thu)001:123: snang ba la / bsgrib pas de dag par byed
NK070(thu)001:124: pa la lam thabs grol gnyis las rag las par
NK070(thu)001:125: snang ba la / snang ngo // nyes pa nyes
NK070(thu)001:126: pa la lnga gang yin snyam pa la 'khrul pa'i
NK070(thu)001:127: rgyu rkyen byed pa ngo bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:128: 'khrul pa de'i nyes pa dang lnga po ni /
NK070(thu)001:129: rgyal bas rgyud nas gsungs so zhes 'byung ste /
NK070(thu)001:130: rgyu ni 'di nyid kyi gzhung las /
NK070(thu)001:131: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba la /
NK070(thu)001:132: nges shes ma skyes pa ni lhan cig skye pa'i ma rig rtog pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:133: kun tu brtag pa'i ma rig pas bdag gnyis su /
NK070(thu)001:134: pa'i phyir phyi nang gi gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i rkyen gyis /
NK070(thu)001:135: nyon mongs pa skye ba lags so //
NK070(thu)001:137: rkyen ni rang gi sems rnam par rtog pas kun brtag kyi nyon mongs skyes des /
NK070(thu)001:138: las sna tshogs su spyad pas glo bur kyi lus su snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:141: byed pa po ni rgyas pa'i le'u bco lnga pa las sems nyid /
NK070(thu)001:142: ma bcos pa'i don de ngo ma shes pas dag ma dag gi /
NK070(thu)001:144: de'i ma byas pa'i dngos po 'khor ba'i chos gang yang med //
NK070(thu)001:147: ngo bo ni las sna tshogs bsags pa'i stobs kyis lus bzang na dang longs spyod dang //
NK070(thu)001:149: gnas la mtho dman dang 'khor ba spyi bye brag gi sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK070(thu)001:150: ra bsdu ba ni las nyon te /
NK070(thu)001:151: gong gi de la nang du sems bdag dang yul bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK070(thu)001:153: de yang gshis la ma grub pa na bdag dang
NK070(thu)001:154: ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnams kyis tshogs brgyad
NK070(thu)001:155: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK070(thu)001:156: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba 'di rnams ni //
NK070(thu)001:158: ngo ma shes pa'i dbang gis log par rtog pa'i ngo bo tsam nyid du snang ba las //
NK070(thu)001:159: don la ni nyan thos ltar phra zhing rdul phran dang rang rgyal ltar /
NK070(thu)001:160: zab pa'ang 'i 'di skad cig de ma rang rgyud du yod pa ma yin te //
NK070(thu)001:163: gnyis te sdug bsngal myong ba'i nyes pa ni rgyas
NK070(thu)001:164: pa las 'khrul pa'i chos rnams gzhi ye gdod ma
NK070(thu)001:166: 'phrul pa'i rgyu gzung 'dzin phyin ci log gi phyogs su blo log nas //
NK070(thu)001:167: 'bras bu log rtog nyid snang ba'i gnas mtho dman dang longs spyod dang //
NK070(thu)001:168: che chung de dag rgyu ma rig pa las byung
NK070(thu)001:169: ba'i sdug bsngal gyi 'khrul 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab
NK070(thu)001:171: 'phags pa'i lam dang bral ba'i nyes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:173: rgyas pa las 'gro drug gi sems can ma lus pa thams cad la //
NK070(thu)001:174: sems tshogs brgyad kyi ngo bo ye shes lnga'i kun la khyab kyang //
NK070(thu)001:175: rang gi rnam par rtog pas sgrib par byas nas //
NK070(thu)001:176: ye shes lnga'i yin pa don dam nyid ma mthong //
NK070(thu)001:179: 'khrul pa sgrib pa de'i phyir gnyen po /
NK070(thu)001:180: gzhi lam gyi rang gi ngo bo nyid sgrib pa
NK070(thu)001:181: dang bral bar mngon sum du byas pa la tha
NK070(thu)001:182: snyad du 'bras bur zhes ming 'dogs kyang gzhi lam
NK070(thu)001:183: 'bras bu gsum don gyi ngo bo nyid na dbyer
NK070(thu)001:185: lam rim las de nyid lam gyi ngo bo ste /
NK070(thu)001:188: gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni /
NK070(thu)001:189: lam dang 'bras bu thams cad kyi tha snyad gdag pa'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:190: rgyas pa las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang
NK070(thu)001:191: rig pa byang chub kyi sems de ni rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:192: gyis sgro bkur dang bral bar nges pas /
NK070(thu)001:193: lung gi tshad mar bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:194: de tshad ma rtogs pa gazhi'am mnyam pa bzhis gtan la phabs pa'i don yin te /
NK070(thu)001:195: snod bcud rgyud rnams yab yum ye shes su /
NK070(thu)001:196: dag pa gsum gyi tshul du rang la gnas shing /
NK070(thu)001:197: de dag mtshan byed yig 'bru lnga'i ngo bor 'dus pa'i phyir de nyid rtsal ma 'gag par /
NK070(thu)001:199: 'gro ba drug po kun la rang bzhin ngam shugs kyi gnas so //
NK070(thu)001:203: 'bras bu thob tshul dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK070(thu)001:204: gzhi dang 'i nyes pa ma rig pa /
NK070(thu)001:205: lam gyi nyes pa shes sgrib rtsol ba /
NK070(thu)001:206: gnyis zad pa gang yin pa de ni /
NK070(thu)001:207: bde gshegs pa'i snang ba'i yin pa phyir 'bras bu zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:210: ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa /
NK070(thu)001:211: 'bras bu dang lam gnyis byin rlabs kyi 'brel pa dang ste thob bya thob byed du 'brel pa /
NK070(thu)001:212: bdag don chos sku rang gzugs sku gzhan gyi dgos pa phun sum tshogs pa'i thob pa /
NK070(thu)001:214: bye brag tu bshad pa de la grangs gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:215: 'brel te de la dang po 'bras bu'i ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:216: ni / mtshan nyid gcig dang du ma 'di 'drar gnas so zhes brjod par dka' na /
NK070(thu)001:217: yang gdul bya rmongs pa rnams kyi don du grangs rgyas par bsam gyis mi khyab kyang /
NK070(thu)001:218: mdor sku lnga gsung lnga thugs lnga yon tan lnga phrin las lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:219: nyi shu rtsa lngar bsdu bar mdzad do //
NK070(thu)001:220: gnyis pa de thob pa'i tshul ni /
NK070(thu)001:221: gnyen po lam gyi lta ba gtan tshigs dang /
NK070(thu)001:222: bsgoms pa'i rtsol ba nyes pa dang gnyis zad pa'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:223: gzhan nas ma byung ste gzhi'i don rang rig pa'i
NK070(thu)001:224: mngon sum du snang ba la 'bras bu 'dogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:226: sems nyid cir yang ma yin pa la cir yang
NK070(thu)001:227: snang ba ngo mtshar ba'i cho 'phrul sku rigs rgyan
NK070(thu)001:228: 'khor nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun gyi grub pas na
NK070(thu)001:231: de dag gzhan nas yod pa gcig par du 'ong ba ni ma yin te //
NK070(thu)001:232: 'o na gang las byung zhe na thabs 'gags pa
NK070(thu)001:233: med pa la brten pa'i shes rab rang bzhin med
NK070(thu)001:234: pa dang tha dad med pa nyid //
NK070(thu)001:237: rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba de lta
NK070(thu)001:238: bu'i rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i ngang du rang
NK070(thu)001:243: rgyu 'bras sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rang chas su
NK070(thu)001:244: dbyer med ye nas gnas pas dus la snga phyi
NK070(thu)001:246: de bas ye nas pa gnas pa'i 'bras bu shes
NK070(thu)001:247: shing thob par byed pas lam du gyur par byas
NK070(thu)001:248: nas rgyu 'bras / dus gcig ngo bo mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:249: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:250: gsum pa gdul bya lam gyis snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:251: lam skye na yi ge'i rgyud dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK070(thu)001:252: gzhi don de dag shes par byed pa dang 'bras
NK070(thu)001:253: bu bsgrub par byed pa la lam du btags te
NK070(thu)001:254: / de'ang blo'i shes rab che chung gi bye brag
NK070(thu)001:255: gis phye bas theg pa rim pa dgu tha dad
NK070(thu)001:257: de la drug ste rgyud kyi ngo bo dang nges
NK070(thu)001:258: tshig dang dgos ched dang byung tshul dang rgyud don
NK070(thu)001:259: du gnyer ba dang rgyud bshad thabs kyi dbye ba'o
NK070(thu)001:261: dang po rgyud kyi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:262: phyag na rdo rjes dbang bskur ba'i rgyud la sogs pa bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK070(thu)001:263: de kho na nyid bsdus pa'i rgyud la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:264: skor thub pa'i rgyud dang rnal 'byor nang pa thabs
NK070(thu)001:266: nang pa'i rgyud de la yang gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:267: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud la sogs pa thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK070(thu)001:268: dpal bde ba mchog gi rgyud la sogs pa shes rab kyi rgyud dang /
NK070(thu)001:269: dpal sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i rgyud la sogs pa gnyis med ma ning gi rgyud do //
NK070(thu)001:270: de la dpal gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni /
NK070(thu)001:271: rgyud thams cad kyi brjod bya'i don dang brjod bya
NK070(thu)001:272: la'ang rgyu mtshan nyid dang 'bras bu gsang sngags phyi
NK070(thu)001:273: nang gi don kun tshang bar 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:274: rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi yin par rtsa rgyud kyi le'u tha ma dang /
NK070(thu)001:275: rgyas pa'i le'u bdun pa las gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:277: shes bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud dang thob bya 'bras bu'i rgyud dang rnam pa gnyis las //
NK070(thu)001:278: de gnyis shes par byed pa dang thob par byed
NK070(thu)001:279: pa la'i de'i ming gi lam gyis rgyud du brtag
NK070(thu)001:280: pa'i don gyi gzhan las thob pa'i nges tshig gnyis
NK070(thu)001:282: lam rgyud de 'byung bar byed pa la rgyu gleng
NK070(thu)001:283: gzhi rkyen gleng bslang dang de ltar thabs byung dang
NK070(thu)001:284: rgyu dang 'bras bur 'brel pa dang de la dgos
NK070(thu)001:285: pa dngos po med rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:287: lam gyis rgyud rang gis thob pa'i nges tshig bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:291: gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i
NK070(thu)001:292: don sems can thams cad la yongs su grub pa
NK070(thu)001:293: de / lam gyi rgyud thabs shes ma ning gsum
NK070(thu)001:294: gyi phyin ci ma log par mngon gsum du yongs
NK070(thu)001:295: su grub par bya ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:296: des thob bya 'bras bu'i rgyud mngon gsum du snang bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:297: dang po ji ltar byung ba'i tshul ni rgyal ba
NK070(thu)001:298: drug pa'i ston pa la rtsol med du lhun gyis
NK070(thu)001:299: grub pa'i sa thugs rje skye ba thabs dang gdul
NK070(thu)001:300: bya'i / smon lam gyi go phye nas le'u dang
NK070(thu)001:301: por rgyu gleng gzhi snang bar mdzad le'u gnyis par
NK070(thu)001:302: rkyen gleng bslang sbyar le'u gsum par thun mong bca'
NK070(thu)001:303: gzhi'i ston pa thub pa drug snang bar mdzad de
NK070(thu)001:304: bya'i / / thun mong ma yin par 'og min du gsungs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:305: mi yul du thun mong ba gsungs pa rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:306: yang na thub pas thun mong dang thun mong ma
NK070(thu)001:307: yin pa gsungs pa rnams dus mtshungs par theg pa
NK070(thu)001:308: tha dad par snang ba'i mado'am rgyud rnams 'byung ngo
NK070(thu)001:309: // gnyen bya don gyi ngo bo de ni gzhi'i rgyud mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:310: lam ngo bo'i rgyud phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs su grub pa gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:311: gdul bya tha mal pa'i blo chung ba rnams lam
NK070(thu)001:312: la brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir thob bya 'bras bu'i
NK070(thu)001:313: chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid brjod pa'i gnyer yod pa'o
NK070(thu)001:314: // rgyud kyi khog gzhung bshad pa'i thabs ni /
NK070(thu)001:315: gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyis don du /
NK070(thu)001:316: rgyud don bshad thabs mtshan bstan rnam dbye 'bru gnyer gsum mo //
NK070(thu)001:317: gsum po de la dang po rab kyis don du
NK070(thu)001:318: rgyud kyis mtshan bshad pa sa go ba la yang
NK070(thu)001:319: / rgyud 'dir gsum ste rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyis
NK070(thu)001:320: ngo bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i mtshan thun mong
NK070(thu)001:322: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa'i bstan pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:323: che ba las mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:324: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyis lung gi spyi'o //
NK070(thu)001:325: brjod bya don gyi ngo bo nyid las mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:326: bod skad du gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:328: de la gsang ba la gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:329: rang bzhin du gnas lugs sbas pa dang spyod pa'i khyad par /
NK070(thu)001:332: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba ni gzhung nyid las /
NK070(thu)001:333: e ma'o don dam ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK070(thu)001:334: kun rdzob sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK070(thu)001:335: bden pa dbyer med ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang //
NK070(thu)001:336: 'bras bu rang la gnas pas spyod yul dang bral ba gzhan du min la shin tu gsang //
NK070(thu)001:338: dang po ye nas gsang ba'i ngo bo ni snang
NK070(thu)001:339: stong gnyis su med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:340: la che ba'i yon tan gyis chos skor bdun ril
NK070(thu)001:341: lhun gyis grub pa'i don de 'gro ba thams cad
NK070(thu)001:342: la rang chas su yod kyang lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:343: ma rig pas ngo ma shes pas rang rigs la
NK070(thu)001:344: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa kho na la
NK070(thu)001:346: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK070(thu)001:347: rang byung ye shes de nyid rang snang ba'i kun
NK070(thu)001:348: rdzob sna tshogs snang ba'i dngos po 'bras bu sku
NK070(thu)001:349: gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin ril mi zad pa rgyan
NK070(thu)001:350: gyi 'khor lo rang bzhin gyis rgyud du gnas pa
NK070(thu)001:351: la dngos po rang kha mar kun tu brtag pas
NK070(thu)001:352: don sku ye shes bsgrib pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:356: shes bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don la yul sems dang rgyu 'bras dang /
NK070(thu)001:358: tha dad du dbye ba las grol te thams cad
NK070(thu)001:359: rig pa rang snang ba'i phyir dbyer med kyis don
NK070(thu)001:360: rang gi ngo bo nyid blo yul du bya bar
NK070(thu)001:362: yin kyang snang stong tha dad du bzung bas ngo ma shes pa rab tu gsang ba /
NK070(thu)001:366: 'bras bu'i rgyud bsgrub par bya ba de rang gi sems las gud na ste gzhan du med kyang /
NK070(thu)001:367: nyon mongs pa dug gsum mam /
NK070(thu)001:368: ma rig pa dang de'i gnyen po shes bya dang /
NK070(thu)001:369: 'og ma'i lta ba'i la zhen pas gong mas don
NK070(thu)001:370: la sgrib pas na shin tu gsang ba de bas
NK070(thu)001:372: 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad rang rig pa la snang ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:373: sbas pa'i gsang ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK070(thu)001:374: gab spas na spyod pa'i khyad par mi spang ba lnga /
NK070(thu)001:378: sta na sgrol ba g+ha na dang sbyor ba /
NK070(thu)001:379: sngags kyis spangs par bya ba med pa la sogs pa'i sgras rdzun ma byin len ngag barlanga po /
NK070(thu)001:380: rnams dgag sgrub med pa'i lta ba dang blang dor med pa'i spyod pa ma go //
NK070(thu)001:382: gzod sngags kyis spyod pa la 'jug par gsung pa de dag gang la sbas na /
NK070(thu)001:383: spyad kyang mi gso ba'i kasngags kyi man ngag med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:384: don ma rtogs par khasgra ci bzhin spyod pa'i sngags
NK070(thu)001:385: la log pa ru tra dang phyi rol pa rnams
NK070(thu)001:386: kyis rang kha mar spyad na shin tu ltung ba'i
NK070(thu)001:387: nyes pa che bas tshul ci ltar du sbas na
NK070(thu)001:388: lus ngag gi bdar sbas nas so gang gis 'byin
NK070(thu)001:389: na / gsang sngags kyis man ngag dang ldan pa gcig gis bstan dgos pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:391: dbu ma pa kakha gcig lta ba stod thog tu mnyam par gnas kyang /
NK070(thu)001:392: spyod pa rdzogs par ma byas pas bskal pa grangs med du thog pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:393: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:396: mu stegs kha cig khamnyam pa'i don nyid ma rtog
NK070(thu)001:397: par sbyod pa byas kyang phal cher ngan song du
NK070(thu)001:398: 'agro'o // zhes 'byung ba la sogs pa'i mu stegs pa kha cig spyod par rdzogs byed kyang /
NK070(thu)001:399: mnyam pa'i lta ba yongs mi shes /
NK070(thu)001:400: zhes gsungs don gyi snod med la gsang dgos pa'i
NK070(thu)001:401: phyir lus brda dang ngag brda sna tshogs su rngam
NK070(thu)001:405: gab pa'i gsang ba ni ngo bo gang na gab
NK070(thu)001:406: na lam rkyen gyi kargyud kyi don phun sum tshogs
NK070(thu)001:408: rang bzhin gyis khargyud don gzhi 'bras rnams gang la gab na 'gro drug /
NK070(thu)001:409: kha'khrul pa can dang man ngag la ma ltos par
NK070(thu)001:410: ras chod byed pa rnams la tshul ci ltar na
NK070(thu)001:411: rgyud 'khrug / lung gcus man ngag gab pa de
NK070(thu)001:412: lam rkyen dang rang bzhin gyi rgyud de gnyis gang
NK070(thu)001:413: gi 'byin na lung man ngag gi tshad ma gnyis
NK070(thu)001:414: rgyud 'khrug / kyis / bdag pos rgyud kyi ston pa dang slob dpon gyi 'byin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:415: snying po zhes bya ba la gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:417: theg pa thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyu snying po ni /
NK070(thu)001:418: mngon sum du rgyud 'di'i byin brlabs kyis bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:420: gdul bya las tha ma'i pa mthar lam ba'i shes
NK070(thu)001:421: sgrib sbyangs ba don du rgyud 'di ston pas bstan
NK070(thu)001:422: par mdzad pas rang don du rtogs nas gzhan don
NK070(thu)001:423: du rgyud 'di zhu ba'i go phye nas gdul bya
NK070(thu)001:424: mtha' dag gi don du theg pa /
NK070(thu)001:425: thams cad kyang 'byung ba ste yin gzhung las /
NK070(thu)001:426: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK070(thu)001:428: 'beb par snang ba'i phyir theg pa kun gyis 'byung gnas mthar thug pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:429: gnyis pa theg pa dgu po kun gyi 'bras bu'i snying po ni /
NK070(thu)001:430: theg pa'i sgo kun nas bsgrub pa'i mtha' ra thug
NK070(thu)001:431: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid mngon du
NK070(thu)001:434: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK070(thu)001:435: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK070(thu)001:436: zhes pa la sogs theg pa gzhi'i nges 'byung la theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas /
NK070(thu)001:438: gsum pa chos thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pas don gyis snying po yin pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:439: shes byed dag mnyam rtogs gzhi'i gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas rmal gzhig brtags gtan la phab nas /
NK070(thu)001:441: mthar gtugs pa nges pa'i dgongs pa'i spyod yul ni
NK070(thu)001:442: rtog tshogs su phung khams skye mched brtag pa ril
NK070(thu)001:443: te thams cad 'bras bu sku dang ye shes bzhi
NK070(thu)001:444: bcu rtsa gnyis su kyis dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas pas
NK070(thu)001:445: ra gsal ba 'khor ba'i rtog tshogs sku dang ye
NK070(thu)001:446: shes su kar dag pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:448: shes bya don gyi bcud btus pas /
NK070(thu)001:449: gsung rab ste nges pa'i lung lha bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK070(thu)001:451: de las lhag pa'i don du smra ba //
NK070(thu)001:452: de ni rnam par dag pa'i lam min te //
NK070(thu)001:453: rang gis blo bsam pas ni 'khrul pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:456: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK070(thu)001:457: gsang ba 'i don 'di las lhag pa gzhan mi mnga' //
NK070(thu)001:460: de kho na nyid ces bya ba la gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:462: rgyu'i 'bras bu'i gnyis su med pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:463: de kho na nyid kyis ngo bo ngos gzung ba'i gnas skabs kyis gsum du 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:465: phung po la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs ril rang gi
NK070(thu)001:466: rig pa las mi gzhan pa'i phyir sems yin la
NK070(thu)001:467: / de nyid la snang stong tha dad pa gnyis
NK070(thu)001:468: dang bral ba'i rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor rtogs
NK070(thu)001:469: pa'i ngang la blo ma bcos par bzhag pa ni
NK070(thu)001:470: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:471: skabs kyi bzhag pa las 'bras bu 'byung bas ni /
NK070(thu)001:472: rgyu'i de kho na nyid de zhes 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:473: de nyid la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya 'i dkyil 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:474: mang por snang ba mngon sum du 'byung ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:475: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid de rgyu 'bras kyi /
NK070(thu)001:476: spros pa la dga' ba rnams kyis 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid zhes 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:477: 'bras bu de dag kyang mngon par zhen pa'i sgrib
NK070(thu)001:478: pa dag pa'i skabs las byung ba ma rtogs pa
NK070(thu)001:479: rgyu las 'bras bu gzhan ma yin pa ni de
NK070(thu)001:480: gzhan ma yin pa kho na nyid de ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:481: la rgyu 'bras kyis dbye ba ma grub pas rgyu
NK070(thu)001:482: 'bras gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid do
NK070(thu)001:484: nges pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:485: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las gzhi dang ra nges pa
NK070(thu)001:486: lam dang du nges pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo yis
NK070(thu)001:487: // nges pa rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK070(thu)001:489: rgyud kyi gzhi ni ra nges pa rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ste /
NK070(thu)001:490: rang bzhin gyi sgro skur dang bral bar nges pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:491: de yi ge'i rgyud 'dis nges par ston pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:493: yod pa sgro 'dogs dang med pa skur pa 'debs
NK070(thu)001:494: pa'i mtha' gnyis zhi ba'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying
NK070(thu)001:496: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas gnas lugs phyungs //
NK070(thu)001:499: lam du nges pa ni 'di'i lugs kyis ye nas
NK070(thu)001:500: gnas pa'i 'bras bu nyid nges par ma nor rtogs
NK070(thu)001:501: pa'i lam du byed pa'i phyir yang lam rkyen 'di
NK070(thu)001:503: 'bras bu nyid lam du byed pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:505: 'bras bu nges pa ni rgyud 'dir rang gi ngo
NK070(thu)001:506: bo de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa ma lus pa
NK070(thu)001:507: mngon sum du ston pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:508: 'di nyid las dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lhag ma ma lus pa la /
NK070(thu)001:509: don 'di las gsang ba 'i ra bya ba nges don med do //
NK070(thu)001:511: drang don nges don gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:512: gsang sngags rtogs pa'i skal pa'i las can la dbang
NK070(thu)001:513: rnon yang rab nges pa'i don du gsungs pas nges
NK070(thu)001:514: pa'o // spros pa la dga' ba dbang po 'bring gi don du /
NK070(thu)001:515: rgyud kyi don rnams dbye ba lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:516: rgyud kyi rgyu dang gleng gzhi rkyen dang gleng bslang
NK070(thu)001:517: yongs su shes par bya ba dang 'i dngos po
NK070(thu)001:518: lnga dgos 'brel dang bzhi rgyud don yongs su gtad
NK070(thu)001:519: pa'o // de la rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu /
NK070(thu)001:520: gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:521: thun mong dang gi gleng gzhi thun mong ma yin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:522: ba'i gleng gzhi thun mong gi gleng gzhi la gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:523: rgyud khyad par dang can gyi gleng gzhi bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:524: rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi la phun sum tshogs pa drug go //
NK070(thu)001:525: de la dang po ston pa la /
NK070(thu)001:526: ngo bo dang ni mdun brgyab med pa zhes sogs /
NK070(thu)001:527: rang bzhin dang de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs 'chad pa'i skyes bu'o //
NK070(thu)001:528: ni rigs lnga ste 'dir rdor sems yin pa gnas
NK070(thu)001:529: la rang bzhin gsum dang 'og ces sogs gnas kyi
NK070(thu)001:530: / gzhi tshad med pa zhes sogs gzhal yas khang dang gtso bo la rgyu dang dbyibs dang /
NK070(thu)001:533: mi 'jigs zhes sogs gdan dang ye shes bsam gyis
NK070(thu)001:534: mi khyab ces sogs rgyan du ma dang bcas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:535: mtshan nyid do // 'khor la 'ang bcom ldan 'das
NK070(thu)001:536: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs ston pa nyid dang
NK070(thu)001:537: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang rigs lnga
NK070(thu)001:538: mtshan nyid do // yab yum / de nas byang
NK070(thu)001:539: chub chen po zhes sogs rig pa khyad par can
NK070(thu)001:540: gyi 'khor dang sems dpa' yab yum /
NK070(thu)001:541: chos kyi dbyings zhes sogs khyab pa dang mang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:542: tshad dang de dag kun kyang zhes sogs sku mdog
NK070(thu)001:543: dang ston 'khor gnas gsum 'dzoms pa'i dus dang /
NK070(thu)001:544: sdud pa dang po phyag rdor bstan pa'i ston pa'i thugs la gnas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:545: yang na 'og nas 'byung ba'i rgyud don no //
NK070(thu)001:546: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi gzhi la gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:547: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs rgyu dang /
NK070(thu)001:549: ngo bo la thub pa chen po zhes sogs ston pa dang thub pa drug /
NK070(thu)001:550: 'thon nas kyang zhes sogs zhing khams dang stong gsum mdzad pa dang 'dul ba bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:551: 'khor gdul bya dang 'gro ba lnga de dag gis bstan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:552: ni gsung gi mdzad pa theg pa lnga /
NK070(thu)001:553: rgyud non 'byung ba'i rkyen gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:554: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ba /
NK070(thu)001:555: gsang dbang bskur bas lhan cig pa'i 'khor la shes
NK070(thu)001:556: rab ye shes dang dbyer med bde ba chen po'i
NK070(thu)001:557: dbang gnyis kyis don dam rtogs pa'i skabs phye ba
NK070(thu)001:558: dang / gnyis pa thun mong du gleng bslang ba
NK070(thu)001:559: ni de nas de la zhes sogs thun min dang
NK070(thu)001:560: thun mong gi bstan pa tha dag bshad par zhus
NK070(thu)001:561: pa dang de la thams cad ces sogs ston pas
NK070(thu)001:562: dang / gnang ba'o // gsum pa'i smad nas nyer
NK070(thu)001:563: gcig gi bar ni rgyud rang gi ngo bo yongs
NK070(thu)001:564: su shes par bya ba'i dngos po yin pa de
NK070(thu)001:567: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK070(thu)001:568: phrin las bsgrub pa'i thabs lam gyi rim ba dang bdun gyis //
NK070(thu)001:569: gsang sngags rgyud kyi don dbye ba bya //
NK070(thu)001:571: de la lta ba la gzhal bya gzhal ba'i gtan tshig la dag mnyam rtogs gzhi dang /
NK070(thu)001:573: ni grub mtha' bden pa dbyer med pa /
NK070(thu)001:574: spyod pa la le'u dgu pa'i skabs su sbyar te /
NK070(thu)001:575: de'ang de nyid ni shes rab rang bzhin med pa dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:576: kun ting ni snying rje chen po thabs dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:577: phyag rgya gcig pa ni rnal 'byor phyogs gcig pa'i
NK070(thu)001:578: spyod pa dang spros pa ni spyod yul lha dang
NK070(thu)001:580: tshul khrims tshogs kyi spyod pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:581: ni yo byad lnga la spyod pa ste rgyas par bcu gcig par gsal ba dkyil 'khor ni /
NK070(thu)001:583: rgyud 'dir ni gang bstan na gzhi 'bras rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK070(thu)001:584: rig pa rang snang ba'i lha rtog gzugs brnyan dang las dang bya ba /
NK070(thu)001:586: zung 'jug cig car du rtogs shing sgoms pa ting
NK070(thu)001:587: nge 'dzin dang bsgom pa'i lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:589: phyi nang gsang gsum byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog sgrub pa zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor dang bdun bstan //
NK070(thu)001:592: de las rang bzhin la'ang gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:593: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK070(thu)001:595: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:597: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la zhi khro gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:599: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum ste de'ang zhi ba la sku'i dkyil 'khor le'u drug pa /
NK070(thu)001:602: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor le'u brgyad pa /
NK070(thu)001:603: khro bo la le'u bcu drug ba gsung /
NK070(thu)001:604: bcu bdun pa sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis ka ste /
NK070(thu)001:606: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni le'u drug pas
NK070(thu)001:607: ston lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la
NK070(thu)001:608: zhi khro gnyis sku gsung thugs gsum gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:609: drug 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor dang rjes su mthun no //
NK070(thu)001:610: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor ni kun la phal cher 'jug go //
NK070(thu)001:611: lhag pa mtshon cing 'dra bas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la bcu ste /
NK070(thu)001:613: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyam bya zhes pa sa chog dang /
NK070(thu)001:614: dkyil 'khor khru gang zhes sogs tshad dang /
NK070(thu)001:615: phur bu sprad bu zhes sogs /
NK070(thu)001:617: lte ba rtsibs dang zhes sogs /
NK070(thu)001:621: sku gsung thugs ldan zhes dbye ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:623: bcos bu'i ras ni zhes sogs rab gnas dang /
NK070(thu)001:628: bde ba chen po zhes sogs zhugs pa'i yon tan dang bcu'o //
NK070(thu)001:629: byang sems dkyil 'khor le'u dgu pas ston no //
NK070(thu)001:630: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la zhi khro gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:631: de re re la'ang gsum gsum ste bcu gnyis pas ston /
NK070(thu)001:633: rgyas pa'i rgyud nas gsal lo //
NK070(thu)001:634: dam tshig la le'u bcu dgu pa /
NK070(thu)001:635: dam tshig rnams ni zhes sogs rang bzhin dang /
NK070(thu)001:636: bla med theg pa zhes sogs che ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:637: bla med mi spangs zhes sogs rnam grangs dang /
NK070(thu)001:638: rtsa ba nyams zhes sogs skyon dang /
NK070(thu)001:639: gzhan yang zhes sogs dam tshig gis yon tan no //
NK070(thu)001:640: dbang la le'u dgu pa dang bcu pa dbang phan nus zab gsum gyi ngo bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:641: dad brtson ces sogs dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:642: nyan byed ces sogs dbang bskur thabs dang /
NK070(thu)001:643: slob dpon mnyes par zhes sogs skyon dang /
NK070(thu)001:644: dus 'di phyin chad ces sogs yon tan no //
NK070(thu)001:645: le'u nyi shu pa phrin las la lhag pa hom gyi las ni le'u dgu par bstan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:646: lhag pa rdzas kyi las dang /
NK070(thu)001:647: bdud rtsi lnga'am zhes sogs lu gu rgyud kyi las dang /
NK070(thu)001:648: ni lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdam nas zhes sogs /
NK070(thu)001:649: khro bo bsgrub pa'i zhes sogs yon tan no //
NK070(thu)001:650: bsgrub pa'i thabs lam gyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:651: dang po bskyed pa'i rim pa ni le'u lnga pa ltar /
NK070(thu)001:653: kun ting rgya gcig phyag rgya spros pa tshogs /
NK070(thu)001:654: sgrub kyi ting nge 'dzin lnga'i sgo nas rim par 'jug pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:655: rdzogs pa'i rim pa ni shes bya'i chos thams cad dag pa gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:656: mnyam pa rnam pa gnyis sam lnga'i ngang du sangs rgyas pa de /
NK070(thu)001:657: shes byed rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas gtan la phab pa'i lam gyis yid ches te /
NK070(thu)001:658: de nyams su blang ba la rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:659: dgos pa 'brel pa yang dgos gyi lam mtshon nas bsnyen sgrub bzhis don mthar phyungs te /
NK070(thu)001:660: spangs bya bdud bzhi yang btul te /
NK070(thu)001:661: thob bya 'bras bu lhun gyis grub par sa ma brtsal ba /
NK070(thu)001:664: thun mong dang grol lam thun mong ma yin pa'i thabs lam pa tshul gyi gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:665: de yang brjod pa 'brel pa dgos pa dang yang dgos pas /
NK070(thu)001:666: rgyud kyi yan lag bzhi ru 'gyur /
NK070(thu)001:668: thun mong du lam gyi rkyen yi ge'i rgyud brjod par byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:669: gzhi 'bras kyi rgyud gnyis ni brjod par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:671: rgyu gleng gzhi'i tshogs nas rkyen gleng bslang ba ni thabs de las rgyu 'di nyid snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:672: thabs de las nges par 'byung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:673: thabs grol gyi lam gnyis ni rgyud sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:674: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo ni 'bras bu'o
NK070(thu)001:675: // rgyud kyi dngos po bdun gyi don rtogs pa ni dgos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:676: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo thob pa ni dgos pa'i yang dgos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:677: thun mong ma yin pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:678: rdo rje rtse mor bcu 'dus pa'i thig le chen
NK070(thu)001:679: po dbab bzung la sogs pa sbyor ba'i thabs dang
NK070(thu)001:680: bcas pa ni / brjod par byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:681: rten thig le'i dga' ba bcu drug gi bde ba 'i ye shes bcu drug ni brjod par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:682: steng 'og gi bde ba myong bar byed pa'i thig le sdom pa'i nus pa yan lag gi /
NK070(thu)001:683: rlung dang bcas pa ni thabs so //
NK070(thu)001:684: des shes bya rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i gsang
NK070(thu)001:685: ba'i snying po'i don bde stong gnyis med nyams su
NK070(thu)001:686: myong ba ni thabs de las byung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:687: rten thig le bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis nang la gnas pa ni rgyu'o //
NK070(thu)001:688: rten can ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon sum gsal bar shar ba ni 'bras bu'o //
NK070(thu)001:689: g.yo ldang la sogs pa sems lnga rim par rgyud
NK070(thu)001:690: du skye ba ni dgos pa dga' ba bcu drug
NK070(thu)001:691: ldog cha ste tha ma la rdzogs pa'i lhan cig
NK070(thu)001:692: skyes pa'i ye shes chen po ni dgos pa'i sems
NK070(thu)001:694: le'u tha ma rgyud yongs su gtad pa ni gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:697: kye zhes sogs rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po la ye nas sangs rgyas pa /
NK070(thu)001:698: lam gyis rtsol sgrub ril da nga bral bar gdams pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:700: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs sdud pa po gsang bdag la zungs la spros shig pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:701: de pa thams cad kyi zhes sogs ma 'ongs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:702: rnal 'byor ba la yon tan brjod de zungs shig
NK070(thu)001:703: pa'o // rnam par dbye ba de dag kyang /
NK070(thu)001:704: rgyud rang gi dkyus thad kar ngo sprad nas ston no //
NK070(thu)001:706: shes rab kyis dbang po tha ma'i don du gsang
NK070(thu)001:707: sngags spyi'i rgyud dgongs 'dus la sogs kyis bshad thabs
NK070(thu)001:708: 'dren pa'i tshig bcu'i 'bru gnyer bar 'i sgo nas
NK070(thu)001:709: dbye ba'o // de la bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK070(thu)001:710: zhes bya ba ni'i ngag don /
NK070(thu)001:711: gang gis na sdud pa pos badz+ra pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:712: dus gang gis na ma la yar tshig don du
NK070(thu)001:713: gnyer ba de'i tshe gang la na rang gi ston
NK070(thu)001:714: pa kun bzang la phyag gi mchod par brjod pa'o
NK070(thu)001:717: thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang ba'i 'og sgo gleng
NK070(thu)001:718: gzhi ste pha'i rgyud man chad kyi gzhung gzhan las
NK070(thu)001:719: khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:721: 'di zhes pa nye bar mtshon pa'i tshig ni //
NK070(thu)001:722: e bam ma ya la rtsogs pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i dbyings can yum gyi b+ha ga ni /
NK070(thu)001:725: skad ces pa'i rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i las kyi ming can //
NK070(thu)001:726: ni gsang ba rdo rje'i rtser yi ge bam gi
NK070(thu)001:727: dbyibs can gyi thig le bde ba dang bcas pa
NK070(thu)001:728: ni ston pa'o // ma'i sgra la drangs nas ma
NK070(thu)001:729: ta kana ma nu khana rlung bsdoms kapar byed pa'i
NK070(thu)001:730: ni ston pa'o // yidkha // ni 'khor las kacan rnam shes khabrgyad po de dag la //
NK070(thu)001:731: bde ba ye shes su gsal bar go ba ni
NK070(thu)001:732: tshig tu brjod pa dang bral bas bshad par 'dod
NK070(thu)001:735: pa ra ma tha ma'i sgra la drang na don
NK070(thu)001:736: dam byang sems nges pa'i don gyi rgyud ma h+aa
NK070(thu)001:737: ya na theg pa chen po ste rgyud 'di yin
NK070(thu)001:738: no // de'i dus ni phyogs gcig tu brjod du med pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus /
NK070(thu)001:740: na ma na de'i ming can zhes bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:742: de la 'di zhes nye bar mngon sum mtshon pa'i
NK070(thu)001:743: tshig ni gnas te phyi khyams dang 1 grum bar
NK070(thu)001:745: sna rtse bya'i 3gdong pa dang zlum po /
NK070(thu)001:746: skye gnas kyis za ma 4tog rnams zla'am dang de drag rgyas zhi dbang du gnas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:747: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sku ril gyi
NK070(thu)001:748: bzhugs gnas su yin par gsang 'dus las gsungs pa'o
NK070(thu)001:749: // gu h+ya badz+ra'i ste gsang ba rdo rje'i bum
NK070(thu)001:750: pa dbang bskur rdzogs thig le phra'u thams cad dus
NK070(thu)001:751: gcig tu pa'i thig le ba bde ba skyes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:753: bde ba ma lus pa'i ye shes gsal bar byed pa po'i yin pa phyir ston pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:755: rlung gis bde ba bsdom par byed pa de g.yo
NK070(thu)001:756: ldang la sogs pa sems lngas gleng bslang ba'i las
NK070(thu)001:757: kyis ma nu na yid de la sogs pa tshogs
NK070(thu)001:758: brgyad rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang yin pa
NK070(thu)001:759: / de rdo rje mthong ba thos rnams myong ba /
NK070(thu)001:760: la sogs pas phyin ci ma log par sku dang ye shes su brda 'phrod cing /
NK070(thu)001:762: tshig tu brjod pa dang 'dra bar gsal ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:763: 'khor la bshad do bar tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:764: bstan pa go ba nyid gang yin snyom pa la
NK070(thu)001:765: pa sa ra ma ta na don dam pa byang
NK070(thu)001:767: sems lnga'i tha ma rdzogs pa byang sems skad cig
NK070(thu)001:768: ma dga' ba bcu drug gis rang bzhin lhan cig
NK070(thu)001:769: skyes pa'i ye shes byang chub sems de la snang
NK070(thu)001:770: stong ngam stong phyogs re'i mtha' ma reg pa ni
NK070(thu)001:771: / ma h+aa ya na theg pa chen po ste rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud 'adi'o //
NK070(thu)001:773: mngon du gyur pa de'i dus ni phyogs gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:774: brjod du med pas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK070(thu)001:775: dus zhes bya bar ming tha snyad 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:776: de'i ming gi rgyu mtshan ni gdul bya las sbyangs
NK070(thu)001:777: pa'i tha ma pa ste mthar lam pa dang kun
NK070(thu)001:778: tu 'dod rnams kyi don gyi phyir na thun mong
NK070(thu)001:780: zhes bya da ni zhes pa skabs su bab ba'i tshig ste thun mong gi gleng gzhi la /
NK070(thu)001:782: dang po ston pa'i rang bzhin ston te /
NK070(thu)001:783: mtha' gnyis dang bral bas rgyal ba drug don ye
NK070(thu)001:784: shes lnga lhun grub rtags rig lnga lhun grub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:785: yon tan bsam yas pa gcig yod na yang mdor
NK070(thu)001:787: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:788: 'khor 'das sam snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rig
NK070(thu)001:789: pa rang de rgyu rkyen dang bral bas byung gi
NK070(thu)001:790: ye shes tshon ni byed pa pos 1ma bcos par
NK070(thu)001:791: yon tan ril lhun 2 gyis grub pa'i phyir na
NK070(thu)001:792: / de bzhin nyid do dam bca' /
NK070(thu)001:793: khyab par der gzhi ci bzhin pa nar 2son pa
NK070(thu)001:794: ni gshegs pa ste rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:795: nyid du gyur pas na gzung 'dzin nam sgrib byed
NK070(thu)001:796: kyi zhen pa gnyis dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:797: rdo rje dang le'u lnga las chos nyid de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:798: nyid kyi ngang du nar son cing gshegs pa yang
NK070(thu)001:799: / gzung 'dzin sna tshogs kyi zhen pa las rang grol bar zad /
NK070(thu)001:802: da ni gzhi ci bzhin par nar son pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:803: yang dag par rdzogs pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:804: snang stong ngam 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i chos
NK070(thu)001:805: nyid byang chub kyi sems ni ril te 'khor 'das
NK070(thu)001:806: thams cad gyi ngo bor gyur pas na ma dag
NK070(thu)001:807: pa spangs bya mi dmigs pa'i ste ma grub phyir
NK070(thu)001:808: yang dag pa'o // gtan tshigs de nyid kyi phyir
NK070(thu)001:809: chos thams cad sku dang ye shes 'bras bu rang
NK070(thu)001:810: snang ba la rdzogs pa'i phyir bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:811: de ni yon tan btsal ba med par lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:812: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:813: nyon mongs bag la nyal dang sa bcu pa la
NK070(thu)001:814: sogs pa'i khong du kun tu 'od bsdu ba'i lta
NK070(thu)001:815: ba ngan pa thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir sogs
NK070(thu)001:816: la rang byung ye shes mtha' dbus med par thams
NK070(thu)001:818: ye shes bla ma'i sa mngon du byas bas rgyas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:819: de ni sgrib pa dang bral zhing ye shes kyis khyab pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:820: bcom ldan 'das zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:821: nyon mongs pa'i bdud bzhi la sogs pa /
NK070(thu)001:822: mi mthun pa'i bdud bzhi nyid rang rig nyid du gsal bas bcom /
NK070(thu)001:823: de dag ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga la sogs pa'i 'bras bur mnga' mdzad pas ldan kyang /
NK070(thu)001:824: rang gi ngo bo nyid phyogs gcig 'di 'drar rtsal
NK070(thu)001:825: bas mi rnyed pas blo'i spyod yul du byar med
NK070(thu)001:827: de ni bdud bzhi 'bras bur mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:828: longs spyod chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:829: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi ro ma 'gag
NK070(thu)001:830: par myong yang thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen
NK070(thu)001:831: po'i ra longs spyod pa phyir /
NK070(thu)001:832: blang dor gyis spyod yul gyis zhen pa dang bral
NK070(thu)001:833: bas longs spyod bya spyod byed kyi zhen pa can
NK070(thu)001:834: gzhan la khyad par du gyur pas chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:835: de ni thams cad kyis ro myong ba yang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:836: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK070(thu)001:837: kyis sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:839: tha snyad phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i
NK070(thu)001:840: de bzhin gshegs pa ril gyi spyir yon tan gyi
NK070(thu)001:841: grangs stobs la sogs brjod pa las 'das pa yang
NK070(thu)001:842: mdo ra bsdu na sku lnga dang gsung lnga dang
NK070(thu)001:843: thugs lnga dang yon tan lnga dang phrin las lnga
NK070(thu)001:844: ste / nyi shu rtsa lngar 'dus te /
NK070(thu)001:845: de dag kun bzang gi dgongs par yang dag par
NK070(thu)001:846: rdzogs shing dbyer med pa'i phyir rdo rje rgyal ba
NK070(thu)001:847: drug pa'i yon tan gyi khyad par las nyer lnga
NK070(thu)001:848: rang snang bas gcig dang du ma bral bas sangs
NK070(thu)001:849: rgyas kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can dang gyis cha lugs
NK070(thu)001:851: rigs las ming btags pa rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK070(thu)001:852: po ste bdag nyid zhes tha snyad du ming 'dogs
NK070(thu)001:853: so // de ni 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dngos
NK070(thu)001:854: po thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po'i rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:855: so // no // ma lus mi lus lus pa
NK070(thu)001:856: med pa thams cad dang so so ma yin tha
NK070(thu)001:857: mi dad dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:858: so // no // ba ni / ma lus na 'das pa /
NK070(thu)001:860: lus pa med pa ma 'ongs pa ste dus gsum
NK070(thu)001:861: gyis bsdus pa'i sems can chos thams cad bsdus pa
NK070(thu)001:862: ni su zhig bsdu snyams pa la /
NK070(thu)001:863: drug pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa bsdu ste /
NK070(thu)001:865: de dag kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma'i yin pa phyir so so ma yin /
NK070(thu)001:866: don dam sems nyid du ma skyes pas tha mi dad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:867: bden pa gnyis tha dad kyi tha snyad las 'das
NK070(thu)001:868: par dbyer med du ngo bo gcig pa ste'i rang
NK070(thu)001:869: bzhin / gdul bya gdul byed dam 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang de dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:870: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK070(thu)001:871: snying rje chen po skye zhes bya ba'ang de kho
NK070(thu)001:872: na'o // de ni ston pa dus gsum 'du 'bral
NK070(thu)001:873: med pa 'khor ba'i chos rgyun chad med par 'brel
NK070(thu)001:875: ston pa de'i gnas gang yin snyams pa la /
NK070(thu)001:876: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK070(thu)001:877: zhes bya ba gnas kyi rang bzhin bstan te /
NK070(thu)001:879: sgyu 'phrul rgyal matsho'am rdo rje las gzugs khams gtsang ma'i rigs kyi 'og min dag spangs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:881: dbang phyug chen po gnas gzhan gyi 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK070(thu)001:882: tu gyur pa longs sku'i gnas de /
NK070(thu)001:883: ston pa rigs thams cad kyis bdag po'i sku phyag rgya lnga char lhun gyis grub pa'i sku //
NK070(thu)001:884: 'i mtshan nyid ni sngar bzhin gcig dang du ma'i mtha' rnams par spangs bas //
NK070(thu)001:885: phyogs dus kyi'am rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can te //
NK070(thu)001:886: dus gdod ma nas gsang ba'i theg mchog mi zad par 'byung ba'i mdzod nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:887: sgrib pa gnyis kyi mtha' bag la nyal spangs pa'i gdul bya la //
NK070(thu)001:888: kun tu 'od dang mthar lam pa /
NK070(thu)001:889: dus skad cig ma gcig gi bstan pa mngon gsum du snang bar mdzad //
NK070(thu)001:892: sangs rgyas kho na'o spyod yul yin pas khyad par
NK070(thu)001:893: can gyi gnas de ni chen po he du rang
NK070(thu)001:894: rig pa'i ye shes kho na'i yin pa phyir mtha'
NK070(thu)001:896: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba las zhes 'byung ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:897: 'og gzhi'i 'khor lo chen po de ni don rgyu
NK070(thu)001:898: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis phyir snang ba yin
NK070(thu)001:899: pa'i gdul bya'i snang bas 'di tsam zhes blos tshad
NK070(thu)001:901: de yang don ye shes lnga'i rtsal ma 'gag par
NK070(thu)001:902: rang snang ba'i phyir rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte
NK070(thu)001:903: ba dang lnga phan tshun du ma 'dres par gsal
NK070(thu)001:905: gnas kyi rgyu ci snyam pa la yin /
NK070(thu)001:906: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK070(thu)001:908: gnas kyi rgyu ni rang rig pa 'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:909: nyid gzhal yas khang gi kha dog dang dbyibs su
NK070(thu)001:910: snang ba la ni gdul bya'i snang bas tha snyad
NK070(thu)001:913: dgos 'dod skongs pa'i las kyang mi 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:914: te de'ang sngon gyi dge ba'i las kyi 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:915: gdul bya'i re ba skongs pa don yin pa la
NK070(thu)001:916: rtags rin po che'i 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK070(thu)001:917: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:918: ba ni / rgya khyon gyi rang bzhin te /
NK070(thu)001:920: rgyu'i yin pa phyir rgya chad dang bral zhing rang
NK070(thu)001:921: rig pa'i ye shes de nyid yod med kyi mtha'
NK070(thu)001:922: / dbus kun dang bral ba sa phyogs bcur yongs
NK070(thu)001:923: su ma chad pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang
NK070(thu)001:925: de'i phyir ston med pas phyal bar 'gyur ro snyam du dgos pa la /
NK070(thu)001:926: yon tan dpag tu med par rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK070(thu)001:927: zhes gsungs pa rgyu ye shes kyi phyir de la
NK070(thu)001:928: 'bras bu'i sangs rgyas kyi chos stobs la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:929: ril ye nas lhun gyis grub pa che ba'i yon
NK070(thu)001:930: tan dpag tu med par rgyas pa don yin la
NK070(thu)001:932: 'i phyir rtags gzhal yas dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK070(thu)001:933: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bul gyis mdzes pa /
NK070(thu)001:935: don gang rtogs pa'i ye shes la ni bye brag
NK070(thu)001:936: tu lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi mngon sum du
NK070(thu)001:938: rtags la de nyid kyi rtsal rin po che'i glo
NK070(thu)001:939: 'bur bzhir snang ba ni kha dog dkar ser dmar
NK070(thu)001:940: ljang gi rgyan lta bur mdzes pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:941: slob dpon pad+mas zlum por bzhed /
NK070(thu)001:942: b+hi ma las mkhar thabs su bzhed /
NK070(thu)001:944: rtse mo phyogs bcu'i dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:945: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so so ma yin
NK070(thu)001:946: ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil
NK070(thu)001:948: rtags gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo zlum por mtho
NK070(thu)001:949: ba nyid don rang rig pa nyid sangs rgyas kyi
NK070(thu)001:950: zhing khams thams cad du ma 'gag par rang snang
NK070(thu)001:951: bas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:952: ma lus pa thams cad rang rig tu gyur pa
NK070(thu)001:953: ni / so sor ma yin ngo bo nyid gcig
NK070(thu)001:954: pa'i don gyis mtha' gang du'ang mi gnas pa'i rang
NK070(thu)001:955: byung gi ye shes chen po ste ra kun tu
NK070(thu)001:956: ni / 'khyil pa / don rang bzhin dang rags gdul bya'i /
NK070(thu)001:957: snang ba gnyis ka las ma 'das pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:958: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa ye shes rin
NK070(thu)001:959: po che'i dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs pa rnam
NK070(thu)001:960: pa tha dad pa'i bye brag dang /
NK070(thu)001:961: khyad par du gyur pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:962: mi gnas pa'i ye shes kyi gnas skabs las bye
NK070(thu)001:963: brag gi grangs bsam gyis ma khyab par rang snang
NK070(thu)001:964: ba nyid don yin la rtags ye shes kyis rgyan
NK070(thu)001:965: rin po che / sna tshogs kyi rdo rje la sogs pa'i dbyibs dang /
NK070(thu)001:966: kha dog sna lnga la sogs pa'i 'od zer dang /
NK070(thu)001:967: sprul pa'i rnam pa tha dad pa'i phyogs dang ye
NK070(thu)001:968: shes rang snang ba'i rgyan de dag 'jig rten gyi
NK070(thu)001:969: rgyan las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:970: bltas pas mi ngoms par rgyan rdzogs par snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:971: 'phags pa tshad khadpag tu med pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:972: don lam thun mong gzhan kalas ma h+aa 'dir 'phar
NK070(thu)001:973: ba dang ma h+aa'i don kha'di nyid mthar thug pa
NK070(thu)001:974: med pa'i phyir rtags ka sgo'i them skas la sogs
NK070(thu)001:975: pa'i mtho dman gyi rim pa dang ni rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:977: ni steng gi bya skyibs kyi khabum pa'i mtho dman gyi tshad dpag tu med pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:978: sangs rgyas kyi spyi gtsug bltar mi mngon pa lta bur gnas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:979: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs zhes pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:980: klubs pa'i mthar thug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:981: rang byung gi ye shes snang stong gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:982: pa nyid don yid la rtags rin po che sna
NK070(thu)001:983: tshogs kyi dbyibs dang kha dog de'ang /
NK070(thu)001:984: thugs rje dang sprul pa rgyun du ldan pa don yin la rtags rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:985: bden gnyis mi phyed pa don yin la rtags rin po che'i chun 'phyang dang /
NK070(thu)001:986: thabs sna tshogs ma 'dres pa don yin la rtags rin po che'i shar bu'i rgyan dang /
NK070(thu)001:987: 'dod yon lnga po gang yang ma spangs pa'i longs
NK070(thu)001:988: spyod chen po'i dang ldan pa phyir don la rtags
NK070(thu)001:989: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya sna tshogs dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:990: pa'o // de yang rin po che dang /
NK070(thu)001:991: 'dod yon gyi rgyan de dag gis mdzes pa yang /
NK070(thu)001:992: rang bzhin grub pa'i dbang du phyogs bcur bar mtshams med par 'khrig pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:993: bsgom pa'i dbang du 'dod snam du bsgom mo //
NK070(thu)001:994: rgyu rkyen gyis 'dus ma byas pas rang byung de
NK070(thu)001:995: la rgyan de dag rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:996: phyir don yin la rtags phyi dang nang gcig la
NK070(thu)001:997: gcig sgrib pa med par mi bsgrib par gsal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:998: rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pa klub pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:999: dper na gser gyi sbu gur 'i mig g.yul spras
NK070(thu)001:1000: pa lta bu rin po che'i sil kha bcug pa
NK070(thu)001:1001: lta bu'o // rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK070(thu)001:1003: don ni rang byung gi ye shes chen po ni
NK070(thu)001:1004: yod med kyi mtha' kun dang bral ba'i phyir stong
NK070(thu)001:1005: pa nyid rang gi mtshan nyid 'di 'drar ngos bzung
NK070(thu)001:1006: med pa la 'bras bu 'di chos kyis ril tshang
NK070(thu)001:1007: bas gzhan thob par 'dod pa dang bral bas smon
NK070(thu)001:1008: pa med de / nyid 'gag med du cir yang snang ba'i rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:1009: de ltar mtshan sgom stong pa nyid la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:1010: rnam thar pa'i bzhi mtshan tshul ma 'dres pa yongs
NK070(thu)001:1011: su rdzogs par rtogs pa'i sgo nas ni mtshan bya
NK070(thu)001:1012: mi gnas pa'i ye shes a ti yo gar 'jug
NK070(thu)001:1013: go // zhes tha snyad du 'dogs na rtags gzhal
NK070(thu)001:1014: yas khang gi phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi ni thang sgo
NK070(thu)001:1015: lta bu ma yin te sgo khyud can /
NK070(thu)001:1016: kha dog bzhi ldan gis so sor gsal ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:1017: rnam pa thar pa brgyad kyi rta bab dang ldan pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1018: don 'das ma thag pa nyid 'khor ba las rnam
NK070(thu)001:1019: par thar par byed pa'i mtshan nyid sde gsum phyi
NK070(thu)001:1020: rgyud sde gsum ma h+aa'i bskyed rdzogs gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:1021: theg pa brgyad la blo sbyangs pa las snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1022: phyir nye bar mtshon pa'i rtags su rta bab bang
NK070(thu)001:1023: rim brgyad dang ldan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1025: ni rta rkang ste pha gu ma chags ste pad+ma /
NK070(thu)001:1026: rin po che'i dar sna tshogs kyis za ra tshag
NK070(thu)001:1027: mu tig gi dra ba'i sna 'phyang rin po che
NK070(thu)001:1028: phreng ba'i chun 'phyang shar bu'i phreng ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:1029: rin po che sna tshogs kyi sgrom bu khyung mgo
NK070(thu)001:1030: dang rgyan rnam pa brgyad rim par 'khrig zhes pa'o
NK070(thu)001:1031: // phyi dang nang med par kun tu yang nang du gyur pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1032: rang rig pa ni chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:1033: chen po'i yin pa phyir de la phyi gzung ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1034: yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems tha dad du byas
NK070(thu)001:1035: nas bsal bar bya ba mi dmigs pas /
NK070(thu)001:1036: yod med mtha' dang dbus med pa'i don la phyi
NK070(thu)001:1037: dang nang gnyis su yod par mi 'gyur te med
NK070(thu)001:1038: pa ba sa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa
NK070(thu)001:1039: ni / de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba ste gnas kyi rang bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:1041: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i zhes pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:1042: gdan la zhes mthar thug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1043: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes chen po lam gyi
NK070(thu)001:1044: mngon du byas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:1045: rig pa ni / 'bras bu'i b+hud+ha chos mi 'jigs
NK070(thu)001:1046: pa bzhi dang rdzu 'phrul gyis rkang pa bzhi ste
NK070(thu)001:1047: ye shes bzhi dang phrin las thogs pa med pa
NK070(thu)001:1048: bzhi ste bzhi tshan gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:1050: bcu dbang bcu ste bcu tshan gnyis dang de rnams
NK070(thu)001:1051: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa rgyal ba drug pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1052: ye shes nyid la rdzogs pas na yang dag par
NK070(thu)001:1053: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su yin par bstan zhing thob
NK070(thu)001:1054: par nges par byas pa'i don de yang lam theg
NK070(thu)001:1055: pa brgyad la bsgrod pa'i stobs kyis nges par 'byung
NK070(thu)001:1056: ba'i phyir / rtags seng ge la sogs pa ra
NK070(thu)001:1057: snang ba'i chos mthun ni seng ge ni gzhan gyis
NK070(thu)001:1058: ba'i phyir / mi 'jigs / glang po che 'deg
NK070(thu)001:1059: stobs cher myur mgyogs kyis rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa
NK070(thu)001:1060: rma byas dug dbang du byed pas nam mkha' lding
NK070(thu)001:1061: nam mkha' la thogs pa med par 'phur bas so
NK070(thu)001:1062: ba'i phyir / mi 'jigs / // smon lam gyi
NK070(thu)001:1063: dbang gis chos mnyan pa dang sgrib pa sbyang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1064: phyir du'ang rang dbang can du skye bar bzhes pa
NK070(thu)001:1066: chub sems dpa'i lha gcig kyang gdan khri brgyad brgyad
NK070(thu)001:1068: // rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:1070: don rang rig pa ra yod pa'i mtha' mi bsgrib
NK070(thu)001:1071: pas cir yang ma skyes 1pa nyid med pa'i mtha'
NK070(thu)001:1072: ma sgrib pas / kun 2tu snang bas rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:1073: gyis 'od gsal ba thabs 2dang shes 1rab gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:1074: med pa'i phyir don yin la rtags nyi ma zla
NK070(thu)001:1076: snying kha'i srog mi shig pa'i thig le chen po
NK070(thu)001:1077: dang khu ba byang sems 1sa bon ni thabs kyis
NK070(thu)001:1079: 11thams cad kyi byed pa po'i yin pa phyir rigs
NK070(thu)001:1080: kyis bdag po dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:1081: ste sems dpa' / yum gyi nyi ma'i dbus na
NK070(thu)001:1082: yab kyi zla ba blar ste steng du gnas so
NK070(thu)001:1083: ste sems dpa' / // gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK070(thu)001:1085: snang stong gi mtha' gnyis dang bral ba'i rig 11pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1086: snang stong phyogs re ba 1gang du yang ma nges
NK070(thu)001:1087: pas mtha' gcig kyang ma gos pa de gos pa
NK070(thu)001:1088: med pa dang / de pad+ma'i gdan /
NK070(thu)001:1089: mdzad pa 1ci byas ba dang gdul bya'i dngos po
NK070(thu)001:1090: ci snang ba ril don rang rig pa las gzhan
NK070(thu)001:1091: du mi g.yo bar byed pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1092: dper na rin po che chu dwangs rnyog mas mi
NK070(thu)001:1093: 'gyur ba lta bu de nyid che ba'i yon tan
NK070(thu)001:1094: bskor la du snang 2 ba'i phyir rtags gser la
NK070(thu)001:1095: sogs pa rin po che sna tshogs kyi ka bas
NK070(thu)001:1096: brgyad kyi btegs 1pa'i gdung bzhi po re re la
NK070(thu)001:1098: ka gdung des rtags pad ma sna tshogs btegs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1099: gdan de dag la gang bzhugs snyam na 'ong nas ston 'khor rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:1100: ston pa'i rang bzhin dang gnas de dag ni gdul
NK070(thu)001:1101: bya'i mos pa tha dad dang chags pa che chung
NK070(thu)001:1102: gis snang bas thabs grol gnyis su yang 'gyur te
NK070(thu)001:1104: ston pa'i rang bzhin ni lus kyi bcud thig le
NK070(thu)001:1105: thams cad rdo rje'i rtser 'dus pa'i thig le bam
NK070(thu)001:1106: gi dbyibs can ni las dang ngo bos chen po
NK070(thu)001:1107: nyid // kyi yon tan gyi cha shas mtshan grangs bzhin brtags pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1108: de'ang rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK070(thu)001:1109: thab sa kyi dngos po lhan cig skyes pa mngon sum du byas pas gshegs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1110: de lta bu ma nor ba yang dag pa'i don
NK070(thu)001:1111: de la 'bras bu thams cad tshang bas rdzogs pa
NK070(thu)001:1112: dang / lta ngan dang bral bas sangs /
NK070(thu)001:1113: ye shes kun tu khyab pas rgyas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1114: de'i tshe bdun bzhi rang grol bas bcom /
NK070(thu)001:1115: thams cad 'grub kyang mtha' la mi gnas pa bcom ldan 'das so //
NK070(thu)001:1116: snang ba dang bde ba stong pa dang yod med dang 'dod don la sogs pa //
NK070(thu)001:1117: thams cad la dbyer med du longs spyod pas longs spyod chen po rang bzhin lhan skyes de la /
NK070(thu)001:1118: brjod bya'i dngos po ma lus pa thams cad rdzogs par rang snang //
NK070(thu)001:1120: thig le'i 1rtog tshogs 2sangs rgyas bzhi bcu lnga //
NK070(thu)001:1121: nyid du snang ba ni phyogs bcu zhes pa nas rdo rje'i bdag nyid ces pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1122: rtog ma rtog gi snang bas phye bas ma rtogs
NK070(thu)001:1123: pa la ma lus mi lus pa 'khor ba dus
NK070(thu)001:1124: gsum gyis chos dang 'das pa de rnams tha mi
NK070(thu)001:1125: dad pa'i phyir gnyis su med //
NK070(thu)001:1126: de so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin re zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1127: ston pa de'i gnas yum gyis mkha' pad+ma rim pa gsum po //
NK070(thu)001:1128: yin te gang zhe na phyi ma'i pad ma 'dab ma gnyis gsum bar ma 'dab ma /
NK070(thu)001:1129: nang ma 'dab brgyad kyi nang nas khyad par can //
NK070(thu)001:1130: ni tshig gi tha ma 'dab brgyad kyi 1gnas la
NK070(thu)001:1131: ston pa bzhugs pa dang der bde ba skyes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1132: 1yon tan 11gyis // bde stong gnyis med kyis ye
NK070(thu)001:1133: shes de shes bya gang gis gong ma chod pas
NK070(thu)001:1134: mngon par mtho ba'i sa na gsang ba 'og min
NK070(thu)001:1136: sbyor ba'i byed las dang bcud yab yum kyi byang
NK070(thu)001:1137: sems 'dres pa'i tshe bde stong phyogs re'i mtha' dbus
NK070(thu)001:1138: dang bral ba // sa mtha' dang dbus med pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:1140: dbus dang lngar khams lnga'i thig le gnas pa 'di
NK070(thu)001:1141: ye shes bzhi ru snang ba de la gdul bya'i
NK070(thu)001:1142: blos dpag tu med pa'i don rig /
NK070(thu)001:1143: par myong ba ni gzhi tshad med pa nas gsal ba zhes pa'i don /
NK070(thu)001:1144: de la yon tan gyi dgos pa thams cad 'byung
NK070(thu)001:1145: ba dang ldan pas rgyu ye shes rin po che
NK070(thu)001:1146: // 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang zhes pa dang yon
NK070(thu)001:1147: tan dpag tu zhes nas gru bzhir gyur pa'i don
NK070(thu)001:1148: // no // khams lnga'i ngo bo ye shes lnga'i ru gsal ba 'khor lo gcig la lhag pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:1149: ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pas /
NK070(thu)001:1151: ba sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams ngo bo ni yum gyi mkha' rtsa /
NK070(thu)001:1152: snod kyi nang du bcud yab kyis //
NK070(thu)001:1153: thig le gu h+ya badz+ra'i spyi bo dang yum gyi sna rtser shin tu zlum por 'khyil par gnas //
NK070(thu)001:1154: pa ni rtse mo phyogs bcu zhes pa nas kun tu 'khyil ces pa'i don dang /
NK070(thu)001:1155: tshad dpag tu med pa zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1156: 'dab ma las lte ba'i thig le yungs kar por 1tsam de /
NK070(thu)001:1158: dpag pa zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1159: de dus rtsa sa ya phrag bcu gsum rten thig le dang rten can /
NK070(thu)001:1161: pa ni ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab ces nas khyad par du gyur pa'i bar dang /
NK070(thu)001:1162: ye shes rin po che zhes nas /
NK070(thu)001:1165: bde ba'i 'dod yon la longs spyod khyad par can gyis mdzes //
NK070(thu)001:1166: pa ni gzugs sna tshogs zhes pa nas klub ces pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1167: lus gang yang bde bas khyab par byed pas na
NK070(thu)001:1168: phyi lus dang nang bde ba gnyis kyi mtha' dang
NK070(thu)001:1170: ba ni phyi dang nang med ces nas gyur pa na zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1171: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyi ro nyid la //
NK070(thu)001:1172: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos kun rdzogs par ldan //
NK070(thu)001:1173: pa ni mi 'jigs pa seng ge zhes nas nam
NK070(thu)001:1174: mkha' lding gi khri chen dang zhes pa'i don no
NK070(thu)001:1175: // don dam kun rdzob bam yab yum gyi byang
NK070(thu)001:1176: chub mchog tu nyi zla thig le dus gcig du
NK070(thu)001:1177: // 'char // na ni rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal
NK070(thu)001:1178: ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang zhes pa'i don no
NK070(thu)001:1179: // 'char // // yab yum gyi mkha' de nyid
NK070(thu)001:1180: ston pa gsang ba'i sku yi bzhugs gnas yin par
NK070(thu)001:1183: sgo la sogs pa pad gdan rta bab ci lta bu snyom pa la /
NK070(thu)001:1185: rtags rdo rje don rtogs pa nub pa'i phyogs gsang ba'i 'og min gyi gnas mchog tu //
NK070(thu)001:1186: chags pa nyid ma chags par byed pa skye gnas
NK070(thu)001:1187: kyi rtsa pad ma'i gdan 'dab brgyad pa bting ba
NK070(thu)001:1188: // de ni dus gsum gyi rgyal ba gsang ba'i sku bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK070(thu)001:1189: ni gos pa med pa pad ma'i gdan zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1190: don lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la rnam par thar pa'i bzhi tshang ba /
NK070(thu)001:1191: phyir rtags phyogs kyi rtsa sgo bzhi la //
NK070(thu)001:1192: dzahmh'u bam hoh'i yi ge bzhi la gsung chos kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang nges par ldan //
NK070(thu)001:1193: pa ni rnam par thar pa zhes nas /
NK070(thu)001:1194: sgo khyud can zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1195: zab mo'i dbang dang thabs lam bgrod pa'i skal med
NK070(thu)001:1196: pa dge slong rgan po byis sba ma ning dang
NK070(thu)001:1198: gsang ba'i sna rtse thun mong ma yin pa'i bde
NK070(thu)001:1199: ba ni nang rten thun mong gi bde ba ni
NK070(thu)001:1200: phyi rim du lcag ngo tsha dang ldan //
NK070(thu)001:1201: pa ni rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta bab dang ldan pa zhes pa'i don /
NK070(thu)001:1203: de ni bla mas gdams ngag gi sgo nas 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:1204: sku mdun dang rgyab med par thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing /
NK070(thu)001:1206: rgyud kyi ston pa'i drug pa ngo bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:1207: 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i mtshan rigs lnga /
NK070(thu)001:1208: gnyis char thun mong du bstan te /
NK070(thu)001:1209: drug pa la sogs pa'i rigs lnga /
NK070(thu)001:1211: ye shes kyi sku kho na'i yin pa phyir sku
NK070(thu)001:1212: mdun dang rgyab med pa gdul bya'i snang ba ltar
NK070(thu)001:1213: ma mdun dang rgyab tu grub ba /
NK070(thu)001:1215: phyogs thams cad du yang zhal thal le'o //
NK070(thu)001:1216: bar gsal zhing snang ba mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1217: phyag dang zhabs la 'khor lo 'i mtshan dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:1218: pa la sogs pa thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan
NK070(thu)001:1219: dpe la phyi nang gsang gsum las dang po phyi
NK070(thu)001:1220: ltar na drug pa kun bzang yab yum gyi dgongs
NK070(thu)001:1221: pa'i chos nyid de nyid kyi yon tan la sems
NK070(thu)001:1223: 'phrin las kyi bye brag la sems dpa' bcu drug go //
NK070(thu)001:1224: de ltar mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:1225: sems dpa' bcu drug po de rnams la ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1226: lnga'i ngo bo dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga'i khyad
NK070(thu)001:1227: par can gyis brgyan pa ni dpe byad bzang po
NK070(thu)001:1228: brgyad bcur snang ba'i phyir ro nang gi mtshan dpe
NK070(thu)001:1229: ni rtsa 'dab sum cu so gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:1231: gsang ba'i mtshan dpe ni yab yum gyis dga' bzhi
NK070(thu)001:1232: re re pa'ang bzhi bzhi mtshan bzang sum cu gnyis
NK070(thu)001:1233: / dga' ba bcu drug re re la'ang ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pa dpe byad do //
NK070(thu)001:1234: thun mong dang khyad par gang yang ma spangs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1235: par longs spyod pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:1236: bsam gyis mi khyab par thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1238: phyogs dus kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:1239: gyis thams cad la khyab pa dang rang la rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:1240: pa'i phyir grangs mtha' yas pa'i gdul bya'i dag ma
NK070(thu)001:1241: dag gi ngo la zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab
NK070(thu)001:1242: par thams cad du zhi khro la sogs pa sku
NK070(thu)001:1243: sna tshogs dang theg dgu la sogs pa'i gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:1244: yan tshogs dang ye shes lnga la sogs pa'i kyi
NK070(thu)001:1245: mdzad pa cir yang ma nges par kun tu snang
NK070(thu)001:1246: ba'o // thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam
NK070(thu)001:1247: pa'i brtul zhugs kyis dkyil mo drung du bzhugs pa
NK070(thu)001:1249: dgos ched snyom 'jug bde ba chen po'i spyod pas
NK070(thu)001:1250: chags pa can gyis gdul bya 'dul ba'i phyir thabs
NK070(thu)001:1251: yab kyis rdo rje dkyil mo krung dang de la
NK070(thu)001:1252: shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis 'khyud pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1253: mkha' gsang gi rtsa'i rtse sprad pa'i bde ba la
NK070(thu)001:1254: thig le phar 'gro ba rgyu'i theg pa'i lam dang
NK070(thu)001:1255: tshur bzlog pa la 'bras bu'i theg pa'i sa gsum
NK070(thu)001:1256: gyi chos ril mnyam par rdzogs pa'i phyir mi 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:1257: bar ni mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyis dkyil mo krung
NK070(thu)001:1258: du bzhugs pa'o // ye shes drug gis phyag ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK070(thu)001:1260: de 1bzhin nyid du ye shes 1su snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:1261: yul 1shin tu rnam par dag pas de bzhin nyid
NK070(thu)001:1262: kyis rang snang ba'i rnam par dag pa'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1264: de la thun mong dang ba'i ye shes thun min
NK070(thu)001:1265: gsang sngags kyi ye shes me long mnyam nyid sor
NK070(thu)001:1266: rtogs bya grub bzhi dang lnga /
NK070(thu)001:1267: rang byung ye shes dang drug gi don rdzogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1268: rtags su phyag drug dang de'i rtsal nyid cir yang
NK070(thu)001:1269: ma 'gag pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i phyir ye
NK070(thu)001:1270: shes rin po che'i phyag rgya ni /
NK070(thu)001:1271: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams
NK070(thu)001:1272: pa la sogs pa bar ma gnyis 'khor lo dang
NK070(thu)001:1273: rin po che / tha ma gnyis pad+ma dang ral gri /
NK070(thu)001:1274: de rnams kyis rigs kyis kha dog 'od zer 'bar ba can dang bcas par 'dzin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1275: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan pa /
NK070(thu)001:1277: stong smon mtshan ma med pa'i rnam par thar pa
NK070(thu)001:1278: gsum thugs su chub pa'i rig pa'i ye shes ni
NK070(thu)001:1279: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su rang snang ste /
NK070(thu)001:1281: mtshan med gsung smon pa med pa sku de gcig
NK070(thu)001:1282: kyang k+aa b+aa tsa gsum gsum la sogs pa'i bsam
NK070(thu)001:1283: gyis mi khyab par rang snang ba phyir de ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1284: snang ba la grangs dang bral ba yang gdul bya'i
NK070(thu)001:1285: snang bas dbu gsum ni g.yas zhal dkar ba sku
NK070(thu)001:1287: dbus zhal mthing ba thugs dang ldan pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:1288: ngo bo dang mtshan nyid de dag kyang gdul bya'i gnas skabs kyi gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:1289: thabs ltar thal ba'i rgyud las /
NK070(thu)001:1290: khams lnga'i bcud dwangs ma lnga'i don ye shes lnga kho'i na yin pa phyir //
NK070(thu)001:1291: dwangs ma'i mdun dang snyigs ma'i rgyab med par thams
NK070(thu)001:1292: cad kun tu 'od stong gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1293: su gsal // ba ni sku mdun dang rgyab med
NK070(thu)001:1294: par thams cad du zhal tham le bar gsal zhing
NK070(thu)001:1295: su gsal // / zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1296: sgra yig k+aa li so gnyis dang dbyangs yig +aa
NK070(thu)001:1297: li bcu drug gsung gi yi ge de dag spyi
NK070(thu)001:1298: bo la sogs gnas 'khor lo bzhi yis //
NK070(thu)001:1299: dbye bas snying kha stong pa'i ngo bo yin la
NK070(thu)001:1300: lhag ma gsum po la phye ste de'ang glad pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1301: sgra yig gsum bcu po ni ngo bo mtshan bzang
NK070(thu)001:1303: mgrin pa'i dbyangs yig bcu drug dang /
NK070(thu)001:1304: lte bar sgra yig so gnyis g.yas dang /
NK070(thu)001:1305: dbyangs yig bcu drug g.yas g.yon du yod pa ni
NK070(thu)001:1306: bzhi bcu phrag gnyis su 'gyur ba ni dpe byad
NK070(thu)001:1307: brgyad cu yin // te mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa zhes so //
NK070(thu)001:1308: rtsa sa ya bcu gsum la sogs par //
NK070(thu)001:1309: lus de la gnas pa'i thig le skye ba sku
NK070(thu)001:1310: 'gag pa gsung gnas pa'i ngo bo thugs dang gsum
NK070(thu)001:1312: bde ba sku gsung thugs su gnas pa'i rten can
NK070(thu)001:1313: ci lta ba bzhin rten thig le la yod pa
NK070(thu)001:1314: de bzhin // du de'i rten rtsa la yang de
NK070(thu)001:1315: bzhin du yod pa'i don ni bsam gyis mi khyab
NK070(thu)001:1316: ces nas kun tu snang ba zhes dang /
NK070(thu)001:1317: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1318: yab yum gyis nyi zla dus gcig du shar ba'i bde ba thabs dang stong pa shes rab kyis //
NK070(thu)001:1319: don bde stong gis ro gnyis gsal stong mnyam par dus gsum mi 'gyur bar bzhugs //
NK070(thu)001:1320: pa ni thabs dang shes rab ces nas /
NK070(thu)001:1321: dkyil krung du bzhugs pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1322: dwangs ma'i lnga 'dus pa thig le chen po yi //
NK070(thu)001:1323: bde ba'i bco lnga dngos po'ang ye shes su snang //
NK070(thu)001:1324: ba ni ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin
NK070(thu)001:1325: po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can zhes pa'i don
NK070(thu)001:1327: zhes 'phro tshol ba ni gang zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:1328: ldan pa zhes bya ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:1331: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:1332: 'du byed kyi rgyal po'i dang zhes pa bar du ni /
NK070(thu)001:1333: 'chad pa'i skyes bu dang rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:1335: bcom ldan 'das dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan thun
NK070(thu)001:1336: mong ba gnyis sngar ston pa'i rang bzhin du thal
NK070(thu)001:1337: te / kun gzhi la sogs pa'i rnam par shes pa /
NK070(thu)001:1338: gzugs kyi tshor ba'i 'du shes kyi 'du byed kyis
NK070(thu)001:1339: rtog pa phung po lnga lha'i mtshan du smos pa
NK070(thu)001:1341: bzhi pa rang bzhin dang kyi dbang du phung po
NK070(thu)001:1342: lnga dang rigs lnga gnyis snang mnyam stong mnyam yin
NK070(thu)001:1343: pas bzang ngan med pa thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1344: rgyud 'di'i skabs su lha rtogs dbyer med du ngos
NK070(thu)001:1345: zin pa'i phyir smos pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1346: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i skabs su rtogs pa /
NK070(thu)001:1347: de dag kar dag pa thugs su chud pa las /
NK070(thu)001:1348: phung po lnga ma spangs ma bsgyur bar lha rdo rje 'dzin pa la stsogs par rigs lnga /
NK070(thu)001:1351: rang bzhin ye nas yin pa las khyad par du
NK070(thu)001:1352: lam gyis mngon du byas pa 1dang 'khor 'das la
NK070(thu)001:1353: spyod kyang zag pa med pa'i chos nyid la longs
NK070(thu)001:1354: spyod pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i 1phyir na /
NK070(thu)001:1357: de dag kun kyang mthing ka dang /
NK070(thu)001:1361: ljang gu'i mdog tu 'tsher ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1362: rang bzhin ye nas yin pa las ma 'das ste mngon du byas pa'i phyir kha dog smos te /
NK070(thu)001:1363: don ye shes lnga po rnams kyi rtsal ma 'dres
NK070(thu)001:1364: pa nyid don yid la rtags ni de dag kun
NK070(thu)001:1365: kyang zhes pa nas mtsher pa zhes pa'i bar ni
NK070(thu)001:1366: gdul bya'i snang bar kha dog /
NK070(thu)001:1367: cir yang snang bas blta bas mi ngom pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1368: sde tshim de dag gdul bya'i snang bas gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:1370: phung po lnga'i rtog pa'i mtshan ma kun bcom bde ba 00chen po //
NK070(thu)001:1371: 'i ye shes kyi ro dang ldan pa /
NK070(thu)001:1372: bde ba rang gi ngo bo phyogs cig car yang ma grub pas //
NK070(thu)001:1373: 00rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mngon gsum du byas pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:1374: dper na 0bcom ldan 00'das de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod /
NK070(thu)001:1375: gzugs las sogs pa phung po lnga'i mtshungs ldan lhag pa'i thig le ni /
NK070(thu)001:1377: thabs kyis zin na lnga phung 'joms pa'i las dang
NK070(thu)001:1378: rigs lngar snang ba'i yon tan sngon nas ldan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1379: phyir // rigs kyi rgyal po zhes su brjod //
NK070(thu)001:1380: de de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa'i nas rgyal po dang zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1381: khams lnga'i bcud lnga khu ba'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i thig le ni //
NK070(thu)001:1382: thog mar lus grub pa'i rgyu thig le yang dam rdzas lnga /
NK070(thu)001:1383: dang gnas rtsa'i mdog kyis kha dog lnga dang ldan //
NK070(thu)001:1384: pa ste lte ba'i rtsa na sha chen gnas pa de sngo /
NK070(thu)001:1385: long ka na dri chen ser /
NK070(thu)001:1388: rkyang ma na dri chu ljang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:1389: dri chen kha ba la sogs pa'i ro dang nad
NK070(thu)001:1390: sel sman lnga grub pa'i las kyang de bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:1392: de dag kyang zhes pa nas ljang gu'i mdog tu zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1393: de ltar rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres par kun tu snang //
NK070(thu)001:1394: zhes pa ni mtshar ba'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1398: sa sogs pa'i bar du ni /
NK070(thu)001:1399: yab gang zhig gis spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1400: btsun mo ste lnga de dag yon tan gyi rtsal
NK070(thu)001:1401: sems ma man chad la khyad par du gyur pas
NK070(thu)001:1402: dam pa'i snang ba nam mkha' la sogs pa 'byung
NK070(thu)001:1403: ba lnga'i rtog pa smos pa'i rgyu mtshan gsum ni
NK070(thu)001:1404: yab kyis rjes su mthun pa te sra ba'i sa
NK070(thu)001:1408: 'byung ba lnga ni phung po lnga'i rgyu'i snod bcud
NK070(thu)001:1409: kun gyis rgyur gyur pa ni skabs kyis nas dbyings
NK070(thu)001:1410: zhes so // la sogs par bsdu ba ni 'og gi btsun mo'i tshogs zhes pa mthun pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1412: rgyud 'di'i thabs shes thams cad kyi spyi rgyud du
NK070(thu)001:1413: khas len pa'i phyir na ston pa nyid 'khor bud
NK070(thu)001:1414: med kyi dkyil na gsung tshig tu brjod pa gnyis
NK070(thu)001:1416: pas shes rab kyi rgyud du yang 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:1417: chos kyi dbyings zhes pa nas bzhugs so zhes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1418: bar ni til gyi gong bu bu'i dpes 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:1420: chos kyi dbyings mtha' yas par khyab pa'i rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:1421: mngon du byas pa dang rang bzhin rig pa ni
NK070(thu)001:1422: thams cad kyis bdag nyid chen po'i las gzhan med
NK070(thu)001:1423: pa phyir til gong bzhin du gzhan gyi sel med
NK070(thu)001:1424: pa ni tshad med pa kho nas te khyab par
NK070(thu)001:1426: de dag kyang thal ba'i rgyud las /
