NK070(thu)001:1427: nam mkha' la sogs pa phyi rol kun btags kyis
NK070(thu)001:1428: 'byung ba ni nang gi dngas ma ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:1430: ste de'ang dngas ma ye shes kyi 'byung ba lnga'i byed las dag gis //
NK070(thu)001:1431: phyi kun brtags kyis 'byung ba lnga bskyed pa'i phyir na dbyings su brjod pa ste //
NK070(thu)001:1432: de bas na btsun mo'i dngos por yang dwangs ma ye shes kyi 'byung ba de brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:1433: byang sems thig le ni snod kyi rtsa ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK070(thu)001:1434: til gong lta bur rtsa spubs kyi mkha' gang ba //
NK070(thu)001:1437: ye shes la skus khyab pa /
NK070(thu)001:1438: des na rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs chen po brjod kyis mi lang //
NK070(thu)001:1441: de nas byang chub chen po zhes pa nas myong bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:1443: 'di nas mar 'bras bu'i sems dpa' sems ma yin
NK070(thu)001:1444: pas thugs rig pa'i ye shes khyad par can gyi
NK070(thu)001:1445: 'khor ston te / gdul bya kun tu 'od dang mthar lam gyi zhes pa byang ba /
NK070(thu)001:1447: drug pa'i sangs rgyas kyi gdul bya'i zhing du gyur pas chub te /
NK070(thu)001:1448: de dag rgyu'i sa bcu man chad gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas te /
NK070(thu)001:1449: lta ba'i sgrib pa bag la nyal phra ba 'jam pa'i phyir las kyi sgo nas rdo rje'o //
NK070(thu)001:1450: lha'i mtshan nyid mig la sogs pa'i rtog pa smos
NK070(thu)001:1451: pa pa'i rgyu mtshan ni gtso bo rjes su mthun
NK070(thu)001:1452: te / mthong ba mig gi rnam shes de lta na sa'i snying po dang /
NK070(thu)001:1453: snom pa nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK070(thu)001:1454: myong ba spyan ras can dang /
NK070(thu)001:1455: thos pa phyag na rdo rje de dag gzugs l+aa
NK070(thu)001:1456: s+ye ma dang dri ma le dang ma ro glu
NK070(thu)001:1457: ma dang sgra gar du ldan par bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:1458: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed ces pa nas ma byon pa zhes pa'i bar du ni /
NK070(thu)001:1460: dus bzhi ni dbang po mig la sogs pa dwangs
NK070(thu)001:1461: ma'i las kyi shes pa lnga la yul snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1462: dus kyi go 'byed pa'i phyir dbang po dang dus
NK070(thu)001:1463: de dag thabs yab dang shes rab yum tu smos
NK070(thu)001:1464: so // mthong byed mig gi dbang po de dag kyang lha na byams pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1465: rna ba'i dbang po sgrib sel dang /
NK070(thu)001:1466: sna'i dbang po kun po dang /
NK070(thu)001:1467: lce'i dbang po 'jam dpal rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:1468: 'das pa spos me dang da ltar me tog dang phyis 'byung ba mar me dang /
NK070(thu)001:1469: ma byon pa'i tshogs bsil byed mar ldan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1471: mig la sogs rnam shes bzhi'i rang gi thig le ni //
NK070(thu)001:1473: he du las bya ba byed pa dang ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:1474: chos nyid rig pa 'bras bu'i lta'i ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:1475: yin pa phyir // sems dpa' chen po'i byang chub chen po nyid du brjod //
NK070(thu)001:1477: rtog pa bzhi'i nyes pa zad par byed pa'i phyir las 'jams pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK070(thu)001:1478: shes pa rang gi 'byung gnas dbang bo'i bye brag kyis phye ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:1479: gzugs la sogs pa yul bzhi'i mtshungs ldan gyi thig
NK070(thu)001:1480: le nang nyid phyir rol gyi yul bzhir snang ste
NK070(thu)001:1481: // rang gi snod rtsa dang bcud thig le bcas pa de las //
NK070(thu)001:1482: bde ba bskyed pa'i phyir na btsun mo'o //
NK070(thu)001:1483: zhes dus ni skad cig bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:1484: 'byung ba bzhi'i rlung gis go phyes te //
NK070(thu)001:1485: byis pa la sogs pa tshad med bzhi'i ye shes bzhi //
NK070(thu)001:1487: de'i bde ba skad cig ma bzhis rim par skye ba yang //
NK070(thu)001:1488: dad pa la sogs pa dbang po lnga la sogs
NK070(thu)001:1489: pa bsgom nas snang bas ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang
NK070(thu)001:1490: po dag du nges par gsung //
NK070(thu)001:1492: 'jam pa chen po rdo rje reg pa zhes pa nas bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar ni /
NK070(thu)001:1493: sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las kyi gsang ba'i khams kyis rtog pas rtog pa gzhan 'jom pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:1497: gnod sbyin srin po la sogs pa las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1499: lus kyi reg pa reg byed reg bya reg shes la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1500: gsang ba'i khams gsum dang sum 'dus kyis reg pa gang bzhi po rnams yin te /
NK070(thu)001:1501: gzhan yang lus kyi spyi'i chos bzhi kyang dor ba ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:1502: rtag pa la so gas pa ni'i /
NK070(thu)001:1505: mtshan ma ste lta ngan bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:1506: dngos po rnams la phyin ci log par 'dzin pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1507: sa lus grub pa phyir yab yum du 'brel pa
NK070(thu)001:1508: ste / rtog pa smos pa'i rgyu mtshan ni gtso
NK070(thu)001:1509: bo dang rjes su mthun pa dang phyin ci log
NK070(thu)001:1510: bzhi de dag mi gnas par byed pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:1511: ste / // ma yin zhes bya rtog pa de
NK070(thu)001:1512: dag kyang gshin rje dang gsang ba'i rnam shes ni
NK070(thu)001:1513: ste / // lha na thugs / sprul sku stobs
NK070(thu)001:1514: po che dang dbang po'i gsung rta'i rgyal po dang
NK070(thu)001:1515: ste / // lha na thugs / / reg pa
NK070(thu)001:1516: phrin las bdud rtsi 'khyil pa rnams yum bzhi dang
NK070(thu)001:1517: 'khril bas rngams pa'i tshul gyis gdug pa can 'dul
NK070(thu)001:1518: ba'i phyir zhal phyir bltas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1519: log pa de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang
NK070(thu)001:1520: ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:1521: ba ni / rigs lnga dang rang bzhin dang dgongs
NK070(thu)001:1522: pa gnyis su med pa yum lnga dang thun mong
NK070(thu)001:1523: min pa dang 'i phyir gnyis su med pa bdag
NK070(thu)001:1524: nyid chen po dang rang bzhin gyis snang grags gcig
NK070(thu)001:1525: pa'i phyir go phye ba'i 'khor dang gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:1526: ba ni / pa / lhan cig pa'i 'khor dang
NK070(thu)001:1527: gnas 'og min kyi snang bar gcig pa'i phyir gnyis
NK070(thu)001:1528: su med par bzhugs so zhes bzhag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1529: yang na rang bzhin 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1530: thun mong ma yin pa ston 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:1534: zhing khams mthang gnyis su med par bzhugs so zhes bzhag go //
NK070(thu)001:1536: gsang ba'i yul dang dbang po dang rnam par shes pa sum 'dus kyi reg /
NK070(thu)001:1538: lus kyi chos bzhi po de 'dus te snyom par 'jug nas bde ba la longs spyad pas //
NK070(thu)001:1539: rtogs tshogs gzhan ma lus pa 'joms pa'i phyir khro bo ste //
NK070(thu)001:1540: mtshan gyis khro bo nyid dang gsang ba'i khams so //
NK070(thu)001:1541: gzhan rnams dbang po yul sogs thams cad 'joms pa'i byed las kyi khro bo bzhir phye ba yin //
NK070(thu)001:1543: gsang ba'i khams gsum thabs kyi spyod pa 'di nyid //
NK070(thu)001:1545: rtags sogs phyin ci log gis mtshan ma las kyis bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:1546: lta ngan bzhi la btsun mo zhes su bstan pa ste //
NK070(thu)001:1547: sbyor ba bde ba'i byed las kyi skabs kyi rtog pa phyin ci log bazha la mi gnas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1550: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK070(thu)001:1551: gnyis su med pa'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag
NK070(thu)001:1553: ces bya ba ni 'di nas mar rgyud khyad par can gyi /
NK070(thu)001:1554: gleng gzhi bsdus pa ston te /
NK070(thu)001:1555: pas na de nas zhes bya /
NK070(thu)001:1556: de sa thabs yab bco brgyad dang btsun mo'i tshogs /
NK070(thu)001:1557: shes rab yum bco brgyad gnyis su med par 'byor
NK070(thu)001:1558: pa'i bde ba chen po'i ngo bo la 'bras bu'i
NK070(thu)001:1559: yon tan ril lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1561: rtogs dka' ba'i phyir kun gyis thun mong ma yin
NK070(thu)001:1562: pas na gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor te de bzhin gshegs
NK070(thu)001:1563: pa / yab yum de dag gi dgongs pa'i ngo
NK070(thu)001:1564: bo nyid kyis don ni ston par snang ba dang
NK070(thu)001:1565: gnas 'khor gsum ni reg pa'i sems su mi phyed
NK070(thu)001:1566: pa / pa'o // de nye bar mtshon pa ni gsang ba 'di nyid 'og nas ston pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1567: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:1569: lnga'i ngo bo ni rigs lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:1570: de dag tu snang bas gcig dang drug pa las
NK070(thu)001:1571: ma g.yos pas 1du ma dang 11bral bas rigs lnga
NK070(thu)001:1572: dbyer med mi phyed pas rdo rje'o //
NK070(thu)001:1573: rgyud kyis ston pa'i ngo bo yang rdo rje yin la /
NK070(thu)001:1574: gdul bya'i mos pa snang bas thugs sgyu 'phrul /
NK070(thu)001:1575: 'chad pa'i skyes bu mi bskyod pa ni rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:1576: rigs kho na'i rgyu snang ba phyir rdo rje ste
NK070(thu)001:1578: mngon du snang bas na phyung ngo zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:1581: e ma zhes pa ston pa dang phun sum tshogs pa la ngam pa /
NK070(thu)001:1582: e ma zhes pa 1gnas dang e ma'o zhes pa
NK070(thu)001:1583: 1'khor de rnams gzhan las 111khyad par can du gyur
NK070(thu)001:1585: ston pa'i dgongs pa rang rig pa nyid ston 'khor
NK070(thu)001:1586: gnas gsum gyi khyad par du snang ba la ngom
NK070(thu)001:1587: pa gsum mo // de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid /
NK070(thu)001:1588: ces pa ni gnas kyi rang bzhin ston te /
NK070(thu)001:1589: de yang sems nyid la yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i de 0bzhin nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:1590: mnyam pa nyid kyi 0dbyings su ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1592: de yang yang lci na 'og min zhes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:1595: zhes tshigs rkang gsum pa bsdud pa dbang bsgyur zhes bya ba ni ston pa'i ngo bo ste /
NK070(thu)001:1596: de yang shes bya'i don gong ma 00de nyid shes
NK070(thu)001:1597: byed yid byed pa po rang byung gi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1598: kyi rtogs par mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1600: de'ang sku mdun pa dang rgyab ces pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:1601: dbu gsum dang ldan zhes pa'i bar sdud pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1602: ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang zhes bya ba ni ston pa'i rang bzhin te de yang /
NK070(thu)001:1603: rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lngar gsal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1604: bye brag rnams las 'bras bu'i chos sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:1605: yon tan phrin las lnga'i dkyil 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:1606: ril du snang ba la zhes mya ngan las 'das dang /
NK070(thu)001:1607: de nyid 'khor ba dus gsum gyi chos kun tu
NK070(thu)001:1608: rgya ma chad pas thugs rjes ngang gi ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:1610: de yang de ba zhes pa nas dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1611: rang snang ba nyid ces bya ba ni gnas kyis ngo bo ston te /
NK070(thu)001:1612: don de rtogs pa'i rig pa las 'bras bu sku
NK070(thu)001:1613: dang ye shes thabs cad rdzogs pa nyid kyi rtsal
NK070(thu)001:1614: ma 'gag par rang snang ba ni nyid rtags gru
NK070(thu)001:1615: bzhi / glo bur dang bzhi rtse mo'i dbyibs dang kha dog rgyan sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:1616: de'ang gzhi tshad med ces pa nas mi khyab par klub pa zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1617: ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba ni sgo bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:1618: de yang ston pa nyid la sogs pa'i rnam thar
NK070(thu)001:1619: bzhi ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pas na
NK070(thu)001:1620: ste de'ang rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug
NK070(thu)001:1621: pa'i sgo khyud can zhes sgo bzhir bsgom pa'ang de
NK070(thu)001:1622: thun mong lam steg gi theg pa brgyad kyi sgo
NK070(thu)001:1623: nas don mtshon dgos pa'i phyir de'i mtshon byed gzugs
NK070(thu)001:1624: brnyan rta bab brgyad de de'ang rnam par zhes pa
NK070(thu)001:1625: nas ldan pa zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1626: sgyu ma rnam dag gsal ba zhes bya ba ni gdan ste /
NK070(thu)001:1627: don rtogs pa'i rig pa sgyu ma lta bu nyid
NK070(thu)001:1628: stobs mi 'jigs rdzu 'phrul dbang phrin las bzhi la
NK070(thu)001:1629: sogs pa'i 'bras bu'i chos su snang bas rtags seng
NK070(thu)001:1630: ge la sogs pa lngar bsgom pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1631: de'ang mi 'jigs pa nas khrid dang zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1632: rnam dag ni chos thams cad rig pa'i yin pa
NK070(thu)001:1633: phyir gang la spyad kyang nyes pas mi gos pa
NK070(thu)001:1635: gsal la ba zhes bya ni /
NK070(thu)001:1636: ma skyes pa'i ye shes nyid thabs dang shes rab tu gsal bar snang bas nyi zlar bsgom pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1637: de'ang rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang zhes pa'i don no //
NK070(thu)001:1638: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa der lha ci zhig bsgom snyoms pa las /
NK070(thu)001:1639: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhes gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:1640: 'chad pa'i skyes bu dang rang bzhin gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:1641: pa'i 'khor te phung po dang 'byung ba dkar dag
NK070(thu)001:1642: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rigs
NK070(thu)001:1644: de'ang bcom ldan 'das zhes pa nas btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis medapara zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1645: sel med pa zhes bya ba ni 'khor gyi tshad de /
NK070(thu)001:1646: de yang phung po lnga dang 'byung bas lnga pos /
NK070(thu)001:1647: rtog tshogs ril bsdus pas rtog tshogs thams cad kyang
NK070(thu)001:1648: sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor gsal bas gzhan
NK070(thu)001:1649: gyis sel med par gyur pas 'khor de dag mang
NK070(thu)001:1650: ba dang khyab pa'i tshad ni dpe til gyi gong
NK070(thu)001:1651: bu ltar spyod yul thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1652: kyis dkyil 'khor du yongs su dag pa dag pa
NK070(thu)001:1653: kho na'o // de'ang chos dbyings zhes pa nas bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1654: yon tan yid bzhin rin po che zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1655: sku mdog ste lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por gsal
NK070(thu)001:1656: ba de dag thabs ma 'dres par yon tan gyi
NK070(thu)001:1657: don mdzad pa'i phyir rin po che sna tshogs kyis
NK070(thu)001:1658: tshon shel du bcug pa ltar phyi nang med par
NK070(thu)001:1660: de'ang de dag kun zhes pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:1661: tshor ba zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:1662: yang na yid bzhin rin po che'i gdan du 'dod pa yang yod /
NK070(thu)001:1663: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo zhes bya ba ni rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:1664: de yang phung po dang 'byung ba de dag bye
NK070(thu)001:1665: brag tu phye ba khams dang skye mched la sogs
NK070(thu)001:1666: pa'i tha snyad ril 'bras bu sku dang ye shes
NK070(thu)001:1667: kyi dkyil 'khor mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK070(thu)001:1669: rgyas par phye bas grangs las 'das pas na /
NK070(thu)001:1670: de nas byang chub chen po zhes pa nas brjod
NK070(thu)001:1671: kyis mi long ba gnyis su med par bzhugs so
NK070(thu)001:1673: rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do zhes bya ba ni gleng gzhi'i nges tshig ste /
NK070(thu)001:1674: de yang gsang sngags pa rdo rje'i theg pa rgyud kyi mchog gi 'byung ba'i gnas nyid ni /
NK070(thu)001:1675: ston gnas 'khor gsum po 'tshogs pa las 'byung ba ni rjes 'jug gi bstan pa'i che ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:1676: yang sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i gsum po 'bras bu'i 'i mchog ni /
NK070(thu)001:1677: lam bsdu ba'i tshigs bzhis mtshon pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:1678: bsgom gyi nyams su len pa las 'byung ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:1680: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK070(thu)001:1682: ston gnas 'khor gyis snang ba gsum rang rig par mi phyed pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK070(thu)001:1683: rtogs shing nyams su lon par dka' bas gsang ba de dbang mtshon pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1684: ra byed pa'i tshig tu gleng gzhi'i le'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1685: gleng ba ni brjod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1686: 'bras bu bstan pa brjod par bya ba don gyis
NK070(thu)001:1687: bstan pa'i sems nyid dang brjod par byed pa gnyis
NK070(thu)001:1688: tshig gi bstan pa lam gsang snying gnyis kyis gazhi'am
NK070(thu)001:1689: rtsa ba ston pa la sogs pa gnas 'khor gsum
NK070(thu)001:1691: las 'byung ba le'u dang po'i don mdor bkrol ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:1693: // tsam du brda de nas bcom ldan ka'das rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:1694: gayid byed pa po khakun tu bzang po zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:1695: ba ni / de ma thag par rgyud bshad pa'i skabs 'byed pa nas gleng bslang ste /
NK070(thu)001:1696: rgyu gleng gzhi bstan rkyen gleng bslang ston pa nas rgyud kyi rkyen gleng bslang ba la gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:1697: dang po thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:1698: la gnyis kyis dang po 'khor snod du smin par
NK070(thu)001:1699: byed pa gsang ba'i dbang ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:1700: bcom ldan 'das ni sngar bshad zin la yid ni
NK070(thu)001:1701: rtogs ma rtogs kyis gnas skabs kyis sems can gyi
NK070(thu)001:1702: rtog 0pa 1dang sangs rgyas kyi 0ye shes 1kyi bdag
NK070(thu)001:1703: 11nyid kyi phyir / 0'khor ba dang 0mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis ka'i byed pa pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1705: de yang sngags pa ltos pa kun tu brtags pa
NK070(thu)001:1706: can dang ldan pa'i sems tsam pa rnams kyis lus
NK070(thu)001:1707: kyis yid rgyu lnga ma'i rkyen las skye zhing snang
NK070(thu)001:1708: bar 'dod pa de las 'dir khyad par du 'khor
NK070(thu)001:1709: 'das dbyer med kyi bdag nyid du gyur pas na
NK070(thu)001:1711: de'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:1712: don rang byung gi ye shes ngo bo gang 'dus
NK070(thu)001:1713: ma byas pas na mtshan nyid skye 'jigs dang bral
NK070(thu)001:1714: ba'i phyir rdo rje'i yid do //
NK070(thu)001:1715: rang byung ye shes de nyid gzhan nas ma rtsal bar thams cad du rang snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:1716: snang ba thams cad kyang rang byung ye shes kho
NK070(thu)001:1717: na yin bas na rin chen gling bzhin du spangs
NK070(thu)001:1718: bya'i sel mi dmigs pa'i phyir kun tu bzang po'o
NK070(thu)001:1719: // don de nyid rtags rgyal ba drug par snang bas na don las mtshan du btags pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1720: thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyis tshul rdo rjes /
NK070(thu)001:1722: yid ni chos thams cad kyi byed pa po'i yin
NK070(thu)001:1723: pa phyir des gang byas pa'i chos ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:1724: lhag ma ma lus pa'i rang bzhin ni don rang
NK070(thu)001:1725: rig pa'i ye shes su tshul cig la /
NK070(thu)001:1726: don de rang snang ba'i rtags rgyal ba ril yang
NK070(thu)001:1727: rgyal ba drug par tshul cig pas de dag thams
NK070(thu)001:1728: cad dbyer mi phyed pa ni sku gsung thugs rdo
NK070(thu)001:1729: rje'i bdag po'o // btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mo la 'jug par gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:1730: zhes bya ba ni yid kyis yongs su shes par
NK070(thu)001:1731: bya ba'i yul nyid ni 'dus byas dang ni gzugs
NK070(thu)001:1732: tshor ba 'du shes 'du byed bzhi 'dus ma byas
NK070(thu)001:1733: pa'i chos la so sor brtags pa dang brtag min
NK070(thu)001:1735: nam mkha' chos nyid de bzhin nyid dang bzhi'i ril sems nyid kyi phyir rang snang ba yin pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:1736: des pas spangs par bya ba mi dmigs pa nyid
NK070(thu)001:1737: rtags skur rang snang ba ni kun tu bzang mo
NK070(thu)001:1738: chen po'i gzungs ma te don de la tshigs de
NK070(thu)001:1739: skad ces bya'o // yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis su med par snyoms par 'jug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1740: ngo bo rang rgyud can med kyang gdul bya'i ngo na snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:1741: ra gyur to zhes bya zhugs pas phyogs bcu dus
NK070(thu)001:1742: bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus pa thams cad
NK070(thu)001:1743: gcig gi rang bzhin dbyer med pas zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:1744: ni / de ltar zhugs pa'i dgos ched ni dus
NK070(thu)001:1745: gsum ni go sla la rgyu rkyen yod la ma
NK070(thu)001:1746: 'tshogs pa'i 'byung bar ma nges pa'i de pa ni
NK070(thu)001:1747: ni / / 'gro ba drug gi ril su yang
NK070(thu)001:1748: 'gyur ba'i phyir na phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bsdus pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1749: de pa ma lus pa'i chos thams cad lhan cig
NK070(thu)001:1750: skyes pa'i ye shes su gcig gi rang bzhin dbyer
NK070(thu)001:1751: med par gsal ba las 'khor 'das sam rang gzhan
NK070(thu)001:1752: tha dad gnyis mi snang ba'i phyir de pa nyid
NK070(thu)001:1753: de pa nyid la ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK070(thu)001:1754: ni / / zhes gsungs te / de la kun
NK070(thu)001:1755: bzang yab yum nyid kyi lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:1756: de pa nyid la dbang bskur zhing grol ba'i ched
NK070(thu)001:1757: du dgongs pa la gsal bas tshig tu brjod pa
NK070(thu)001:1758: ni / / zhes gsungs te / dang 'dra ba'o
NK070(thu)001:1759: // 'og gi tshig 'di dag brjod pa zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:1760: ni / / zhes gsungs te / dang 'dra ba'o // ba'o // e ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:1761: zhes bya ba ni 0ngom pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1762: ci'i phyir ngom na yab yum snyoms 'jug gi 'dod
NK070(thu)001:1763: chags kyi sgo nas spyod yul thams cad sku dang
NK070(thu)001:1764: ye shes su yongs su dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:1765: bde ba nyams su myong ba nyid la ngom pa de dag gang yin snyoms pa la /
NK070(thu)001:1766: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK070(thu)001:1767: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te lnga phung
NK070(thu)001:1768: gi 0rgyud ni rang rig pa'i ye shes rdo rje'o
NK070(thu)001:1769: // skyen 0ni gsang ba'i rdo rje rtse la dang
NK070(thu)001:1770: 1pad+ma'i lte ba la m+aum du 'brel pa'i rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:1774: rgyu 0rkyen 0gnyis kyi phyir phung po lnga rang rig
NK070(thu)001:1775: gi ngo bo nyid ni snang stong dbyer mi phyed
NK070(thu)001:1777: lnga po de dag rang gi yan lag ni rnam shes brgyad /
NK070(thu)001:1782: brgyad cu dang bcas pa de nyid /
NK070(thu)001:1783: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags /
NK070(thu)001:1784: zhes bya ba spyir rgyu'i theg pa'i 1sangs rgyas dang /
NK070(thu)001:1785: sngags kyi theg pa'i yang dag 2par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 2la /
NK070(thu)001:1789: de ni thabs kyis lam 'dis 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK070(thu)001:1790: pa'i phyir grags pa ni brjod pa 'dra ba'i dgongs
NK070(thu)001:1791: pa gsal ba'o // skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK070(thu)001:1792: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK070(thu)001:1794: skye mched dang khams ni mig la sogs pa yul dbang po rnam shes te lnga gsum bco lnga'o //
NK070(thu)001:1795: rnams kyi sgras ni 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus
NK070(thu)001:1796: bzhi dang rtag chad bdag mtshan phyin ci log bzhi
NK070(thu)001:1797: dang yum lus kyi reg pa dag go //
NK070(thu)001:1798: rtog pa'i bye brag mang po kun kyang de dag
NK070(thu)001:1799: rig pa rang snang bas khams dang skye mched kyi
NK070(thu)001:1800: rdo rje'i phyi byang chub sems dpa' brgyad dang sems
NK070(thu)001:1801: ma brgyad de bcu drug go //
NK070(thu)001:1802: der sgo ba yab yum ma 'dus snyom na khro
NK070(thu)001:1803: bo yang ston pa skus gdul bya'i lugs zlog 'dul
NK070(thu)001:1804: skabs kyi byang chub sems dpa' dang sems ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:1805: ste rtog pa mthun pa sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma ki //
NK070(thu)001:1806: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK070(thu)001:1807: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK070(thu)001:1810: snying nang gis dwangs ma lnga ye shes kyi 'byung
NK070(thu)001:1811: ba lnga po nyid log par brtag pa'i dbang gi
NK070(thu)001:1812: phyi rol kun brtags kyi 'byung ba bzhir nam mkhas
NK070(thu)001:1813: 'phangs go phye par snang ba de dag rang rig
NK070(thu)001:1815: phyir dpe don snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so //
NK070(thu)001:1816: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang lnga po de dag gis phung lnga bskyed pa'i byed /
NK070(thu)001:1817: las kyi sangs rgyas spyan m+aa ma ki gos dkar
NK070(thu)001:1818: mo dam tshig sgrol ma dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma
NK070(thu)001:1819: ste / yum du chad pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:1820: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK070(thu)001:1822: srid pa khams gsum gyis bsdus pa ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:1823: med pa'i ngang las snang bas chags pa dang sprul
NK070(thu)001:1824: sku mi 'gyur ba brtan pa gnas 1pa dang longs
NK070(thu)001:1825: sku zhig / gnas stongs pa 'jigs par chos sku
NK070(thu)001:1826: snang 111ba de dag chos can he du rang rig
NK070(thu)001:1827: gi phyir yang na he du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:1828: sku gsum gyi ngo bo nyid du 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:1829: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su dag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1830: zhes dam bca' thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK070(thu)001:1831: sangs rgyas nyid la gzhan ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:1833: gong ma de dag gis mtshon nas chos ci snyed pa /
NK070(thu)001:1834: thams cad la yang brtag pa'i ming dang ba glang
NK070(thu)001:1835: byed pa'i las smo bzho dang snang ba'i dngos po
NK070(thu)001:1837: mtshon pa mtshan nag po dang lkog shal dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:1838: pa nyid ste tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa'i ril ma
NK070(thu)001:1839: lus chos so chog kun kyang rang rig pa rang
NK070(thu)001:1840: byung gi ye shes yin pa'i phyir 'bras bu sku
NK070(thu)001:1842: dkar dag pas sangs rgyas pa nyid las gzhan ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:1843: de ltar sangs rgyas nyid yin la /
NK070(thu)001:1844: de las gzhan pa'i cho 'phrul pas brtag pa'i tha
NK070(thu)001:1845: snyad bzhi po de dag gis dngos po rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:1847: logs su btsal na sa kyang rgyal ba de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:1848: gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi spyan gyis kyang gzhan du
NK070(thu)001:1849: mi gzigs pas na mi snyed ces pa sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:1851: btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK070(thu)001:1854: thabs lam gyi bde ba'i gnyer bas ye shes kyis khyed pa'i las kyis don du dag gi //
NK070(thu)001:1855: rang kha mar blos brtag pas snang ba rang gi rtog pa'i zhen pa rtog pa bzlog /
NK070(thu)001:1856: par thad kyis dngos po rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo bo la //
NK070(thu)001:1858: rang rgyud pa'i bzlog bya ste spang bya'i zhen pa ston pa ngas kyang mi gzigs so //
NK070(thu)001:1860: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1861: zhes brjod pas rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:1862: kyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams thams cad kyis ston
NK070(thu)001:1863: pa'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur pas mnyes par gyur
NK070(thu)001:1864: to zhes / de nas zhes bya ba nas /
NK070(thu)001:1865: bzang po dang zhes pa'i bar ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:1866: gnyis su med par gyur nas /
NK070(thu)001:1868: rtags nyi zla'i thig le gnyis su med pa ste 'khor rnams /
NK070(thu)001:1869: don dgongs pa dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med yang bsdu'o //
NK070(thu)001:1870: 1yab 1yum gyi snyoms par zhugs pa'i las dang zhugs pa'i dgos pa nyams su /
NK070(thu)001:1871: myong ba dang de'i don 'khor la tshig tu /
NK070(thu)001:1873: 'di dag yi ger snga phyi yod kyang don /
NK070(thu)001:1874: dus la snga phyir ma gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:1876: kye zhes pa 'khor la bos 1pa dang ma'o zhes pa bde ba la ngom 2 pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:1877: de'i phyir bos na bde 1ba 'khor gzhan la bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:1878: gcig 1ni yab kyis rjes su mthun pa yin no //
NK070(thu)001:1879: phyogs 1bcu'i stong khams ye na dben //
NK070(thu)001:1880: zhes bya ba ni gzhi don gyis kun gzhi nyid
NK070(thu)001:1881: phyogs dus kyi tha snyad gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i phyi
NK070(thu)001:1882: rol gyis don dang nang sems can du rang snang
NK070(thu)001:1883: bas de dag nyid kun gzhi ma skyes pa'i dbyings
NK070(thu)001:1884: ye shes kyi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir chos kyi
NK070(thu)001:1885: sku yin ste / de la phyogs bcu gsum stong
NK070(thu)001:1886: khams la sogs pa'i tha snyad thams cad ye gdod
NK070(thu)001:1887: ma nas stong pa bdag nyid kyis bden pa kho
NK070(thu)001:1888: sku yin ste / na'o // srid 1pa gsum ni dag pa'i zhing /
NK070(thu)001:1889: zhes pa yab kyi skabs su bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:1890: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK070(thu)001:1892: lnga brgya tha ma'i dus dang lus chung la nad mang ba'i sems can dang /
NK070(thu)001:1893: tshe dang lo bcu pa las dang sdig pa nyon mongs pa /
NK070(thu)001:1894: dar drags pa rnams bzang po la mar 'grib ste tha ma'i phyir snyigs ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:1896: de nyid zhes pas brtag pa'i phyir gshis las ma
NK070(thu)001:1897: grub ste glo bur yin pas na sems kyi rang
NK070(thu)001:1898: bzhin chos nyid la ni myong ba tsam yang mi
NK070(thu)001:1899: dmigs pas na / bde ba chen po'i rol par ldan par gnas kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:1900: phung po lnga nyid ni mngon sangs rgyas //
NK070(thu)001:1901: ces yab du bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:1902: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK070(thu)001:1904: gong du bshad pa'i ming las dngos po mtshan nyid
NK070(thu)001:1905: bzhis bsdus pa 'i chos ril thams cad ye nas
NK070(thu)001:1906: dben dag pa'i zhing la sogs pa yon tan du
NK070(thu)001:1907: bstan pa ni / thob bya'i 'bras bu'i mchog ste /
NK070(thu)001:1910: gzhan du rgyal bas zhes pa nas mi brnyes so //
NK070(thu)001:1911: zhes bya ba'i bar du ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:1912: chos 1111can yang na ming la sogs pa bzhi po'i
NK070(thu)001:1913: rang bzhin chos sku las 'bras bu sangs rgyas kun
NK070(thu)001:1914: nas mi snyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:1915: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de pa nyid kyis mkhyen te /
NK070(thu)001:1916: zhes bya ba ni yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1917: don ye nas sangs rgyas pa 'bras bu lhan cig
NK070(thu)001:1918: pa'i 'khor rnams la dbri skol med par byin yang
NK070(thu)001:1919: de pa ston pa nyid kyi dgos pa 'khor rtogs
NK070(thu)001:1920: pa po rnams las gsal ba de nyid kyi mkhyen
NK070(thu)001:1921: to 'khor gzhan las don de mi snang ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:1922: na gsang dbang gi nges tshig tu 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:1923: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gnyis su med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1924: bdag nyid chen mo zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:1925: ni / rang rig pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK070(thu)001:1926: shin tu brtan pa'i bde ba chen po dbang gnyis
NK070(thu)001:1927: gis las bskur thabs kyis rim pa thun mong du
NK070(thu)001:1928: bstan pa'o // sa na de nas bya ba gnyis su med pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:1931: don dgongs pa yang gnyis su med pa mi 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:1932: sngon nas gdod ma snyoms par zhugs pa la mnga' mdzad pa'i phyir bdag nyid chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:1933: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i sems ye shes su bskyed pa 'di zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1934: ye nas de'i rtogs pa dngos po ngo bo zer
NK070(thu)001:1935: nyid yab yum gnyis kyi sku dang ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:1936: sangs rgyas par mkhyen pa gang yin pa de'o //
NK070(thu)001:1937: de lhan cig pa'i la 'khor gyi sems rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:1938: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su rang snang bar
NK070(thu)001:1939: byas pa yang / g.yo ldang la sogs pa rim
NK070(thu)001:1940: pa lnga'i bskyed par bya ba'i thabs kyi rim pa
NK070(thu)001:1941: byas pa yang / 'di gsungs so // zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:1942: de la spyir sems rim lnga ni bka' tshad ma las /
NK070(thu)001:1943: g.yo smon 'jug nas mthar phyin la sogs pa lngas
NK070(thu)001:1944: 'bras bu mthar phyin par gsungs pa de dag skabs
NK070(thu)001:1945: 'dir rgyas pa'i le'u bdun pa las /
NK070(thu)001:1946: nges tshig 'og nas 'byung ba ltar bshad 'jigs gadang ldang khadang byang chub kyi sems gnas casmon chapa'i //
NK070(thu)001:1947: g.yo ka dang 'gro ja'ong 'jug ngadang bde gnas pa //
NK070(thu)001:1948: yab kyi gsang ba'i dbang po dang yum gyi pad ma gnyis sbyor ba thob par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:1950: 'dir sbyor ba thabs kyi rim pas sems lnga rdzogs par ston te /
NK070(thu)001:1951: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK070(thu)001:1953: ni ngom pa ste sems lnga ka'i spyir 'agro'o //
NK070(thu)001:1954: don gang la ngo mtshar nas ngom zhe na 'dod chags kyi spyod pa nyid /
NK070(thu)001:1955: bka' tshad ma rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par rmad
NK070(thu)001:1956: du byung ba'i byang chub kyi sems ltar snang ba
NK070(thu)001:1957: ni / thabs kyi theg pa chen po'i chos so //
NK070(thu)001:1958: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK070(thu)001:1960: lam 'dod chags kyi 'bras bu byang chub thob pa
NK070(thu)001:1961: ni drug pa yang dag par rjogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:1962: kun gyi gsal byed kyi rgyu dang dgongs pa'i ngo
NK070(thu)001:1964: 'og ma ba phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:1966: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK070(thu)001:1968: g.yo ldang gi byang chub kyi sems te /
NK070(thu)001:1969: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la byang
NK070(thu)001:1970: sems skye ba med pa las dngos po lhan cig
NK070(thu)001:1971: skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong ba'i dus su
NK070(thu)001:1972: thig le rang gi gnas tsakra bzhi dang lam kun
NK070(thu)001:1973: d+ha ma nas mgo ldang ba'i tshe /
NK070(thu)001:1974: bde ba thams cad nyams su g.yo ba'i tsam du skyes pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:1975: rang bzhin gyi lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni
NK070(thu)001:1976: rgyu las skye ba dang 'jigs smon 'jug ril dang
NK070(thu)001:1977: bral ba ste / de ni sems lnga gdod ma
NK070(thu)001:1978: nas skye ba'i gzhi dang skyes pa'i bsgrub bya'i 'bras
NK070(thu)001:1979: bu ste sems lnga'i spyir shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:1980: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med ces bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1981: skyes pa nyid nas de'i phyi rol yang rang bzhin gyi ye shes las ma 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:1982: skye ba med pa e ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:1983: zhes bya ba la sogs gzhan ni bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:1984: 'gag pa med pa thams cad 'gag zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1985: 'jigs 1pa dang 'jug pa byang chub sems te /
NK070(thu)001:1986: rang bzhin lhan skyes kyi ye shes la nyi zla
NK070(thu)001:1987: byang sems 'gag pa med pa las dngos po lhan
NK070(thu)001:1988: cig skyes pa'i ye shes skye ba'i dus su bde
NK070(thu)001:1989: ba skyes pa bcu drug gi phyi ma la thig
NK070(thu)001:1990: le 'i bde ba la 'jug pa'i tshe 1snga ma'i
NK070(thu)001:1991: 'dod chags kyi bde ba'i ro thams cad 'gag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:1992: phyir ro // 'gag pa nyid na 'gag pa med zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1993: de ltar dngos po lhan skyes kyi ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:1994: bde ba'i rang bzhin la skad cig ma'i bde ba
NK070(thu)001:1997: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:1998: gnas pa byang chub sems yin te //
NK070(thu)001:1999: rang gzhin lhan skyes kyi ye shes la brten thig
NK070(thu)001:2000: le bcu drug gi rten bcas ye shes bcu drug
NK070(thu)001:2001: la blo gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis dngos po
NK070(thu)001:2002: lhan skyes kyi ye shes de thig le thams cad
NK070(thu)001:2003: rang sa na gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2004: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK070(thu)001:2006: de ltar dngos po lhan skyes kyi ye shes la
NK070(thu)001:2007: gnas pa ltar snang ba'i dus nyid na'ang rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:2008: gyi ye shes rig pa rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2009: dmigs pa'i yul dang bral bas gnas bca' ru med de /
NK070(thu)001:2010: shes pa dang shes bya dbyer med kyis don de
NK070(thu)001:2011: ye nas gnas pa'i 'bras bu yin pas de lam
NK070(thu)001:2013: dmigs pa med la thams cad dmigs zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2014: smon pa byang chub sems de rang bzhin gyi ngang la dmigs pa med pa las /
NK070(thu)001:2015: dngos po lhan skyes kyi bde ba'i ye shes snga ma la gnas bzhin du /
NK070(thu)001:2016: bde ba skyes pa'i thig le mtho dman gyi dbang
NK070(thu)001:2017: gis phyi ma'i bde ba skye zhing thob par 'dod
NK070(thu)001:2018: par 'dun cing smon pa nas thams cad dmigs pa
NK070(thu)001:2019: kho na'o // dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK070(thu)001:2021: de ltar dngos po lhan skyes kyis ye shes la
NK070(thu)001:2022: dmigs shing smon pas bde ba gong 'phel gyis bskyed
NK070(thu)001:2024: rang bzhin ye shes la dmigs pa med pa bde
NK070(thu)001:2025: ba de rang rig pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:2026: rkyen tsam ste / don gzhan nas thob pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2027: 'gro 'ong med las 'gro dang 'ong zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2028: rdzogs 'jug pa byang chub sems te /
NK070(thu)001:2029: rang bzhin gyi ye shes la byang sems 'gro 'ong
NK070(thu)001:2030: med pa las dngos po lhan skyes kyis byang sems
NK070(thu)001:2031: de dang po 'jig rten pa dang thun mong ngam
NK070(thu)001:2032: thun mong gi rgyu'i lam lnga pa bcu du 'jug
NK070(thu)001:2033: pa ni 'gro ba ste shes rab ye shes dbang
NK070(thu)001:2034: thob pa'o // de'i dus su rdo rje'i rtser thig le zung 'brel /
NK070(thu)001:2035: bde stong dbyer med kyi ye shes mngon du gyur pas bcu gcig kun tu 'od rdzogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2036: thabs kyi theg pa chen po'i lugs kyi snga ma
NK070(thu)001:2037: dang slar rgyu 'bras go ldog pa ni 'ong ba
NK070(thu)001:2038: sngags kyis lam tshang ba zhes bya ba kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:2041: de ltar byang sems 'gro 'ong du snang ba'i dus
NK070(thu)001:2042: nyid na thabs kyi lam 'dis mthar thug gi 'bras
NK070(thu)001:2044: sngon gyi gnas gang nas 'ong ba'i rtsa gnas su snyegs pas /
NK070(thu)001:2045: rjes su dran pa'i mngon par shes pa'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:2046: slar bzlog pas gang du yang phyir pa med pas na 'gro 'ong med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2048: de'i dus su sngags kyi 'bras bu gnyis rdzogs so //
NK070(thu)001:2049: sems lnga po 'di dag bde ba skye pa thig le dga' ba bcu drug gi skabs /
NK070(thu)001:2050: gcig la'ang lnga char tshang ba'i phyir bartsi'o //
NK070(thu)001:2051: be du ni sems lnga dus gcig tu skye bar
NK070(thu)001:2052: gyur pa'i phyir cig char du 'jug pa'i lam zhes
NK070(thu)001:2053: bya'o // dam bca' zhes brjod pas zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2054: thabs lam gyi sems lnga po des zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:2055: de pa thams cad dang btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad mnyes pas khyab par gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:2056: zhes bya ba ni sems bskyed pa'i thabs lnga po'i
NK070(thu)001:2057: sgo nas ma 'ongs pa'i mthar lam pa de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:2058: gshegs pa ste sems dpa' dang thams cad /
NK070(thu)001:2059: btsun mo'i tshogs sems ma thams cad ril gyis gsang
NK070(thu)001:2060: ba'i dbang gsum gyis phun sum tshogs pa'i 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:2061: lhun grub rnams / gsang dbang mchog gis 'byin par byed //
NK070(thu)001:2062: zhes sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lhun gyis grub ste /
NK070(thu)001:2063: brjod bya'i don gyis rgyud shes bya /
NK070(thu)001:2064: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don mngon sum du
NK070(thu)001:2065: byas nas 'bras bu sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu
NK070(thu)001:2066: rtsa lnga mthar phyin rdo rje 'chang chen po gsang
NK070(thu)001:2067: ba'i gral du bkod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2068: dgyes pa chen po'i phyir mnyes pas khyab par 'gyur ro zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:2071: dkyil 'khor gyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK070(thu)001:2072: phun sum tshogs pa lnga lhun grub rnams //
NK070(thu)001:2073: gsang ba'i dbang mchog gis mngon gsum du 'byin par byed //
NK070(thu)001:2076: de nas de pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas chen du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:2078: 'di nas mar thun mong du gleng bslang bas /
NK070(thu)001:2079: bstan pa tha dag bshad par zhus pa ston te /
NK070(thu)001:2080: zhes bya gang gis zhus na lhan cig pa'i 'khor 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2081: yum dang bcas pa rnams kyis so //
NK070(thu)001:2082: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK070(thu)001:2083: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK070(thu)001:2084: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK070(thu)001:2085: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang //
NK070(thu)001:2086: zhes bya ba 'i 'bras bu ni sngar bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:2087: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'bras bu'i rgyu khyad par can 'di lta bu /
NK070(thu)001:2088: gsang ba bzhis chod pa'i phyir rjes 'jug gi ston
NK070(thu)001:2089: pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i zhal dang dbang ma mthong
NK070(thu)001:2090: ma thob pas mngon du byed mi nus pas na
NK070(thu)001:2091: lam stegs kyi theg pa gzhan la blo sbyangs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2092: mthas sa mthar phyin pa'i sa 'di dag rtogs dgos
NK070(thu)001:2093: pa phyir de'i ched du lam rkyen gyi rgyud dang
NK070(thu)001:2094: thun mong pa'i chos rnams bshad du gsol /
NK070(thu)001:2098: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:2099: nyid gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin par dbyer med na'ang
NK070(thu)001:2101: 'di nas mar gnang bar ston te /
NK070(thu)001:2102: de pa'i rig bsal ba'i bsdu ba'i thams cad ni le'u dang por /
NK070(thu)001:2103: smos pa'i phyir 'dir ma bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:2104: chos thams cad ni 'bras bu'i chos ma rtogs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2105: 'khor ba rang gi rang bzhin dang de'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:2106: 'khrul pa dang 'i blo de'i gnyen po lam 1dang gyis chos tha 11snyad kyis bsdus pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2107: 'khor 'das kyi chos de dag gi ril sems nyid
NK070(thu)001:2108: yin pas sems de ni ye gdod ma nas mtha'
NK070(thu)001:2109: dang bral ba'i pang la rig pa bdag khyab chen
NK070(thu)001:2110: po'i ra rgyas pa ngo bor nyid du gcig pa
NK070(thu)001:2111: ste / de ka yang dag pa'i chos kyi sku'i mtshan nyid pas /
NK070(thu)001:2112: rang gi ngo bo cir yang mi g.yo ba'i ste dbyer med pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2113: na'ang gis sgras ma rtog pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2114: 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa mi rig pa las
NK070(thu)001:2115: 'gro ba lnga'i ris bsam gyis mi khyab par smin
NK070(thu)001:2116: pa la / zhes bya ba ni 'gro ba lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:2117: lha mi ngan song gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:2118: de'i phyir de'i rgyu rnam par rtog pa las 2dang kun slong nyon mongs pa lnga'o //
NK070(thu)001:2119: de dag gi rtsa ba ni'i rgyu /
NK070(thu)001:2120: lhan skyes dang kun brtags kyi ma rig pa rnam
NK070(thu)001:2121: pa gnyis kho na las byung ba'i don de la
NK070(thu)001:2123: 'gro ba lnga'i sems can de dag gi nang ris
NK070(thu)001:2124: mi 'dra ba ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa mang
NK070(thu)001:2125: ste por smin pa khams gsum gyi lha yang 'dod
NK070(thu)001:2126: khams na drug / gzugs khams na bcu bdun /
NK070(thu)001:2128: nyi shu rtsa bdun la sogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2129: thugs rje chen po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen
NK070(thu)001:2130: po skyes nas zhes bya ba ni spros pa dang
NK070(thu)001:2131: bral ba'i rig pa thams cad du mnyam par khyab
NK070(thu)001:2132: pa ni thugs rje chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:2133: de nyid gdul bya gang dag las gsang ba bzhis
NK070(thu)001:2134: chod de sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag pa dang 'i
NK070(thu)001:2135: sems can / 'bras bu gzhan du tshol ba'i 'og ma la de dag la yang snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:2136: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje chen po'i ye shes ni
NK070(thu)001:2137: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' 'i ye
NK070(thu)001:2138: shes dang thugs rje las khyad par du gyur pas
NK070(thu)001:2139: chen po'o // de 1dag skyes pa ni gdul bya'i snang bar brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:2140: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las /
NK070(thu)001:2141: zhes bya ba ni e ma'o ni ngo bo gcig
NK070(thu)001:2142: la 'khor 'das sam gzung 'dzin gnyis la sogs par
NK070(thu)001:2144: ngo mtshar te ma rangs pa'i tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:2145: chos nyid de bzhin nyid la spros pa'i yul dang
NK070(thu)001:2146: ngo bo zug ngu gnyis med pa bde ba ste
NK070(thu)001:2147: / ston pa'i skabs su bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:2150: de yang sbyor ba 'dun pa'i kun gzhi ni don
NK070(thu)001:2151: dang sems kyi 'char sgo snang bar byed pa'i go
NK070(thu)001:2152: 'byed pa po'i bag chags gis gos gzhi don gyi
NK070(thu)001:2153: kun gzhi ni 'bras bu nyer lnga thams cad lhun
NK070(thu)001:2155: de'ang chos thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2157: de dag rang gis ngo ma shes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2158: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2159: ma rig pa de 'khor ba'i gzhir rgyur gyur pa las 'byung khungs kyi sgra /
NK070(thu)001:2161: rang gi rnam rtog h'u las kyis sprul zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2162: ma rig pa'i rgyu de sbyor ba 'dun pa'i kun gzhi la bdag tu bzung ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2163: rang gi rnam par rtog pa ste de las kun
NK070(thu)001:2164: brtag pa'i nyon mongs pa dug lnga skyes pas kun
NK070(thu)001:2165: nas bslang nas ded la las dge sdig sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:2166: su spyad pas gshis la med kyang glo bur du
NK070(thu)001:2167: snang ba'i phyir las kyis sprul pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2168: de nyid kyi ngo bo ci lta bu snyom pa las sna 0tshogs 1111pa'i lus dang longs spyod 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:2170: zhes bya ba ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:2174: sems las bdag dang yul la bdag gi so sor 'dzin //
NK070(thu)001:2176: bshad pa nyid la bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:2177: de yang gnyis par 'khor te sdug bsngal gyis nyams thag go //
NK070(thu)001:2178: de byed pa po sus byas snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2179: sus kyang ma bcing bcings med de //
NK070(thu)001:2180: bcing bar bya ba'ang yod ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:2182: 'ching mkhan gyi byed pa po bdag lta bu sus
NK070(thu)001:2183: kyang ma bcing ba dang 'ching byed rang gi ngo
NK070(thu)001:2184: bo zhags pa dang lta bu kyang bcings pa med
NK070(thu)001:2185: de / bcings par bya ba'i yul dgra bo lta
NK070(thu)001:2186: bu'ang yod pa ma yin pa dang gsum ni ngang
NK070(thu)001:2187: de / gis med de / 'o na rgyu rkyen gang gis nyes snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2188: rnam h+aum rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:2189: nan gyi mkha' la mdud pa dor //
NK070(thu)001:2191: bshad h+aum am pa'i rgyu rkyen gyis rnam rtog bdag
NK070(thu)001:2192: tu 'dzin pa'i 'khrul 'bras bu de dag tu 0snang
NK070(thu)001:2193: ba ni / dper na thang phrom gyi 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:2194: zos pa'i mi nan brtags kyis nam mkha' la skra
NK070(thu)001:2195: shad kyi gzugs sna tshogs mthong nas /
NK070(thu)001:2197: mdud pa byas pa ste dor ba lta bu'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2198: bdag 'dzin gshis la ma grub pas bcings pa med
NK070(thu)001:2199: de de las rnam par grol ba po yang med
NK070(thu)001:2201: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi lung las /
NK070(thu)001:2202: bcings ka par bya ba'i yul bcings kha par byed pa'i bcings pa po //
NK070(thu)001:2204: bdag tu 'dzin pa khams gsum sems can sdug bsngal
NK070(thu)001:2205: du snang ba'i dngos dang po thams cad rang gi
NK070(thu)001:2207: 'chings byed bdag tu 'dzin zhes bya'i ming yang med //
NK070(thu)001:2208: rgyu mtshan des na sems can dang sdug bsngal gnyis po'ang med pa las //
NK070(thu)001:2209: bcings pa las grol ba 'das pa po yang yod pa ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:2213: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK070(thu)001:2215: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas rang rig
NK070(thu)001:2216: pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis rdzogs shing bdal pa
NK070(thu)001:2217: ni / bdag 'dzin sems can sdug bsngal la sogs
NK070(thu)001:2218: pa rang bzhin gyis stong pa nyid sku dang ye
NK070(thu)001:2219: shes su gsal bar rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK070(thu)001:2220: thugs su chud pa dang 'i dgongs pa /
NK070(thu)001:2221: ye ci bzhin pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2223: don de nges ka par mtshon pa'i phyir lam gsang
NK070(thu)001:2224: ba'i snying po 'di nyid bshad cing bstan par bya
NK070(thu)001:2225: ba'i phyir spro ba dgyes pa'i tshul drug ga mdzad
NK070(thu)001:2226: pa dang de zhal 'dzum pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2230: phyag brkyang ba 'od dang sprul pa 'gyed /
NK070(thu)001:2231: lam 'di'i lam stegs kyi theg pa nges 'byung bzhi phyi rgyud gsum /
NK070(thu)001:2232: nang pa'i rgyud gzhan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2233: sprul kha pa thub pa drug la sogs par sku
NK070(thu)001:2234: sna tshogs spros ga pas gdul bya'i don mdzad pa
NK070(thu)001:2235: bstan ka phyir spro kha ba sna ga tshogs mdzad
NK070(thu)001:2237: de pa nyid de pa nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK070(thu)001:2239: lhan cig pa'i 'khor dbang rdzogs pa ril ston pa drug pa nyid du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2240: ston pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:2241: de ba nyid la go phye ba'i 'khor gyis ched
NK070(thu)001:2242: du gleng ngo // don ka dam 1pa dang kun
NK070(thu)001:2243: rdzob kha byang chub kyi 11sems ye shes bskyed pa
NK070(thu)001:2244: du gleng ngo // / zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2245: dang po la gsum pas mtshan nyid ni /
NK070(thu)001:2246: rang gis ngo bo dus thams cad du yang chos
NK070(thu)001:2247: nyid du chos can mi phyed pa'i don dam pa
NK070(thu)001:2248: ste / dbye ba ni gnas skabs kyi rtogs bya rang bzhin dang gyi dbyings /
NK070(thu)001:2249: rtogs pa'i ngos nas gsang bas ye shes 1dang de
NK070(thu)001:2250: la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ni
NK070(thu)001:2253: gsum po de dag mtshon tshul ma 'dres par gsal
NK070(thu)001:2254: bas byed la tha dad kyang don gyis ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:2255: nyid gcig pa'o // de bskyed pa'i thabs de nyid
NK070(thu)001:2256: gong gi thabs lam gyi sems lnga'i rim pa phyin
NK070(thu)001:2257: ci ma log pa las don ye shes su snang
NK070(thu)001:2258: bas bskyed la gnyis pa'i mtshan nyid ni gdul bya'i
NK070(thu)001:2259: dbang gis ston 'khor tha dad du snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:2260: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems bskyed thabs ste rgyu
NK070(thu)001:2261: rkyen ston pa thugs rje skyes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2262: gdul bya las dag pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2263: don la ltos pas snang ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:2264: de gnyis tshar gyi ngo bo gleng bslang gnyis su bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:2265: le'u gnyis pa mdor bkrol ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:2267: // de nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa tha dad 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2268: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:2269: rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi gnyis kyi bar du
NK070(thu)001:2270: gleng bslang gis chod pa dum bur gyur kyang bstan
NK070(thu)001:2271: pa 'byung ba'i rim pa ma nor ba ste 'brel
NK070(thu)001:2272: pa yod kho na'i phyir 'brel pa spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK070(thu)001:2273: med na mi 'byung ba rag las pas gnyis brtsir
NK070(thu)001:2274: mi rung ngo // de nas zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:2276: zhi khro dang rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can gyi phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2277: de bzhin gshegs pa ril thams cad du'ang 'gal ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:2278: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK070(thu)001:2279: zhes bya ba zhes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2280: spros pa dang bral bas thugs rang byung gi ye
NK070(thu)001:2281: shes chen po ni dngos po ril las khyab pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2282: phyir rje chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:2283: su lhun gyis grub pa'i byin de nyid kyis brlabs
NK070(thu)001:2284: pa gdul bya'i snang bas la cir yang ma 'gag
NK070(thu)001:2285: par rang snang pas de ka la don de tshig
NK070(thu)001:2286: skad ces bya'o // rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK070(thu)001:2288: gzhan gsang 'dus kyi le'u tha ma las rig pa'i skyes bu ci ltar lags kyi len /
NK070(thu)001:2289: dag las thub pa rang gi lus ngag yid gsum kun tu bzang po'i rdo rje /
NK070(thu)001:2290: gsum dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i ngo bo ste /
NK070(thu)001:2291: de ltar rig pa dang bcas par ldan pa ni //
NK070(thu)001:2292: rig pa'i skyes bu zhes su brjod //
NK070(thu)001:2295: thub pa de dag kyang sku thub pa stag dang
NK070(thu)001:2296: spre'u lta bu la sogs pa ltar don du mi
NK070(thu)001:2297: 'gyur ba'i bya ba mi mdzad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2298: gsung thub ste ca co spangs pa dang thugs thub
NK070(thu)001:2299: ste mnyam par ma bzhag pa mi mnga' ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:2300: thub pa ste / phrin las las kyi bdud bzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:2301: dpung bcom pa dag kyang mi 'dod pa ma yin
NK070(thu)001:2302: thub pa ste / no // drug gi grangs ni
NK070(thu)001:2303: gdul bya'i 'gro ba drug gi ngo bo nges pa
NK070(thu)001:2305: sprul pa de dag 'byung ba'i gzhi gang las byung snyam pa las /
NK070(thu)001:2306: de pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon te /
NK070(thu)001:2308: le'u dang po nyi zla'i 'grel par rang rig pa
NK070(thu)001:2309: cir yang ma skyes pa nyid kun du snang bas
NK070(thu)001:2310: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2312: le'u bzhi par thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin byang
NK070(thu)001:2313: chub sems tshang rgyu 'khor lo zhes gsungs pas snga
NK070(thu)001:2314: bla med kyi lugs kyis thabs yab dang shes rab
NK070(thu)001:2315: yum gnyis su med pa'i thig le byang chub sems
NK070(thu)001:2316: ni / sprul pa 'byung ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyur gsungs /
NK070(thu)001:2317: de yang de ba sprul pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer med kyi rdo rje las /
NK070(thu)001:2318: ma g.yos par thub drug bkod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2319: zla ba gcig las ma g.yos pa de dang chu zla du ma 'char ba lta bu'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2320: 'thon to zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:2321: thub pa de dag gnas gang du don ci mdzad snyams pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2322: 'then nas kyang las kyi dbang gis snel gzhi dang
NK070(thu)001:2323: yas man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK070(thu)001:2324: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK070(thu)001:2325: rer / thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res /
NK070(thu)001:2327: thub pa drug 'thon pa las kyi ldog pa mi mthun pas 'i dbang gi snang ba'i gnas /
NK070(thu)001:2329: steng 'og yan man gyis ris 'beb lugs so sor drug tu snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2331: de yang rgyal ba drug pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku chen po'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2332: de'i zhing gi khams gsum phyogs mtha' mu med pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2333: sprul pa'i sku zhing nges pa ni gdul bya'i ris
NK070(thu)001:2334: drug po snang bas dbang gi stong gsum gyi stong
NK070(thu)001:2335: chen po re rer thub pa chen po re res
NK070(thu)001:2336: thun mong gis thub drug dang mdzad pa mthun par
NK070(thu)001:2337: bkod de / sprul pa'i sku ril yang drug pa
NK070(thu)001:2338: bdag gi ngo bo las ma 'das pa rgya ma
NK070(thu)001:2339: bkod de / chad do // zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2340: 'dul ba rnam bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad de /
NK070(thu)001:2342: 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis grangs ni dkyus las gsal te /
NK070(thu)001:2343: 'gro ba lnga ni lha dang lha min gcig tu bsdus pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2346: de la dang po skus 'dul ba bstan pa'i phyir bltams pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2348: sogs pa ra ston pa'i thub pa mthar phyin pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2349: drang don mdo sde ba pas 'i gzhung la /
NK070(thu)001:2350: rgyud mas sbyangs pa dam pa tog dkar zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:2351: ba skye ba gcig gis thog pa'i byang chub sems
NK070(thu)001:2352: dpa' dga' ldan gyi gnas nas mi yul du 'bab
NK070(thu)001:2353: par zer ba ni kho rang gi don bden mod
NK070(thu)001:2354: kyis nges don du lhan cig pa'i 'khor byang chub
NK070(thu)001:2355: sems dpa' rnams kyis zab mo'i dbang gsum thob pas
NK070(thu)001:2356: rang don du sangs rgyas te mdzad pa mthar phyin
NK070(thu)001:2357: pa'i phyir / de'i sprul pa'i mdzad par 'gal ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:2358: ci'i phyir zhe na le'u glad nas byung khungs smos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2359: rgyud mas sbyangs kyi mdo sde pa dang mthun par
NK070(thu)001:2360: bstan pa'i phyir yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa dang
NK070(thu)001:2361: / bshang ba mi gtsang ba'i gnas spangs pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:2362: lum pa'i tshal du mchan khung g.yon nas bltams pa
NK070(thu)001:2363: dang rgyal bus rol rtsed mdzad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2364: sa mtsho ma sogs khab bzhes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2365: rab tu byung ba la sogs gzhan go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:2366: bsdu ba ni gyad yul du spur sbyangs te sku gdung cha brgyad du bgos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2367: gnyis pa thugs kyis 'dul ba gang yin snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2368: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2369: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:2370: sngon gyi gnas la sogs pa 'i dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2371: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyu kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2373: pha rol gzhan thams cad gyi sems kyi rgyud la nyon mongs pa che chung dang /
NK070(thu)001:2374: rnam par rtog pa'i ril thams cad rig pa bdag
NK070(thu)001:2375: nyid chen po las mi gzhan pa'i phyir kun tu
NK070(thu)001:2376: mkhyen pa'o // rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan dang snyan zhes
NK070(thu)001:2377: bya ba ni lha'i mig gis gzugs thams cad nye
NK070(thu)001:2378: ring med par kun tu gzigs pa dang rna bas
NK070(thu)001:2379: sgra thams cad nye ring med par kun tu gsan
NK070(thu)001:2381: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho ga ni rdzu 'phrul gyi cho gas bya ba shes pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2385: chus mi gsher lus mi snang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2388: sa la 'dzul ba ste mi mthun pa brgyad la
NK070(thu)001:2389: sogs pa dus gnas kun tu sems can gyi don
NK070(thu)001:2391: zag pa med pa kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa rdzogs pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2392: lnga po de dag 'jig rten pa la yang yod
NK070(thu)001:2393: pa ni bdag tu 'dzin pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:2394: la / 'dir shes bya thams cad kyang gsal 1la bdag 2nyid kyi phyir chen por rtogs pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:2395: dpe na gsal dus mi 2'dzin pas zag pa med pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2396: ma spangs la bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2397: thams cad zag pa med par kun tu bzang po'i
NK070(thu)001:2398: spyod pa rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po
NK070(thu)001:2399: / gsum pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas nyon mongs 'dul ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2400: kun 1tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2401: kun 1tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2402: kun 1tu zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2403: kun 1tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2404: dngul ba'i dus 1111dang gnas skabs kun tu gdul byas
NK070(thu)001:2405: dag ma dag gang la snga bkol bar de dag
NK070(thu)001:2406: gi ngo la zhi ba dang khro bo la sogs
NK070(thu)001:2407: pa'am sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2408: thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2409: gsung gis bstan pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa /
NK070(thu)001:2410: phra man la sogs pa'i zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2411: gsung gis bstan pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa /
NK070(thu)001:2412: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos po dang /
NK070(thu)001:2413: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa 1phyogs gcig pa gang 11du'ang ma nges te /
NK070(thu)001:2414: gdul bya'i snang ngo la thams cad du snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:2415: gzhan sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dag las /
NK070(thu)001:2416: dus res 'ga' zhi la res 'ga' drag /
NK070(thu)001:2417: res 'ga' gdon chen bgegs mdzad de /
NK070(thu)001:2418: de la sogs pa grangs mtha' yas mchog ri dang skye bo thams cad do //
NK070(thu)001:2420: grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:2422: gdul bya'i las dag pa blo dang mthun par grangs med par snang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2423: ston pa lhun gyis grub par rol pa mdzad pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2424: sgo mi 'gag par snang ba kho na'i phyir phyogs
NK070(thu)001:2426: de dag la yang sprul du zhes zer ba na kha gom pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2427: bzhi pa gsung gis 'dul ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2429: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i /
NK070(thu)001:2433: bla na med pa'i theg pa /
NK070(thu)001:2434: zhes bya ba nas mar go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:2435: theg pa lnga po de dag gi dgos ched ci grangs spros na du yod snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2436: ma rig pa rnam par kha rtog pa nyon ka
NK070(thu)001:2437: mongs pa stong phrag ga brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen
NK070(thu)001:2438: por chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so
NK070(thu)001:2442: rtsa ba lhan skyes kun brtags ma rig pa gnyis las gyur pa'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2444: rtog pa stong phrag brgyad bcu rtsa bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:2445: de dag gi rtsa ba ni dug gsum dang bdag tu ngar bar bzung ba las nga rgyal dang /
NK070(thu)001:2446: gzhan la phrag dog pa'i phyir de gnyis gcig tu bsdu bas gcig ste spyir /
NK070(thu)001:2447: bzhi la nang ris su gcig zhe sdang lta bu
NK070(thu)001:2448: kyang nyi khri gcig stong ste spyir brgyad khri bzhi
NK070(thu)001:2449: stong nyon mongs pa de dag la lam gang dag
NK070(thu)001:2450: gis dag par 'gyur bar byed pa ni gnyen po
NK070(thu)001:2451: ste / de yang lha mi nyan rang gi spong ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2452: byang sems kyi sbyong ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2453: sngags kyis dbang 1du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2454: de bas na 111chos ni stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi pa rang phrag gsum du snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:2455: de ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi mdzad
NK070(thu)001:2456: pa mthun par bstan pa dam chos rnams gsungs so
NK070(thu)001:2460: gnyen po gsum po ci lta bu snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2461: de dag thams cad kyang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2462: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba dang
NK070(thu)001:2464: las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2466: chos kyi sgo mo de dag thams cad kyang nyon
NK070(thu)001:2467: mongs pa'i gnyen por gyur tshul ni las dge ba
NK070(thu)001:2468: dang mi dge ba'i las kyi 'bras bu chud mi
NK070(thu)001:2469: za bas na dge ba bcus spyad pa mi dang
NK070(thu)001:2470: lhar nges par 'byung bas na mi dge ba bcu
NK070(thu)001:2472: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa grub tshul ni rdul phran
NK070(thu)001:2473: lus pa las spyod yul du nges par yod pas
NK070(thu)001:2474: na rag par 'dzin pa 'gog pas gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2475: ka yang rag pa spangs pa'i nyes dang /
NK070(thu)001:2476: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel 'byung ba nges par 'byung ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2477: lugs las 'byung bas gzhan na gnas lugs la bzlog pa he dus /
NK070(thu)001:2478: phra rag phyogs gnyis sam khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa 'gog pas spangs pa'i rang rgyal dang /
NK070(thu)001:2479: gsum po de dag ni spong pa'i gnyen por gcig go //
NK070(thu)001:2482: nang 'dzin pa'i sems 'khrul pa'i brtag pa snang ba
NK070(thu)001:2483: la yul du 'dogs pa las gud du yul med
NK070(thu)001:2484: pa'i phyir / shes pa yang ma grub pas yul
NK070(thu)001:2485: sems phan tshun ma skyes par shes na nyon mongs
NK070(thu)001:2486: pa chos nyid stong pa nyid du rgyud sbyang ba
NK070(thu)001:2487: pa'i phyir / dang / las kyis kun nas nyon
NK070(thu)001:2488: mongs pa dang las kyi skye ba'i kun nas nyon
NK070(thu)001:2492: rnams rang gi sems nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir kri ya ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2493: yo gas sems byin rlabs rigs lnga'i lhar snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:2494: dang kri yas brtags pa'i yon tan rigs gsum gyi
NK070(thu)001:2495: ltar snang ba dus na spang bya nyon mongs med
NK070(thu)001:2496: pa dang / tha mal pa'i zhan pa dag pas kri ya dang yo ga ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2498: gos su med pa ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK070(thu)001:2500: bdag nyid kyi sems kyi phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2501: nyon mongs pa rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyi ngo bo ye shes su shes na /
NK070(thu)001:2503: spang bya mi 'thun pa nyon mongs dang gnyen po ye shes ni dbyer med de /
NK070(thu)001:2504: nyon mongs pa la spyad pa nyid gos su med
NK070(thu)001:2505: par slar yon tan du snang bar ston ba'i thabs
NK070(thu)001:2506: kyi theg pa ni rgyu 'bras su snang ba dang
NK070(thu)001:2507: bral ba sa dgongs pa'i mthar thug kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2509: theg pa lnga po de dag byung ba'i dgos pa
NK070(thu)001:2510: ni sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang gsang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:2511: snying po'i ra 'gro ba lam stegs la yongs su
NK070(thu)001:2512: sbyongs ba'i phyir dang rgyud 'di ni byin gyis rlabs
NK070(thu)001:2514: 'dul ba mdor zhes drangs de yan chad du rgyud kyi rgyu rkyen gleng gzhi dang /
NK070(thu)001:2516: gsum pa'i yongs su shes par bya ba /
NK070(thu)001:2517: rgyud don la bdun gyi dang po lta ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2519: des thams cad kyis ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:2520: la sogs pa gsungs te go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:2521: ci kha snyed ka 'jig rten 'khrul ga pa'i chos //
NK070(thu)001:2523: 'di nas mar gzhal bya 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i rgyu rkyen ngo bo gsum ston te /
NK070(thu)001:2524: phyi snod 'jig pa la bcud stong pa grangs mtha'
NK070(thu)001:2525: yas pa'i ci snyed kyi ris su snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:2526: / blo 'khrul pa'i chos kho na snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2527: de'i rgyu ci yin snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2528: ma kariga rtog khapa'i gzung ga'adzina gyis //
NK070(thu)001:2530: sems nyid rang bzhin gyi mthas ma bsgrib par 'od
NK070(thu)001:2531: gsal ba yin kyang nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes
NK070(thu)001:2532: te ma rtogs pa ni rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2534: kha des chos dang gang zag la bdag tu rtogs pa'i na nga ru bltas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2536: kun bslang nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK070(thu)001:2537: ga yul dang 'jig pa'i sems kyis gzhan du snang ba ni rkyen kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2538: tshul phyi nang rten 'brel gnyis su 'khor //
NK070(thu)001:2539: nyes pa mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:2541: rkyen des na phyi nang snod bcud thams cad rten
NK070(thu)001:2542: 'brel bcu gnyis kyi tshul du dngos su 'khor zhing
NK070(thu)001:2543: snang bas tshe 'dir mi mthun bde sdug sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:2544: / 'byung zhing snang nas myong bar 'gyur ba ni 'bras bu kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2545: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK070(thu)001:2547: 'khrul pa chos nyid du shes nas spangs bya 'khrul pa mi dmigs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2549: rang bzhin gyis snang ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:2550: 'khrul pa'i chos de dag gi rang bzhin chos nyid ni /
NK070(thu)001:2552: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kho na las 'gyur zhing nyams ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:2554: don de he dus nges par mtshon par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2555: yang ka dag sgyu khama'i tshul gnyis su //
NK070(thu)001:2556: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:2557: don dam yang dag sgyu ma'i kun rdzob ni nges par bden pa gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:2558: tshul ni don gyi rjes su 'jug pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2559: mdo sde pa 'i theg pa ltar bden pa gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2560: su phye na sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa
NK070(thu)001:2561: / bden pa gnyis la yang dag brtan /
NK070(thu)001:2563: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan med de //
NK070(thu)001:2566: 1ma rig pa'i ra 'dzin pa rnam shes tshogs brgyad /
NK070(thu)001:2567: bdag gis 1myong ba'i phung po dang /
NK070(thu)001:2568: gzhan 'byung ba 1yul sna tshogs pa de dag med
NK070(thu)001:2569: cing ma grub ste ci ltar ma grub zhe na
NK070(thu)001:2570: sems nyid chos gsum du snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:2572: gzhan du ma grub skye sa pa ni don 0dam pa'i tshul lo //
NK070(thu)001:2573: chos gsum po de dag kha sems nyid kyis phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2574: ngo bo ye shes rang snang bas ched du /
NK070(thu)001:2575: ma bkag pa ni sgyu ma kun 0rdzob kyi tshul te /
NK070(thu)001:2576: de 00gnyis su med pa la gsum pa /
NK070(thu)001:2577: de dag ma grub pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2578: de ni bsdus don lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:2579: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go //
NK070(thu)001:2581: dbyer med pas bsdus don mnyam pa ste bshad pa ltar shes nas bden pa gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:2582: de la'ang mi gnas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2583: snang stong ngam yod med kyi mtha' gnyis rnam par
NK070(thu)001:2584: dag pas chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa'i dbyings gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2585: las 'dir snang stong ngo bo mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK070(thu)001:2587: snang ba kun rdzob stong pa don dam gnyis su med pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2588: bden pa gnyis tshul don gcig pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2590: bden pa dbyer med la bden pa gnyis kyi dbye
NK070(thu)001:2591: ba tsam du yang ma grub pa log rtog gsum
NK070(thu)001:2592: ni shin tu yang ma grub na /
NK070(thu)001:2593: 'o na gzhal bya 'khrul pa'i snang ba med do snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2595: log par rtog pa tsam nyid las //
NK070(thu)001:2596: phra zhing zab pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:2599: sems nyid las mi gzhan te ma g.yos bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:2600: ngo shes pas log par rtog pa'i dngos po tsam
NK070(thu)001:2601: nyid du rang rgyud par 'dzin pa dag kyi ris
NK070(thu)001:2602: su rang gzhan gyi snang ni 'khrul pa'i snang ba'o
NK070(thu)001:2604: de las gzhan pa ni rdzas su grub pa rdul phra rab tsam dang /
NK070(thu)001:2605: rang rgyud kyi shes pa zab pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2606: skad cig mar gzung ba med 'ang yod pa ma yin te ngos bzung pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2607: ngang gis med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2608: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod de //
NK070(thu)001:2609: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med //
NK070(thu)001:2611: snang bdo ba dang spyod bdo ba 'di ni ci
NK070(thu)001:2612: zhe na log par rtog pa'i mthu brtas pas log
NK070(thu)001:2613: rtog gi snga ma nyid la phyi mas nyid kyi
NK070(thu)001:2615: sems nyid las gzhan du g.yo ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:2616: chos gsum gyi ris su 'gyur ba ci yang med do zhes gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:2617: des na dngos po ma grub kyang /
NK070(thu)001:2618: log rtog 'khrul snang tsam rang ni nges par bden par yod do snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:2619: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyu nyid kyang //
NK070(thu)001:2620: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK070(thu)001:2622: bsdus don rgyu gcig par rtogs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2623: log rtog gi rgyu ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa bdag dang /
NK070(thu)001:2624: 'bras bu phung po lnga gzhan yul lta bu /
NK070(thu)001:2625: zhen pa sna tshogs snang ba yang /
NK070(thu)001:2626: skad cig ma'i rgyun nyid kyang ma grub pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:2627: bshad pa gsum gyis rjes su ma grub par mthun
NK070(thu)001:2628: te / ci ltar ma grub ce na /
NK070(thu)001:2629: ye phyi mo nas de gnyis kyi rang 11gi ngo bo ma grub ste /
NK070(thu)001:2631: sems nyid kho na'i phyir sems ni snang stong gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2632: su mi phyed pa ni bshad pa'i mnyam pa'i dbyings
NK070(thu)001:2633: so // de log rtog gi skad cig gis skad
NK070(thu)001:2634: cig ma'i rgyun ma grub par 0gong gi gnyis so
NK070(thu)001:2635: so // // ril thams cad sems nyid du gcig pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2636: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK070(thu)001:2637: nyid la dbang bsgyur nyid spyod phyir //
NK070(thu)001:2638: zhes pa 'di nas mar yig 'bru'i tshul dang dag pa gsum ston te /
NK070(thu)001:2639: gong gi bshad 0pa ltar log rtog gi rgyun rnam par dag ste /
NK070(thu)001:2640: rang gis ngo bo sems su 'od gsal bas sems
NK070(thu)001:2641: ma skyes pa'i dbyings de nyid mtshon phyir a lta
NK070(thu)001:2643: skad cig ma'i rgyun med par rang rig nyid rtsal cir yang mi 'gag par snang ba la ni /
NK070(thu)001:2644: ma bcos pa'i skad cig ma ste /
NK070(thu)001:2645: ye shes rang snang zhing dbang bsgyur bas nyid la spyod pa /
NK070(thu)001:2646: kho na'i phyir yul snang zhing blos spyod kyang yul
NK070(thu)001:2647: sems gnyis su spyad par bya ba dang spyod byed
NK070(thu)001:2648: med pa ni / theg pa chen po'i mah+aa gtan tshigs so //
NK070(thu)001:2649: ma skyes pa de nyid g+ha god ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:2650: rang gsal bas a la na ro rgyan snang ba
NK070(thu)001:2651: lta bu'o // bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK070(thu)001:2652: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK070(thu)001:2654: gong du gsum po bshad pa'i byin brlabs kyis bdag phung kapo dang lnga /
NK070(thu)001:2656: rtog pas gabslad pa'i rgyun rnam par shes pa gsum po /
NK070(thu)001:2657: so sor snang ba ngang gis rnam par dag ste
NK070(thu)001:2658: snang stong ngam lha rtog gnyis su med par gsal
NK070(thu)001:2659: ba ni / rtags rigs kalnga yab yum khadang /
NK070(thu)001:2660: ye shes galngar gdod nas lhun h+aum gyis grub pas ye nas yod pa de mngon du rtogs /
NK070(thu)001:2661: de las 'bras bu bla med rdo 1rje theg pa'i mchog zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2662: de ni yi ge rdzogs pa lta bu ste /
NK070(thu)001:2664: dag pa gsum du yang 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:2666: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas //
NK070(thu)001:2668: gong du bshad pa nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi
NK070(thu)001:2669: pa bzhin rang rang gi gzhung ltar ma nor bar
NK070(thu)001:2670: spyod na lha mi ngan song dang gsum nyan rang
NK070(thu)001:2671: 'khor ba dang byang sems mtha' gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:2674: 'das ma thag par ston pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2675: bla med pa'i theg pa bsgrub bya'i don mthar thug
NK070(thu)001:2676: par byed pa'i phyir 'bras bur gnas pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:2677: // yang dag rtogs pas rab brtag na //
NK070(thu)001:2678: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:2681: 'bras bur rang bzhin don dam pa mngon sum mngon
NK070(thu)001:2682: sum du rtogs par byas pa'i blo'i shes rab can
NK070(thu)001:2683: gyis rab tu brtag pa'i dus /
NK070(thu)001:2684: la blo'i spyod yul dang bral bar rang rgyud du
NK070(thu)001:2685: mi snang bas na rang bzhin cir yang med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2686: las cir yang snang ba phyir thabs zhags las yul
NK070(thu)001:2687: du mthong ba med pa'i tshul gyis rang gsal bas
NK070(thu)001:2688: mthong ba dang / zhes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:2689: rgyas las yul du zhen pa'i rnam par rtog h'u
NK070(thu)001:2690: pa mi mnga' bar gnyis su rang gsal bas cir
NK070(thu)001:2693: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK070(thu)001:2694: zhes pa'i la sogs pa tshigs bcad gcig gi don ni /
NK070(thu)001:2695: bshad pa ltar sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub pa la ston pa sangs rgyas dang po /
NK070(thu)001:2696: 'byung dang mthar 'jig nas mya ngan la yongs mi 'da' ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:2697: bstan pa dam chos kyang dar ba dang nub par
NK070(thu)001:2698: mi 'gyur bas na de dag med de ye nas
NK070(thu)001:2699: ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2700: mtshan ma bzhir snang ba na lhun grub ma rig
NK070(thu)001:2701: nas blo dman pa'i gdul bya rnams kyi rgyud smin
NK070(thu)001:2702: par mdzad nas 'dul ba'i thabs la rtag 'dzin sun
NK070(thu)001:2703: dbyung la sogs mdzad pa'i phyir te sangs rgyas 'jig
NK070(thu)001:2704: rten du dang po 'byung nas mthar mya ngan la
NK070(thu)001:2705: 'das bar ston / de ni 1gdul bya'i snang ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2709: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK070(thu)001:2710: zhes pa la sogs pa ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:2711: rgyu 'di'i gsang ba'i snying po rgyu rkyen tshang ba'i byin rlabs las /
NK070(thu)001:2712: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon gyi sde snod gsum
NK070(thu)001:2713: dang dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa ste sngags phyi
NK070(thu)001:2714: pa gsum dang / sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi
NK070(thu)001:2715: rgyud rnams kyi ston pa thub pa drug dang bsam
NK070(thu)001:2716: gyis mi khyab pa'i 'dul ba'i ston pa rnams 'thon
NK070(thu)001:2717: nas bstan pa phyogs bcu kun tu rab tu grags
NK070(thu)001:2718: pa thams cad rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di
NK070(thu)001:2719: las 'phros pa ste lam thun mong bshad pa dang
NK070(thu)001:2720: gsang ba'i snying po 'og min du bshad pa gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2721: pa gsum dang / / dus mnyam du gsung zhing /
NK070(thu)001:2722: de'i phyir rang bzhin gsang ba'i zhes pa nas gtan la bstan /
NK070(thu)001:2723: ston ming tshig la dngos po nges par 'bebs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:2725: de ltar theg pa dgu po de dag grangs dang ngo bo ngos so snyam pa las /
NK070(thu)001:2726: chos rnams ming du btags pa tsam //
NK070(thu)001:2727: ston pas don dang mthun phyogs su //
NK070(thu)001:2728: ming dang tshig tu btags nas bstan //
NK070(thu)001:2729: ston ming tshig la dngos po med //
NK070(thu)001:2731: chos rnams thams cad rang bzhin gyi ngo bos stong
NK070(thu)001:2732: pa'i phyir 'khrul pa dang gdul bya'i snang ba gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2733: kho na'i ngo bor ming du btags pa tsam mo
NK070(thu)001:2734: // de ltar ngo bo ma grub pa'i rjes su
NK070(thu)001:2735: rang rang gi ston pas theg pa rim dgu so
NK070(thu)001:2736: so'i lta spyod bsgrub pa dbang dkyil 'khor la sogs
NK070(thu)001:2737: pa ril yang gdul bya'i ngo bo ra don dang
NK070(thu)001:2738: // / mthun phyogs su ming dang tshig tu brtags nas bstan pa tsam ste /
NK070(thu)001:2740: rang gi ngo bo nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:2741: bstan pa'i ming dang tshig gi rnam grangs la ni
NK070(thu)001:2742: rang rgyud can du grub pa dang nges pa'i dngos
NK070(thu)001:2743: po med do zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2744: de dag kyang gdul bya'i snang bas thabs grol gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:2746: rgyu nyi zla'i thig le gsal stong zung 'jug gi bde ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:2747: sems lnga'i mtha' ma 'ongs pa'i ldog pas byang sems rtsa gnas su /
NK070(thu)001:2749: zhes pa ni de nas nges zhes pa nas rdo rje mas 'thon to zhes pa'i bar gyi don /
NK070(thu)001:2750: lus gnas rtsa'i dkyil 'khor rgyu bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:2751: rkyen gnyis dang drug gi rigs drug gi zhing khams yul rnams su //
NK070(thu)001:2753: stong chen re re zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2754: ston pa sprul pa'i thig le drug rtsa gnas su rang shar ba'i //
NK070(thu)001:2755: don ni thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re re ston pa thig le sku /
NK070(thu)001:2757: bde ba thugs snang ba'i mdzad pa bsam mi khyab //
NK070(thu)001:2758: pa ni 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis /
NK070(thu)001:2762: 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa lnga'am drug dang las gnyis kyi rtog pa'i ril //
NK070(thu)001:2763: 'khor thams cad ston pa yab yum bde stong gnyis
NK070(thu)001:2764: med kyi ye shes kyis 'dul ba'i phyir sprul pa'am
NK070(thu)001:2766: pa ni 'dul ba zhes nas snang bar 'gyur ro zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2767: sgra yig dang dbyangs yig gsung gis yi ge bstan pa rnams //
NK070(thu)001:2768: rtsa 'khor bzhis nges par gsung du grags pa kho na nyid //
NK070(thu)001:2769: de thams cad ces pa nas mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2770: gzhal yas phung po lnga la sogs pa'i khams skye
NK070(thu)001:2771: mched kyi rtog pa'i tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i 'jig
NK070(thu)001:2772: rten kun // ni ci snyed ces nas nyams pa med ces pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2773: log rtog sgyu ma'i ngo bo snang tsam las //
NK070(thu)001:2774: ma grub pa rang gzhan gyi gtan tshigs te /
NK070(thu)001:2775: nyi ma don dam zla ba kun rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis kyi he du'i las nyid kyis //
NK070(thu)001:2776: don ni yang dag ces nas tshul gcig go'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2777: chags rtog rang rgyud du ma skyes zhing gnyis med mnyam pa'i dbyings las gnas par gyur cing //
NK070(thu)001:2778: ni bdag dang bdag gi zhes pa nas nyid spyod phyir gyi bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2779: de'i dus su phung po lnga la sogs pa'i 'byung
NK070(thu)001:2780: ba rnam shes rnams lha'i rigs lnga la yab yum
NK070(thu)001:2782: gsal ba ni dag pa gsum ste bdag dang zhes nas theg pa'i mchog gi bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2783: bde ba'i ye shes su yul med du /
NK070(thu)001:2784: rang snang bas mngon gsum bzhi las rang rig pa'i mngon sum gsal //
NK070(thu)001:2785: ba ni yang dag ces nas cir yang 'grub kyis bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2786: gzhi lam 'bras bu dus gsum du'ang mi 'gyur ba'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:2787: ni sangs rgyas zhes nas 'da' bar ston gyi bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2788: de lta bu'i theg pa 'di thabs kyis theg pa dang rdo rjer theg par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:2789: do ni 'dul ba zhes pa nas dngos med ces pa'i bar ro //
NK070(thu)001:2791: de nas de pa thams cad ces pa la sogs
NK070(thu)001:2792: pa ni rjes su le'u dang po dang mthun no
NK070(thu)001:2793: // a ho zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2794: le'u stod du bshad pa'i 'khor 'das kyis dngos po
NK070(thu)001:2795: gnyis mnyam rtogs dag pa'i gtan tshig gsum gyi ngo
NK070(thu)001:2796: bo chos nyid du gcig par bsgrub pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:2797: // srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK070(thu)001:2798: rgyu drug skye 'gag lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK070(thu)001:2799: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK070(thu)001:2800: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK070(thu)001:2802: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs ni gong du 'khrul skabs su
NK070(thu)001:2803: bshad pa'i lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i bdag
NK070(thu)001:2804: dang du rtog pa de las nyon mongs pa la
NK070(thu)001:2805: sogs pa rang 'phros nas snang ba'i 'gro ba rgyu
NK070(thu)001:2806: drug gi spyod yul ril thams cad skye 'gag lus
NK070(thu)001:2808: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor sogs pa rnams /
NK070(thu)001:2809: rang rgyud du lta ba'i log rtog gi rgyun nyid
NK070(thu)001:2810: las gzhan du ci yang med pa kho na'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:2811: 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni gzhal bu zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:2812: kho na'o // stong nyid bdag med rang rig ye mkhyen thugs //
NK070(thu)001:2813: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang bsgyur //
NK070(thu)001:2814: ngo mtshar sku gsum yon tan zhing khams las //
NK070(thu)001:2815: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK070(thu)001:2817: gzhal bya 'das ma thag pa nyid gsang sngags kyi
NK070(thu)001:2818: mnyam pa rtog pa dag pa'i gtan tshig gsum pos
NK070(thu)001:2820: chos nyid stong pa nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:2821: bdag med par gtan la phab pa'i dus su bdag
NK070(thu)001:2822: dang bdag gi ba'i log rtog gi rgyun las 'das
NK070(thu)001:2823: te / 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i dbyings gnas lugs de
NK070(thu)001:2824: nyid ye shes su rang gsal bar rtogs pa ni
NK070(thu)001:2825: ya ki na yang dag sgyu ma zhes pa nas
NK070(thu)001:2826: 'bras bu rang gnas zhes pa'i bar sdud do //
NK070(thu)001:2827: gzhi'i ye shes nyid la lam gyi ye shes nyid spyod pas rang rig no /
NK070(thu)001:2830: dmigs byed ste shes byed kyi ye shes gnyis ngang gis med la pa'i don /
NK070(thu)001:2831: dran pa rang snang gi ye shes su dbang bsgyur ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2834: grub mtha' ste ya ki na yang dag rtogs pa
NK070(thu)001:2835: zhes pa nas tshig gcig la dngos med ces pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2836: bar sdud do // yon tan thams cad lhun gyis
NK070(thu)001:2837: grub pa'i ngo mtshar las rtags 'dul ba sku mdzad
NK070(thu)001:2838: bar sdud do // pa bcu gnyis / gsung theg pa sna tshogs /
