NK070(thu)001:2839: thugs kyi yon tan mngon shes /
NK070(thu)001:2840: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba /
NK070(thu)001:2841: bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa ril 'gro ba lnga'i zhing khams dang /
NK070(thu)001:2843: mdzad spyod du bcas par snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2845: rang rig pa de nyid la 'bras bu lhun gyis
NK070(thu)001:2846: grub pa'i rtsal de ltar du snang ba yin no
NK070(thu)001:2847: // de la ya ki na 'thon nas zhes pa
NK070(thu)001:2848: nas ston pa'i mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar sdud
NK070(thu)001:2849: // do // gnas skabs kyi ngo bo de ba'i
NK070(thu)001:2850: snang ba dang gdul bya'i snang ba gnyis kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:2851: // do // // le'u'i stod du thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:2852: smad du de 1pa thams cad kyi ngo bo kun
NK070(thu)001:2853: bzang gi gsungs pa yang bsdus tshigs de dag 11tu
NK070(thu)001:2854: 'dul pa 'khor gyis de pa nyid kyis mkhyen no
NK070(thu)001:2856: gong du 'das ma thag pa nyid du rgyas par bshad pas go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:2857: bsdu ba'i tshigs de dag le'u ston smad ril 'dus par go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:2858: ka chos thams cad gtan kha la phab pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2859: 'dul ba mdo sde la sogs pa theg ka pa
NK070(thu)001:2860: dgu'i chos ril thams cad gsang kha ba'i snying po'i
NK070(thu)001:2861: rgyu rkyen tshang ba'i byin brlabs kyis gtan la phab
NK070(thu)001:2862: pa la / le'u'i smad du 'khor 'das kyi dngos
NK070(thu)001:2863: po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i ril 'khrul pa dang gdul
NK070(thu)001:2864: bya'i snang kha ba gnyis las kyang 'das te /
NK070(thu)001:2865: rang bzhin gyi snang ba gcig kho nar gtan tshigs
NK070(thu)001:2866: snga ma gsum gyis gtan la phab pa zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:2867: kho na'o // le'u gsum pa bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2869: // de nas de pa thams cad 0dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas /
NK070(thu)001:2870: zhes bya ba ni 1drug pa'i debazhina gshegs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2871: dgongs pa gcig dang du mar bral ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2872: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad du'ang 'gal ba med de /
NK070(thu)001:2873: de nyid gsung lnga lhun gyis grub par rang snang ba las mi g.yo ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2874: dgongs pa ste gcig tu gyur nas zhes pa ni gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:2875: de nyid rgyas par bstan 0pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:2876: mnyam pa chen po'i tshul rdo rje'i dbyings chos thams
NK070(thu)001:2877: cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting nge 'dzin las
NK070(thu)001:2878: mi g.yo bar zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2879: snang stong gnyis su med pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:2881: bden pa gnyis kyi don ni don dam skye med
NK070(thu)001:2882: du dang kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa las ltos
NK070(thu)001:2883: pa ste / sa na chen po /
NK070(thu)001:2884: de'i tshul lam ngo bo nyid ni kun rdzob don
NK070(thu)001:2885: dam gyi dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos ril
NK070(thu)001:2886: sems nyid du dbyer mi phyed pas rdo rje /
NK070(thu)001:2888: chos thams cad ye gdod ma nas sku dang ye shes su gsal bar rang snang ba nyid /
NK070(thu)001:2889: drug pa'i sangs rgyas ngo bo ste /
NK070(thu)001:2890: bsgom bya sgom byed las 'das pas /
NK070(thu)001:2891: ting nge 'dzin lam mi g.yo bar zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2892: chos thams cad ming tsam du gnas pa'i yi ge phreng ba 'khor lo zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2893: phyi nang gi dngos po chos rnams thams cad ni
NK070(thu)001:2894: ngo bo nyid rang rgyud du med 1pa kho na'i
NK070(thu)001:2895: phyir / ming tsam h'u du gnas pa las 1de'i mtha' yi ge kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:2896: 'i phyir yi ge'i phreng ba'i rgyun ma chad pa nyid gsung gi dkyil 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:2897: sku la sogs pa'i thugs yon tan phrin las bzhi
NK070(thu)001:2898: yang lhun gyis grub pa'i rdo rje de'i gzhi las
NK070(thu)001:2900: phyung kha de dag ni 'di yin te /
NK070(thu)001:2901: a ka kha ga g+ha nga zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:2902: yi ge de dag sngon byung dus kaston pa'i thugs
NK070(thu)001:2903: rje rjes 'jug tu lam pa'i sems khanyid du rang
NK070(thu)001:2904: snang ba ni / 'byung ba'i gnas kadang sgras brjod pa'i kharkyen ni /
NK070(thu)001:2905: a ni lte bar gnas te /
NK070(thu)001:2906: khung nas 'byung la de'i 'od zer mgul du 'phros pas ka kha ga g+ha nga lnga /
NK070(thu)001:2907: dang ljags kyi dkyil dang du 'phros pas tsa tsha dza dz+ny+aa nya lnga /
NK070(thu)001:2908: lce'i rtse mo dang ra ta tha da d+ha na /
NK070(thu)001:2909: ta tha da d+ha na bcu /
NK070(thu)001:2910: zhal gyi sgros dang la pa pha ba b+ha ma lnga lus spyi la bsags te la byin pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:2911: smin ma wa sked par ra sta zur la sogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2924: de dag kyang 'dul bya'i snang bas gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:2926: sems rang snang ba sku'i 'am lus kyis 'khor lo bzhi pa las //
NK070(thu)001:2927: rgyu rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK070(thu)001:2928: thig le yi ge'i dbyibs su gnas pa a li ka li de /
NK070(thu)001:2929: sgra yig g.yas dang dbyangs yig g.yon gyis dbye ba yis //
NK070(thu)001:2930: a ka tsa ta pa ya ha'i sde tshan brgyad kyi yi ge dang byed pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:2932: kun la khyab par 'jug pa g+ho shad tig gsum yang de bzhin tu //
NK070(thu)001:2933: lus la rim par bkod par yi ge di sgra rang snang bas //
NK070(thu)001:2934: 'jig rten las 'das pa dang ma 'das pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:2936: ci ltar mos pa ltar ci snyed bsgyur ba'i sgra rnams 'byung //
NK070(thu)001:2937: yi ge zhe lnga nyid rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sku gsung thugs gsum dang rtsa lnga'i //
NK070(thu)001:2938: ngo bo nyid du'ang nges pa yin pas na //
NK070(thu)001:2939: yan lag gi lha khu ba byang sems kyi snod gzugs dag gi //
NK070(thu)001:2940: de pa'i sku gsung thugs gsum dang yon tan lngar //
NK070(thu)001:2941: snang ba'i 'bras bu gzhan nas ma brtsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:2943: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa rnams pa drug tu g.yos /
NK070(thu)001:2946: chos thams cad ming gi mtshan nyid tsam du gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:2947: zhes bya ba ni yi ge'i 'di dag phyungs pa
NK070(thu)001:2948: mthus cho 'phrul gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu
NK070(thu)001:2949: mtha' yas pa shar mtho na nub dma' ba la
NK070(thu)001:2950: sogs / rnam pa drug tu g.yos pa la sogs
NK070(thu)001:2951: snang la gong bu bshad h+aum pa bzhin 'khor 'das
NK070(thu)001:2952: kyi dngos po ril chos thams cad ming gi bye
NK070(thu)001:2953: brag dang yi ge kho na'i phyir de'i ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:2954: rang rgyud du bstan du med par ming gi mtshan
NK070(thu)001:2957: gzhan yang nang ltar 'og nas 'chad 00pa bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:2958: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo gsal bar gyur pa'i
NK070(thu)001:2959: dus su / lus kakyi phyogs bzhi steng 'og gi
NK070(thu)001:2960: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i dngos po'i ril bde
NK070(thu)001:2961: bar g.yo zhing des mtshon pa'i thig le rtog tshogs
NK070(thu)001:2962: kyi chos thams cad ming gi mtshan nyid kyis bsdus
NK070(thu)001:2963: pa tsam te lus sgyu mar mngon du gyur pa
NK070(thu)001:2964: dus su / kho na'o // a rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las /
NK070(thu)001:2965: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spros //
NK070(thu)001:2966: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK070(thu)001:2968: zhes bya ba ni lam bsgom pa bskyed rdzogs ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang du gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:2970: dkar ba ni byang chub sems kyi ngo la nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:2971: bsgom pa'i gnas ni phyi bskyed pa'i rim pa la
NK070(thu)001:2972: nges par snying kha ra bsgom ste ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:2973: n+ri mig gis bltar yod pa ltar /
NK070(thu)001:2974: brtan par gyur nas de la shin tu phra ba'i a dpag med rnams phar spro la /
NK070(thu)001:2975: des khams gsum gyi ril thams cad byang sems kyi
NK070(thu)001:2976: ngo bo nyid du byin gyis brlabs brlabs par snang
NK070(thu)001:2977: ngo // steng sgo rdzogs 00pa'i rim pa la ni /
NK070(thu)001:2978: a lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo nyid du bsgom
NK070(thu)001:2979: ste spro bsdu'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom lugs rjes su
NK070(thu)001:2980: mthun pa'i lus kyi phyogs bcu ma lus pa'i bde
NK070(thu)001:2982: bde ba bsdu ba'i 'phel 'grib las 'das pa ni
NK070(thu)001:2983: bde ba ye shes brten par 'byung 'di ni rdo
NK070(thu)001:2984: rje'i lta bu / dngos grub kyi ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:2985: dang bde ba'i ngo bo bskyed pas nye bar len
NK070(thu)001:2986: rje'i lta bu / pa'i rgyu'o // yin no //
NK070(thu)001:2987: de 0bzhin 0du ka la sogs pa yi ge kun la yang /
NK070(thu)001:2989: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i 0rgyu'i yin
NK070(thu)001:2990: pa phyir a de las 00ka la sogs pa yi
NK070(thu)001:2991: ge'i ming tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kha dog gsal
NK070(thu)001:2993: kun kyang s+pha ra ni phata kyis spro 0zhing sam
NK070(thu)001:2994: ha ra na h'u gis bsdu ba'ang a de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:2995: no // 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK070(thu)001:2996: brten 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK070(thu)001:2998: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK070(thu)001:2999: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:3000: thams cad ming tsam sangs rgyas kun //
NK070(thu)001:3001: yi ge phreng ba nyid la gnas //
NK070(thu)001:3002: zhes bya ba sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3003: lte ba a'i rang bzhin ni ye nas stong par gnas pa'i de /
NK070(thu)001:3004: rtsal cir yang snang ba'i 1 phyir mi stong par
NK070(thu)001:3005: rang rang gi dbyibs dang kha dog nyid zhen chags
NK070(thu)001:3006: dang bral ba bde ba chen po'i ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:3007: gsal bas 1dbu mar yang brjod du med pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:3008: yod med dbu ma'i mtha' gsum 111las 'das te dmigs
NK070(thu)001:3009: su yod pa ma yin pas na chos kyi sku
NK070(thu)001:3010: kho na'o // mtha' gsum las 'das pa dper na
NK070(thu)001:3011: a de nyid rang snang ba'i yi ge zhes gnyis
NK070(thu)001:3012: thams cad kun dang yi ge dpe mtshon pa'i dngos
NK070(thu)001:3013: po ming tsam gyi ril yang mtha' gsum la 'das
NK070(thu)001:3014: par rjes su mthun par shes na sangs rgyas kun
NK070(thu)001:3015: kho na'o // / kyi chos sku gzhan na med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3016: de yi ge phreng ba de nyid la gnas zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3017: longs spyod kyi sku bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3018: a nyid sna tshogs par snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:3019: ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK070(thu)001:3020: sgra'i ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK070(thu)001:3021: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK070(thu)001:3023: lte ba'i a'i bde ba ma 'gag pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:3024: de nyid thig le sna tshogs par snang ba /
NK070(thu)001:3025: ngo bo ka la sogs pa yi ge bzhi bcu
NK070(thu)001:3026: rtsa gnyis su ma rang 'gag par snang ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:3027: rta rnga brgya shas kyi sgra'i ming gi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:3028: skad cig ma'i bde ba ci lta bar /
NK070(thu)001:3029: phung po la sogs pa'i rtog pa ril thams cad de ltar bde bar bsdus te /
NK070(thu)001:3030: mnga' mdzad pas na mngon rdzogs rgyal po longs spyod
NK070(thu)001:3031: rdzogs pa'i sku ra thig le'i yi ge de nyid
NK070(thu)001:3032: yin par nges pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3033: ye ma'o ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi //
NK070(thu)001:3034: 'phrul chen bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming //
NK070(thu)001:3035: tshig rnams ma lus 'dzin pa'i gnas //
NK070(thu)001:3036: sna tshogs don chen smra zhing ston //
NK070(thu)001:3037: zhes bya ba ni sprul pa'i sku ston te /
NK070(thu)001:3038: e ma'o zhes pa yi ge'i /
NK070(thu)001:3039: ming 1dang gsung ngo mtshar ces pa las 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:3040: ya mtshan zhes pa rang bzhin 1thugs la ngom pa gsum 111mo ste sbyir 'gro /
NK070(thu)001:3041: 'phrul chen yi ge'i bzhi bcu rtsa lnga ming rnams
NK070(thu)001:3042: kyi ni tha snyad ma lus pa tshig thams cad
NK070(thu)001:3043: bsdus la pas 'dzin pa'i gnas tshig gi tha snyad
NK070(thu)001:3044: ma lus pa sna tshogs kyi don chen po brda
NK070(thu)001:3045: sprod cing smra zhing ston pas na ming gi las
NK070(thu)001:3046: yin te sprul sku'i gsung kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3047: gadngos med yi khage'i rang bzhin sems //
NK070(thu)001:3048: bdag ngamed mtha' bral mi dmigs kyang //
NK070(thu)001:3050: kasems nyid 0dngos med yi ge'i rang bzhin du rang
NK070(thu)001:3051: snang ba'i phyir sems nyid bde ba chen po'i rigs
NK070(thu)001:3052: pa las bdag gzhan gnyis su med pas yod med
NK070(thu)001:3053: dbu ma'i mtha' 111gsum las 'das pa'i phyir dmigs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3054: yul dang bral bas mi dmigs pa'i rang bzhin sprul
NK070(thu)001:3056: dbyibs dang kha dog ming tshogs kyis //
NK070(thu)001:3057: rol pa cir yang ston cing sprul //
NK070(thu)001:3059: kyang gi sgras yi ge'i rang bzhin thugs de lta bu'i yin pa phyir sems nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:3060: yi ge 'idabyibasa dang kha dog dang /
NK070(thu)001:3061: ming dang tshig tshogs kyi rol pa /
NK070(thu)001:3062: de las a 'khor ba'i phung po lnga dang 'das
NK070(thu)001:3063: pa'i rigs la sogs pas cir yang sprul cing ston
NK070(thu)001:3064: pas thams cad du snang zhing /
NK070(thu)001:3068: bshad pa'i sku gsung thugs gsum po de dag yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3069: phyogs bcu dus bzhir yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK070(thu)001:3070: rgyas ni mdzad pa'i sngon du ye shes 'gro ba
NK070(thu)001:3071: sems dpa' sku 'i gsung gi thugs kyi dkyil 111
NK070(thu)001:3072: 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga sa phrag gsum po nyid
NK070(thu)001:3073: / yi ge 'i 'go be rga ril nas k+sha yan chad la rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:3075: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK070(thu)001:3076: yi ge'i dngos po yod ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:3078: sems rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi de bzhin yi ger gnas pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3079: de yang sems kun gzhi dang nyon yid dang yid kyi rnam shes dang /
NK070(thu)001:3080: yul lnga la 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa dang
NK070(thu)001:3081: bzhi'i rang bzhin ni lte bar gnas pa a la
NK070(thu)001:3082: sogs pa mgrin par aa'am tig /
NK070(thu)001:3084: spyi bor hem'am shad sde yi ge bzhir nges par
NK070(thu)001:3085: gnas la yi ge de dag re re'i rtsal yang
NK070(thu)001:3086: yi ge du mar snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:3087: yi ge'i dngos po ngo bo nyid ni gcig tu rdzas grub tu yod pa ma yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:3088: de bsag gis du ma yang med gcig dang du ma med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3089: sems yi ger snang ba de lta bas na sems kyi ngo bo yi ge rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:3090: su snang ba snang stong gnyis su med pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3091: dmigs pa'i yul dang bral bas dmigs med rang rig pa kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:3092: yin de nyid sna tshogs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi /
NK070(thu)001:3093: h'u dkyil 'khor sogs pa gang du'ang mi 'gags par snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3095: dmigs med de nyid sna tshogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:3096: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor che //
NK070(thu)001:3100: khadbyings la dbyings kyis bris pa ste //
NK070(thu)001:3101: yi ge zhes ni de phyir brjod //
NK070(thu)001:3103: byed pa'i kalas dang 'grub pa'i khargyu'i ming don la brtags pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3104: bshad kapa'i sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan ni ngo
NK070(thu)001:3105: mtshar gyi ya mtshan 'phrul chen gyi ril rang rig
NK070(thu)001:3106: pa'i mngon sum du rab tu 'gug pa'am ston pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3107: yi ge nyid / tshul khaci ltar du rang snang zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:3108: gang phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs thams
NK070(thu)001:3109: cad sems nyid kyi ngo bo dbyings las mi gzhan
NK070(thu)001:3110: pa ni / sgra'i gnas brgyad kyi gsum pa byed
NK070(thu)001:3111: pa'i las shing la lta res rgyob byas pa lta
NK070(thu)001:3112: bu kho nar gyur la phung sogs 1de dag nyid
NK070(thu)001:3113: rang snang ba'i sems nyid bde ba chen po'i dbyings
NK070(thu)001:3115: las kyis skabs su bshad a h+aum pa bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:3116: phung po lnga la sogs pa sna tshogs su yang
NK070(thu)001:3117: gsal ba'i phyir / bris pa ste sgras gnas gnyis
NK070(thu)001:3118: shing gi glang chen sgyil byas pa lta bu pa
NK070(thu)001:3120: de yang la yi ger rang snang bas rgyu rkyen gzhan gyis byas par thal ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:3121: de rang snang ba de'i phyir yi ge zhes ni brjod /
NK070(thu)001:3122: 'go ni ma nor lam yin te //
NK070(thu)001:3123: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK070(thu)001:3124: shad ni thabs chen tshigs su gcod //
NK070(thu)001:3125: ces bya ba ni rim pa bzlog ste /
NK070(thu)001:3126: rtog pa ni sbyangs gzhi lus kar dag pa don thabs chen kyi ngo bo lha ni sku ste /
NK070(thu)001:3128: las na de nyid yi ge rnams tshigs su gcod pa'i yi ge nang du snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:3129: yi ge tig ni tshigs sde de dag gi las
NK070(thu)001:3130: ni bye brag tu phyes nas ming du smra bar
NK070(thu)001:3131: ston nas rtogs pa ni ngag kar dag par lha
NK070(thu)001:3132: ni gsung rdo rje snang mtha' ste don shes rab
NK070(thu)001:3133: bod dang kyog yi ge na mgo ri sbrul 'khyug
NK070(thu)001:3134: pa lta bus las ni yi ge thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:3135: 'go 'dren pa nyid rtog pa yid dkar dag pa
NK070(thu)001:3136: lha ni thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa nyid yin
NK070(thu)001:3137: pas don ni / thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel pa gnyis su med pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3138: yang dag pa'i ma nor ba lam yin te zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3139: khaa ni ka skye med de bzhin ganyid //
NK070(thu)001:3141: rtog pa chos ka'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi
NK070(thu)001:3142: khams ril don sems nyid pas de na so sor
NK070(thu)001:3143: ma skyes pa'i skye med ni ming gi bla dag
NK070(thu)001:3144: tu de bzhin nyid ces gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:3145: de nyid nges par yi ge ar snang ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3146: de'i phyir chos khams thams cad kyang sems kyi ngo
NK070(thu)001:3147: bor lhun gyis grub pas lha kun tu bzang mo
NK070(thu)001:3148: zhes bya'o // chos dbyings gang du yang ma nges
NK070(thu)001:3149: pas chos thams cad du snang ba sa kun gyi
NK070(thu)001:3151: tha na sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK070(thu)001:3152: ces bya ba la sogs pa lnga ni /
NK070(thu)001:3153: log rtog gis rgyu rkyen 'dus nas snang bas lnga phung sgyu ma lta bu'i rtog pa de don /
NK070(thu)001:3154: sems nyid yin pas ye shes su rang snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3155: don dam par dmigs pa med par kun rdzob tu
NK070(thu)001:3156: sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir 'phrul zhes bya gnas
NK070(thu)001:3157: skabs kyi yi ge ta tha da d+ha na /
NK070(thu)001:3159: de dag la lha rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs
NK070(thu)001:3160: par snang ba'i yid ni rnam dag kun tu rigs
NK070(thu)001:3161: lnga yang tha snyad du nyid 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:3162: khatha ni d+r+wa bas mngon rdzogs nyid //
NK070(thu)001:3163: ces bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3164: 'khrul gzhi'i nang gi dwangs ma ye shes kyi 'byung ba lnga ni /
NK070(thu)001:3165: phyi rol kun brtags kyi 'byung ba lnga po ste /
NK070(thu)001:3166: de'ang mngon rdzogs nam mkha' la sogs pa brten pas lha me mo /
NK070(thu)001:3168: kun tu snang zhing 'byung ba lnga'i ril yang sems
NK070(thu)001:3169: nyid du tha mi dad par bsdus pas na drang
NK070(thu)001:3170: bas 2thams cad sems 1nyid du 3rang snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:3171: yi ge ta tha da d+ha na lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:3172: lha kun mo la sogs pa yum lnga po nyid kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3174: ka khani spyan kagyi thugs gakyi mchog /
NK070(thu)001:3175: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3176: rtogs pa spyan gyi snyan gyi shangs kyi ljags kyis rnam par shes pa bzhi po ni /
NK070(thu)001:3177: rig pa kho na'i phyir thung ste /
NK070(thu)001:3179: 1de'i phyir thugs ye shes de nyid yi ge ka
NK070(thu)001:3180: kha ga g+ha nga bzhi po de nyid lha mchog
NK070(thu)001:3185: nga ni thugs kyang 'jigs byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3187: rtogs pa phyi ltar lus kyi 'bras bu shes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3188: ngo bo nang ltar gsang ba'i rnam par shes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3189: las kyis thugs kyi rnam shes bzhi po de dag
NK070(thu)001:3190: la yang mi gnas par te 'jigs byed pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:3191: / khro bo ste yi ge nga ni lha gshin rje gshed po zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3192: tsa khani spyan kagyi sku'i mchog ga /
NK070(thu)001:3193: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3194: sems nyid yi ge tsa tsha dza dz+ha nya ni
NK070(thu)001:3195: gong du bshad pa bzhin yin pas lha mchog l+aa
NK070(thu)001:3196: s+ya la sogs pa g+airti ma le n+airti bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:3197: nya khani sku yang ga'jigs byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3199: phyi ltar lus kyi yul reg bya nang ltar gsang
NK070(thu)001:3200: ba'i yul pad+ma'i las 0kyis sku yul bzhir 'dzin pa
NK070(thu)001:3201: mi gnas te 'jigs par byed pas khro bo /
NK070(thu)001:3202: rjes su mthun te rang bzhin ye shes nyid yi
NK070(thu)001:3203: ger snang ba lha'i ngo bo nyid ni gong du
NK070(thu)001:3205: yi ge nya ni lha stobs po che'o //
NK070(thu)001:3208: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3209: dbang po rnams ni yul dang shes pa rnams phyi nang gi tshul gyis brda sprod pas gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:3210: bshad pa bzhin yin pas sems nyid yi ge pa
NK070(thu)001:3211: pha ba b+ha bzhi ni lha mchog byams pa la
NK070(thu)001:3213: ma ni gsung yang 'jigs byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3215: gsang ba'i dbang po ste rjes su mthun ste gsung
NK070(thu)001:3216: dbang por bzhir 'dzin pa yong mi gnas te 'jig
NK070(thu)001:3217: par byed pas khro bo dang rang bzhin ye shes
NK070(thu)001:3218: nyid yi ge mar snang ba ni lha rta mgrin
NK070(thu)001:3220: ya khani skye ba karnam par gadag /
NK070(thu)001:3221: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3222: rtog pa dus bzhi kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:3223: 'das pa'i skye ba go 'byed pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3224: da ltar ba bstod pas gnas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3225: ma 'ongs pa'i rgyu rkyen 'dus dgongs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3226: da lta bas 'jigs pas mi rtags pa nyid 'byung
NK070(thu)001:3227: bar ma nges pa'i ngo bo nyid 'di 'drar bstan
NK070(thu)001:3228: du med pa ni stong pa rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:3229: ma ning gi yi ge ya wa ra la bzhir snang ste /
NK070(thu)001:3230: de nyid rnam par dag pa'i lha'i sku d+hu pe la sogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3231: push+pe +aa lo ke g+han+d+he la khasha ni rtag kamed dag gapa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3232: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni gsang ba'i dbang
NK070(thu)001:3233: po dbang yul dbang shes kyi khams su 'dus nas
NK070(thu)001:3234: / o ltar snang ba'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:3235: rtag chad bdag mtshan du 'dzin pa 'di ngang gis stong pa sa med pa nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:3236: yid kyi sems de yang ngo bo nyid ma grub
NK070(thu)001:3237: pa'i dbyings de nyid dri med 'byung ba'i yi ge
NK070(thu)001:3238: sha sha sa ha bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:3239: de nyid lha'i sgo ma lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:3240: k+sha khani ye shes gathugs kyi kathugs /
NK070(thu)001:3242: rtog pa thugs rnam shes kyi sgo lnga'i yul ril
NK070(thu)001:3243: yang yid kho nas gcod pa'i phyir thugs gnyis sam
NK070(thu)001:3245: yid byed pa po rang byung gi ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:3246: shar ba ni rgyu rkyen la sogs pa'i cha shas
NK070(thu)001:3247: kyi rtog pa ril thams cad zad pas mthar thad
NK070(thu)001:3248: pa'i yi ge k+sha ya zhes bya ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3249: yul lnga'i chos thams cad kyang yi rang byung ye
NK070(thu)001:3250: shes su grol ba de bzhin du dag par byed
NK070(thu)001:3251: pas lta na 1kun tu bzang 1 po'o //
NK070(thu)001:3252: e khani rdul snyed kalha rnams gasu /
NK070(thu)001:3253: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3254: thog ma med pa can gyi las dang nyon mongs
NK070(thu)001:3255: gnyis kyi bag chags drug po nang ris su grangs
NK070(thu)001:3256: las 'das pa 'i snyed kyi ril kun yang sems
NK070(thu)001:3258: don ye shes drug gi ngo bo nyid du gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3265: lha la sogs pa rnams kyi gnas su brgya byin la sogs pa thub pa drug go //
NK070(thu)001:3266: o ni thams cad 'jigs par byed /
NK070(thu)001:3267: khani thams cad ba zhig pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:3270: rtog pa gsang ba'i khams su 'dus pa'i rig pa nyid du bde ba skyes pa'i dus ni /
NK070(thu)001:3273: bco brgyad rtag chad la sogs pa'i phyin ci log
NK070(thu)001:3274: bzhi la sogs pa rtog pa ril thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:3275: mthu 'jigs cing nyams par gyur par byed la des
NK070(thu)001:3276: nges par bcad cing nyams su myong pa'i dus na
NK070(thu)001:3277: bde ba nyid du 'dzin pa las kyang 'das te
NK070(thu)001:3278: / bde ba thams cad bde stong gnyis med kyi
NK070(thu)001:3279: ngang du zhig pa yin pas phyogs gcig tu brjod
NK070(thu)001:3280: pa dang bral ba nyid ye shes lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:3281: rtog pa'i bdud rtsi ye shes kyi 'khyil pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3283: yi ge gsung gi 'khor lo yi ge'i tshogs chen po 'dis /
NK070(thu)001:3284: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs kyi phreng ba yi ges bsdus pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3286: de nas le'u dang por zhes pa la sogs pa ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:3287: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin byang chub sems tshogs rgyu 'khor lo //
NK070(thu)001:3289: thabs yab dang shes rab yum gyi nyi zla sbyor ba gnyis su med pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3291: byang sems de nyid dgyes pa ni nam mkha' sprin
NK070(thu)001:3292: lta bur lus gnas rtsi'i 'khor lo bzhi la sogs
NK070(thu)001:3293: pa rtsa gnas kun la khyab pa nyid yi ge'i
NK070(thu)001:3294: +aa li k+aa li tshogs su rang snang bas thig
NK070(thu)001:3295: le bde stong 'dus ma byas pa las ma g.yos
NK070(thu)001:3296: par rang la gnas pa ni sku dang ye shes
NK070(thu)001:3297: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyu kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:3298: lus kyi rtsa khams thams cad la rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3299: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor te 'khor lo nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:3300: rjes 'jug gi sgrub pa pos kyang rang bzhin gsung
NK070(thu)001:3301: gi dkyil 'khor rjes su mthun par rgyu ma nor
NK070(thu)001:3302: ba rtsa ba'i sngags las grol lam steng sgo'i ting
NK070(thu)001:3303: nge 'dzin nam steng sgo'am 'og sgo yum la bstan
NK070(thu)001:3304: pa'i thabs kyi sku ye shes la bkod pa ni'i
NK070(thu)001:3305: thabs rkyen lhag pa ting nge 'dzin kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3306: lam des 'bras bu ci zhig 'ong snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:3307: 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub ngo mtshar ming tshogs bcu gnyis /
NK070(thu)001:3308: 'dus ma byas nyid 'dul byas rdo rje dkyil 'khor 'byin pa'i dam /
NK070(thu)001:3310: lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya rmad du byung
NK070(thu)001:3311: ba 'bras bu rgyal ba'i ngo bor smon cing rang
NK070(thu)001:3312: rig pa'i mngon sum du grub pa ni ngo mtshar
NK070(thu)001:3313: ba'o // de dag yi ge ming gi tshogs las byung ba'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:3315: lam sas bsgrub pa'i dbang du de nyid 'dus byas
NK070(thu)001:3316: su brjod kyang yi ge rang sku ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:3317: ngo bo nyid ni gzhi lam 'bras bu'i dus gsum
NK070(thu)001:3318: du dbyer ba med mi phyed pa rdorje'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:3319: de nyid do // mngon du 'byin pa las mi 'da' pas dam tshig gi /
NK070(thu)001:3320: don las 'da' bar mi mdzad pas 'bras bu mi
NK070(thu)001:3321: 'byung ba'i dbang med rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'i mthu chen
NK070(thu)001:3322: yin / zhes bya ba ni mi 'da' ba'i phyir dam tshig ste /
NK070(thu)001:3323: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyud la rang gnas thabs lam
NK070(thu)001:3324: bsgom pa'i las sam grol lam gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:3325: gyi rkyen gyis lhan cig 'tshogs par byas pas 'bras
NK070(thu)001:3326: bu smin par snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3327: gdul bya'i ngo na snang ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3328: rang snang ba de nyid mthu chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:3329: ra gyur pa yin pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yi ge'i 'khor lor gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:3331: de ba rang bzhin nyid dang rang bzhin lhun grub
NK070(thu)001:3332: gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:3333: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa lngar 'dus shing /
NK070(thu)001:3335: de dag nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor gnyis de'i ngo bo bas gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:3336: don de la tshig de skad ces bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3337: yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo bkod pa'i zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3338: yi ge'i phreng ba gsung gi 'khor lo dkyil 'khor gyi phyung pa'i rim pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3340: las dang kyis nges tshig che ba'i yon tan dang sku gsung du gnas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3341: yi ge'i nges tshig dang rang bzhin /
NK070(thu)001:3343: bye brag bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ngo bo tha dad
NK070(thu)001:3344: par snang ba'i rnams ma nor bkod pa phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:3348: // de nas yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin bkod pa las /
NK070(thu)001:3351: le'u bzhi par ting nge 'dzin gyi gsung yi ge
NK070(thu)001:3352: 'khor lo sprin bkod pa'i nus mthu las sgyu 'phrul
NK070(thu)001:3355: thun mong gis dngos grub dang gsum la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:3356: snang mchog gi dngos grub rnam par 'phro ba'i ched
NK070(thu)001:3357: du brjod do // zhes bya ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3358: gdul bya'i ngo la ma grub kyang snang ba kho nar ston to //
NK070(thu)001:3360: de nyid kyi phyir bskyed pa'i bsgrub pa rim pa'i dbang du rgyud kyi rim pa spangs te /
NK070(thu)001:3361: man ngag gi rim pa 'khrug rten la 'jug par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3362: de la dang po 'bras bu byang chub grub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3363: rgyu bstan pa'i phyir ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa
NK070(thu)001:3364: gsal / dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK070(thu)001:3365: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK070(thu)001:3368: ston pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa /
NK070(thu)001:3369: rang bzhin can gyi bla ma rdo rje slob dpon yang dag par de /
NK070(thu)001:3370: rang gi sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas mnyes pa gsum gyi mchod par byas nas /
NK070(thu)001:3371: phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang rnams rim par thob par bya ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3372: brtson 'grus kyis bsgrub pa'i sngon du bya ba'i sgo gsum gyi spyod pa yongs su sbyong ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3374: 'chad pa bzhin lta ba yongs su dag par rtogs
NK070(thu)001:3375: pa de nyid ting nge 'dzin tu gsal bar bya
NK070(thu)001:3376: ba dang / rtsa ba lnga dang lan lag bcu
NK070(thu)001:3377: dang bco lnga po la sogs pa'i sum brgya drug
NK070(thu)001:3378: cu dam tshig rnams ma nyams par /
NK070(thu)001:3379: yongs su dag par bya ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3380: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po /
NK070(thu)001:3381: dang sngags kyi yan lag lnga po rnams ma nyams par bsgom bzlas shes shing /
NK070(thu)001:3383: gnas khang sum rim dang bro gar la sogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3384: longs spyod kyi yo byad bzhi po dag dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:3386: tshang bar mi ldan par bsgrub kyang /
NK070(thu)001:3387: don med pas na rigs chad pa'i gnas su gyur pa'i phyir brlag ces bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3388: de bas na 'grub pa'i rgyu de dag nges par rjogs par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3390: gnyis pa lta ba bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:3391: gang gis dmigs med mi shes pa //
NK070(thu)001:3392: de'i chos kyis dbyings mi shes //
NK070(thu)001:3394: gang ni nyer len gyi rgyu blo'i skal ba dman zhing /
NK070(thu)001:3395: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen bla ma'i man ngag gis ma zin pa dag go //
NK070(thu)001:3396: sems nyid ni ci'i ngo bor yang ma yin te
NK070(thu)001:3397: phyogs gcig tu dmigs su med de de'i don mi
NK070(thu)001:3398: shes pa'i phyir / ming tshig gi mtshon pa'i don /
NK070(thu)001:3399: zhig yod byed pa rnams ni blos dmigs pa can
NK070(thu)001:3400: de'i chos nyid 'dus ma byas kyi dbyings kyang mi
NK070(thu)001:3401: shes zhes bya'o // de dag ni dper na 'o
NK070(thu)001:3402: ma 'dod pas nu ma la mi bzho bar rwa
NK070(thu)001:3405: 'jigs pas dmigs med shes par gyis //
NK070(thu)001:3408: tshigs kyi gtan la phab pa sngar thal te chos
NK070(thu)001:3409: nyid rang byung gi ye shes dang ldan pa can
NK070(thu)001:3410: ni rgyu rkyen 'dus pa kho na'i de phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3411: dngos po 'jigs par byed pa'i rgyu las mi ltos
NK070(thu)001:3412: te rang grol du 'gro bas phyi nang gi dngos
NK070(thu)001:3413: po'i ril sems nyid 1spros bral du 'jigs pa las
NK070(thu)001:3414: de 1nyid yongs su rang gsal bas dngos med stong
NK070(thu)001:3415: pa nyid du bzhag pa kyang 'jigs te /
NK070(thu)001:3416: sems kyi ye shes ni 'og nas 'chad pa bzhin yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:3417: ngang gi dmigs su med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3418: de shes bar gyis shig pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3419: de nyid ci'i phyir dmigs su med snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:3420: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK070(thu)001:3421: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK070(thu)001:3422: mtshan med ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK070(thu)001:3423: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:3424: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK070(thu)001:3425: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK070(thu)001:3427: rten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3428: sems nyid ni phyi mo'i rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i
NK070(thu)001:3429: phyir / rang byung gi ye shes de /
NK070(thu)001:3430: de ni chos can ngo bo he du nyid ma grub pas /
NK070(thu)001:3431: sems can gyi mtshan ma gsum dang pho dang mo
NK070(thu)001:3432: yang ma yin la ma ning yang ma yin pa
NK070(thu)001:3434: sgo nga lta bu dang ma yin pa 'gro ba
NK070(thu)001:3435: drug dang gi rigs rgyud min pa gzugs kyis mtshan
NK070(thu)001:3436: ma kha dog dbyibs gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:3438: sems nyid rten par bya ba'i yul dang chos de
NK070(thu)001:3439: ni brten par byed pa'i dbang po'i gnas gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:3440: grub pa yang ma yin pa la sogs pa'i don
NK070(thu)001:3441: gang gis ngo bo nyid du ye gdong ma nas
NK070(thu)001:3442: ma grub ste dam bca' pas na min pa ni
NK070(thu)001:3444: de nyid mu mtha' dang bral zhing chos 0thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pas mnyam pa'i dbyings te /
NK070(thu)001:3445: de nyid rig pa kho nar gsal bas ming de bzhin nyid dang chos kyi dbyings /
NK070(thu)001:3446: ye shes dang gnyis su'ang 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:3448: don de nyid rang bzhin gyi rtogs pa lha'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:3449: 'khor du gsal ba bzhi dang lhar bsgom pa lam
NK070(thu)001:3451: lhag pa'i thabs kyi phyag kargya dang /
NK070(thu)001:3452: gsum po kun gyis rgyu du'ang mi 'gag khapar snang ga ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:3453: thabs khakyi phyag rgya kun gyi ga rgyu //
NK070(thu)001:3455: gsum pa rtogs pa de ltar lam pas bsgom dgos par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3456: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pas //
NK070(thu)001:3457: rtog pa'i dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK070(thu)001:3459: gong du lta ba'i skabs su bshad pa ltar 'khor
NK070(thu)001:3460: 'das kyi dngos po ril rnams sems nyid kho nar
NK070(thu)001:3461: gsal la sems nyid ni gong du bshad pa ltar
NK070(thu)001:3462: ma grub pa kho na yin bas 'khor bcas kyi
NK070(thu)001:3463: dngos po rnams dus nam du yang phyogs gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:3464: grub ma myong bar med pa shes nas rtogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3465: don de nyid la ma yengs pa'i dbang bsgyur ba
NK070(thu)001:3466: ni btang snyoms chen po'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa
NK070(thu)001:3467: ni shin tu gces pa yin par gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:3468: bzhi pa bsgom pa'i thabs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3469: gang gi glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK070(thu)001:3470: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK070(thu)001:3472: gang zag gang gi gong du bshad pa ltar dngos
NK070(thu)001:3473: po rnams nyid dngos po med par shes nas rtogs
NK070(thu)001:3475: sa bya 'khrul pa'i yul sdug mi sdug sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:3476: kyi thog ma med pa nas g.yeng ba'i sems ni
NK070(thu)001:3477: dper na glang po che rgun 'brum gyi chang gis
NK070(thu)001:3478: myos pa gnod pa sna tshogs byed pa lta bu
NK070(thu)001:3479: ste / de dag 'dul ba'i thabs ni lta ba
NK070(thu)001:3480: med pa zhi gnas rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:3481: gyi bsgom pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK070(thu)001:3482: lta ba'i don phyogs gcig cir yang ma grub rtogs
NK070(thu)001:3483: pa'i rjes su bsgom pas blo shes pa mi dmigs
NK070(thu)001:3484: pa ni mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su zhes
NK070(thu)001:3485: bya ste / yod med kyi mtha' bral zhing dbus su zhes pa las kyang 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:3486: bzhi chos ci bzhin par gyur te 'khor 'das mi
NK070(thu)001:3487: gnyis te tha dad med blo gshis thog tu pheb
NK070(thu)001:3488: par phab pa ni thul ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3489: de ka gnas lugs de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:3491: lnga pa cir yang ma grub pa de nyid chos thams cad du snang bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3492: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK070(thu)001:3493: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK070(thu)001:3494: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK070(thu)001:3495: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK070(thu)001:3497: rtsa ba med pa'i shad bar gcig ni lta ba'i skabs bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:3498: don de lta bu la rang bzhin gyi ting nge
NK070(thu)001:3499: 'dzin gyis lhag pa 'bru'i phyag rgya gsum po dang
NK070(thu)001:3500: 'am yang na skugasunga thugs kyi phyag rgya gsum /
NK070(thu)001:3501: 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i chos rnams kyi ril yang snang
NK070(thu)001:3502: bas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kun kyi rtsa
NK070(thu)001:3503: ba yin te / chen po 'khor 'das gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:3504: snang ba de dag don sems nyid de nyid du
NK070(thu)001:3505: gnyis su med par shes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3506: 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i snying rje'o //
NK070(thu)001:3508: sems chos thams cad du snang ba las 'dir gnas
NK070(thu)001:3509: skabs kyi rgyu'i yi ge'i rang bzhin a ru snang
NK070(thu)001:3510: ba yin te yi ge a de las yid bzhin
NK070(thu)001:3511: gyi nor bu rin po che ltar dran pa tsam
NK070(thu)001:3512: gyis yi ge phreng ba zhe gnyis po yang 'byung
NK070(thu)001:3513: la yi ge de dag sprin ltar nam mkha' khyab
NK070(thu)001:3516: drug pa yi ge de las gzhal yas khang dang lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3517: thabs las thabs byung thabs bsam yas //
NK070(thu)001:3518: tha dad min la tha dad pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:3519: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK070(thu)001:3520: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes rol //
NK070(thu)001:3521: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK070(thu)001:3523: rang rig pa nyid rgyu'i yi ger snang ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:3524: rtsa ba'i thams cad bskyed pa thabs zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3525: thabs de las gzhal yas khang kham gdan dang bcas
NK070(thu)001:3526: pa snang ba ni thabs las byung ba lha'i rten
NK070(thu)001:3527: gzhi'i thabs so // de dag tu lha'i dkyil 'khor bkod nas bsgom pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3528: mang bas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thabs bsam yas pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3530: de dag kyang rang rig pa kho na yin pa
NK070(thu)001:3531: tha dad pa min pa las dman pa'i rims kyis
NK070(thu)001:3532: blo tha dad par snang ba'i nang gi lha'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:3533: 'khor rnams dang gang gi phyi rol gyi gzhal yas
NK070(thu)001:3534: kyi gnas khang de dag rgyu rkyen 'dus ma byas
NK070(thu)001:3535: te / de ltar dkyil 'khor stong dang nyi khri
NK070(thu)001:3536: bzhi stong dang bsam yas lhun grub la sogs blos
NK070(thu)001:3537: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes su rang snang
NK070(thu)001:3538: bas lha la lha gshis kyi ye shes la bsgom
NK070(thu)001:3539: pa'i lam gyi ye shes rol pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3540: rnam par rtog pas brtag pa'i don min pas kun
NK070(thu)001:3541: brtag 1pa dang rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas gzhan
NK070(thu)001:3543: ste gnas tshul rtogs tshul de ni spyod yul thams
NK070(thu)001:3544: cad sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor yongs su
NK070(thu)001:3546: khams gsum 1'khor ba dang rtag chad 1lam gyi 11g.yang
NK070(thu)001:3547: sa 'i 'jigs pa dang bral te med bas de'i
NK070(thu)001:3548: ngang las mi 'da' bas na phyag rgya chen po'i
NK070(thu)001:3549: mchog ste / ci bder nos shig ces gsungs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3551: de nyid kar dag pas blang dor dang bral bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3552: de nyid ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK070(thu)001:3553: ming tshogs gzugs stsogs yid bzhin gyi //
NK070(thu)001:3554: mun la snang byung ci bzhin du //
NK070(thu)001:3557: thabs gsum po de nyid gzhi ci zhig gi ngang la snang zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:3558: gdod ma nas sems kyi ye shes rang snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:3559: ngo bo lus 'khor lo bzhi'i yi ge'i ming tshogs
NK070(thu)001:3560: dang gzugs kyi phung po la sogs pa khams gsum
NK070(thu)001:3561: gyi rtog pa'i ril thams cad sems nyid kyi ngo
NK070(thu)001:3562: bo yin pa'i phyir lha dang gzhal yas khang cir
NK070(thu)001:3563: yang snang bas yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'dra bas
NK070(thu)001:3564: rtog tshogs 1de dag gong gi thabs gsum du ting
NK070(thu)001:3565: nge 'dzin gsum gyis rang dbang bsgyur yang thabs gsum
NK070(thu)001:3566: po dang blangs pa dang rtog tshogs dor ba med
NK070(thu)001:3567: pa ni nges par ma nor bar mun snang gser
NK070(thu)001:3568: 'gyur sman gyi tshul gyi dpe gsum gyis tshogs brgyad
NK070(thu)001:3569: ye shes dang / 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dang /
NK070(thu)001:3570: rtog tshogs ltar dag pa'i don mtshon te /
NK070(thu)001:3571: go sla bas so sor ma bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:3572: brgyad pa thabs gsum pa de dag la ting nge 'dzin 'dris par bsgom pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3573: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brten na //
NK070(thu)001:3574: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:3576: thabs gsum po de dag la phra mo dang phyag
NK070(thu)001:3577: rgya gcig pa snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i spros
NK070(thu)001:3578: pa ting nge 'dzin gyis lha'i sku phyag rgya chen
NK070(thu)001:3579: por sngags kyi yan lag sku gsung thugs ye shes
NK070(thu)001:3580: sems dpa' dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga dang ldan par
NK070(thu)001:3581: gsal ba la yul gyi rkyen gyis mi phrog pa
NK070(thu)001:3582: par rab tu brtan las dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK070(thu)001:3583: po mchog thun mong rnam gnyis nges par 'byung bar
NK070(thu)001:3584: 'gyur ba bstan pas gnas pa kho nar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3586: dgu pa phyag rgya gcig spros de'i thun mong gi
NK070(thu)001:3587: dngos grub tshogs gnyis bstan pa'i phyir bdud rtsir 'byung
NK070(thu)001:3591: zhes bya ba'i bar du tshigs rkang bcu gnyis gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:3592: dug las bdud rtsir bsgyur ba la sogs pa bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3593: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3594: gzhan yang sel ba la ljon shing /
NK070(thu)001:3595: bye ma la gser la sogs pa dngos po thams cad phan tshun mi mthun par bsgyur ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:3597: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung la sogs pa 'byung
NK070(thu)001:3598: ba lnga'i dngos po stobs khyad par du gyur par
NK070(thu)001:3599: byas pa dang la sogs pa'i sgras dgug btang la
NK070(thu)001:3600: sogs pas sems can gyi bsam pa yongs su skong
NK070(thu)001:3601: ba ste / phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad
NK070(thu)001:3602: kyang rig pa bdag nyid nyid chen po las mi
NK070(thu)001:3603: gzhan par shes nas stobs su gyur pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:3604: ba ste / // de dag thams cad phyag rgya
NK070(thu)001:3605: gcig pa dang spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyi
NK070(thu)001:3608: bcu pa mchog gi dngos grub bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3610: dra ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pas //
NK070(thu)001:3611: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:3614: gang zag gang gis phung po lnga la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:3615: sgru 'phrul lha'i dkyil 'khor yab yum bzhi bcu rtsa
NK070(thu)001:3616: gnyis su med par dra ba'i dkyil 'khor rang rig
NK070(thu)001:3617: mngon sum du gsal zhing rdzogs pas phyogs bcu dus
NK070(thu)001:3618: bzhis bsdus pa'i kakhams gsum gyi ril thams cad lha'i
NK070(thu)001:3619: 0dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs su gsal ba bsod nams kyi
NK070(thu)001:3620: tshogs yang ye shes kyi spyod yul gyis zhen pa
NK070(thu)001:3621: dang bral 0bas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs 00chen gnyis
NK070(thu)001:3624: 'bras bu lus pa med pa sa na rgyal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:3625: dkyil 'khor thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ba kho na'i
NK070(thu)001:3626: zhes bya'o // bcu gcig pa mchog gis dngos grub de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3627: dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs chud pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:3628: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'di //
NK070(thu)001:3629: zad pa'i dus med yid bzhin mdzod //
NK070(thu)001:3631: dngos po med la dngos po'i sprin //
NK070(thu)001:3635: dngos po thams cad 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su gsal ba ni 'i don de /
NK070(thu)001:3636: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i dgongs pa rang gi ngo bo nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:3637: shugs su chud pa'i lta ba dang mchog gi dngos grub snying po dang gsum ka yin pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3638: gzhan rmad byung las kyang chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs pas /
NK070(thu)001:3639: sangs rgyas kun gyi yang snying yin pas nyin sha can //
NK070(thu)001:3640: nga ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi dur //
NK070(thu)001:3641: gnas shul sdud pas dngos grub chen po'ang nga nyid yin //
NK070(thu)001:3643: byang chub sems de nyid dngos po'am ngo bo rang
NK070(thu)001:3644: rgyud can gcig du ma grub par med pa las
NK070(thu)001:3645: gdul bya blo che chung la mdzad pa phrin las
NK070(thu)001:3646: kyi dngos po'i sprin sna tshogs pa'i rnams par snang
NK070(thu)001:3647: nas 'byung zhing 'gyur yang 'phel ba dang 'grib pa
NK070(thu)001:3649: de nyid zad pa'i dus med de /
NK070(thu)001:3650: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'am rgyal po'i dkor mdzod lta bu ngo bo nyid rtag pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3651: de pa thams cad gzigs mos mnyes par gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:3653: zhes gzhung don de dag brjod pas 'khor gyi de pa nyid /
NK070(thu)001:3654: ting nge 'dzin gyis gom pa de mthu las dngos
NK070(thu)001:3655: grub sna tshogs su snang ba ril thams cad bdag
NK070(thu)001:3657: ma bltas par gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3660: blta byed mi phyed pa ni gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa ste mnyes par gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:3662: sgyu 'phrul bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3663: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK070(thu)001:3664: phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis kyi mthus /
NK070(thu)001:3665: las brgyad la sogs pa dang dngos grub gnyis ma
NK070(thu)001:3666: lus pa bsgrub pa'i stobs kyis 'grub pa ste le'u
NK070(thu)001:3669: // de nas de pa thams cad kyis rang bzhin gcig
NK070(thu)001:3670: dang du ma med pa'i bdag nyid thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:3672: de bzhin gshegs par ma zad de 'khor ba'i chos
NK070(thu)001:3673: thams cad kyi rang bzhin rang rig pa gsal bas
NK070(thu)001:3674: ma 'dres la gcig tu yongs su rdzogs pa'i 1phyir
NK070(thu)001:3675: / gcig 10dang du mar bral bas med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3676: gcig du bral gang 0yin pa'i don de nyid mngon du byas pa ni bdag nyid chen po ste /
NK070(thu)001:3677: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid de ltar mtshungs par bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:3679: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad la nyid kyi che ba'i dkyil 'khor 'byung bar bzhes nas /
NK070(thu)001:3681: khams gsum gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bzhi mtshams
NK070(thu)001:3682: brgyad 1dbus steng dang 'og ste bcu po 1thams cad
NK070(thu)001:3683: du rig pa rang snang ba de nyid kyi ril
NK070(thu)001:3684: yang 'og nas 'byung ba ltar che ba /
NK070(thu)001:3685: ye shes 00lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bdal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3686: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ngo bo yang yin la /
NK070(thu)001:3687: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor de nyid 'khor la gsal
NK070(thu)001:3688: bar bstan par dgongs pa mngon du bzhag pa ni
NK070(thu)001:3689: / 'byung bar bzhed pa zhes kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:3691: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te /
NK070(thu)001:3692: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK070(thu)001:3694: 0rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid phyogs bzhi dbus kyis
NK070(thu)001:3695: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad du rang rig pa'i ngo
NK070(thu)001:3697: phyogs dbus de dag 0rang rig pa'i ye shes de'i ngo bo nyid du /
NK070(thu)001:3698: gsal la mi rtog 1pa dang me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:3699: phyogs dbus thams cad 0rang rig pa de'i ngo bor 1gcig pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3700: la bzang ngan med pa mnyam pa nyid /
NK070(thu)001:3701: phyogs dbus thams cad ma 'dres 1pa dang so sor rtogs pa /
NK070(thu)001:3702: yin tshul rang rig tu yongs su rdzogs pas logs su bya ba med 1pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3704: snang tshul gyis phyogs dbus sam yod med kyi mtha'
NK070(thu)001:3705: thams cad las 'das pa'i 11111phyir chos dbyings ye shes
NK070(thu)001:3707: de'i ngo bo blos gzhal ba las 'das par gnas
NK070(thu)001:3708: pa ni 'og gis rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:3709: ba ste / shes bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'o //
NK070(thu)001:3710: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ste bsam yas shing lhun gyis grub pa pas //
NK070(thu)001:3713: rnal 'byor pa gang gis rdzogs pa chen po'i don de rtogs shing mngon du byas pa'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:3714: snang spyod thams cad ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor las mi 'da' bas /
NK070(thu)001:3715: zhing khams dang spyod yul thams cad ye shes kyi ngo bor yongs su dag pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:3716: de ka la che ba'i yon tan kun ting nge
NK070(thu)001:3717: 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor chen po bsgom pa la 'byung
NK070(thu)001:3718: ba sa na spyod zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:3719: don ye shes lnga de'i rtsal mi 'gag pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:3720: rtags lhag pa ting 'dzin gcig par ba de blos
NK070(thu)001:3721: mi lcog pa blo chung ba rnams kyi phyir rim
NK070(thu)001:3723: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK070(thu)001:3724: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i tshig bzhi po ni go sla ste ma bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:3725: 'dir mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim bsdeb na le'u
NK070(thu)001:3726: lnga pa de ting kun ting rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:3727: gsum gyi rjes su bdun pa ltar b+h+r+aum las 2gzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:3728: thabs ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang 'di ltar mngon
NK070(thu)001:3729: du bya ba / de la 1nang lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:3730: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi cha byad can gyi sprul
NK070(thu)001:3732: gzhal yas der gdan ci zhig bsgom snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:3733: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK070(thu)001:3734: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK070(thu)001:3735: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK070(thu)001:3737: don dgongs pa rang byung gi ye shes la mi 'jigs pa bzhi stobs bcu /
NK070(thu)001:3739: dbang bcu phrin las bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:3740: 'bras bu'i chos lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa des gdul
NK070(thu)001:3741: bya la thams cad tshim par byed pa nyid don
NK070(thu)001:3742: yid la rtags sems can chen po seng ge glang
NK070(thu)001:3745: lnga dang rin po che'i khri sna tshogs su mdzes pa /
NK070(thu)001:3746: brtan pas pad+ma bsteg pa ni sems dpa' man chad
NK070(thu)001:3747: gzhan gyi gdan la dpag pas khri chen ces ba'o
NK070(thu)001:3748: // gnyis po de dag la sogs par lnga brtsegs su dgod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3749: kathabs zla ba dang shes rab nyi ma dang spyod
NK070(thu)001:3750: pa'i nyes pas mi gos pas pad+ma gdan sum brtsegs
NK070(thu)001:3751: te / de'i don ni chos kathams cad rang rig par gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:3753: 'khor ba'i chos khagang la spyad kyang mi gos par 'bras bur pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:3754: de ltar rigs lnga la lnga brtsegs /
NK070(thu)001:3755: sems dpa' yab yum la sum brtsegs /
NK070(thu)001:3756: kun bzang yab yum la bzhi brtsegs /
NK070(thu)001:3757: thub pa la pad+ma khro bo la nyi ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:3758: gdan de dag la ci zhig khabzhugs snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:3759: gdan ka la rdzogs gadang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK070(thu)001:3761: gdan de dag la gtso bo rigs lnga ni /
NK070(thu)001:3763: rdzogs pa'i dkyil mo krung dang /
NK070(thu)001:3764: rigs kyi yum lnga ni brtul zhugs te nyon mongs
NK070(thu)001:3765: pa bde stong gnyis med kyis ngang gi dkyil mo
NK070(thu)001:3768: bdag don gyi mdzad pa mthar phyin pas zhabs g.yon
NK070(thu)001:3769: bskum gzhan don gyi mdzad pa yongs su ma rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:3770: pas g.yas pa gdan la bab pa'i tshul lo //
NK070(thu)001:3771: sems ma rnams ni brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo krung gi tshul gyis yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3772: 'khor lo rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK070(thu)001:3773: g.yas nas mthong thos bsnam pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:3774: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK070(thu)001:3776: 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi la rgyal po
NK070(thu)001:3777: rigs kyi yab lnga rgyal mo yum lnga dang bcas
NK070(thu)001:3778: pa dang / rtsibs mchan bzhi la thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:3779: g.yas nas mthong thos snams pa zhes pa'i dkyus kyis
NK070(thu)001:3780: tshig rim pa ni sa snying gis yi ge'i ka
NK070(thu)001:3781: 'og nas kha yod pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs
NK070(thu)001:3782: pa ste / dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i gral ni
NK070(thu)001:3783: le'u bdun pa'i lugs su mthun pa ste rang rang
NK070(thu)001:3784: gis btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:3785: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang /
NK070(thu)001:3786: zhes pa la sogs pa ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:3787: gru chad bzhi la ni mthong byed byams pa la
NK070(thu)001:3788: sogs pa'i yab yum rnams dkyil 'khor du bzhugs tshul
NK070(thu)001:3789: gyi rim pa yang gong dang rjes 00su mthun no
NK070(thu)001:3790: // bar 'khyams te lha snam la ni thub pa drug dang //
NK070(thu)001:3791: mdun shar dang rgyab nub tu byed pa po kun tu bzang po dang //
NK070(thu)001:3792: bya ba mo kun mo dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK070(thu)001:3795: sdud 0pa'i don gyis 'khyams 'dir lha brgyad kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:3796: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi rnams mnyam par bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:3797: sgo khyud bzhi la gdug pa can 'jam pa'i khro bo bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:3798: btsun mo lcags kyu la sogs pa'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK070(thu)001:3800: bar chad gdug pa can la rngam pa'i tshul gyis zhal phyir bltas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3801: lha zhe gnyis po de dag gi phyag mtshan ci zhig /
NK070(thu)001:3803: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK070(thu)001:3804: zhes bya ba la stsogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:3806: ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK070(thu)001:3807: mdzes tshul gnyis pa'i yo byad 'dzin //
NK070(thu)001:3808: zhes phyag na 'dzin pa'i rim pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:3810: g.yas gsum na rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri 'bar //
NK070(thu)001:3811: g.yon gsum na dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK070(thu)001:3812: de ni gtso bo rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag mtshan gyi rim pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3813: rigs bzhi gzhan gang yin pa'i gnas su skyin po rdo rje shes //
NK070(thu)001:3815: g.yas dang po rang rtag gis phyag mtshan thugs khar
NK070(thu)001:3816: bsnams pa dang g.yon dang po yum la 'khyud pa'o
NK070(thu)001:3817: // sa snying gis rin chen myu gu nam snying
NK070(thu)001:3818: gis ral gri 'od 'bar ba spyan ras gzigs kyis
NK070(thu)001:3819: // pad+ma dkar po / phyag rdor gyis rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:3820: 'od 'bar ba 'jam dpal gyis ud+pala byams pas klu
NK070(thu)001:3821: shing sgrib sel po ti kun bzang gis rin po
NK070(thu)001:3822: // pad+ma dkar po / che'i snye // ma /
NK070(thu)001:3823: nang gi sems ma bzhi mdzes pa'i tshul 'dzin te
NK070(thu)001:3824: gzugs l+aa s+ya mas mdzes pa bskyed pa me long
NK070(thu)001:3825: m+aa le mas rin chen gyi phreng ba dang //
NK070(thu)001:3826: g+ai rtis pi wang n+ai rtis gar sgyur phyi'i sems
NK070(thu)001:3827: ma bzhis mdzes pa'i yo byad 'dzin te gdug pa
NK070(thu)001:3828: / sogs kyi shing gu gul me dang //
NK070(thu)001:3829: push+pe me tog +aa lo kes mar me dang //
NK070(thu)001:3830: gan+d+hesa byug pa dri'i dung chos de rnams dang po
NK070(thu)001:3831: gtso bo'i phyag mtshan 'khor gyi bar du rim pa
NK070(thu)001:3834: gshin rje gshed kyis n+ri mgo stobs po ches rdo
NK070(thu)001:3835: rje rta mgrin gyis thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa
NK070(thu)001:3837: sgo ma bzhis lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta lcags sgrog ho //
NK070(thu)001:3839: kun po'i sor mo'i rtse la 'od 'phro ba ltar
NK070(thu)001:3840: byas pa mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya kun mo rdo
NK070(thu)001:3842: yang na kun tu bzang po ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga g.yon dril bu /
NK070(thu)001:3843: yum kun mo chos khams dril //
NK070(thu)001:3845: thugs ka la bsnol nas brten pa nyid du'ang gnyis su gsungs //
NK070(thu)001:3846: drug gis phyir ma nges kyang thub pa chen po
NK070(thu)001:3847: rnams nges par byas na zhal gcig phyag gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:3849: mi yis bsreg shangs dang par bu lha yis pi wang lha min gyis go mtshon brdeg /
NK070(thu)001:3851: yi dwags kyis sgrom bu stobs pa byol song gis po ti ni chos 'chad pa'i tshul //
NK070(thu)001:3852: chos rgyal gyis me dpung dang chu'i bum par shes par bya //
NK070(thu)001:3855: lha de dag gi sku ci zhig yin snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:3856: mthing ka bdun ni mi bskyod pa yab yum /
NK070(thu)001:3861: dkar po lnga ni rnam snang sa snying /
NK070(thu)001:3868: bzhi ni snang mtha' spyan ras gzigs so //
NK070(thu)001:3869: ljang gu gnyis ni don grub yab yum 0la sogs pa'i sgras bcu dagu'am nyer lnga /
NK070(thu)001:3872: byams pa dkar ser la sogs pa mtshams kyi sems
NK070(thu)001:3873: dpa' dang khro bo gshin rje gshed smug nag la
NK070(thu)001:3874: sogs pa'i phyir na kha dog nyi shu rtsa lngar
NK070(thu)001:3875: te byams pa yab yum dkar ser /
NK070(thu)001:3877: sgrib sel dmar ser kun bzang dmar ljang /
NK070(thu)001:3883: byol song gi thub pa smug nag /
NK070(thu)001:3885: chos rgyal dud ka la sogs sna tshogs pa /
NK070(thu)001:3889: sgeg pa'i tshul gyis yab yum thabs dang shes rab 'khril sbyor du snyoms par zhugs kyang /
NK070(thu)001:3890: sku dang yan lag mnyan pa'i phyir sku drang zhing
NK070(thu)001:3891: yan lag so sor ma 'dres par gsal lo zhes
NK070(thu)001:3892: bya'o // gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi brjid che //
NK070(thu)001:3894: mtshan sum cu gsal ba dang dpe byad brgyad cu
NK070(thu)001:3895: 'tsher ba dang de dag sku la yongs su rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:3896: pas lhun sdug pa shin tu gzi brjid che pa'i
NK070(thu)001:3897: phyir gzhan thams cad kyang zil gyis gnon pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3900: gsal la rno ba'i phyir 'od zer te /
NK070(thu)001:3908: dngul gnyis gyi mdog lta bu sngo skya dang drug go //
NK070(thu)001:3909: de dag nang ris su dkar po lta bu gcig kyang grangs bye ba phrag drug drug ste /
NK070(thu)001:3910: de dag gi gnas btus pa 'grel chung ltar spyan
NK070(thu)001:3911: dang snyan dang la sogs pa'i 'od kyi grangs nges
NK070(thu)001:3913: 'dir sku'i ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kha
NK070(thu)001:3914: dog drug gis bye ba phrag drug drug phyogs bcur
NK070(thu)001:3915: 'phros pa'i snang bas khyab par byed pa ni tshogs
NK070(thu)001:3919: sgo ba khro bo dang khro mo'i me dpung 'bar ba'i phreng ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:3920: rtse mo rdo rje rtse lngar 'khrigs pa'i tshul re 'khyil pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3921: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:3922: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK070(thu)001:3923: ces bya ba ni rang bzhin dkyil 'khor mtha' dbus
NK070(thu)001:3924: med pa khyab pa'i nyi rjes su lhag pa'i ting
NK070(thu)001:3925: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor yang chos kyi dbyings mtha'
NK070(thu)001:3927: lhun gyis grub pa de dag gi ngo bo nyid du rang gsal ba'i ngo bo las /
NK070(thu)001:3928: gdul bya mos pa tha dad pa'i rang gi snang
NK070(thu)001:3929: bas go skabs phyes nas sna tshogs su snang bas
NK070(thu)001:3930: gdul bya'i don bya bar 'i phyir du bsgom pa
NK070(thu)001:3931: ni nyid las phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas su
NK070(thu)001:3932: / 'dul ba'i don rnams so sor ston //
NK070(thu)001:3936: bzhi pa rang bzhin lhun grub sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi sku lnga so so'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:3937: gzugs sku gnyis kyis gzhan don mdzad pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:3939: 'bras bu sku lnga de bsgrub pa'i tshul bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3940: rtsa rgyud bshad rgyud la tshogs ni med phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pas //
NK070(thu)001:3941: sku'i phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK070(thu)001:3942: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK070(thu)001:3943: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang //
NK070(thu)001:3945: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK070(thu)001:3947: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i snang stong zung 'jug gi
NK070(thu)001:3948: sku la ni sku lnga lhun gyis grub pas lha'i
NK070(thu)001:3949: sku phyag rgya chen po bsgom pa las khyad par
NK070(thu)001:3950: du gyur pa'i phyir mchog ni drug pa spyi'i gzan
NK070(thu)001:3951: kho na'o // de dag gang zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:3952: snod bcud 'khor 'das ci snang yang sems nyid kho na'i yin pa phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3953: snang stong gnyis su med pa ni zung 'jug chos kyi sku nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:3955: 'jig pa la rten pas rten snod g.yo ba bcud la sogs pa'i sgras 'das pa //
NK070(thu)001:3957: snang ba nyid na rang rgyud du ston pas ngo bo phyogs gcig tu grub pa med //
NK070(thu)001:3959: de nyid dbu ma'i chos sku las lhag pas na chen po yin //
NK070(thu)001:3962: de nyid ni de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK070(thu)001:3963: mnyam pa'i dbyings de la sa /
NK070(thu)001:3965: ma brtsal ba ni ma g.yos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3966: zhes pas lam pa'i gnyen po'i /
NK070(thu)001:3967: rtsol ba dang sdug bsngal las grol bar ston pa
NK070(thu)001:3968: ni yang dag pa'i thar pa thun mong ma yin
NK070(thu)001:3969: pa'i mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i gzugs can ste /
NK070(thu)001:3970: longs spyod chen po'i sku dang /
NK070(thu)001:3971: gdul bya 'gro ba drug ma lus pa 'dul ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:3972: gdul bya dang mthun par byas pa'i sku bstan pa'i thub drug ni sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK070(thu)001:3973: gdul bya sna tshogs la mdzad pa bsam gyis mi
NK070(thu)001:3974: khyab pas bzhi 'dul ba rnams su ston nas snang
NK070(thu)001:3978: gzugs sku gnyis po de dag kyang ston pa ni
NK070(thu)001:3979: chos sku lhun gyis grub pa'i nyid mdzad pa'i go
NK070(thu)001:3981: gdul bya las dag pa'i stobs kyis bdag rgyan dang
NK070(thu)001:3982: rgyu'i rkyen gnyis gyis snang ba kho na las 'i
NK070(thu)001:3983: phyir sgyu ma dang mig yor gyi tshul de /
NK070(thu)001:3984: rang rgyud du snang bar bzung ba rnams ni 'khrul pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:3985: zhes bya ba'i ste rang rgyud med pa tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:3986: 'o na don gyi ngo bo nyid ci lta bu zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:3987: tshul nyid dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK070(thu)001:3989: tshul dper 11de nyid kyi phyir gdul bya la gzugs sku sna 0tshogs su snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK070(thu)001:3990: sems 0kyi dbyings nyid kho na las ma g.yos pas
NK070(thu)001:3991: bden 0pa 0gnyis su dbyer mi phyed pas gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:3993: brgal ba khung nas 'byung bas 'o na ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:3994: nyid rang rgyud du med pa'i sna tshogs su snang
NK070(thu)001:3995: bas / rtsol bas 'i rtog pa byas so bar dogs pa las /
NK070(thu)001:3996: len dkyus su 'debs pa ni ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa //
NK070(thu)001:3997: de'i tshe mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa la //
NK070(thu)001:3998: sku so sor shar ba ni gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:3999: de bzhin dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK070(thu)001:4000: las 'phros gdul bya mos pa dbang gis so sor snang //
NK070(thu)001:4002: gzhan don gzugs sku thams cad ma brtsal bar rang rig pa'i ye shes lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4003: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ste /
NK070(thu)001:4004: gzugs sku gnyis po de yang gdul bya blo'i rim
NK070(thu)001:4005: pa dang mthun par sku sna tshogs so sor snang
NK070(thu)001:4006: ba ni / las dag ma dag gi rkyen kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4008: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:4010: gzugs sku de dag chos sku las ma g.yos par zhing khams kun tu snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4014: chos sku las 'gro 'ong med par kun tu khyab pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4015: nam mkha'i zla ba la 'gro 'ong med par chu thams cad du zla ba'i gzugs brnyan bzhin nam /
NK070(thu)001:4017: 'di la gsum ste de tshe 'gro drug sems can la snang tshul thams cad la //
NK070(thu)001:4018: sdig pa spangs ba thub drug gam 'khor lo bsgyur
NK070(thu)001:4019: rgyal gyi gzugs su rnam par snang zhing dge tshul
NK070(thu)001:4020: nos / rnams la 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i gzugs /
NK070(thu)001:4022: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul /
NK070(thu)001:4023: ste grogs po gnyis kyi lo rgyus bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:4024: zhes bya ba ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:4025: de las dgar bas gzhan yang chos theg mchog ni gdul bya la snang tshul rim pa bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:4027: rgyu'i theg pa'i mos pas spyod pa sbyor lam pa man chad pa la sprul pa'i sku nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:4028: kri ya dang yo ga la sogs pa phyi nang
NK070(thu)001:4029: gi mos spyod la theg pa so so'i ston pa
NK070(thu)001:4030: rnams kyang de bzhin du snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:4031: 'og min gtsang ma rigs kyis gnyis 'gyur gyis dpag pa'i bla med gnas mchog nas //
NK070(thu)001:4032: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad chos bdun tshul //
NK070(thu)001:4033: sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK070(thu)001:4034: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK070(thu)001:4036: longs sku nges pa bzhi ldan zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4037: 'og min bla na med pa'i chen po'i gnas mchog
NK070(thu)001:4038: tu longs spyod kyi sku ni rnam par snang mdzad
NK070(thu)001:4039: kyi tshul du sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems
NK070(thu)001:4040: dpa'i 'khor rnams la sprul pa'i sku de bzhin gshegs
NK070(thu)001:4041: pa ltar tshig gis gsung gi mchog tu gyur pas
NK070(thu)001:4042: chos mi ston pa'am mi smra te /
NK070(thu)001:4043: brda ston pa ni mdo gzhan dag las ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa la 111la ni /
NK070(thu)001:4044: kun rdzob tu chos ma 'dres pa'i brda' /
NK070(thu)001:4045: spyan phye bas chos ston to //
NK070(thu)001:4046: la la ni don dam la snang ba med pas bcum pas chos ston te /
NK070(thu)001:4047: la las ni thabs kyi 'gro don mdzad pas phyag brkyang bas chos ston to //
NK070(thu)001:4048: la las ni shes rab kyi chos kun chos nyid du bsdus pas bskum pas /
NK070(thu)001:4051: la las ni khyim pa'i cha byad can la sngags
NK070(thu)001:4052: kyi lam btsun mo dang bcas pas chos ston to
NK070(thu)001:4053: // la la ni rab tu byung ba'i cha byad
NK070(thu)001:4054: can la pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam gyi brda'
NK070(thu)001:4055: btsun mo med pas chos ston to //
NK070(thu)001:4058: gnyis las dang po dpe ni /
NK070(thu)001:4059: me long bstan pa'i tshul kha bzhin du //
NK070(thu)001:4060: byad kadngos kyi mdog ngan pa'i dri ma thams cad mthong nas sel //
NK070(thu)001:4062: gnyis pa don pa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i
NK070(thu)001:4063: 'khor 0gyi de bzhin du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK070(thu)001:4064: la bltas na // byang chub sems dpa'i sgrib pa de gting dpag dka' bas med //
NK070(thu)001:4065: de me long dpe'i bzhin du ston pa'i sku la snang //
NK070(thu)001:4069: de pa'i ye shes kyi sku ni ma bltas pas
NK070(thu)001:4070: de gcig tu ma grub par sku thams cad du
NK070(thu)001:4071: snang ba'i phyir / sgyu ma las 'das pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4072: 'khor de 0dag ston pa de ltar ma gyur pa te sgyu ma tsam du 'dug /
NK070(thu)001:4073: ni sgrib pa ngos zin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4074: de pa'i ye shes thabs kyi lus ni rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:4075: rtse mo'i thig le thig le chen po'i gnas yum
NK070(thu)001:4076: gyi b+ha ga na bzhugs pas 'khor dam chos thams
NK070(thu)001:4077: cad kyang dbang bskur ba'am rang byung gi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:4078: chen por byin gyis brlabs nus pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:4079: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' de dag gi thabs dang
NK070(thu)001:4080: lam dang mi mthun pa ni dper na 'o ma
NK070(thu)001:4081: 'dod pas nu ma la mi bzho bar mgo'i rwa
NK070(thu)001:4082: la bzhos pa ltar shes nor par pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:4083: // ngos zin pa de 'grub tshul bstan pas nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byangs /
NK070(thu)001:4085: sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:4086: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa la nges par phyin
NK070(thu)001:4087: ci ma log par dbang kho na la rim gyi
NK070(thu)001:4089: de'i 'thad pa lang ka'i mdo las /
NK070(thu)001:4090: ston pas blo gros chen po zhes bos nas ston
NK070(thu)001:4091: pas byin 00brlabs gnyis kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i 'khor
NK070(thu)001:4092: sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi byang chub
NK070(thu)001:4093: sems dpa' dag ston pa de pa'i zhabs la phyag
NK070(thu)001:4094: 'tshal ba'i tshe mgo gtug cing don gyi 'dri ba
NK070(thu)001:4095: yongs su 'adri'o // gnyis 00gang zhe na dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gsang dbang zer /
NK070(thu)001:4097: brda' sku dang zhal dang phyag gnyis gis las gnyis kyi las rim zer /
NK070(thu)001:4098: dbang bskur ba'i byin gyis brlabs so //
NK070(thu)001:4099: gnyis pa de la 'khor byang chub sems dpa' sa
NK070(thu)001:4100: dang po rab tu dga' ba la gnas pa la
NK070(thu)001:4101: / ston pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK070(thu)001:4102: de'i mthus byang chub sems dpa' rgyud pa ting nge 'dzin 2theg pa chen po rab tu snang ba /
NK070(thu)001:4103: zhes bya ba sa gnyis pa'am sa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:4104: de la zhugs ma thag tu phyogs bcu'i de pa
NK070(thu)001:4105: brgya yi sprul pa 'gyed nus zhing zhing bzhi brgyar
NK070(thu)001:4106: 'gro nus / rnams kyi zhal ston to //
NK070(thu)001:4108: yang zhal mthong ba pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs spang bya /
NK070(thu)001:4109: sgrib pa nges zin pas na rtogs par khung du
NK070(thu)001:4110: chud de spangs pas mthar sa bcu pa chos kyi
NK070(thu)001:4112: de la de pa'i longs sku'i zhal nas lung ston dang phyag gis spyi bor 'jog /
NK070(thu)001:4115: de ltar sa bcu pa dag dbang gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:4116: rim par khung du chud nas spang bya rnams kyang de bzhin du rim par dag pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4117: sa bcu pa de'i rjes su bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la nges par snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4118: bla na med pa'i 'bras bu byang chub yang dag thob ces gsungs so /
NK070(thu)001:4119: dus de nyid du mdo sde pa'i theg pa'i sku gsum bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4120: chos sku gnyis med de blos dpag tu med ngag tu brjod du med //
NK070(thu)001:4121: longs spyod kyi sku ni sprul pa zad pa med
NK070(thu)001:4122: par 'byung bas rin chen gyi gter lta bu'o sprul
NK070(thu)001:4123: pa'ii sku ni bye ba phrag bsam gyis mi khyab
NK070(thu)001:4126: kun tu 'od de las kyang sngags kyi pad+ma spyan
NK070(thu)001:4127: dang yi ge 'khor lo'i sa gnyis bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4128: du / thabs dang shes rab mchog /
NK070(thu)001:4130: pad+ma spyan du sangs rgyas pa de'i tshe snying rje
NK070(thu)001:4131: chen po mngon du byas pas gzugs sku thams cad
NK070(thu)001:4132: du snang yang / bdag nyid chen po'i ra rtogs
NK070(thu)001:4133: pa phyir mi dmigs pa shes rab yin pas na
NK070(thu)001:4134: nyon mongs cis kyang gos pa med pa'i sa ni
NK070(thu)001:4135: kun tu 'od las ltos nas mchog kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4136: de nyid du yi ge 'khor lo'i sa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4137: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:4138: spyod yul kun tu ma d+ha la //
NK070(thu)001:4139: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol //
NK070(thu)001:4141: chos dbyings ye shes ma yin pa'i ye shes bzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:4142: brlabs kyis ye shes re re la'ang bzhi bzhi ste
NK070(thu)001:4143: bcu drug gam / yang na yab yum gyi dga'
NK070(thu)001:4144: ba bzhi po re re la'ang dga' bzhi bde stong
NK070(thu)001:4145: gnyis med kyi ye shes bzhi'i shar ba byin brlabs
NK070(thu)001:4146: bcu drug gam / las / las kyis 1ye shes
NK070(thu)001:4147: bcu drug dang yum gyi yul dbyings bcu drug gi
NK070(thu)001:4148: brlab la sems dpa' dang bcu drug sems ma bcu
NK070(thu)001:4149: drug mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:4150: sems dpa' bcu drug la ye shes lnga'i lnga /
NK070(thu)001:4152: rigs lnga lnga dbu brgyan pa ni dpe byad brgyad
NK070(thu)001:4153: cu la sogs pa thams cad lhun 11gyis grub cing
NK070(thu)001:4154: rdzogs pas rang snang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:4155: 'khor 'das kyi spyod yul gyi ril kun bdag gi
NK070(thu)001:4156: sems las mi gzhan pa'i ye shes lha dang dkyil
NK070(thu)001:4157: 'khor du snang ba bsod nams dag ni tshogs chen
NK070(thu)001:4158: po gnyis kyang ma rtsal bar lhun gyis grub pa
NK070(thu)001:4159: ste rdzogs par rol zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4160: de'i yon tan kabgrang bar mi nus pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4161: de la kasogs te yon tan bsam yas pa dang ldan pas mchog /
NK070(thu)001:4163: sa gnyis so de la sngags kyi lugs su 'bras
NK070(thu)001:4164: bu sku lnga lhun gyis grub par bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4165: / skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku /
NK070(thu)001:4167: 1chos kyi sku ni gong du bshad pa bzhin yin
NK070(thu)001:4168: pas sems nyid ye nas skye shi med pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4169: skad cig ma'i skye 'jigs dang bral bas na ngo
NK070(thu)001:4170: bo nyid kyis rtag pa ste 'gyur ba med pa
NK070(thu)001:4171: g.yung drung chos kyi sku kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4172: nyon mongs kun gyi zhing du kagnas //
NK070(thu)001:4173: zad khamed rin chen gter du ga'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:4175: longs spyod chen po'i sku 1ni 'dod yon gang yang ma spangs pa kho na bas /
NK070(thu)001:4177: nyon mongs pa drug po kun sbyangs pa'i zhing tshogs gnyis bsags /
NK070(thu)001:4178: zhing du gyur pa sprul pa sku'i 'byung gnas mi
NK070(thu)001:4179: bzad khapa'i 'byung kakhung gagi gter du gyur pa ni
NK070(thu)001:4181: rdo rje rig pa 'dzin pa'i sku //
NK070(thu)001:4183: chos gang du yang rang rig par gsal bas /
NK070(thu)001:4184: snang stong gnyis su mi phyed pa ni rdo rje'o //
NK070(thu)001:4185: 'dzin pa ni 'chang ba zhes bya ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:4186: gang gi rig pa de ltar 'dzin pa dang ldan pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4188: thams cad dbyer med mnyam pa'i sku //
NK070(thu)001:4190: phung po lnga la sogs pa rtogs pa'i rim thams
NK070(thu)001:4191: cad rang rig par dbyer med mnyam pa ni rtog
NK070(thu)001:4192: pa / thams cad kyang rig pa /
NK070(thu)001:4193: bdag nyid chen po'i sku dang ye shes su gsal bas mngon par 1byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK070(thu)001:4194: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes sku //
NK070(thu)001:4196: 1sprul pa'i sku gdul bya thams cad kyi 'dul ba'i dus 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:4197: 'dul thabs thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gang
NK070(thu)001:4198: ltar bsam pa dang 'tsham par don mdzad par mi
NK070(thu)001:4199: 'da' 1ba dang ma 'dres par kho nar snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4200: phyir ro // lnga po 11111de dag gis phyir na /
NK070(thu)001:4201: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:4203: zhes rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi don de dag
NK070(thu)001:4204: brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i gdul bya'i
NK070(thu)001:4205: gnas mtha' yas mu med pa thams cad du sku'i
NK070(thu)001:4206: dkyil gyis rol pa 'khor brjod kyis mi lang ba
NK070(thu)001:4207: zhing gi rdul snyed du rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:4208: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar gyur to
NK070(thu)001:4209: // zhes pa ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:4210: che ba'i ye shes lnga dkyil 'khor mngon sum du 'bung ba'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:4211: drug pa'i sku'i rol pa yongs su bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:4212: sdud par byed pa'i tshig 'byung ba sngar dang 'dra'o //
NK070(thu)001:4213: dmigs bya dmigs byed mi dmigs dpag med bsam mi khyab //
NK070(thu)001:4214: ye shes rang rig dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod mi lang //
NK070(thu)001:4216: phyi nang snod bcud kyi ril thams cad sems kyi
NK070(thu)001:4217: ye shes su sngar gsal ba'i dus na dmigs bya'am
NK070(thu)001:4218: shes bya chos kyi dbyings dang dmigs byed dam shes
NK070(thu)001:4219: byed rang rig pa'i ye shes gnyis kyi tha snyad
NK070(thu)001:4220: las 'das te / mi dmigs pas blo'i spyod yul
NK070(thu)001:4221: dang bral bas ting nge 'dzin dpag med yon tan
NK070(thu)001:4222: bsam gyis mi khyab bar gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4223: ming du rdzogs 1pa chen po'o don te ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4224: de 1la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi ril
NK070(thu)001:4225: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa nyid rang rig pa'i
NK070(thu)001:4226: rgyal pos rang dbang bsgyur te /
NK070(thu)001:4227: ye shes rol pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK070(thu)001:4228: dkyil 'khor lha dang gzhan yang khang sna tshogs su
NK070(thu)001:4229: brjod kyis mi lang bar rang snang ba nyid /
NK070(thu)001:4230: rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor du snang
NK070(thu)001:4231: bas des na spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4232: / ya ki na de nas zhes pa nas /
NK070(thu)001:4233: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub /
NK070(thu)001:4236: mnyam dang mi mnyam kun khyab khyab med khyab pa'i dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:4238: drug pa'i sku'i rol pa gzugs sku gnyis po de /
NK070(thu)001:4239: nyid longs sku ni gdul bya dag pa sa bcu la snang bar go mnyam pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:4240: 'jig rten pa ma dag pa ril la sprul skur
NK070(thu)001:4241: snang ste longs sku mi snang bas go mi mnyam
NK070(thu)001:4242: pa / kun la khyab par don mdzad pa mngon du byung tsam na /
NK070(thu)001:4243: de dag chos sku de bzhin nyid las mi 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4244: gzugs sku 0snang ba dang stong pa gnyis su song
NK070(thu)001:4245: ba med par khyab bya khyab byed gnyis med du
NK070(thu)001:4247: gnyis med de dag 0ci'i phyir snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:4248: ye nas kun gsal dkyil 'khor rnams spro spros pa med /
NK070(thu)001:4250: gzhi la dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin ye gdod
NK070(thu)001:4251: ma nas 'bras bu sku lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK070(thu)001:4252: ba las lam gyi de bzhin nyid du mngon sum
NK070(thu)001:4254: yang dag mngon par 'bras bu ma lus pa rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:4255: 1pa nyid kyi 11phyir gzhi 'bras gnyis su med par
NK070(thu)001:4256: lhun gyis grub pa de nyid rang snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:4258: 'phro ba zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:4259: de dag gdul bya las dag ma dag kyi rim
NK070(thu)001:4260: pa ci lta bar gzugs sku gnyis su snang yang
NK070(thu)001:4261: / rang rgyud par 'byung ba med pas spros pa med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4264: zhes bya ba ni ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:4265: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzhal yas khang dang lha'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:4266: zhi ba rang bzhin lhun grub sku'i dkyil 'khor lnga po spros pa de dag gi ngo bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:4268: mdzad pa'i phrin las yongs su bshad pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4270: // da ni stod na zhi ba lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:4271: sngags gsum gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4273: de pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:4274: b+h+r+aum 00ni cir yang 'gyur ba ste 'dir gzhal yas khang gi sa bon no //
NK070(thu)001:4275: b+hi sha sna tshogs b+hi shud+d+he rnam par dag pa
NK070(thu)001:4276: zhes bya ba ni 'byung ba lnga 'dzin gyi rtog
NK070(thu)001:4278: 'dis phyi ltar gzhi'i thabs gzhal yas khang yongs su bskyed cing snang bar byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4281: b+h+r+aum gis dbyibs can yum gyi b+ha gar rtsa sna tshogs 'dus //
NK070(thu)001:4283: sbyor ba'i byed las 00dang nyi ma'i thig le rang
NK070(thu)001:4284: gi ngo bo la chag rtogs rang kha ma rnam
NK070(thu)001:4288: dang 'dra ba de ci'i phyir sngags zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:4289: byin brlabs che ba dang yid skyobs pa'i phyir na sngags su brjod //
NK070(thu)001:4292: zhes bya ba la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:4293: rigs lnga bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4296: tsit+ta 0snying kha khams dngas ma lnga'i snod shi ra la //
NK070(thu)001:4298: badz+ra 1rdo rje dz+hi na rgyal ba rat+na 1rin chen a ro 1chos //
NK070(thu)001:4299: pra nya ni 1shes rab las kyis rigs lnga dang
NK070(thu)001:4300: 11111ldan pa'i bcud thig le'i kyi ngo bo la h'u
NK070(thu)001:4303: nges par hri dz+hig lig 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK070(thu)001:4306: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni yum lnga'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4309: 0de nyid kyi dwangs ma lnga'i ye shes lnga //
NK070(thu)001:4311: lhan skyes kun brtags kyi ma rig gnyis ni gti
NK070(thu)001:4312: mug sogs sgras zhe sdang nga rgyal 'dod chags sa
NK070(thu)001:4313: 'og gi phrag dog bzhi po dang //
NK070(thu)001:4314: de dag dang dbyer mi phyed pas phrag dog rdo rje sngags //
NK070(thu)001:4315: dug lnga chos kyis dbyings su skyob pas zhe sdang dga' ma /
NK070(thu)001:4316: gti mug nga rgyal 'dod chags phrag dog /
NK070(thu)001:4319: k+shi hi ra ts+aa ya ni sa snying dkar po
NK070(thu)001:4320: myu gu 'dzin pa'i bskyod sngags zhes bya ba la
NK070(thu)001:4321: sogs pa ni / thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4322: h'u la se sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK070(thu)001:4323: ni la s+ye dkar mo me long 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4324: zhes bya ba la sogs ni /
NK070(thu)001:4325: de dag ni yum bzhi'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4327: 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi cha'i las kyi bde bas rgyas pa sgeg pa ni //
NK070(thu)001:4329: yab kyis sa ma ya s+t+wam ni chags pa'i sa
NK070(thu)001:4330: spyad dam tshig gi dus la bab pa yin no
NK070(thu)001:4331: // yab kyi ci ltar slar yang yum gyi bstan chos kyi cha'i len gyis 'brel ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:4333: yab yum gnyis ka bde ba dgyes pa'i mchog tu bshad //
NK070(thu)001:4334: pa ni sa ma ya ho zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4335: g+airti glu ma ni bskyod pa ha dang si'i bde sgra dag /
NK070(thu)001:4336: ra ga ya ho ni bdag gis chags pa thob pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4337: lus stod smad shin tu bskyod pa'i sa ni n+airti'i gar bsgyur bde ba nyid //
