NK070(thu)001:4338: ra ga ya mis kun nas bskyod pa'i rlung zhes bya //
NK070(thu)001:4340: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK070(thu)001:4341: ni byams pa dkar ser klu shing 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4342: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4343: gsung gi byang chub sems dpa' bzhi'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4344: dza d+hu pe pra be sha ni bdug spos dkar ser spos me 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4345: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4346: de dag gi yum bzhi'i sngags te /
NK070(thu)001:4348: nyi zla'i thig le gnyis 'dres pa de gsang ba
NK070(thu)001:4349: rdo rje'i rtser 'dzin pa dza lcags kyu zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:4350: ste / d+hu pe bde bas tshim pas de nyid rdo rje /
NK070(thu)001:4351: nor bu dang pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru kha phye ba las byung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:4353: push+pe kun+d+ha dang pad+ma'i me tog gnyis gcig tu bsdus pa'i h'u ni zhags pa ma'i ngo bo nyid //
NK070(thu)001:4354: slar 0dbyings 0ye shes 00bdag po'i so so zhal du thim par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:4356: lus stod smad shin tu bam lcags sgrog gis bsdam pa'i rim pa las byung //
NK070(thu)001:4358: rnam pa ril gsal ba'i ye shes bde ba che //
NK070(thu)001:4359: na po ni pu ki ni mar me /
NK070(thu)001:4360: lus kun ho dril bu mas bder gsal ba'i sgra ni brjod pa dang 'dra ba'i g+han+d+he sgra //
NK070(thu)001:4362: gnyis med tsit+ta thugs su shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4365: ni gshin rje smug nag mi mgo kha gdangs 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4366: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4367: khro bo sgo ba yab yum brgyad kyi sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:4369: ni kun bzang mthing ka mnyam bzhag can gyi bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4370: a a +aahbadz+ra sa tra sa man ta +aa /
NK070(thu)001:4373: byed pa po yab yum gyi sngags te /
NK070(thu)001:4376: h'u gsum ni kun ni nyon yid /
NK070(thu)001:4378: kun tu tshol ba'i rjes su dpyod pa'i gtan la
NK070(thu)001:4379: phab pa'i yid gsum gyis rnam shes gsum rang kha
NK070(thu)001:4380: ma la 'das pa badz+ra skye 'jigs dang bral bas
NK070(thu)001:4381: rdo rje ni // mo ye shes lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i tsit+ta thugs nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:4382: a gsum ni skye ba med pa'i mnyam pa'i lhun
NK070(thu)001:4383: gyis grub pa'i dbyings gsum rnam par dag pas badz+ra
NK070(thu)001:4385: dus kun tu'ang pa ta pa min ta de bzhin nyid la gnas bar byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4388: lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK070(thu)001:4389: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4390: sprul pa thub pa rnams kyi sngags te yang //
NK070(thu)001:4392: snying kha'i thig le rigs drug gis //
NK070(thu)001:4393: sa bon zung gsum a n+ri sum pre tri du drug po /
NK070(thu)001:4398: las nyon gnyis las 'byung ba'i 'gro ba'i rtog pa rnams /
NK070(thu)001:4399: 'dul ba'i phyir na mu ne thub par gsung //
NK070(thu)001:4401: ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyi 'go 'dren /
NK070(thu)001:4402: e ha hi bos b+ha ga ban bcom ldan 'das
NK070(thu)001:4403: ma h+aa ka ru ni thugs rje chen po tri
NK070(thu)001:4404: sha ho gshegs shig sa ma ya s+t+wam dam tshig
NK070(thu)001:4407: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor la dam tshig bskul te /
NK070(thu)001:4409: dzahmh'u bam ho zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4411: gur khang gyi steng du bzhugs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4413: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4414: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog pa ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:4415: nyid 'bras bu sku dang ye shes nyer lngar 'i
NK070(thu)001:4416: ngo bo shes pa'i dus na 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK070(thu)001:4417: thams cad gnyis su med par gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4418: de pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las thams cad kyi rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4419: dkyil 'khor thams cad du bzhugs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4420: gnyis su med pa de nyid du gyur par phyag
NK070(thu)001:4421: rgya bzhis nan tan gyis byin gyis brlabs par bskul
NK070(thu)001:4422: ba'i phyir / ye shes lnga ldan gyi glu'i 'go drangs /
NK070(thu)001:4423: chos thams cad spangs pa med par rig pa'i ye shes su bsgyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4424: rgyal po de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs /
NK070(thu)001:4425: yon tan phrin las rnams gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na /
NK070(thu)001:4427: dus de nyid 'di du ni bdag dang mnyam par
NK070(thu)001:4428: sbyor bas thugs rjes mnga' sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK070(thu)001:4429: phrin las kyi phyag rgya chen por bdag kyang sbyor
NK070(thu)001:4431: ye shes lnga ldan badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya h'u /
NK070(thu)001:4433: badz+ra sa ma ya ho zhes gsungs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4434: sa ma ya h'u ni rang bzhin grub pa'i ye
NK070(thu)001:4435: shes su dam tshig gcig par sdud cig sa ma
NK070(thu)001:4436: ya s+t+wam ni byin gyis brlab pa'i dus la bab
NK070(thu)001:4437: pas sa ma ya ho ni de bdag la mnyes
NK070(thu)001:4440: dza h'u bam ho zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4441: phyag rgya bzhis rim pas bdag dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la ye shes pa bstim nas bzhugs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4442: zhes brjod pas gsung gi dkyil 'khor dag gi 'jig
NK070(thu)001:4443: rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas par khyab par
NK070(thu)001:4446: zhes brjod pas gsung sngags kyis dkyil 'khor 'di dag
NK070(thu)001:4447: gi mthus 'jig rten 'gro ba drug gi phyogs bcu'i
NK070(thu)001:4448: gdul bya ba thams cad kyi lus la sngags yi
NK070(thu)001:4449: ge nyid gnas pa'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu las khyad
NK070(thu)001:4450: par grags so // de 'bras bu lha'i dkyil 'khor dang du gsal bas na rab tu grags pa /
NK070(thu)001:4452: mchog thun mong gi 1dngos grub dang gsum gyi 111ril
NK070(thu)001:4453: du snang ba de nyid rim pa ltar bskyed sngags
NK070(thu)001:4454: spyan drang ba la sogs pa'i bskyed sngags si ti
NK070(thu)001:4457: sa na kun tu grags de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK070(thu)001:4458: byed pa po rdo rje dang bya ba mo kun
NK070(thu)001:4459: tu bzang mo dang thabs shes rab gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:4460: pa'i don de rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:4461: 'khor la thim par mdzad pa do //
NK070(thu)001:4463: gang la dbang bskur na lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:4464: gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha zhe gnyis so thams cad
NK070(thu)001:4465: la gang gis na rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:4466: ste rgyud dag pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum
NK070(thu)001:4467: gnyis su med pa'i ci lta na byang chub sems
NK070(thu)001:4468: kyi chu rgyun kho nas dbang bskur bar bya ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4469: phyir ro // bdag nyid chen po'i ye shes lnga dbang bskur pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:4470: sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlab bsdu ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4471: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi yan lag gi
NK070(thu)001:4472: lha dgu rnams ni ye shes lnga'i 1chu rgyun gyis
NK070(thu)001:4473: dang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba'i 1sku gsung thugs byin 11brlabs
NK070(thu)001:4474: phab pa las byung bas ye shes lnga dang sku
NK070(thu)001:4475: gsung thugs gsum po de dag nyid du nga'am bdag
NK070(thu)001:4476: yin no bar nga rgyal 0byed pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4477: ye shes lnga ldan ma h+aa chen po shud nya
NK070(thu)001:4478: ta stong pa nyid badz+ra rdo rje s+w+aa b+h+aa ba
NK070(thu)001:4479: rang bzhin dag pa 0ad ma ko&a ham /
NK070(thu)001:4480: nga'am bdag yin no zhes mi bskyod pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4482: mi 1bskyod pa dang byed 1pa po yum 11dang bcas //
NK070(thu)001:4484: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgyar ste rigs lnga ldan //
NK070(thu)001:4486: rnam snang yab yum byams pa yab yum sa snying
NK070(thu)001:4487: yab yum de bzhin rigs rnam snang gi gtso byas
NK070(thu)001:4488: pa yin no // lha gzhan dag rang gi rigs
NK070(thu)001:4489: kyi bdag po rang rang gi phyag rgya dbu rgyan
NK070(thu)001:4494: sgrib sel yab yum rnams la /
NK070(thu)001:4497: spyan ras gzigs yab yum kun bzang yab yum la snang mtha' gtso bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:4500: 'jam dpal yab yum rnams la don grub kyis gtso byas pa'i rigs lnga'am /
NK070(thu)001:4501: gshin rje gshed kyi dbu rgyan gyi gtso bo /
NK070(thu)001:4502: la rtag par rnam snang yin par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:4504: de bzhin du stobs chen rin 'byung /
NK070(thu)001:4506: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa la las kyi rigs kyi gtso bo byas par 'dod /
NK070(thu)001:4507: thub pa chen po drug gi dbu rgyan gyi gtso bo rdo rje 'dzin cing 'chang ba //
NK070(thu)001:4509: thub pa drug pa yum med pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:4510: zla dang bral ba dpa' bo che //
NK070(thu)001:4512: gnas gsum gyi yi ge gsum las 'od zer 'phro 'du bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4513: ye shes lnga ldan sarba thams cad ta th+aa ga
NK070(thu)001:4514: ta de bzhin gshegs pa ma h+aa chen po k+aa
NK070(thu)001:4515: ya sku badz+ra rdo rje swa b+ha ba rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:4517: zhes pa de ba thams cad kyi sku'i rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4519: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4522: spyi mgrin snying kha'i gnas gsum khyab 'jug yi ge shad tig g+ho /
NK070(thu)001:4525: 'od zer phar 'phro ba'i tshogs chen po //
NK070(thu)001:4526: khams gsum gyi sgo dang rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi byin 1brlabs gzi 11byin bsdus //
NK070(thu)001:4527: rang bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum rang la gnas pa //
NK070(thu)001:4528: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyud rang de ltar bsgom pa nyer len gyi rgyud /
NK070(thu)001:4529: gnyis tshul gyis ngo bo sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum rang snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:4531: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu ra
NK070(thu)001:4532: ga rjes su chags pa badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma
NK070(thu)001:4533: ko&a ham / de pa'i yon tan gyi nga rgyal dang /
NK070(thu)001:4534: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pu tsa mchod pa badz+ra sam b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK070(thu)001:4535: de pa'i phrin las kyi nga rgyal bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:4539: lte ba dang gsang gnas rnam gnyis la zla ba'i gdan las //
NK070(thu)001:4540: sngo ljang yi ge s+w+aa h+aa gnyis //
NK070(thu)001:4541: kha dog dang rjes su mthun pa de la 'od
NK070(thu)001:4542: zer 'phros pa las yon tan dang phrin las las
NK070(thu)001:4544: yan lag bcu gcig gi lha bdun du rdzogs pa'i gzi byin dang ldan //
NK070(thu)001:4548: thim par gyur gsal bar gyur /
NK070(thu)001:4551: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun du bab pas gnyis su med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:4552: sa thim par gyur pa sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum mngon du snang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:4554: yon tan phrin las kyi yan lag gi lha gnyis
NK070(thu)001:4555: kyi gzi byin dang ldan pas 'od zer 'bar bar
NK070(thu)001:4557: de nas zhi ba rang bzhin lhun gyis grub gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi rnam grangs dang /
NK070(thu)001:4558: gzhan don mdzad pa'i las dang mtshan nyid gcig du ma dang bral bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4559: e ma zhes pa don gyis gsung la ngam ngo
NK070(thu)001:4560: mtshar zhes pa de brda 'phrod pa la ngam rmad
NK070(thu)001:4561: kyis chos // zhes pa gsung gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa la ngam /
NK070(thu)001:4562: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung //
NK070(thu)001:4563: sgra dang ming tshig kun la 'das //
NK070(thu)001:4564: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK070(thu)001:4565: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:4566: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi'i
NK070(thu)001:4567: gzugs can rgyal ba kun gyi bdag nyid drug pa'i
NK070(thu)001:4569: chos can he du khabarjoda bya'i gnas lugs rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:4570: ngo bo sems las nyid gud na 'di 'drar grub
NK070(thu)001:4571: pa med pa'i phyir dam bca' /
NK070(thu)001:4572: snang ba'i ka yi ge dang /
NK070(thu)001:4573: brjod pa'i sgra dang brtags pa'i ming dang mtshon pa'i tshig thams cad kun las 'das te /
NK070(thu)001:4574: brjod pa dang bral ba nyid sna tshogs tshig don
NK070(thu)001:4575: blos bsam pa dang ngag gis brjod pa'i sgra rnams
NK070(thu)001:4576: ma lus pa'i gzhir gnas par gsungs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4578: gsung cig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK070(thu)001:4579: bsam gyis mi khyab kun tu khyab //
NK070(thu)001:4580: sgra dang ming tshig so sor grags //
NK070(thu)001:4581: thams cad gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK070(thu)001:4585: de pa'i drug pa don gyi 1gsung gcig pu de
NK070(thu)001:4586: nyid brjod bya'i dkyil 'khor thams cad rang snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4587: phyir / 1de dag mtshon par byed pa'i yan lag
NK070(thu)001:4588: ni sum brgya drug cu po la sogs pa tshig
NK070(thu)001:4589: gi grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa las 'das par
NK070(thu)001:4590: gdul bya kun tu khyab pa'i sgra dang ming tshig
NK070(thu)001:4591: so sor grags nas snang ba thams cad kyang tshig
NK070(thu)001:4592: re don re mtshon pa las ma 'das pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4593: gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog de pa'i gsung nyid do
NK070(thu)001:4594: phyir / // zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:4595: de nas de nas longs sku bde ba chen po'i gsung /
NK070(thu)001:4596: mngon byang gi gsung gi gsung rdo rje'i gsung dang /
NK070(thu)001:4597: ming gsung gis mtshon pa'i gsung gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4598: rgyud mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK070(thu)001:4599: bde ldan gsung gis don 'byung ba //
NK070(thu)001:4600: thams cad pad+ma'i ngang gyur nas //
NK070(thu)001:4601: kagrol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK070(thu)001:4602: gaci skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK070(thu)001:4603: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:4605: gsang ba'i snying po la rnam rtog gi zug rngu
NK070(thu)001:4606: med pas bde ba chen po'i dang ldan pa gsungs
NK070(thu)001:4608: gang zhe na 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK070(thu)001:4609: pa'i sgra thams cad sems nyid rang snang ba kho
NK070(thu)001:4611: 'khor ba las grol thar ba'i lam myang 'das dang
NK070(thu)001:4612: mthar ba 'khor ba'i sgra skad thams cad la snyan
NK070(thu)001:4613: mi snyan gyis chags sdang so sor 'dzin pa med
NK070(thu)001:4614: na pa thams cad pad+ma'i rang bzhin du gyur nas
NK070(thu)001:4615: phyi nang gi chos yul ci snang gi sgra ci
NK070(thu)001:4616: skad 'don kyang chags sdang gis gos pa med pas
NK070(thu)001:4617: thams cad gsung du gyur pas na /
NK070(thu)001:4618: shin du yangs pa'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:4619: 1bde ba chen po'i phyir gsung mchog ste zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4621: ming mngon par byang chub pa dang rdo rje'i gsung gnyis kyi don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4622: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK070(thu)001:4623: log 'gre thams cad ma lus sgra //
NK070(thu)001:4624: byang chub rdo rje gsung du bsdus //
NK070(thu)001:4625: bsdus nyid phyogs bcur rnam par grags //
NK070(thu)001:4626: grags nyid ma chags ngang du gsung //
NK070(thu)001:4627: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du med //
NK070(thu)001:4629: de pa'i gsung bstan pa theg pa mtho dman gyi sngags mtshan nyid thams cad dang /
NK070(thu)001:4630: log pa mu stegs rtag chad 'gro ba rigs drug
NK070(thu)001:4631: gi sems can ma lus pa thams cad gyi sgra
NK070(thu)001:4632: skad kyi ril thams cad sems nyid yin pas sems
NK070(thu)001:4633: rig pa bdag nyid kyi ye shes chen po'i gsung
NK070(thu)001:4634: du gsal ba ni mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung
NK070(thu)001:4635: zhes bya'o // dus de nyid du grags stong gnyis
NK070(thu)001:4636: su med pas na rdo rje'i gsung du bsdus la
NK070(thu)001:4637: zhes bya'o // / de ltar bsdus pa'i dus de
NK070(thu)001:4638: nyid na phyogs bcu'i gdul bya'i snang ba dang mthun
NK070(thu)001:4640: sgra skad grags pa nyid na ma chags mi 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:4641: pa gnyis med kyi ngang du gsung la de ltar
NK070(thu)001:4642: gsungs pa'i dus nyid na phyogs gcig tu brjod du
NK070(thu)001:4643: med de / mtha' gnyis su mi phyed pa'i phyir rdo rje'i gsung zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4644: tshangs pa'i gsung bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4645: brjod med de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK070(thu)001:4646: kun la grags shing so sor kamjal //
NK070(thu)001:4647: dper gana de bzhin sbrid bsang bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:4648: gsung gcig sgra yis so sor go //
NK070(thu)001:4649: 'di ni gsung mchog rgyal po yin //
NK070(thu)001:4650: theg kha pa mtho dman bsam yas kyang //
NK070(thu)001:4651: de bzhin nyid las ma gsungs te //
NK070(thu)001:4652: 'dul dbang thabs su so sor thos //
NK070(thu)001:4653: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:4654: don gyi gsung brjod du med pa de nyid las
NK070(thu)001:4655: tshig gi gsung sna tshogs pa'i sgra rnams gdul bya
NK070(thu)001:4656: kun la so sor grags shing brda mjal ba'i theg
NK070(thu)001:4657: pa mtho dman bsam yas pa snang ba rnams kyang
NK070(thu)001:4658: de ni / ston pa de bzhin nyid gcig 'ba'
NK070(thu)001:4659: zhig las sam gsung ste des na gsung de nyid
NK070(thu)001:4660: las sgra'i bye brag gi ril thams cad rdzogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:4661: de ni / phyir / gdul bya'i yul ba /
NK070(thu)001:4662: thabs su rang rang gi mos pa bsam pa dang
NK070(thu)001:4663: mthun par ci lta bar so sor thob pa 1ni
NK070(thu)001:4664: / dper na de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das
NK070(thu)001:4665: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa'i sbrid bsangs pa las lha
NK070(thu)001:4667: chung ma gsum las go tshul re re byung ba
NK070(thu)001:4668: lta bu ste mdo sde ting 'dzin rgyal po las
NK070(thu)001:4669: kyang ke'u din zhes bos nas ston pas /
NK070(thu)001:4670: ngas ni chos can gzugs kyi chos nyid de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:4671: nyid 'ba' zhig gsung 'khor theg pa chen po pa
NK070(thu)001:4672: la la ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos so
NK070(thu)001:4673: // 'khor theg pa chung ngu na la la don
NK070(thu)001:4674: par mi stong ste rdul phra rab tu yod zhes
NK070(thu)001:4676: gsang sngags kyi gdul bya la la gzugs tshor ba bde ba zhes bya bar thos so //
NK070(thu)001:4677: nyan rang gis la la ni tshor ba sdug bsngal zhes bya bar thos so //
NK070(thu)001:4678: rtag mi rtag bdag yod med zhes bya ba la sogs pa 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:4679: 'o na sprul pa'i sku sa tshig tu gsungs pa
NK070(thu)001:4680: ltar sku bzhi po gzhan yang tshig gi gsung cig
NK070(thu)001:4682: snyam pa la ci ltar gsung rab kun brjod kyang /
NK070(thu)001:4683: de bzhin nyid kyis gsungs pa med //
NK070(thu)001:4685: longs spyod kyi ston pa'i gdul bya la bstan pa
NK070(thu)001:4686: ji ltar gsang sngags kyi gsung rab kyi chos rnams
NK070(thu)001:4687: kun kyang / tshigs su brjod nas snang mod kyi
NK070(thu)001:4688: de bzhin gshegs pas de nyid kyi don la gsungs
NK070(thu)001:4690: 'o na ci'i phyir gdul bya'i blo la snang snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:4691: ming gsum pa'i rig pa'i gsung mnga' bar ston pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4692: yi ge med dang rig pa'i gsung //
NK070(thu)001:4693: ljags kyi rtse mor ma phyung yang //
NK070(thu)001:4694: thugs rje'i gsung gi byin brlabs kyis //
NK070(thu)001:4695: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor gsal //
NK070(thu)001:4696: gsal nyid gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK070(thu)001:4698: rig pa'i gsung ni rig pa kho na'i yin pa
NK070(thu)001:4699: phyir yi ge dang bral bas med pa nyid yin
NK070(thu)001:4700: pas ljags kyi sgrar brjod du med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4701: sa rtse mor ma byung ba /
NK070(thu)001:4702: thugs rig pa nyid spros pa dang bral ba /
NK070(thu)001:4703: des chos thams cad du khyab pa rje chos nyid
NK070(thu)001:4704: sems kyis zin pa zin gyis sgra ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:4705: sems bdag nyid chen po'i ngang du lhun gyi grub
NK070(thu)001:4706: pa'i phyi rig pa gsung gi byin brlab kyis ni
NK070(thu)001:4709: gdul bya'i 'gro ba rang rang de bsam pa gzhan
NK070(thu)001:4710: ni don sna tshogs so sor brda dus gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:4711: gsal ba sprod par byed pa gsal pa'i dus nyid
NK070(thu)001:4712: na'ang rang bzhin las ma g.yos pa ni gsung gi
NK070(thu)001:4714: drug pa'i gsung du 'gyur ro zhe'o //
NK070(thu)001:4715: de bzhin gsung gi 'gro don rnams //
NK070(thu)001:4716: de bzhin ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK070(thu)001:4717: dper na brag cha'i dgra bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:4720: bshad pa de bzhin du gsung gi sgo nas 'gro
NK070(thu)001:4721: don byed pa rnams kyang de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK070(thu)001:4722: las g.yos kyang rtsis pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4723: ston pas tshig so sor brjod du med bzhin du gdul bya ba brjod par snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4724: dper na brag cha'i sgra ni /
NK070(thu)001:4726: bos pa ltar thos kyang dngos po la brag gis smra ba med bzhin no //
NK070(thu)001:4727: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang gsang sngags kyi le'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4728: gsung sngags gi dkyil 'khor ci snyed pa'ang /
NK070(thu)001:4729: gsung lnga kho nar bsdus pa'i lnga'i ngo bo dang /
NK070(thu)001:4730: gzhan don mdzad pa'i las dang /
NK070(thu)001:4733: 1lha 1rnams kyi bskyed pa'i sngags kyi ngo bo dang
NK070(thu)001:4734: las kyis rim pa'i sngags rnams bshad pa'i le'u ste
NK070(thu)001:4736: lha'i phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:4737: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK070(thu)001:4738: yan lag thams cad dkyil 'khor lhun grub tu byin gyis brlabs par /
NK070(thu)001:4740: yan lag ni 11gnyis kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:4741: 1lus kyi yan lag mgo bo la sogs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:4743: 1rtog pa'i yan lag phung po lnga dang khams skye mched la sogs pa'o zhe gnyis pa /
NK070(thu)001:4744: de 11dag thams cad rigs lnga la sogs pa'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:4745: 'khor du ye nas lhun gyis grub par gnas pa
NK070(thu)001:4746: ni / rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya yin te //
NK070(thu)001:4747: rgyas pa'i rgyud don drug pa las /
NK070(thu)001:4748: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK070(thu)001:4750: 1phyi nang 'byung ba lnga dang snod bcud phung po lnga /
NK070(thu)001:4752: rigs lnga bde gshegs yab 1yum gyi //
NK070(thu)001:4753: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du ye nas gnas //
NK070(thu)001:4755: gnas pa de dag yin pa de ltar du lam pa gang gis ngo shes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4758: de ltar du rig nas ting nge 'dzin gyis goms brtan par byas pa las /
NK070(thu)001:4759: gzhan nas ched du ma brtsal bar thams cad du snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4761: de ltar du byin gyis brlabs pa bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4762: de las rang bzhin lta ba ting nge 'dzin 'bras
NK070(thu)001:4763: bu'i phyag rgya gsum thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:4764: / sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:4765: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK070(thu)001:4768: thams cad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i te lha yab yum
NK070(thu)001:4769: zung du 'brel pa dkyil 'khor du ye nas mngon
NK070(thu)001:4770: gsum du gsal bar rjogs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4771: dbang po'i spyod yul du ci snang ba'i ril thams
NK070(thu)001:4772: cad lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo nyid las 'da'
NK070(thu)001:4774: gzhi rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4775: 1de nyid rtog pas de ltar gyur pa ni rtogs pa lha ba'i phyag rgya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4776: 1de dag lam gyis mngon du gyur pas rtog tshogs
NK070(thu)001:4777: thams cad rir lnga drug pa kun po la sogs
NK070(thu)001:4780: de gsum dang ldan pa de ga ni byang chub mchog gis phyag rgya ste /
NK070(thu)001:4782: gsum po de dag rgyud gang gi gzhung gis ston snyam pa las /
NK070(thu)001:4783: kagsang ba de kho nar ganyid nges pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:4784: gzhung gis ston pa'i kha snying po'i ngaphyag rgya 'di ni nges tshig 'da' daka'o //
NK070(thu)001:4786: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya 'byung ba'i 00rgyu gnyis bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4787: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK070(thu)001:4788: rin chen zla ba dkyil yi ge //
NK070(thu)001:4789: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las //
NK070(thu)001:4790: sbyor ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK070(thu)001:4792: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis ni g.yas mi bskyod rdo
NK070(thu)001:4793: rje dang g.yon rin po che'i rigs kyis rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:4794: kho na'i gung mo dang mdzub mo dang /
NK070(thu)001:4795: mthe bong dang srin lag mathe'u chung gi bre ga rnams la /
NK070(thu)001:4796: g.yas par nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor g.yon par zla ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4797: dkyil 'khor sran ma sleb pa tsam rnams kyi steng
NK070(thu)001:4798: la / g.yas su gung mo la h'u dang mdzub mo la mthe bong 'am srin lag la s+w+aa /
NK070(thu)001:4799: srin lag gam mthe bong la am /
NK070(thu)001:4800: mathe'u chung la ha rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:4801: g.yon du gong mo la yum la sogs pa bsgom ste de'ang mdzub mo la lam /
NK070(thu)001:4802: mthe bong ngam srin lag la mam /
NK070(thu)001:4803: srin lag gam mthe bong la pyam /
NK070(thu)001:4806: 'od du zhu ba las lha rigs lnga yab yum
NK070(thu)001:4807: so so'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya rdo rje la
NK070(thu)001:4809: lag gnyis de dag g.yas g.yon gyi sor mo zung du sprod pa las thad kar sbyar ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:4810: dngos grub blang ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4811: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyor te /
NK070(thu)001:4812: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK070(thu)001:4813: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:4814: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK070(thu)001:4816: dngos grub blang ba'i phyag rgya ste /
NK070(thu)001:4817: rang gi ngo bo rngam glog gam thabs zhag gis rgyud nyid las dang mum du rtse sbyar te //
NK070(thu)001:4818: de bzhin h'u dang lam du sbyar //
NK070(thu)001:4819: ham dang pyam yang de bzhin te //
NK070(thu)001:4820: am dang tam du sbyar ba las //
NK070(thu)001:4821: rgyab sbyar swa dang mam sbrengs pa //
NK070(thu)001:4822: 'di ni yab kyis spyi rgya yin //
NK070(thu)001:4823: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba las //
NK070(thu)001:4824: dang mum sbyar h'u dang ni //
NK070(thu)001:4825: lam sbyar s+w+aa dang pyam du sbyar //
NK070(thu)001:4826: dang mum sbyar ha tam sbrengs //
NK070(thu)001:4827: yum gyis spyi rgya yin par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:4829: g.yas pa'i mdzub mo'i dang g.yon gyi gong mo'i mum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK070(thu)001:4830: g.yas kyi gong mo'i h'u dang g.yon gyi mdzub mo'i lam gnyis sprad de /
NK070(thu)001:4832: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas so sor rtse sprad pa ni
NK070(thu)001:4833: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rigs lnga po kun dang
NK070(thu)001:4834: mnyam sbyor ba'i bde ba chen po'i dngos grub blang
NK070(thu)001:4835: ba'i sa rang gi rgyud la sbyin pa phyag rgya'o
NK070(thu)001:4836: // de dag kyang gdul bya'i snang bas gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:4838: mi bskyod pa ni gsang ba'i rdo rje rtse steng phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga'i rtsa /
NK070(thu)001:4840: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lnga po'i steng na zla'i ba thig le yab lnga'i yi ge lnga'i dngos //
NK070(thu)001:4842: yum gyi pad+ma dgod do 'byung bas rin chen par bu'i 'dab ma nyi ma lnga la //
NK070(thu)001:4844: gdan zla ba'i la nyi ma thig le yum gyi yi ge lnga nyid //
NK070(thu)001:4845: de ltar yum gyi thig le thabs dang shes rab lnga phrag gnyis po rnams //
NK070(thu)001:4846: phan tshun zung du 'phrad pa'i dus la bde ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK070(thu)001:4848: ngo bo phyag rgya chen po'i bde stong gi dngos grub 'byung //
NK070(thu)001:4850: yum gyi 1dbyings dang yab kyi 2ye shes kyi bdag po nyid //
NK070(thu)001:4852: 1 dang 2mum du rang bzhin ye nas gnas //
NK070(thu)001:4853: rdo rje 1rwa ste de gnyis rtse sbyor bas /
NK070(thu)001:4854: bzhi dang pad+ma'i 1'dab ma'i 11thig le rnams //
NK070(thu)001:4856: rang rang gi gnas kyi g.yas g.yon mdun rgyab tu bsnol mar 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:4857: zla'i thig le gnyis rab tu 'dres par gyur pa las //
NK070(thu)001:4859: rgyal ba'i kun gyis dgongs pa /
NK070(thu)001:4860: thugs ye shes kyi dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i bde ba chen po //
NK070(thu)001:4861: nyams su myongs phyir thob pa sbyin par 'gro ba'i phyag rgya zhes su gsungs //
NK070(thu)001:4863: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK070(thu)001:4864: h'u khabsgreng kartse mor rdo rje ga'bar //
NK070(thu)001:4865: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK070(thu)001:4866: 'grel ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK070(thu)001:4867: zhes bya ba la sogs pas /
NK070(thu)001:4868: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis so so'i phyag rgya bstan te /
NK070(thu)001:4869: rang d+hor sems su bsgom pa sku phyag rgya chen
NK070(thu)001:4870: po g.yas pa'i rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis khu tshur
NK070(thu)001:4871: du byas pas 'bru bzhi sbas pa las /
NK070(thu)001:4872: gong mo gyen du bsgreng ba'i thugs kar gtad nas bkan la /
NK070(thu)001:4873: de'i rtse mo'i h'u bsam pa ni chos rgya de
NK070(thu)001:4874: nyid rdo rje lnga 0par 'od 'bar ba gyur pa
NK070(thu)001:4875: ni phyag rgya 0bcings pa dang phyag mtshan 0bsam pa
NK070(thu)001:4876: gnyis 11ka dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4877: g.yon pa zla ba'i gdan lnga bskul zhing yum gyi
NK070(thu)001:4878: yi ge 'bru rnams spas pa ni gong du bshad
NK070(thu)001:4879: pa'i gnod sbyin khu tshur du gnas pa'i dril bu
NK070(thu)001:4880: bsil zhing rang sgra dang bcas pas yum la 'khril
NK070(thu)001:4881: ba'i tshul gyis 'khyud nas barla g.yon pa chos kyi
NK070(thu)001:4882: rig la bzhag nas khu tshur dkur brten pa ni
NK070(thu)001:4883: / 1bcings pa dang de ltar ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa 1bsam pa'i las kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK070(thu)001:4884: ci zhe na phyag rgya de yab yum thabs dang shes rab 'khril bar snyom par 'jug cing /
NK070(thu)001:4885: sbyor bar 'di las byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:4886: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs par gsal ba phyag len sngags brjod pa chos rgya /
NK070(thu)001:4887: spyi bca' ba'i gnas bsgyur ba'i sa /
NK070(thu)001:4888: bkrol ba'i thabs dang gsum gsum du sbyar /
NK070(thu)001:4889: g.yon gyi yi ge 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar gyen du bkan //
NK070(thu)001:4891: mum bsgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK070(thu)001:4893: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK070(thu)001:4896: gong mo'i rtse mo'i mum nyid 'od du zhu ba
NK070(thu)001:4897: las de bkan thabs su bsgrid pa'i dril bu'i 'od
NK070(thu)001:4899: sgra dang bcas par gyur pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4901: bsam pa'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:4902: g.yas kyi sor mo'i nyi ma 'bru lnga la du ste phyag rgya bsnol mar /
NK070(thu)001:4903: yab la 'khril cing 'khyud pa ni btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta'o //
NK070(thu)001:4904: de la bcings pa dang bsam pa'i las kyi phyag rgya gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:4905: rigs bzhi yang rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag rgya de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4906: ut+pala klu shing la sogs ya mtshan /
NK070(thu)001:4907: zhes bya ba sogs pa ni sems dpa' dang sems
NK070(thu)001:4908: ma sgo ba yab yum rnams kyi dam tshig dang
NK070(thu)001:4909: las kyi phyag rgya gnyis po de thams cad de
NK070(thu)001:4910: ma gtogs pa'i g.yas g.yon so so'i sor mo bzhi
NK070(thu)001:4911: bzhi la / g.yas nyi ma g.yon zla'i ba steng
NK070(thu)001:4912: du 1yab 1yum so so'i yi ge ste g.yas la
NK070(thu)001:4913: k+shem tram hri dz+him bzhi g.yon du h'u tram h+r+ai
NK070(thu)001:4914: +aah bzhi bkod de phyag rgya bca' lugs dang bsam
NK070(thu)001:4915: pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni rjes su mthun pa kho
NK070(thu)001:4916: bzhi la / na'i phyir / dang po sa snying gi phyag rgya ni /
NK070(thu)001:4917: 'bru gsum sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK070(thu)001:4918: k+shi gram pa rtse mor myu gu 'bar //
NK070(thu)001:4919: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK070(thu)001:4920: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK070(thu)001:4921: gzhan la'ang de ltar du shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:4922: yum rnams kyi las kyi phyag rgya yab kyi mgul
NK070(thu)001:4923: la 'khril zhing yab rnams kyi yum la 'khril ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4924: barla g.yon pa chos kyi rigs la la brten //
NK070(thu)001:4926: yab kyi dbu rnams yum la 'phyo zhing yum gyi dbu yab la 'dud pa'i tshul //
NK070(thu)001:4928: gong gi rigs lnga yab yum gyi phyag rgya chen po bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:4930: gnyis med mnyam pa'i dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril //
NK070(thu)001:4933: lha kun kyang zhal 'dzum pa dang chas pas /
NK070(thu)001:4934: yab yum phan tshun gcig gi gcig la bltas shing 'khyud pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:4935: de dag kyang gdul bya'i snang bas gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:4937: yab kyi rdo rje'i phyogs kyi thig le 'bru bzhi
NK070(thu)001:4938: dbus su sbas nas bsdus pas thig le gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:4939: 'gyur ba de rlung gi gnas su bsdus pas thugs
NK070(thu)001:4941: rdo rje'i rtse mor thig le h'u gi rnam par
NK070(thu)001:4942: sgreng ba'i rdo rje'i zhal gyi lam rtsa bzhi dag
NK070(thu)001:4943: gang ste bde ba h'u du gsal zhing rgyas pa
NK070(thu)001:4944: la phyag rgya rdo rje 'bar ba zhes pa'i sgra
NK070(thu)001:4945: / zla ba'i thig le btul zhing nyi mas bsgribs te sbangs pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:4946: chu skyes pad ma bde bas rab tu rgyas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:4947: kyem kun d+harma sgra sgrags pas dril bu'i gsil ba sgra dang ldan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:4948: rdo rje'am thig le gnyis shor gnyis mnyam phyed byung
NK070(thu)001:4949: bas 'khril ba'i tshul gyis rol pa'i gar bskyod pa
NK070(thu)001:4950: / dus su rlung gis bzung bas phyed yum gyi mkhar /
NK070(thu)001:4951: ltung ba med pa'i phyir bde ba'i ye shes brten pas chos la brten par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:4952: yum yang yab kyi zla ba'i thig le'i las byed
NK070(thu)001:4953: dang dam tshig gi rjes su mthun te 'bru bzhi
NK070(thu)001:4956: dril bu yum gyi thig le nyi ma 'bru lnga
NK070(thu)001:4957: phyed kyi yab yum las la 'khril cing sbyor ba'i
NK070(thu)001:4958: dus su bde ba dgyes pa //
NK070(thu)001:4959: ni btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta zhes so //
NK070(thu)001:4960: de'i dus snang stong ngam 'khor 'das kyi mtha' gnyis mnon cing mi gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK070(thu)001:4962: chos sku'am phyag rgya chen por lha'i yin pa de rgyud nas brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:4964: 'gro drug 'dul ba thub drug gi phyag rgya ni
NK070(thu)001:4965: gcig tu ma nges par sna tshogs dang mthun pa
NK070(thu)001:4966: te // mdor bsdus na 'gro drug 'dul pa'i thabs su phyag rgya drug tu bstan pa yin no //
NK070(thu)001:4968: le'u drug par pi wang dang ni sreg par dang /
NK070(thu)001:4969: go cha po ti rin chen sgrom //
NK070(thu)001:4970: me dang chu ni rab tu bstan //
NK070(thu)001:4972: thub drug de dag lha gzhan kun ltar yab yum phan tshun 'khyud par ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4973: rtags kyi yum ni du dmigs su med /
NK070(thu)001:4975: 'o na yum med na rgyud 'di'i gzhung gis ltar
NK070(thu)001:4976: du mi 'gyur ro snyam du dgos pa la len
NK070(thu)001:4979: dngos po gang yang rang bzhin phyogs gcig ma skyes pa nyid chos kyi dbyings kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:4980: de don gyi yum nyid yin pas gang du yang dgongs pa chos dbyings dang ma bral ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:4981: rgyas pa la snang ba mi 'gog la thabs yab yin te /
NK070(thu)001:4982: rang bzhin med pa ni shes rab bo //
NK070(thu)001:4985: kun bzang mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK070(thu)001:4986: yum gyur mnyam rdzogs pad+mo'i dkyil //
NK070(thu)001:4987: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK070(thu)001:4988: yang na de bzhin gshegs nyid dam //
NK070(thu)001:4989: yang na rdo rje thal mo nyid //
NK070(thu)001:4991: kun tu bzang po'i phyag g.yon gyi thog tu g.yas
NK070(thu)001:4992: mnyam par bzhag pa las sor mo lnga po kun
NK070(thu)001:4993: la ye shes lnga'i 'od du 'phro ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:4994: yum gyi phyag rgya ni de las 'gyur bas ma nges te /
NK070(thu)001:4995: g.yas pa'i thog tu g.yon pa mnyam pa bar bzhag
NK070(thu)001:4996: pa la chos thams cad rdzogs pas mthe bong rtse
NK070(thu)001:4997: sprad de pad mo'i dkyil ltar byas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:4998: phyag rgya gnyis ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:4999: ste yang na de bzhin gshegs pa kun bzang dang rjes su mthun pa nyid dam /
NK070(thu)001:5000: yang na rdo rje thal mo rtse sprad pa de nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:5002: gzhan yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK070(thu)001:5003: chos khams dril bu thugs kar brten //
NK070(thu)001:5005: don chos nyid cir yang snang ba'i phyir phyag rgya gcig du ma nges par sna tshogs so //
NK070(thu)001:5006: lta ba'i phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:5007: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog ni //
NK070(thu)001:5008: thabs dang shes rab 'byor ldan na //
NK070(thu)001:5009: ma bskyod ma bsgul thams cad kun //
NK070(thu)001:5010: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK070(thu)001:5012: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs kyi ril
NK070(thu)001:5013: thams cad lha yab yum sku gsung thugs kyi phyag
NK070(thu)001:5014: rgya chen po par snang ba tshogs mchog ye nas
NK070(thu)001:5016: thabs snang la 'gag pa med pa dang shes rab
NK070(thu)001:5017: mi 'dzin par 'i don de dang gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:5018: pa gsal zhing ldan par 'byor ba'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:5019: lus ma bskyod cing ma bsgul ba la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:5020: sgo gsum ci byas pa dang ma byas pa thams
NK070(thu)001:5021: cad kun kyang sku gsung thugs las 'da' ba med
NK070(thu)001:5022: par phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas pa ni
NK070(thu)001:5025: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK070(thu)001:5026: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5027: lus kyi yan lag dang rtog pa'i yan lag las
NK070(thu)001:5028: 'dir rtog pa'i yan lag byin gyis brlabs ston te
NK070(thu)001:5029: / rtsa ba dang bdag tu lta ba'i las byung
NK070(thu)001:5030: ba yan lag rtog pa rnams spros pa bsgom pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5031: rnal 'byor pa yab yum zung zhig la yang bzhi
NK070(thu)001:5032: bcu rtsa gnyis yod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5033: de yang rtsa ba'i lha mi bskyod pa yab yum
NK070(thu)001:5034: gyi mig la sogs pa rtog pa'i so so gnas
NK070(thu)001:5035: su yab la yab bco brgyad rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5036: yum la yum bco brgyad rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5037: yab la thub pa drug rnams te yab nyer bzhi po gsal bar bkod de bsgom pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5039: de ni thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5040: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste /
NK070(thu)001:5042: thabs kyi lha yan lag spros pa bzhi bcu po
NK070(thu)001:5043: de dag nyid kyi kho na dang kha dog mtshungs
NK070(thu)001:5044: pa'i ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang pa re re
NK070(thu)001:5045: nges par snying la gnas te phra ba'i cha nas
NK070(thu)001:5046: shes rab bo // bdag ste zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:5047: gong du bshad pa'i lha brgyad cu po rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5048: 'og tu 'chad pa'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum
NK070(thu)001:5049: gyi lha brgya nyi shu ste gnyis brgya bo rnams
NK070(thu)001:5050: la / rigs kyi bdag nyid dbu rgyan rigs kyi
NK070(thu)001:5051: lha lnga lngas dbang bskur bas dbu rgyan gyi gtso
NK070(thu)001:5052: bo bdag po rigs so sos mtshon pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:5053: la / // de dag ni ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor te dbu rgyan gyi lha stong kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5056: lus la bkod pa 'i thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:5057: la sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum gsum 'aphro'o //
NK070(thu)001:5059: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK070(thu)001:5061: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso bo mi bskyod pa yab yum la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor stong /
NK070(thu)001:5062: thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu sku gsung
NK070(thu)001:5063: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i lha brgya
NK070(thu)001:5064: nyi shu'o // de dag mngon du gsal ba ni rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin mchog go //
NK070(thu)001:5065: gtso bo de las 'khor gyi lha gzhan la'ang stong stong bsgom par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5066: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin du //
NK070(thu)001:5069: kun tu bzang po ni rigs kyi bdag po'i yin pa phyir rgyal mchog ste /
NK070(thu)001:5070: de ltar lha yab yum bcu la yang rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:5071: sems dpa' yab yum la de ltar du bkod pa
NK070(thu)001:5072: bzhin du bsgom stong stong mo zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5074: zhes bya ba ni yab yum bcu gnyis pa phrag
NK070(thu)001:5075: gnyis kyis sems dpa' yab yum dang sgo ba yab
NK070(thu)001:5076: yum rnams la yang de ltar gsal ba la /
NK070(thu)001:5077: 'od rim las dbu rgyan med par bshad de /
NK070(thu)001:5079: thub drug re re la yang g.yas kyi cha las
NK070(thu)001:5080: yab g.yon gyi cha las yum 'am yang na 'khril
NK070(thu)001:5081: sbyor bsgom la de ltar stong stong gsal ba ni
NK070(thu)001:5082: / 'i lha rnams 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar bar bsgom pa /
NK070(thu)001:5083: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5084: de la sogs pa bsam mi khyab //
NK070(thu)001:5085: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas su //
NK070(thu)001:5086: 'dul ba'i don rnams so sor ston //
NK070(thu)001:5088: nyi khri bzhi stong po de dag sgoms pa las
NK070(thu)001:5089: su rung nas phyi nang gi dngos po ril lha'i
NK070(thu)001:5090: dkyil 'khor du ma gyur pa stong gsum nam mkha'
NK070(thu)001:5091: chos dbyings kyis khyab tshad ltar gsal rigs gsum gyi
NK070(thu)001:5092: yul yin / med pa sa de la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:5093: snod bcud thams cad sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:5095: des phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i gdul bya
NK070(thu)001:5096: ma lus pa'i gnas bsam yas rnams su gong ltar
NK070(thu)001:5097: lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyis gdul bya ba'i don rnams
NK070(thu)001:5098: mos pa ltar so sor ston cing /
NK070(thu)001:5099: re ba skong par byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:5100: 'o na lhar snang na don byed pa'i gzhi de'i
NK070(thu)001:5101: phyir lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba kho nas don
NK070(thu)001:5102: byed do snyam pa du dgos la /
NK070(thu)001:5103: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK070(thu)001:5104: phyin ci log rnams bsam yas dang //
NK070(thu)001:5105: so sor mthun byas kun tu snang //
NK070(thu)001:5107: theg pa mtho ba gsang sngags dang dman pa mtshan
NK070(thu)001:5108: nyid pa thams cad mu stegs rtag chad la sogs
NK070(thu)001:5109: pa phyin ci log pa rnams bsam yas pa dang
NK070(thu)001:5110: mthun par theg pa che chung la sogs so so'i
NK070(thu)001:5113: bdud dang srin po la sogs pa zhi ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:5114: khro bo'i tshogs chen thams cad yul bya rang rang
NK070(thu)001:5115: gang la mos pa ltar so sor bsam yas dang
NK070(thu)001:5116: mthun par byas pa kun tu snang bas gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:5118: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las sa khams gsum gyi zhing /
NK070(thu)001:5120: byang chub sems dpa' chen po ba rdzu 'phrul ston par byed pa //
NK070(thu)001:5122: 2dus reg g+ha zhig la mngon par byang chub pa dus res g+ha yab yum gyis lhums //
NK070(thu)001:5123: su zhugs res g+ha zhi ba zhi ba la ris g+ha drag /
NK070(thu)001:5124: po la drag po res g+ha zhig la gdon chen po bgegs ltar du mdzad de //
NK070(thu)001:5125: de la sogs pa mdzad pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5126: res 'dul ba la ri dang skye bo thams cad do //
NK070(thu)001:5127: gyis 'dul ba la skye bar mdzad zhes 'byung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:5128: gzhan don de dag kyang ched du rtsol bar byed pa la yin te /
NK070(thu)001:5129: ston pa rang la lhun gyis grub pa nyid gnyan po kun tu snang nas don byed ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5130: de ni dper na gar mkhan nyid dang 'dra bas /
NK070(thu)001:5131: lus la ma g.yos pa gar gyi bkod pa sna tshogs ston //
NK070(thu)001:5134: phyag rgya'i rnam grangs ma nges par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:5135: mdor na phyag rgya thams cad ni //
NK070(thu)001:5136: 'di zhes gcig tu brjod du med //
NK070(thu)001:5137: gnyis dang gsum du rnam par 'phro //
NK070(thu)001:5138: bskyed dang spro ba de bzhin te //
NK070(thu)001:5140: phyag rgya 'i ril thams cad tshig gis mdor bsdus na /
NK070(thu)001:5141: lus kyis yan lag gis phyag rgya thams cad bskyed pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5142: kun kyang bya ba mo'i kun tu bzang mo phyag
NK070(thu)001:5143: rgya ltar 'i kho na zhes cig tu zhes nges
NK070(thu)001:5145: lus kyi yan lag gi dbang du zhabs gnyis dang
NK070(thu)001:5146: 1dbu phyag gnyis dang gsum ste de ltar du lus
NK070(thu)001:5147: kyi yan lag lnga po re re la yang rigs
NK070(thu)001:5148: lnga yab yum bcu ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par
NK070(thu)001:5149: gyur pa las phyag rgya lnga bcur yang 'phro bar
NK070(thu)001:5150: 'gyur ro // yang na rtog pa'i yan lag rnam
NK070(thu)001:5151: par spro ba'i dbang du phyag rgya la yang thabs
NK070(thu)001:5152: kyi lha bzhi bcu la sku gsung thugs gsum dang
NK070(thu)001:5153: gsum dang ldan pas brgya nyi shu thabs dang shes
NK070(thu)001:5154: rab gnyis kyis lha brgya dang thabs shes rab dang
NK070(thu)001:5155: sku gsung thugs kyi lha de dag la dbu rgyan
NK070(thu)001:5156: ye shes kyi phyag rgya stong dang la sogs par
NK070(thu)001:5157: 'i sgras nyi khri bzhi stong dang bsam yas lhun
NK070(thu)001:5158: 'gyur ro // gyis grub pa / rnam par 'phro bas de ltar lus bskyed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5159: ting nge 'dzin spro ba lha'i phyag rgya'i grangs ni de bzhin du ma nges pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5160: mdor na bsgul bskyod thams cad kun //
NK070(thu)001:5161: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK070(thu)001:5162: gnas nyid mi gnas gnas pa med //
NK070(thu)001:5163: de skad dag mchog nyid kyis bshad //
NK070(thu)001:5165: grangs de lta bus mtshon nas /
NK070(thu)001:5166: phyag rgya brjod kyis mi lang ba'i grangs rnams tshig gis mdor bsdus na /
NK070(thu)001:5167: lus bsgul zhing bskyod pa thams cad kun gzhi rang
NK070(thu)001:5168: bzhin gyi phyag rgya gnas pa de rtogs lta ba'i
NK070(thu)001:5169: phyag rgya mngon du byas na /
NK070(thu)001:5170: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgyas gsal bar bsgom pa'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:5171: lus ngag gis ci snang ci byas pa thams cad
NK070(thu)001:5172: bdag nyid chen po lha'i sku gsung thugs kho na
NK070(thu)001:5173: las mi 'da' bar phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du
NK070(thu)001:5174: gnas na / de tsam du'ang gnas pa nyid na
NK070(thu)001:5175: blos mi 'dzin pas mi gnas pa dang gnas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5176: tha snyad med pas na phyag rgya lhun gyis grub
NK070(thu)001:5177: par byin gyis brlabs pa zhes bya ba /
NK070(thu)001:5178: de skad ni spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i rgyal mchog kun bzang nyid kyis bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:5181: de dag nyid kho na'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5182: lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag thams cad phyag rgya gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlab nas /
NK070(thu)001:5183: yan lag gi phyag rgya rnam grangs spros pa zhes gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:5184: le'u brgyad pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:5186: // lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK070(thu)001:5187: dkyil 'khor de'i rjes su lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi
NK070(thu)001:5188: dkyil 'khor rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5189: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:5190: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:5191: spyir thun mong gi dga' ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:5193: dga' ba'i dga' 1 ba dag ste /
NK070(thu)001:5194: rim pa de dag gi don 1ni 'dod pa'i khams kyi 'khrigs pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5195: nye bar longs spyod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5196: gzugs khams bsam gtan bzhi dang dga' bde sa dang
NK070(thu)001:5197: po rab tu dga' ba 1mthong lam ba rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:5199: 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5200: thugs su chud pa dgyes pa'i dga' ba ni snga
NK070(thu)001:5201: ma gsum las ltos pa tsam ma yin gyi 'khor
NK070(thu)001:5202: 'das mnyam pa nyid la spang blang med par longs
NK070(thu)001:5203: spyod pas rang gi ngo bos kyang chen po yin
NK070(thu)001:5204: ba ste / kun tu bzang po'i mtshan don gyi gnas skabs las btags pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:5205: rdo rje gsang ba'i dam tshig bkod pa /
NK070(thu)001:5207: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:5208: gyi sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya thams cad ye
NK070(thu)001:5209: shes rdo rje'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa de
NK070(thu)001:5210: phal gyis blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas gsang
NK070(thu)001:5211: don de mtshon cing 'bras bu de la sbyor ba
NK070(thu)001:5212: las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig ni 1lhag pa gzugs
NK070(thu)001:5214: de dag gi bsnyen pa sa mchog gi las kyi rim pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5218: bzhugs gnas bskyed pa'i rim pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5219: de'i 'bras bu'i gnyis po bar rnams gsal bar bkod
NK070(thu)001:5220: pa ston pa'i rgyur nye bar gnas pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:5221: // gzhan don dbang dang dkyil 'khor nye bar ston
NK070(thu)001:5222: pa'i le'u dgu pa 'di yang lnga pa ltar rgyud
NK070(thu)001:5223: kyi rim pa ring du spangs te 'khrugs ldebs nas
NK070(thu)001:5224: man ngag gi rdo rje las rim rim pa la
NK070(thu)001:5226: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5229: nye bar ston pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nyid kyang shin tu phra ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK070(thu)001:5231: shin tu phra la sbyangs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:5232: bsam yas dag la'ang de bzhin bya //
NK070(thu)001:5234: tshig 'di ni don zur gnyis pa kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:5235: gzhan don du dbang bskur nye bar byed pa'i bla mas sngon du bsnyen pa bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:5236: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum la blo sbyangs te /
NK070(thu)001:5237: rgyas pa'i le'u nyer gnyis las 'byung ba'i phra ba'i yi ge phyag mtshan sku'i /
NK070(thu)001:5238: dkyil 'khor dang gsum la phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting
NK070(thu)001:5239: nge 'dzin gyis goms nas sngags kyi bzlas pa gras
NK070(thu)001:5240: dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa gang rung rdzogs par bya
NK070(thu)001:5241: ba la mi 'da' bas dam tshig mchog kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:5243: de nas gnas brtag pa'i bzang por rung pa'i cho
NK070(thu)001:5244: ga bya ba'i phyir yang gdams ka ni rgyud 'khrugs
NK070(thu)001:5245: pa sdebs pa'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5246: ma 'khrugs pa'i dbang du byas pa gnyis na sa gzhi rab tu bsnyams la /
NK070(thu)001:5255: bsrung ba rnams mngon par rtogs pa rdo rje las rim nas 'byung ba ltar sbyang bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5256: de nas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gi tshad bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5257: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK070(thu)001:5258: yang na lus gang tshad du'am //
NK070(thu)001:5259: yang na lus ni gsum gyis tshad //
NK070(thu)001:5261: sgyu 'phrul bsdus pa'i lha bco brgyad pa dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:5262: ni gtso bo stong yab dang dpyal yum gnyis la
NK070(thu)001:5264: de'i tshad la dkyil 'khor logs re la khru gang
NK070(thu)001:5265: gi tshad du bya ba ngam yang na lus gang
NK070(thu)001:5266: gi tshad kyi khru bzhi par bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:5268: ru phyag gzo ba mi bzo'i sbyor ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:5270: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:5271: de'i tshad la lus gsum gyi tshad du byed pa ste logs re la khru bcu gnyis sam /
NK070(thu)001:5273: yang na logs re la khru ni bcu drug dang /
NK070(thu)001:5274: zhes bya ba dang gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:5275: dkyil 'khor logs re la khru nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lngar bya /
NK070(thu)001:5277: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshad gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:5279: de dag las nang du lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:5280: goms pas phyi rol du thig tshan gyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:5281: du snang bas gzugs brnyan gyi tshad bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:5282: / yang na gzhu 'dom lnga brgya rgyang grags de brgyad dpag tshad dam /
NK070(thu)001:5283: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK070(thu)001:5284: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor sna tshogs bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:5286: gsum po de yang dgos pa mthon dman yod par sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK070(thu)001:5287: slob dpon mthar thug sangs rgyas la /
NK070(thu)001:5288: nye 'am mthar lam rig 'dzin la nye ba /
NK070(thu)001:5289: spros pa dang tshogs sgrub kyi lam la gnas pas rnal 'byor pa /
NK070(thu)001:5290: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad rgyang grags dang dpag tshad dam nam mkha' dbyings /
NK070(thu)001:5292: rdo rje'i thig gi tshad dor tsam gyis /
NK070(thu)001:5293: lha'i sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar ldang ba /
NK070(thu)001:5294: dkyil 'khor sna tshogs kyi tshad kyi nang nas mchog tu gsungs /
NK070(thu)001:5296: rgyas pa las dpag pas mchog gi yang mchog gi dkyil 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:5297: slob bu drod dang ldan pas las dag pa rnams kyi snang ngo'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:5298: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum de dag las gang byed kyang las dang bya ba sbyar nas /
NK070(thu)001:5299: sa bsrung ba la sbyar ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5300: 'bru lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NK070(thu)001:5301: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK070(thu)001:5302: bdud rtsi lnga ni rab bsnyams la //
NK070(thu)001:5303: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK070(thu)001:5305: gzhan sel ba'i dgos pa phung po lnga dag pa
NK070(thu)001:5306: don du gnyer ba'i sku lnga thob par bya ba'i
NK070(thu)001:5307: phyir 'bru ni nas sran gro 'bras til lnga dang
NK070(thu)001:5308: / gzhan la des 'dres yum lnga'am dbang po lnga
NK070(thu)001:5309: dag pa phrin las lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:5310: / / gur gum tsan dan dkar dmar gnyis gla rtsi dz+aa ti ste /
NK070(thu)001:5312: 'byung ba lnga'am yul lnga dag pa yon tan lnga
NK070(thu)001:5313: thob par bya ba'i phyir rin po che byu ru
NK070(thu)001:5319: rnam shes lnga dag pa ye shes lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5321: me tog gi snying po sbrang rtsi /
NK070(thu)001:5322: shing thog gi snying po bu ram /
NK070(thu)001:5323: rtsi thog gi snying po mar /
NK070(thu)001:5326: dbang po lnga'am 'dod yon lnga dag pa gsung lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5329: seng tsher ha pa d+he ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:5335: sman lnga dang sa chu me rlung nam mkha'i khams
NK070(thu)001:5336: lnga dag pa rigs lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:5342: sum cu po de dag ni cha rab tu snyoms
NK070(thu)001:5343: pa'i 'jim pa'i 'de gus 'thug srab glang gi rko
NK070(thu)001:5345: der mtshams bcad la sa bsrung bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5346: de nas rig pa ma yengs pas thig gdab par bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:5347: de'i phyir 'gying phur bu shul du kasrad bu kha tshon phye dang /
NK070(thu)001:5349: gos rgyan mdzes pa yid 'ong grogs //
NK070(thu)001:5350: thig gdab cho ga phun sum tshogs //
NK070(thu)001:5351: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK070(thu)001:5353: srad bu skud pa'i rgyu yang me tog pad+ma'i rgyus
NK070(thu)001:5354: pa'am yang na ras bal la bya ste de yang
NK070(thu)001:5355: rig ma mtshan ldan lo bcu drug mas rnal 'byor
NK070(thu)001:5356: pa'i yid du 'ong ba'i grogs mo /
NK070(thu)001:5357: bkal ba'i skud pa tshon gyi kha dog dkar dmar
NK070(thu)001:5358: mthing gsum du phye ba'i re re la gsum gsum
NK070(thu)001:5359: ste dgu sgril gyi dam tshig gi thig ste /
NK070(thu)001:5360: ring thung gi tshad man+dala 'khor bar tshud pa tsam ste /
NK070(thu)001:5361: sku gsung thugs bye brag gsum gsum du byin gyis
NK070(thu)001:5362: brlab pa'i cho ga phun sum tshogs pa'i thig thogs
NK070(thu)001:5363: te / yum bcu drug ma rgyan gyis mdzes pa
NK070(thu)001:5364: dang gnyis kyis thig drangs te rgyan gyi rta bab
NK070(thu)001:5365: brgyad kyis mdzes par gdab bo //
NK070(thu)001:5366: de nas ye shes kyi thig kha dog mthing ka
NK070(thu)001:5367: dkar ser dmar ljang sna lngar phye la de re
NK070(thu)001:5368: re la yang kha dog lnga lnga'o //
NK070(thu)001:5369: ye shes nyi shu rtsa lngar byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5370: cho ga phun sum tshogs pa de thog la yab
NK070(thu)001:5371: yum gyis lha'i sku phyag rgyar gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams
NK070(thu)001:5372: nas byang chub sems kyi ye shes su drang bas
NK070(thu)001:5373: btab thig pas dus su mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrim
NK070(thu)001:5374: ste bya'o // dam tshig gi thig thams cad sku
NK070(thu)001:5375: gsung thugs gcig kyang ye shes lnga lngar gsal bas
NK070(thu)001:5376: ste bya'o // / mdor na thams cad sku dang
NK070(thu)001:5377: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i gzhal yas
NK070(thu)001:5378: ste bya'o // / kho na'o // de nas sa
NK070(thu)001:5379: bzung ba'i cho ga lha sta gon la gnas par
NK070(thu)001:5380: ste bya'o // / kho na'o // byas nas /
NK070(thu)001:5381: thig skud pa dang rdul tshon lnga ci ltar byin
NK070(thu)001:5383: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:5385: 'dir rgyas pa'i dbang du tshon sna lnga po re
NK070(thu)001:5386: re yang yi ge 'bru lnga lngas brel zhing bsgom
NK070(thu)001:5387: ste / re re la yang kha dog nang ris su lnga lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:5388: nyi shu rtsa lnga 'phros 'dus pa las /
NK070(thu)001:5389: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor yab yum lnga'am /
NK070(thu)001:5390: yab yum nyi shu rtsa lnga'i dam tshig pa rnams
NK070(thu)001:5391: bskyed cing bsgom de la ye shes pa nyi shu
NK070(thu)001:5392: rtsa lnga spyan drangs zhing dam tshig pa la bstim
NK070(thu)001:5393: nas don ye shes nyi shu lnga rtags rin po
NK070(thu)001:5394: che nyi shu rtsa lnga kho nar gyur par bya'o
NK070(thu)001:5395: // de ltar tshon nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bkye ba dgos pa dang nges tshig ci snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5396: ma mthong rmongs la bstan phyir tshon //
NK070(thu)001:5397: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK070(thu)001:5398: lnga'i tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK070(thu)001:5399: 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK070(thu)001:5401: don rang gi sems nyid ye shes lnga'am nyi shu
NK070(thu)001:5402: rtsa lngar gdod nas dag par gnas kyang ma mthong
NK070(thu)001:5403: zhi nga blo rmongs pa rnam la rang la yod
NK070(thu)001:5404: pa de mtshon cing bstan par bya ba'i phyir te
NK070(thu)001:5406: 'gro drug gi sems can ma lus pa thams cad la //
NK070(thu)001:5407: ye shes lnga'i kun la khyab kyang //
NK070(thu)001:5408: rang gi rnam rtog gi bsgrib par byas nas //
NK070(thu)001:5409: ye shes lnga'i don rang la gnas pa de ma mthong //
NK070(thu)001:5410: de ltar blo rmongs pa'i sems can thams cad la //
NK070(thu)001:5411: ye shes lnga'i mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:5412: kha dog dkar dang dmar dang ser ba'ang //
NK070(thu)001:5413: ljang ku la sogs nyer lnga nag por bstan //
NK070(thu)001:5415: de lta bus 'i tshon gyi bri ba yang rgyas
NK070(thu)001:5416: pa kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rgyas 'bring bsdus
NK070(thu)001:5417: pa gsum po ni 'bring bsdus gnyis la lnga'i tshon
NK070(thu)001:5419: slob bu gang la dad pa ste 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du bri'o //
NK070(thu)001:5420: zhing dgye de dag gi dbyibs ci ltar snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5421: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:5422: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK070(thu)001:5423: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi yi //
NK070(thu)001:5424: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK070(thu)001:5427: gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i steng du yang rtsibs
NK070(thu)001:5428: bzhi dang ldan pa steng du yang rtsibs bzhi pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5429: 'khor lo mu khyud zlum po dang bcas pa cha
NK070(thu)001:5430: lnga ste / spyir 'khor lo drug pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:5432: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi'i bar 'khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya /
NK070(thu)001:5434: rgyas 'bring gnyis ka las mthun no //
NK070(thu)001:5438: rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum thams cad la yang bri bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5439: gzhal yas khang dkyil 'khor de dag tu lha rnams
NK070(thu)001:5440: kyi mtshan ma gsum ci ltar dgod snyam pa la
NK070(thu)001:5441: / sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK070(thu)001:5443: bsdus pa khru gang ba la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor tsaka li dgod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5445: h'u mum la sogs pa'i snying po yig 'bru ta tha la sogs pa dgod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5447: lha rang rang gi phyag mtshan /
NK070(thu)001:5448: phyag rgya dgod pa ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gang rung dang ldan pa'i gzugs kyang dgod /
NK070(thu)001:5450: gcig bkod gnyis bskyed re re'ang gsum gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:5451: dkyil 'khor de dag gi rgyan ci ltar bri snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5452: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK070(thu)001:5453: rgyan phreng btung ba bro bas bskor //
NK070(thu)001:5455: bla rgyan kha dog sna tshogs su bres pa bcos
NK070(thu)001:5456: bu'i ras kyi ni bla re dang 'phan gdugs yol
NK070(thu)001:5457: ba dar 'phyang ba dan la sogs pa dbyibs kyi
NK070(thu)001:5458: bye brag gi rigs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs dang
NK070(thu)001:5459: / bar rgyan rin po che'i rgyan cha phreng ba sna tshogs dang chun 'phyang dang /
NK070(thu)001:5461: 'og gis bza' ba dang btung ba g.yos kyi bye
NK070(thu)001:5462: brag bro ba sna tshogs kyis dkyil 'khor bskor ba'o
NK070(thu)001:5464: dkyil 'khor de dag gi rab tu gnas pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5465: stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod yul dag par sbyangs ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:5466: rnal 'byor pa rang dang sems can gyi lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK070(thu)001:5467: gang la'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pa //
NK070(thu)001:5468: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba'i yi //
NK070(thu)001:5469: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:5471: gong gi gzugs brnyan gsum gyi phyag rgya bkod pa rnams /
NK070(thu)001:5472: phyi gzhal yas gis mtshon pa'i chos thams cad sems
NK070(thu)001:5473: nyid kyi snang ba tsam las ma rtogs pa dngos
NK070(thu)001:5474: po gzhan phyogs gcig tu gang la'ang mi gnas shing
NK070(thu)001:5475: rang rgyud du'ang mi dmigs te dmigs su med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5476: phyir / cir yang snang ba ni dper na mig
NK070(thu)001:5477: yor lta bur 'i tshul du snang lta sbyor bas
NK070(thu)001:5478: rang gi ngo bo nyid med par rtog pa la
NK070(thu)001:5480: dngos po 'di lta bu'i phyogs gcig pa ngo bor
NK070(thu)001:5481: yang dmigs su med pa rgya chad phyogs lhung dang
NK070(thu)001:5482: bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5483: don de la ni bsgom byed kyi blo yang nam
NK070(thu)001:5484: mkha' ltar yul du mi dmigs par rang gsal bar
NK070(thu)001:5486: de la chos nyid rnam par dag pa shu&a ta
NK070(thu)001:5487: zhes bya ba'i sngags nyer gcig gis nga rgyal bya'o
NK070(thu)001:5488: // stong pa de'i ngang la dper na rol mo
NK070(thu)001:5489: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:5490: bskyed par bstan pa'i phyir ting 'dzin rol mo mtha'
NK070(thu)001:5491: // yas mchog / yi ge'i gdan nam snying po'am //
NK070(thu)001:5492: phyag rgya sku gsung thugs ldan par //
NK070(thu)001:5493: byin brlabs ya mtshan rmad po che //
NK070(thu)001:5496: dper na rol mo ni gzhi ma nges pa las /
NK070(thu)001:5497: thabs kyis drangs nas sgra sna tshogs su snang ba bzhin du /
NK070(thu)001:5498: bshad 0pa'i stong pa nyid rnam par mi rtogs pa'i ye shes de rang gi ngang las /
NK070(thu)001:5499: ye shes rang gsal skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:5500: gyi mthas mchog gi don la rang dbang bsgyur nas
NK070(thu)001:5501: / 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK070(thu)001:5502: gdan dang bcas par snang la gzhal yas khang de
NK070(thu)001:5503: dag du sngar bkod pa'i h'u mum la sogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5504: snying po'am ta tha la sogs pa'i yi ge bkod
NK070(thu)001:5505: pa rnams gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:5506: nyi zla la sogs pa'i gdan nam tsaka li bkod pa sku'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:5507: phyag rgya bkod pa thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gang yin pa yang /
NK070(thu)001:5508: bkod pa de nyid sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'i lhar byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK070(thu)001:5509: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor yang drangs te /
NK070(thu)001:5511: bstim nas bsgom na dngos grub ya mtshan can thun
NK070(thu)001:5512: mong ma yin pa'i rmad po che'i 'dod pa yongs
NK070(thu)001:5515: spyan drangs pa 'bras bu gnyis dang lhag par ting
NK070(thu)001:5516: nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang gsum 'tshogs pa'i don la
NK070(thu)001:5518: sangs rgyas kun kyi dam tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:5519: 'o na 'bras bu gzhan du 'tshol lam snyam du dgos pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5520: sa la sogs te phyag rgyar byas //
NK070(thu)001:5521: rnam grol rim pa thob 'gyur na //
NK070(thu)001:5522: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pa //
NK070(thu)001:5523: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK070(thu)001:5525: sa la sogs ste ra shing rdo ras la sogs
NK070(thu)001:5526: pa rin po che'i 'byung ba dang de las gyur
NK070(thu)001:5530: sku tsaka li gsung yig 'bru thugs phyag mtshan kyi phyag rgya'i dbyibs byas pa tsam gyi kyang /
NK070(thu)001:5531: rgyu dang bzang ngan sems dag ma dag kyi rim
NK070(thu)001:5532: pas 'khor dang ngan song gi sdug bsngal las rim
NK070(thu)001:5533: par rnam par grol nas 'bras bu thob bar 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:5534: na / dag pa'i stong pa nyid dang kyi ting
NK070(thu)001:5535: nge 'dzin rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis
NK070(thu)001:5536: kyi lhar rtog pa sbyangs te /
NK070(thu)001:5537: ye shes pa'i byin brlabs kyang 'dus pa te thim
NK070(thu)001:5538: pa de ni nyid 'bras bu thob pa ni smos
NK070(thu)001:5539: ci dgos te lus ngag yid gsum de nyid de
NK070(thu)001:5540: bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK070(thu)001:5541: gsal ba de nyid rang 'bras bu kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5544: de pa de'i byin brlabs zhugs pa'i thabs rab tu gnas pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5545: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK070(thu)001:5546: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK070(thu)001:5547: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:5548: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor las //
NK070(thu)001:5549: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:5550: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:5551: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:5552: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5554: de yang gang nas spyan drangs na phyogs bcu dang
NK070(thu)001:5555: dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:5556: ril thams cad gyi bdag nyid chen po ni byang
NK070(thu)001:5557: chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye shes kho na
NK070(thu)001:5558: yin la / de'i ngo bo nyid ni cir yang
NK070(thu)001:5559: mi dmigs pa'i thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK070(thu)001:5560: kyi ngang la ye shes lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5561: yin la / dkyil 'khor ro // de nyid cig
NK070(thu)001:5562: kyang don ye shes lnga lnga la sogs par nyer
NK070(thu)001:5563: lnga gsal ba las rtags rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK070(thu)001:5564: cad du rang snang ba de la spyan drang ngo
NK070(thu)001:5565: de nas bstim mo de yang gud na med de
NK070(thu)001:5566: sems nyid rang snang ba'i phung po la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:5567: rtog pa rnams rtogs tshul ni rig pa rang snang
NK070(thu)001:5568: ba'i 'bras bu sku dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5569: dkyil 'khor de la phyag rgya bzhis bstim nas ye
NK070(thu)001:5570: shes dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:5571: gnyis su med par gyur pa de la /
NK070(thu)001:5572: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid kyis nyams su len par
NK070(thu)001:5573: bsgoms shing mnyam pas ra sbyor ba de la phyogs
NK070(thu)001:5574: dus kun nas gshegs pa'i yon tan sngar bsnyen pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5575: yi dam lha rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ril gyi yon
NK070(thu)001:5576: tan thams cad rab tu rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5577: dus nye bar gyur pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK070(thu)001:5578: tshig gi mchog 'bras bu ci 'dod pa yongs su
NK070(thu)001:5580: gnyis su med par gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor de 1la phyi nang gi mchod pa bya dgos pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5581: gaglu tshig bro gar kharol mo kayi //
NK070(thu)001:5582: sprin dpung tshogs kyis rab tu mchod //
NK070(thu)001:5584: ci taltar 'dod pa'i las nyabzhin mchod //
NK070(thu)001:5586: 1phyi'i mchod pa spos la sogs pa rnam pa lnga dang /
NK070(thu)001:5589: sgra yi ril mo'i bye brag rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5590: nang gi dam rdzas lnga po rnams rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5591: bro gar su ra to bcu drug gi mchod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5592: glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:5594: rgyal byed rmongs byed ste gsang ba'i mchod pa'i yum
NK070(thu)001:5595: bzhi dang phyi nang gi sems ma brgyad dang 'jol
NK070(thu)001:5596: ma sgo ma bzhi po de dag kyang sprin dpung
NK070(thu)001:5597: gi tshogs kyis nam mkha' khams thams cad rab tu
NK070(thu)001:5599: de dag gi sems kyi bsam pa dang bskul ba'i
NK070(thu)001:5600: tshigs ni ci ltar rang gi zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK070(thu)001:5601: gi las bzhi dang gang 'dod pa'i skabs kyis dabye'o
NK070(thu)001:5602: // zhing gzhung bzhin du mchod pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5603: dkyil 'khor de dag la 1lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5604: gsang ba'i mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5605: 1mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK070(thu)001:5606: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:5607: spyir thabs gang gis rgyal ba mnyes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5609: de las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya /
NK070(thu)001:5610: 'dir 'dod pa'i yon tan lngas 'gro ba'i rigs pa
NK070(thu)001:5611: tshim par byed pa sa na yid bzhin gyi nor
NK070(thu)001:5612: bu ltar de dag mang bas sprin tshogs kyi phung
NK070(thu)001:5613: po bzhin de dag 'og ma ltar ma spangs par
NK070(thu)001:5614: sems nyid kyi ngang du shes pas so so skye
NK070(thu)001:5615: bo las khyad par du byas te chen po zhing
NK070(thu)001:5616: dngos po gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor phul ba
NK070(thu)001:5617: ni 'khor gsum yongs su dag pas mchod pa'i mchog
NK070(thu)001:5619: mchod pa de dag gi ngo bo ni gang zhe
NK070(thu)001:5620: na tshig bzhi ste phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK070(thu)001:5622: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su dag pa ste de'ang gnyen 'jam reg na bde ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:5623: sna tshogs pa'i rin po che'i gzhi mdzes par bris shing spras par byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5624: ri dang spang la sogs pa thams cad tram las
NK070(thu)001:5625: dgos 'dod kun 'byung ba'i rin po che'i phung por
NK070(thu)001:5628: chu thams cad a las dbyibs legs pa rin po
NK070(thu)001:5629: che'i bdud rtsi'i rdzing bu bro mchog bsil ba la
NK070(thu)001:5630: sogs sna tshogs pa bde rim dang ldan par brlab
NK070(thu)001:5631: pa dang / 'gro ba so so'i gnas khang thams
NK070(thu)001:5632: cad b+h+aum las rin po che'i khang pa sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:5634: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad tram las rin po
NK070(thu)001:5635: che'i rgyan dang dpag bsam gyi ljon shing rgyas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5636: tshal sna tshogs su brlab pa dang sems kyis zin
NK070(thu)001:5637: ma zin gyi sgra skad thams cad h+r+aihls rgyal ba
NK070(thu)001:5640: tshigs su bcad pa dang sems can la chos nyid
NK070(thu)001:5641: sgra sna tshogs su grags pa dang par byin gyis
NK070(thu)001:5642: brlabs pa gos thams cad 'am mam las gdugs bla
NK070(thu)001:5643: re rgyan na bza' lhab lhub sna tshogs su snang
NK070(thu)001:5645: 'gro ba so so'i rin po che'i rgyan thams cad
NK070(thu)001:5646: tram las rin po che'i phreng ba'i do shal dang
NK070(thu)001:5648: se mo do sna tshogs su brlabs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5649: 'gro ba so so'i bza' btung gi longs spyod thams
NK070(thu)001:5650: cad aa'am +amo las bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin bza' ba
NK070(thu)001:5651: dang btung ba dang ro bro ba'i tshogs kyi longs
NK070(thu)001:5652: spyod sna tshogs rnams su brlab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5653: 'gro ba pho mo rnams kyang lha pho dang lha
NK070(thu)001:5654: mo'i rnams kyi rang la mdzes pa rgyan gyis khyad
NK070(thu)001:5655: par du mdzes shing par gnas /
NK070(thu)001:5656: rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:5657: bsam yas pa sna tshogs kyis lag na mchod rdzas
NK070(thu)001:5659: nas phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams thams cad bkang /
NK070(thu)001:5661: de dag gis rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun la mchod pa rgyas par 'bul bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5663: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:5664: rim gyis yang na cig char du //
NK070(thu)001:5665: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:5666: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:5668: skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i blo che
NK070(thu)001:5669: chung gi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang mi gsal
NK070(thu)001:5670: ba'i khyad par gyis rim pa ltar blo chung na
NK070(thu)001:5672: yang na cig car du skad cig gis chos kyi
NK070(thu)001:5673: dbyings dang mnyam sbyor ba chos nyid la chos nyid
NK070(thu)001:5674: thim pa'i tshul du 'bul ba ni mtshan pa'i phyag
NK070(thu)001:5677: 2gsang ba'i sbyor ba mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:5678: kagsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs las //
NK070(thu)001:5679: khastong gsum yungs 'brur bzhugs tshul du //
NK070(thu)001:5680: gadbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK070(thu)001:5681: ngamnyes nas cagrub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5684: shes rab ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:5685: ldan pas lha rnams mkha' dang phung khams skye mched la rang gi lha bsgom pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:5686: mi ldan na gtso bos yab kyi /
NK070(thu)001:5688: stong gsum yungs 'brur 'jug pa'i tshul du yum gyi mkha'i /
NK070(thu)001:5689: sna rtse yungs 'bru tsam gyi gzhal yas su lha'i dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs tshang bar bkod de /
NK070(thu)001:5690: rang bzhin 'og min gyi dbyings nas mthar phyin /
NK070(thu)001:5693: pas mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5694: yab yum bdag nyid chen po rol pa'i ba de
NK070(thu)001:5695: ba sa mchod pas rang gis ci ltar myong ba
NK070(thu)001:5696: ltar thams cad sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK070(thu)001:5697: pa mnyes pa dang ldan zhing srid gsum 'gro ba
NK070(thu)001:5698: thams cad la bde ba chen po khyab ste /
NK070(thu)001:5701: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba brten pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:5702: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:5703: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK070(thu)001:5704: khams gsum 'gro rnams mngon du gyur //
NK070(thu)001:5706: de dag kyang thabs grol gnyis su yang 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:5708: gsal ba dang ldan pa'i shes rab yum dang thabs yab kyi rtsa gnas su //
NK070(thu)001:5709: rtsa'i d+r+wa ba'i nang na thig le nyid yi ge'i dbyibs nyid //
NK070(thu)001:5711: sgyu 'phrul te lha yab yum gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis su byin gyis brlabs //
NK070(thu)001:5712: yab yum gyi b+ha khaga ra rtsa sna tshogs stong
NK070(thu)001:5713: gsum dang 'dra ba 'dus pa'i sna rtse yungs 'bru
NK070(thu)001:5715: lus ngag yid gsum khams gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams bsdus par byas te //
NK070(thu)001:5716: de lta bu'i rtog tshogs zhe gnyis lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar mngon du byas //
NK070(thu)001:5717: pas dbyings phyogs gabcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba rnams spyan drangs te //
NK070(thu)001:5718: rig pas ting nge 'dzin gyis yab yum so so'i lha'i gnas su bstims //
NK070(thu)001:5720: thabs shes rab rol cing bskyod pa'i dus su ha si'i sgras bskul bas //
NK070(thu)001:5721: bdag nyid chen po ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun //
NK070(thu)001:5723: steng sgo bde chen nas byung ba'i bde ba'i bcud //
NK070(thu)001:5724: de yab yum so so'i lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la thim //
NK070(thu)001:5726: lus kun nas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:5729: rgyal ba mnyes pa'i ni mchod pa mchog tu gsungs //
NK070(thu)001:5730: yab yum cabco brgyad pa phrag gnyis thabs shes rab
NK070(thu)001:5731: gnyis kyi byang sems kyi chu rgyun ye shes lnga
NK070(thu)001:5732: dang ldan pa'i / bum kapa dang //
NK070(thu)001:5733: sa bon drug gnyis dag pa thub pa ste de
NK070(thu)001:5734: ltar lha zhe gnyis po'i byang sems kyi 'od zer
NK070(thu)001:5735: gyis sgo gsum sbyangs nas khani //
NK070(thu)001:5736: kadbang bskur sgo gsum sku gsum thugs su khabyin gyis brlabs pa'i bde ba thob pa //
NK070(thu)001:5737: sdug bsngal dang rtog pa las grol bas theg pa
NK070(thu)001:5738: chen por dbug dbyung ba ste grub pa'i ma tshogs
NK070(thu)001:5740: bdag nyid chen po brnyes pa'i sho lo ka gnyis ni yar 'khor du shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5742: de lta bu'i rab gnas kyi dus su sbyin sreg bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5743: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK070(thu)001:5744: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK070(thu)001:5745: bza' btung bro'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK070(thu)001:5746: sa chog gi dus su zhi ba /
NK070(thu)001:5747: dal rab gnas kyi dus su rgyas pa /
NK070(thu)001:5748: sta gon slob ma rab gnas kyi dus su drag po /
NK070(thu)001:5749: dbang bskur ba'i dus su'ang dbang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:5750: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK070(thu)001:5753: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las bzhi las ham khung gi dbyibs la zlum po sum brtsegs sam /
NK070(thu)001:5754: tsakra dbyibs brgyad zla'am sum brtsegs gam /
NK070(thu)001:5760: 'dir rab gnas kyi skabs kyi rgyas pa'i thab ni
NK070(thu)001:5761: brtsegs dbang du gru bzhi'am bri dbang du rin chen
NK070(thu)001:5763: kha dog ser po mtshan dang ldan par byas la /
NK070(thu)001:5764: bang rim gsum gyi nang ma la rin po che'i sgram bu dang /
NK070(thu)001:5766: rdo rje dang rgyab ma la zhags pas ser pos bskor ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:5767: me lha'i zhal du gyur pa'i bsreg lha ni ma
NK070(thu)001:5768: brum las rgyas pa de nyid kho na'i dang 'dra
NK070(thu)001:5770: de yang 'di las ra skyes kyi sga gong du
NK070(thu)001:5771: nyi zla'i steng du tram las rgyas pa'i me lha
NK070(thu)001:5772: ser po g.yas na rin po che'i sgram bu thogs
NK070(thu)001:5773: par pa g.yon na bgrang phreng 'dzin bskyed pa dang
NK070(thu)001:5775: de la ye shes pa spyan drangs nas bos la
NK070(thu)001:5776: bstim ste thun mong gi mchod pa dang sbyin sreg
NK070(thu)001:5777: gis mchod de / me lha'i lto bar rgyas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5778: gzhal yas khang du lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang
NK070(thu)001:5779: gis mchod de / / dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs /
NK070(thu)001:5780: de la ye shes pa spyan drangs nas bstim ste
NK070(thu)001:5781: bza' btung bro'i tshogs rnams kyi thun mong dang khyad
NK070(thu)001:5782: par gyis mchod pa bdud rtsi la sogs pas mchod
NK070(thu)001:5783: de / rab tu sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5784: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5785: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK070(thu)001:5786: shin tu phra la sbyangs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:5787: bsam yas dag la de bzhin bya //
NK070(thu)001:5788: rig pas dpag pa tsam du bya //
NK070(thu)001:5790: khro bo'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan la sogs pa'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:5791: 'khor byed na'ang sa gzhi mnyam pa la sogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5792: las lnga dang sbyin sreg kyang de bzhin nyid de
NK070(thu)001:5793: zhi ba dang rjes su mthun no //
NK070(thu)001:5795: rgyang grags dpag tshad la sogs pa bsam yas mchog
NK070(thu)001:5796: gi dkyil 'khor dag la'ang zhi ba'i skabs ltar de
NK070(thu)001:5797: bzhin te rnal 'byor pa rang gi rig pas dpag
NK070(thu)001:5798: pa tsam du bsgom par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5799: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:5800: de ltar sbyin sreg yan chad kyis mchod pa rdzogs nas /
NK070(thu)001:5802: dkyil 'khor du ru dang slob bu 'jug pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5803: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK070(thu)001:5804: de nas slob ma zhugs par bya //
NK070(thu)001:5806: sngar bshad pa'i las brgyad po rnams kun rdzogs par
NK070(thu)001:5807: byas nas phyi nang gsang gsum de dbang gi phyug
NK070(thu)001:5808: pa'i rdo rje slob dpon khrus byas te dbang gos
NK070(thu)001:5809: dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor me tog
NK070(thu)001:5810: pus btsugs thal sbyar gus pas 'dug ste /
NK070(thu)001:5811: le'u bdun par bshad pa ltar ye shes rgyal por dngos grub bskul zhing zhugs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5812: rig pas me tog dor te /
NK070(thu)001:5814: de nas slob ma dkyil 'khor du zhugs par bya ba la chos bcu drug ste /
NK070(thu)001:5815: bu rnams dri'i chus khrus byas ras sam dar dmar
NK070(thu)001:5816: pos gdong g.yog 'dri ba dang len byas dgos pa
NK070(thu)001:5818: ba dang bgegs bskrad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5820: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig sbyin pa dang dam tshig de nyid dbog pa /
NK070(thu)001:5821: chu gnyis kyis nan chag bya ba /
NK070(thu)001:5823: rin po che me tog gi phreng ba dor ba /
NK070(thu)001:5825: dbog pa de nyid nan tan bya ba mig spyan dar dbye ba /
NK070(thu)001:5826: dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags kyis ngo bstan yon 'bul bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5827: de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i phan yon dang /
NK070(thu)001:5828: yi dam phog pa'i lha mi spang bar gdams pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5829: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK070(thu)001:5830: stang dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK070(thu)001:5831: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK070(thu)001:5834: rigs lnga yab yum thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel par snyoms par zhugs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5835: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:5837: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor skabs su dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:5838: stong ni yab dpyal ni yum ste gtso bo yab yum gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:5840: yang na dkyil 'khor rgyas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5841: 'bring po la gtso bo rigs lnga rab gnas dang ldan par byas /
NK070(thu)001:5843: dkyil 'khor gsum po de dag tu slob bu dad
NK070(thu)001:5844: pa dang ldan pa gong du bshad pa bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:5845: chos bco brgyad kyis rab tu zhugs pa'i ra 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:5847: 'dod pa'i don dngos grub yid du 'ong ba sngon
NK070(thu)001:5848: 'og min du mthar las pa bzhugs pa dang 'bras
NK070(thu)001:5850: rgyud gzhan dag rdo rje las /
NK070(thu)001:5851: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs rigs lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:5852: sangs rgyas yi ge 'khor lo'i sa'i dkyil 'khor mngon sum du mthong ba yi //
NK070(thu)001:5853: bsod nams mi 'gyur bas rtag pa gang yin pa /
NK070(thu)001:5854: lhun gyis grub pa ltar phyis rjes 'jug gi rnal
NK070(thu)001:5855: 'byor pas byas pa'ang 'bras bu de bzhin du thob
NK070(thu)001:5857: de ltar zhugs nas me tog phog pa'i lha rang bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5858: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes te //
NK070(thu)001:5859: gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK070(thu)001:5860: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK070(thu)001:5861: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
