NK070(thu)001:5863: bdag gis lus ngag yid gsum gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK070(thu)001:5864: lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje ye nas lhun gyis
NK070(thu)001:5865: grub pa la ni bdag dang lha khyad par med
NK070(thu)001:5866: 1pas skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes can /
NK070(thu)001:5867: kho na de ltar yin mod kyis tha mal pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5868: sgo gsum du blo kun tu 1 brtags pa'i ma
NK070(thu)001:5869: rig pas de la 1sgrib pa 1 de bsal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:5870: thabs ni / le'u lnga pa ltar ting nge 'dzin gsum don du gnyer na /
NK070(thu)001:5871: dus nye bar 'byung ba'i dngos grub ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges te /
NK070(thu)001:5873: rtsa ba'i dam tshig bla med mi spang ba dang sngags phyag rgya /
NK070(thu)001:5874: gnyis su char lha'i bsgom bzlas byas pa yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:5876: bsgrub pa la nan tan che bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:5877: gal te lha bsgom pa'i dad pa med nas dam
NK070(thu)001:5878: tshig nyams na tshe 'di phyir phung bar 'gyur ro
NK070(thu)001:5880: de nas dbang thob pa'i rgyu yin 'bul ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5881: dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba rdzogs pa de nas dal
NK070(thu)001:5882: du zhugs pa'i rigs kyi bu mchog dbang thob par
NK070(thu)001:5883: 'dod pa des / sngon du yon 'bul bar bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:5884: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK070(thu)001:5885: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK070(thu)001:5888: rang gi yi dam gyi lha de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5889: rigs rnam snang la me tog phog na rgyal srid
NK070(thu)001:5890: dam rang dbang ba'i dngos po ci yod 'bul lo
NK070(thu)001:5891: // rdo rje rigs mi bskyod pa la ni rang gi lus 'bul lo //
NK070(thu)001:5892: pad+ma'i rigs snang mtha' la bu dang chung ma'o //
NK070(thu)001:5893: rin po che rigs rin 'byung la de nyid dam nor gyi dbyig ste snying po nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:5894: las kyi rigs la rang la gang rab tu gces pa 'bul lo //
NK070(thu)001:5895: rigs kyi bdag po'i rigs drug pa la bla ma'i
NK070(thu)001:5896: thugs yid dang mthun par las rgya'am ci 'thad pa
NK070(thu)001:5898: yon tan ci zhig yod snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5899: dbang phyug slob dpon la gang gi yon rnams dang
NK070(thu)001:5900: gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i longs spyod lngas mchod na
NK070(thu)001:5901: // dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:5902: te slob dpon gyi nye ba'i ra nyams su blangs pa dbang byed pa /
NK070(thu)001:5903: yi dam dkyil 'khor mnyes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:5905: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:5907: bla ma mnyes pas rang bzhin dang bcas pa'i kha
NK070(thu)001:5908: nas ma tho ba thun mong gi nyes pa mi
NK070(thu)001:5909: dge ba bcu mtshams med lnga lci ba bzhi log
NK070(thu)001:5911: dang thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang sngags kyi rtsa ba yan lag gi chags nyams dang /
NK070(thu)001:5912: sdig pa thams cad byang zhing dag par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5913: de bas na yon 'bul ba la ser sna spang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:5915: de nas gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i snod kyi rim pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:5916: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK070(thu)001:5917: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK070(thu)001:5918: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK070(thu)001:5919: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK070(thu)001:5921: snod kyi mtshan nyid rab tu rtogs nas sngags kyi
NK070(thu)001:5922: theg pa 'di la dad pa dad ldan pa rnams
NK070(thu)001:5923: la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcus tshe 'di dang phyi
NK070(thu)001:5926: brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga sbyin
NK070(thu)001:5927: te de yang bdag don gyi brtson pa can la
NK070(thu)001:5928: nyan bsgom gyi dbang gnyis po sbyin no //
NK070(thu)001:5929: gzhan don gyi brtson pa can la phrin las dang 'chad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5930: rdo rje rgyal po rab 'byams kyi las dang nus pa'i dbang gsum sbyin no //
NK070(thu)001:5931: brtul zhugs can la ni gsang ba zab mo'i dbang
NK070(thu)001:5932: gsum sbyin te de la blo rab 'bring tha ma
NK070(thu)001:5933: gsum mo // dam rdzas la gtsang sme med par spyod pa'i brtul zhugs 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:5934: ni lo nyi shu ma la bstan pa /
NK070(thu)001:5935: bde ba rang rig pa'i brtul 2 zhugs ni bcu drug ma dang /
NK070(thu)001:5936: shin tu brten pa mnyam pa'i brtul 3zhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:5937: ni bcu gnyis ma la bstan /
NK070(thu)001:5939: gsang ba dam rdzas lnga kun la spyod pa'i gsang dbang dang /
NK070(thu)001:5940: rang rig shes rab ye shes thams cad mkhyen pa'i 2dbang /
NK070(thu)001:5941: shin tu brtan pa'i dbyer med pa bde ba chen
NK070(thu)001:5942: po'i dbang 2dang gsum po de dag snod kyi rim
NK070(thu)001:5943: pa bzhin du rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams /
NK070(thu)001:5945: snying rjes kun nas bslangs pa'i sems kyis slob ma
NK070(thu)001:5946: de dag skas kyi sdong bu 'i rim pa ltar
NK070(thu)001:5947: 'dzeg nas chud ma zos par rjes su bzung nas
NK070(thu)001:5948: bar ma dor blos mi dor ro //
NK070(thu)001:5949: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:5950: rigs kyi bdag po'i dkyil 'khor la yid 'thad 'bul ba /
NK070(thu)001:5951: yon tan dang brtul zhugs kyis can zab mo'i dbang
NK070(thu)001:5952: bskur ba'i dbang du gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor sor bzhi
NK070(thu)001:5953: pa yum gyi mkha' ru thun mong du gsungs pa
NK070(thu)001:5954: shin khatu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:5955: kaphyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du /
NK070(thu)001:5956: de ni gathugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gzhan la dpags pas /
NK070(thu)001:5959: che chung ni rin po che dang shel la blugs
NK070(thu)001:5960: pa dang brkos la sor ni bzhi'i tshad du bya
NK070(thu)001:5963: yab nyid kyi mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i chen po mthil
NK070(thu)001:5964: steng du shin tu phra ba'i las mi 'da' ba
NK070(thu)001:5965: dkyil 'khor dam tshig gi mchog gis bkod do //
NK070(thu)001:5966: gzhan du na thal ba'i rgyud las /
NK070(thu)001:5967: rdo rje slob dpon phyag rgya chen po phyag mthil
NK070(thu)001:5968: du bde ba'i ye shes nam mkha'i dang 'dra skye
NK070(thu)001:5970: ni yum gyi mkha' sor ni bzhi'i tshad du rang bzhin gyis gnas //
NK070(thu)001:5972: bde ba'i ye shes ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor //
NK070(thu)001:5974: kha dog bzhi'i mtshan dang ldan zhing dbyibs rang gsal
NK070(thu)001:5975: ba'i phyi 'khyam gru gsum gru bzhi zla'am zlum po
NK070(thu)001:5977: bde ba skye ba sbyor ba thabs kyi 'dod pa'i
NK070(thu)001:5978: bstan bcos kyis rab gnas dang sbyor thabs kyi cho
NK070(thu)001:5979: gar ldan // nas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la 'jug
NK070(thu)001:5980: pa pos slob bu kyang yum de la me tog
NK070(thu)001:5981: gar ldan // 'bul zhing / gsol ba gdab //
NK070(thu)001:5984: dkyil 'khor de'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya dgod pa gang zhig yin snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5985: sor bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor pad+ma'i lte ba dang 'dab
NK070(thu)001:5986: ma la sen mo zlum po tsam gyi nyi zla'i
NK070(thu)001:5987: gdan la // sren ma tsa na'i ka slob pa 'bru tsam gyi pad mo'i gdan //
NK070(thu)001:5990: phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri //
NK070(thu)001:5992: 'og gi mdzub gang ba'i dkyil 'khor la gsung /
NK070(thu)001:5993: yi ge yungs 'bru tsam las sku phyag rgya nas 'bras tsam bkod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:5994: sor bzhi pa'i dal la gsung yi ge til 'bru
NK070(thu)001:5995: tsam las sku phyag rgya yungs 'bru tsam bkod pa'o
NK070(thu)001:5996: // sor bzhi pa de la gang gi dkyil 'khor gzhan ltar du zla med dam snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:5998: yang na rdo rje tshad ni phyag gi thal mo rab tu bsnol nas //
NK070(thu)001:5999: sku phyag rgya chen po'i bsgom pa dpang du ni //
NK070(thu)001:6000: bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i rten gsang ba'i rdo
NK070(thu)001:6001: rje mtshon byed rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:6002: che chung ni / mdzub gang ba'i tshad du yang //
NK070(thu)001:6004: lag len la bzo bo mkhas pa'i rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK070(thu)001:6005: cho ga ci lta ba bzhin du bzo bar bya //
NK070(thu)001:6008: de ni thal ba'i rgyud las /
NK070(thu)001:6009: thal mo zhes bya bya ni brdab pa'i sgra //
NK070(thu)001:6011: yab kyis gsang ba'i dbang po rdo rje dang de'i
NK070(thu)001:6012: kha yul ka yum gyi pad+ma'i ga du rab tu
NK070(thu)001:6013: sbyor bas // phyag rgya mo lo bcu drug gam
NK070(thu)001:6014: bcu gnyis ma chen po bde ba nam mkha'i khams
NK070(thu)001:6015: kyi yon tan thams cad bskyed pa'i dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:6016: de mnyam dang rig pa'i brtul shugs nyid kyis gsang
NK070(thu)001:6017: dbang gi dus su slob dpon gyi dbang gnyis po'i
NK070(thu)001:6018: dus su slob bus pang du blangs //
NK070(thu)001:6019: te gsang ba'i rdo rje mdzub gang pa'i rtse mo'i dang yum gyi sna rtse dag tu //
NK070(thu)001:6020: thig le til 'bru tsam phyin pa'i dus su nam mkha'i khams kyi gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6021: bde ba ye shes kyi rang gzugs lha ri rab tsam gyi sku phyag rgya dgod //
NK070(thu)001:6022: de la ye shes pa spyan drangs la bstim /
NK070(thu)001:6023: bde ba skye thabs kyi cho ga 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyi rab gnas dang //
NK070(thu)001:6025: mkha' ham khung sna rtse mo lha rdo rje blugs gzar pad+ma /
NK070(thu)001:6026: dgang gzur byang sems bco brgyad rdzas te gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su thig le dkar dmar 'bul //
NK070(thu)001:6028: dbang de dag gi las rim ni bla mas 'chad par 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:6029: dbang lnga rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK070(thu)001:6030: de ltar dbang thob nas thob pa'i don nyams su
NK070(thu)001:6031: len pa bskyed pa'i rim pa le'u lnga pa la
NK070(thu)001:6032: sogs pa ltar de ting kun ting /
NK070(thu)001:6035: ting nge 'dzin bzhi la gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6036: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas la //
NK070(thu)001:6037: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK070(thu)001:6038: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK070(thu)001:6040: ting nge 'dzin dang po de ting kun ting gnyis
NK070(thu)001:6041: kyi dus su shes rab dang thabs kyi spyod pa
NK070(thu)001:6043: shes dang rang bzhin de pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6045: kun ting gi dus su snying rje chen po thabs
NK070(thu)001:6046: dang mthun pa'i spyod pa nyid dang yang ldan par
NK070(thu)001:6047: byas nas / de nas sku phra mo gsung yi ge thugs phyag mtshan /
NK070(thu)001:6048: kyi cho ga gsum gyis lha'i sku bskyed de /
NK070(thu)001:6049: phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin gyi skabs su bya ba
NK070(thu)001:6050: spangs pa rnal 'byor phyogs cig pa'i spyod pas blo
NK070(thu)001:6051: sbyangs pas na de ltar lnga ni rdzogs par bya
NK070(thu)001:6052: zhing zhes bya'o // man ta'i sgra rtog bcas kyi yid skyob 1pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6053: dngos grub gnyis kyi byin brlabs kyi chen po 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6054: lha sngags tha mi dad pa sngags te lha'o //
NK070(thu)001:6056: lha de nyid lus kyi yan lag mgo bo la
NK070(thu)001:6057: sogs pa lnga la rigs lnga'i phyag rgya pho brang
NK070(thu)001:6058: gi lha lnga bcu thams cad pa rgyas pa'i rgyud
NK070(thu)001:6061: rtog pa'i yan lag phung po lnga la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:6062: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lha'i dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK070(thu)001:6063: bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba rnal 'byor 'byed par
NK070(thu)001:6065: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis de nyid kyis yan lag lha
NK070(thu)001:6066: gcig la'ang ye shes sems dpa' de dag tshang bar
NK070(thu)001:6067: shes rab kyi lha zhe gnyis dgod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6068: de dag la yang sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum
NK070(thu)001:6069: ste mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i lha brgya
NK070(thu)001:6071: ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba'i yan lag dang lnga
NK070(thu)001:6072: ste ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor stong lnga bcu rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:6073: te / yang na dbu rgyan lnga bcu po de
NK070(thu)001:6074: ming bgrang na dbu rgyan gyis lha stong kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:6075: te / // snang ba rnam par 'byed pa la dbang thob nas /
NK070(thu)001:6076: tshogs kyi yo byad bza' btung dang /
NK070(thu)001:6077: glu tshig rol mo'i sgra dang /
NK070(thu)001:6081: a li ma rnams 'khor khang sum rim gi nang du tshang bar bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:6082: snang la ma zhan par longs spyod pas tshogs kyi spyod pa zhes bya bas bsgrub pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6083: sngags bsgrub pa de sgrub pa'i dus dang /
NK070(thu)001:6084: dngos grub tshe dbang bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6085: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson pas //
NK070(thu)001:6086: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK070(thu)001:6087: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK070(thu)001:6088: dbang bskur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:6090: gong ma lnga gsum bco lnga pa'i don rang la rdzogs shing /
NK070(thu)001:6091: lta ba rtogs pa dang rtsa ba yan lag gi
NK070(thu)001:6092: dam tshig ma nyams par bsgrub pa la 'jug pa
NK070(thu)001:6093: la rab tu brtson pa la gnas na /
NK070(thu)001:6094: blo dang brtson 'grus drag zhan gyi dbang gis rab
NK070(thu)001:6095: kyi zhag ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba
NK070(thu)001:6096: drug nas bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gi bar
NK070(thu)001:6097: gyis dbang bcu las tshe la dbang bsgyur ba thob
NK070(thu)001:6098: par 'gyur te / de ni lhag ma'i lus mi 'dor ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6099: rnam smin dang tshe dbang gzhan gsum las lhag pas rig 'dzin gyi mchog grub pa po //
NK070(thu)001:6100: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu de nyid kho na'am snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6101: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK070(thu)001:6102: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK070(thu)001:6104: rgyas pa'i rgyud don gsum pa las /
NK070(thu)001:6105: tshe tshad ni brgya phrag bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK070(thu)001:6106: lo brgya brgya lon pa dang gzhon nu lo bcu drug pa lta bu dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK070(thu)001:6108: lhag ma'i lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa //
NK070(thu)001:6111: tshe dbang thob pa de'i tshe blo dang brtson 'grus kyi shugs che chung gis che na /
NK070(thu)001:6112: lo brgya nas brgya phrag bcu drug gi tshun chad
NK070(thu)001:6113: kyi bar du bsnur zhing tha ma des sku lnga
NK070(thu)001:6116: de 'grub pa'i tshul ni ci lta bu zhe /
NK070(thu)001:6117: ye shes thig le de nyid la //
NK070(thu)001:6118: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK070(thu)001:6119: bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' yas mchog /
NK070(thu)001:6121: bsgrub pa po'i tshe dbang lhun gyis grub pas /
NK070(thu)001:6122: rig 'dzin gyi rig pa'i ye shes mtha' bral gyi /
NK070(thu)001:6124: sangs rgyas kyi kun ye shes kyis yon tan gyi grangs /
NK070(thu)001:6125: brjod pa las 'das pa rang snang ba yang /
NK070(thu)001:6126: lam pa'i rig pa sgrib pa dang bral ba nyid /
NK070(thu)001:6127: rgyal ba'i ye shes su gsal bas lhun 'grub dang
NK070(thu)001:6128: 'bras bu gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:6130: nyid las ye shes thig le nyid /
NK070(thu)001:6134: sna rtser bde pa 'dus cing gsal ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i thig le la //
NK070(thu)001:6135: mtha' yas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes lnga la
NK070(thu)001:6136: sogs pa thams cad rang rig pas rang snang ba
NK070(thu)001:6137: // de bas na 'bras bu gzhan nas ma btsal
NK070(thu)001:6138: bar rang gi rig pas bde ba'i ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:6140: lhun gyis grub pas na rig 'dzin gyi mchog /
NK070(thu)001:6142: ces pas thabs lam gyi lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6145: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:6146: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6147: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi bsdus pa'i chos kyi dbyings
NK070(thu)001:6148: mtha' klas pa'i thams cad mngon gsum du rdzogs pa
NK070(thu)001:6149: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhing khams rnam
NK070(thu)001:6150: par dag pa ma dag pa bar ma gsum dang
NK070(thu)001:6151: / bsam yas pa rgyan dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK070(thu)001:6152: 'khor lo rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs kyi rgyan dang /
NK070(thu)001:6153: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:6154: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa ma yus bsam
NK070(thu)001:6155: yas pa'i ril thams cad kun /
NK070(thu)001:6156: dus gcig tu rang rig pa'i mngon gsum du /
NK070(thu)001:6157: gsal bar snang ste mthong nas /
NK070(thu)001:6158: de'i don nye bar mnyes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6159: rgyal ba de dag gi rgya chen po rig pa'i gsung gis che ba'i yon tan gyi bstod pas /
NK070(thu)001:6162: dgongs pa'i chos ston pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6165: de las mi slob pa'i don 'byung ba bsam yas
NK070(thu)001:6166: lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du byas
NK070(thu)001:6167: pa ni / gzhi rang byung gi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6168: de ma rig pa'i ye shes dang /
NK070(thu)001:6170: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes mngon sum du byas pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:6171: gsum po tshul gcig tu 'gyur bas na mthun pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:6174: rang snang ba'i tshul ci lta bu yin snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6176: lha ma yin gyi yul na dpag bsam gyi shing dang /
NK070(thu)001:6177: mi'i yul na yid bzhin gyis /
NK070(thu)001:6179: lha'i yul na rin po che'i bum pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:6181: ste dgos 'dod 'byung ba kun de dag rdzas yod
NK070(thu)001:6182: du grub pa ni ma yin te gang zhe na
NK070(thu)001:6183: 'gro ba dang rang gi sems kyi snang ba la
NK070(thu)001:6184: bsod nams cha mthun gyi mthus bstan pa min no
NK070(thu)001:6185: // ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK070(thu)001:6186: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK070(thu)001:6188: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK070(thu)001:6191: gzhi ci yang ma yin pa las /
NK070(thu)001:6192: cir yang snang bas ngo mtshar sems kyi cho 'phrul sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las /
NK070(thu)001:6193: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa mtha' yas par
NK070(thu)001:6194: rang 'byung ba ni rmad kyis chos du byung ba
NK070(thu)001:6195: ste / de dag gzhan nas yod pa gcig 'dir bkug pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6197: dper na der bgrod cing phyin pas thob pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6198: de dag rgyu rkyen gang gyi sgo nas ma byas te ma yin /
NK070(thu)001:6199: bar phung po lnga la sogs pa rtog tshogs lha'i /
NK070(thu)001:6200: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar gsal ba 'i thabs snang la 'gag pa med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6201: shes rab rang bzhin med pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:6202: thabs shes rab de nyid rang rig par rgyun du brtan par bsgom pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6203: dpe de lta bu rgyu 'bras gnyis su med par snang ba'i ngang du rang byung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6204: thabs shes de'i rgyu las 'bras bu byung ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6208: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK070(thu)001:6209: thabs kyi phyag rgyar 'gyur ba'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:6210: ye shes la ni ye shes rol //
NK070(thu)001:6212: rig pa ni chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid kho na'i yin pa phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6213: de nyid dngos po gang du yang ma dmigs par rang gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6214: ngo bo nyid kyi shes rab bo //
NK070(thu)001:6215: de ka la ming gi rnam grangs su mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings zhes kyang bya /
NK070(thu)001:6217: de ka theg pa chen po'i chos nyid de bzhin nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:6218: don dam de nyid ye gdod ma nas 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:6219: bkor lnga thams cad lhun gyis grub pa nyid thabs
NK070(thu)001:6220: kun ye shes phyag rgyar rang snang ste /
NK070(thu)001:6221: gyur pa'i phyir ni gdul bya'i ngo na lam gyi zhen pa dag pa'i stobs kyi /
NK070(thu)001:6224: gzhi don dam 00lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:6225: nyid la ni 'bras bu kun rdzob grangs bsam gyis
NK070(thu)001:6226: mi khyab pa'i ye shes su rang snang bas 'dus
NK070(thu)001:6227: byas min pa de la ni rol zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:6228: kho na'o // 'o na 'bras bur snang ba de
NK070(thu)001:6229: dag yod pa'i mtshan mar gyur pa dogs pa la
NK070(thu)001:6230: kho na'o // / gong gis ye shes 00rol pa nyid 1kyang gsos /
NK070(thu)001:6231: te gsob snying po med pa ya ma rla ste /
NK070(thu)001:6234: ye shes rol 1pa de'i ngo bo nyid kyang ni dngos po rang rgyud pa /
NK070(thu)001:6235: cir yang gzung du med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6236: sa gsod ces bya ste snying po med /
NK070(thu)001:6237: 'o na snying po med pa dpe 'gro ba'i don
NK070(thu)001:6238: brten par byed mi nus so snyam du dogs pa
NK070(thu)001:6239: la / rgyal ba mngon byung skyob pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:6240: byin brlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK070(thu)001:6241: bya byed nus pa'i gzi byin gyis //
NK070(thu)001:6242: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po'i mchog /
NK070(thu)001:6244: rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams gdul bya 'gro ba drug
NK070(thu)001:6245: la mngon sum du 'byung ba sdug bsngal las skyob
NK070(thu)001:6246: par / snang ba'i sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK070(thu)001:6247: byin brlabs kyis chos de dag ston pa'i longs spyod
NK070(thu)001:6248: kyi sku'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyang gis sgras gong
NK070(thu)001:6249: du bshad pa'i ye shes la ni ye shes rol
NK070(thu)001:6250: / ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog /
NK070(thu)001:6251: ces dpe don tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyi tshul kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6252: de bzhin du don chos nyid rang byung ye shes rang snang ba yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:6254: gsungs yan lag drug cu dang /
NK070(thu)001:6255: thugs ye shes kyi don bya byed nus pa'i gzi byin dang /
NK070(thu)001:6256: sgyu ma'i lta bu rol pas phrin las kyi gzugs
NK070(thu)001:6257: sku gnyis cir yang snang nas don byed tsam na
NK070(thu)001:6258: / rgyal ba rang gi ngo bo nyid ni chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6259: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir skye 'jig med pas 1 rdo rje'i sku ste /
NK070(thu)001:6261: de 'das byas las khyad par 'phags pa sa na mchog kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6263: mthar phyin pa 'bras bu de dag gis dbyer med
NK070(thu)001:6264: dam lhun grub kyi ngo bo nyid bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:6265: / gcig khadang ka du mar bral ba'i //
NK070(thu)001:6266: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nganyid //
NK070(thu)001:6267: sangs chargyas kyi kyang mi gzigs te //
NK070(thu)001:6268: rang kabyung ye shes cagnas jamed snang //
NK070(thu)001:6270: rgyal ba gcig gi ngo bo la yang chos thams
NK070(thu)001:6271: cad rig pa bdag nyid chen por 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:6272: / phan tshun tha dad ma yin pa'i tshul gyi gsal bas du ma dang bral /
NK070(thu)001:6274: gnyis med de nyid kyi tshul gyis thabs snang ba rnams ni ma 'dres par snang tshogs /
NK070(thu)001:6277: thabs chen po ma 'dres par snang ba rnam par thar pa'i sa /
NK070(thu)001:6278: don dmigs su med par bde gshegs nyid kyi chos
NK070(thu)001:6279: kyi dbyings thugs su chud pas nad du mar bral
NK070(thu)001:6280: / dus bzhi rgyal ba kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can yin pa dang mnyam pa 'ub /
NK070(thu)001:6283: de la yod pa 'o mtha' dang /
NK070(thu)001:6285: de gnyis spangs pas dbus dang /
NK070(thu)001:6288: skye 'gag 'gro 'ong la sogs pa'i mtha' dbus thams cad kun las 'das pa'i phyir ngo bo nyid /
NK070(thu)001:6290: bstan du med par 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK070(thu)001:6291: lhun gyis grub pa nyid rgyu rkyen med par rang
NK070(thu)001:6292: snang ba'i rang byung ba'i de bzhin 1nyid mngon du
NK070(thu)001:6293: byas pa'i phyir / ye shes te /
NK070(thu)001:6294: de ka la ming grangs su de 1bzhin nyid du gshegs so //
NK070(thu)001:6297: sangs rgyas de nyid kyis kyang yul yul can du mi gzigs te /
NK070(thu)001:6298: de ni gnas bya'i yul dang /
NK070(thu)001:6300: 1gnyis su med pas 'khor 'das kyi thams cad du rang snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6302: 'o na yul dang yul can 1gnyis su bya ba med pas /
NK070(thu)001:6303: gdul bya 'gro drug rgyal ba'i ye shes dam rdzas thugs rjes mi gzigs so bar dogs pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6304: log par rtog brtag rnam dag cing //
NK070(thu)001:6305: ye shes dbyings la mi gzhan phyir //
NK070(thu)001:6306: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK070(thu)001:6307: 'gro drug dus nas ma lus snang //
NK070(thu)001:6309: dus thams cad du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK070(thu)001:6310: rang rig pa kho na'i yin pa phyir gzung 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:6311: gnyis su med pa la gzung 'dzin gnyis su rtog
NK070(thu)001:6312: pa ni / de ma yin la der 'dzin pas log par rtog pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:6313: log rtog la gom pa 1de'i rgyun gyis gzung 'dzin de nyid du snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6315: gshis la ma grub pas glo bur pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6316: gang gnyis su snang ba dang zhen pa de las log pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6321: dper na chu rnyogs ma dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar /
NK070(thu)001:6323: dag pa'i phyir 'gro ba drug po ril rang rig
NK070(thu)001:6324: pa'i ye shes 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i dbyings las mi
NK070(thu)001:6326: 'gro ba gdul bya thams cad ye shes des mkhyen cing /
NK070(thu)001:6327: zin pa'i thugs dang dbyings des thams cad la khyab pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6329: ye shes dbyings la mi gzhan pa'am gdul bya gdul
NK070(thu)001:6330: byed gnyis su mi rtog pa'i phyir ram chen po
NK070(thu)001:6331: 'brel pa'o // de ltar gtan tshigs gsum 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6332: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na /
NK070(thu)001:6334: gnyis su mi phyed pa de kho na theg pa mchog gsang sngags gi lugs kyi thugs rje'o //
NK070(thu)001:6336: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med rtogs na //
NK070(thu)001:6337: thugs rje chen po skyo zhes de la bya //
NK070(thu)001:6339: gnyis su med pa de'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6340: rgyal ba'i ye shes la gdul bya 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus thams cad yul yul can gyi /
NK070(thu)001:6341: rtog pa med par gsal zhing snang ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6344: man ngag gi rim pas bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6347: dgu pa dad brtson brtul shugs zhes bshad pa'i rjes su dbang bskur nye bar 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6351: rang don du che ba'i yon tan 00thams cad thob pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6352: gzhan don du chos thams cad la rang dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6355: 0don gnyis dang ldan par 0yang rjes su mthun pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6357: de nyid rang gzhan gyi don gnyis kyi phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6358: de'i phyogs kyi dbang gis nges pa'i tshigs su 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:6359: de lta bu dad brtson brtul zhugs kyi snod gsum
NK070(thu)001:6360: po rang gi blo la 'tshams par thob par byed
NK070(thu)001:6361: pa'i phyir / thob pa sbyin par 'gro bas sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6362: gsang sngags dbang po rab kyi spyod yul yin pas
NK070(thu)001:6363: gdams ngag 'jug pa'i go rim la brtul zhugs can
NK070(thu)001:6365: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK070(thu)001:6366: bde ba'i rgyu tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK070(thu)001:6367: rdo rje'i lam nas pad+mora bskyil //
NK070(thu)001:6368: rtse nas gtim nas dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK070(thu)001:6370: de ni bdag gis brjod par mi nus kyang /
NK070(thu)001:6372: bla ma mi khabskyod pa yab yum du gsal ba'i rol pa las byung ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:6373: yab kyi bde 1ba 'i rnam pa gsal zhing yum gyi bde ba'i ngo bo mi dmigs pa //
NK070(thu)001:6374: kashes rab yum lo nyi shu ma 1thabs yab kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6375: ra gsal ba las zhes pa /
NK070(thu)001:6376: yab kyi ga rdo rje'i lam nas byung ba'i bde
NK070(thu)001:6377: ba'i ye shes yi ge h'u gi 'bru tshogs su
NK070(thu)001:6378: rgyal ba'i byang chub sems kyis //
NK070(thu)001:6379: chu rgyun yum gyis pad mo'i las byung ba'i byang sems bde ba /
NK070(thu)001:6380: ye shes kyang bsdus te rtsa'i rtse mo gnyis su 'khyil pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:6381: byang sems yungs kar gyi tshad tsam dkar la 'tsher ba'i rnam pa rdo rje sems //
NK070(thu)001:6383: rdo rje sna rtse'i rtse nas slob bu'i lce rtse ru 'i thabs kyis rdo rje dang /
NK070(thu)001:6384: yum gyi sna rtse dang bu'i lce rtse gsum po gang rung gis shes rab kyi /
NK070(thu)001:6385: thabs shes gnyis kyi gsang dbang sbyin pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:6387: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i snying kha chos kyi khams la bstim zhing de'i tshe /
NK070(thu)001:6389: rtsa bzhi'i nang na yod pa'i 'gro drug bskyed pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:6390: sa bon ni chos nyid kyi rtsa na sum tri gnyis /
NK070(thu)001:6392: yon tan na pre du gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:6393: zung gsum 1dang rang rgyud kyi rtsa na sems las byung ba'i gnyid kyi rtog pa 1dang bcas //
NK070(thu)001:6395: 1gnas ngan len pa'i 'i bag chags dang /
NK070(thu)001:6398: cir 'gyur na yul sems su dmigs pa /
NK070(thu)001:6403: gsal bas dper na sa bon tshigs pa las myu gu mi skye ba'i bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:6406: thabs kyi dbang gis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6407: gsang dbang de las gzhan pa yang gnyis shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bshad par bya ba //
NK070(thu)001:6409: rjes su mthun par slob bu thabs mi rnyed par
NK070(thu)001:6410: gsal pa'i nga rgyal gyi 'jug pa'i shes rab yum
NK070(thu)001:6411: phyag rgya mo lo bcu drug lon pa nyid //
NK070(thu)001:6412: la sbyor ba zil pa'i lta bu /
NK070(thu)001:6413: byang sems kyi thig le sngon ltar rdo rje'i lam
NK070(thu)001:6414: nas bde ba'i ye shes yi ge h'u gi 'bru
NK070(thu)001:6415: tshogs su gsal ba'i byang sems chu rgyun yum gyis
NK070(thu)001:6419: dga' ba bcu drug gis phyed la brgyad de'i phyed la bzhi /
NK070(thu)001:6420: de lhan cig skyes pa'i gsang gnas su thig le gcig /
NK070(thu)001:6421: du bsdus pa de yum gyi phan tshun rdo rje rtse dang sna rtse nas /
NK070(thu)001:6422: thig le bzhi bzhi las bzhi shogs gnyis mnyam du /
NK070(thu)001:6423: dgod pa'i stobs kyis 'dres par gnyis pas /
NK070(thu)001:6424: yab la bde ba'am gsal ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:6425: yum la mi rtog pa'i bde ba gnyis po'i ngo bo nyid //
NK070(thu)001:6426: ni gsum pa'i zung du 'brel pa /
NK070(thu)001:6428: gyi ngang gsal bar shar bas bsgyur ba'i sgra //
NK070(thu)001:6430: de rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor te
NK070(thu)001:6431: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:6432: // gnyis po de las gzhan pa yang gsum pa bde chen gyi dbang bshad par bya ba //
NK070(thu)001:6434: thabs slob bu rdo rje sems dpa'i nga rgyal gyis
NK070(thu)001:6435: shes rab yum lo bcu gnyis ma la nyi ma
NK070(thu)001:6436: la byang sems 'dzeg pa'i dus su /
NK070(thu)001:6439: rol pa las phung po lnga la /
NK070(thu)001:6440: sogs pa rtog tshogs zhe gnyis lha'i sku phyag rgya'i chen po tshogs dang ldan //
NK070(thu)001:6441: nas yab gyi gsang ba rdo rje de'i lam nas
NK070(thu)001:6442: bde ba'i ye shes zla ba byang sems yi ge
NK070(thu)001:6443: h'u gi 'bru tshogs su gsal ba'i chu rgyun yum
NK070(thu)001:6444: gyi pad+mora bsil bar byed cing 'khyil pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6445: shes rab yum gyi nyi ma dngos //
NK070(thu)001:6446: gnyis yab yum gnyis kas dus gcig tu bde stong ro mnyam pa'i thig le che //
NK070(thu)001:6448: yab yum gyi dga' ba re re la bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug pa phrag gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:6449: sum cu rtsa gnyis la mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis rdzogs shing //
NK070(thu)001:6450: yab kyi zla ba'i thig le dga' ba bcu drug re re la /
NK070(thu)001:6451: ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pa lnga phrag /
NK070(thu)001:6453: ni dpe byad brgyad cu la sogs dpag tu med //
NK070(thu)001:6454: cing rtsis las 'das pa'i mtshan dape'o //
NK070(thu)001:6455: pha rol gzhan gyi sems shes pa'i mngon par shes pa dang ldan //
NK070(thu)001:6457: sems lnga'i ma mtha' thig le phan tshun 'gro 'ong du shes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6458: rdzu 'phrul kyi bya shes pa'i mngon shes //
NK070(thu)001:6460: lhan cig skyes dag'i gnas nas slar log pa ni rtse nas thim zhes pa'i sgras //
NK070(thu)001:6461: yod med kyi mtha' gnyis kyi ma gos pa bcu gnyis /
NK070(thu)001:6464: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i rtsa /
NK070(thu)001:6465: gnas nas byang sems rtsa gnas so sor bkye ba yis //
NK070(thu)001:6466: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa lnga la stsogs pa grangs mtha' yas pa kun //
NK070(thu)001:6467: ye nas lha'i rang bzhin nyid yin pa las thabs
NK070(thu)001:6468: kyi lha sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK070(thu)001:6469: rang gsal bas // ra bsgyur ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6470: bcu gsum pa yi ge'i 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis ru brjod //
NK070(thu)001:6473: nyan byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6474: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6475: bdag don gyi brtson 'grus can la nus pa'i dbang nyan dbang dang bsgom dbang gnyis ston te /
NK070(thu)001:6476: dang po nyan dbang ni slob bu rnams kyi nyan byed de /
NK070(thu)001:6477: rna ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i nang na bcud 'dus
NK070(thu)001:6478: pa'i thig le shin tu dwangs ba gnas pa ni
NK070(thu)001:6480: nus su yod pa de mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK070(thu)001:6482: rtsa ni rdo rje slob dpon kun bzang yab yum du bsgom pa'i thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum las /
NK070(thu)001:6483: 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi lte ba mu khyud dang bcas pa bar 'khyams med pa /
NK070(thu)001:6484: gzhal yas khang sgo dang bcas par bsgom /
NK070(thu)001:6485: la de'i nang du sgra gsal bar byed pa'i thig
NK070(thu)001:6486: le reg shes kyi ngo bo nyid tram zung lngar
NK070(thu)001:6487: ya bcu dang dzahmh'u bam hoh gyur pa las /
NK070(thu)001:6488: cho ga gsum gyis rin po che'i dkyil 'khor rin
NK070(thu)001:6489: 'byung yab yum gyis gtso bo byas pa'i rigs chung
NK070(thu)001:6490: gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad bcu sgo ba yab
NK070(thu)001:6491: yum bzhi dang bcas par lha bco brgyad kyi phyag
NK070(thu)001:6492: rgya'i tshogs mchog bskyed pa la rin po che 'byung
NK070(thu)001:6495: yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams nas byang sems
NK070(thu)001:6496: 'phro 'du las lha 'od du gyur nas bu la
NK070(thu)001:6497: thim pas / slob bu yang 'od du zhu pa las 'od dpung ser por gyur pa las /
NK070(thu)001:6498: rin chen 'byung ldan du byas shing dbang rdzas po ti gtad la /
NK070(thu)001:6499: tram ni glu'i mgo drang la /
NK070(thu)001:6500: gsang ba ma h+aa gsang chen a nu gsang mchog a ti'i bstan pa /
NK070(thu)001:6503: zhes bya ba la rtsoogs pa nas gzhan du smra bar bya ba min gyi bar /
NK070(thu)001:6505: bsgom dbang ni dran pa gsal ba'i ra byed pa /
NK070(thu)001:6506: rten snying kha'i rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6507: zhes bya ba la sogs pa lha bsgom pa ni nyan dbang dang /
NK070(thu)001:6509: snying la yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa'i rigs
NK070(thu)001:6510: kyi dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs su bskyed pa nas bzung
NK070(thu)001:6511: ste / dus gsum rgyal ba la sogs pa la dbang rdzas /
NK070(thu)001:6513: lag pa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6514: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6515: gzhan don gyi brtson 'grus can la nus pa'i dbang
NK070(thu)001:6516: gnyis las dang po phrin las kyi dbang ston ste
NK070(thu)001:6517: / sbyin pa ni nyan dbang dang rjes su mthun te /
NK070(thu)001:6518: lag pa'i 'dom rtsa gnyis la 'khor lo'i gzhan nas bzung ste /
NK070(thu)001:6519: las kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor yan chad kyi bar snga bzhin bsgom mo //
NK070(thu)001:6520: khyod ni rdo rje can zhes sogs brjod la dbang rdzas rdo rje rgya gram sbyin no //
NK070(thu)001:6521: smra byed lce'i 'dam rtsar b+h+r+aum 'phros pa las 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi pa gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6522: zhes bya ba nas gsal spros thim zhes pa la sogs pa ni 'chad pa'i dbang ste /
NK070(thu)001:6523: pad+ma'i rigs lha bco brgyad bsgom pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:6524: chos kyi bdud rtsi zhes sogs brjod la dbang rdzas 'khor lo sbyin no //
NK070(thu)001:6525: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang ni /
NK070(thu)001:6526: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK070(thu)001:6527: zhes bya ba la stsogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6528: dbang phyug rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams chen po'i dbang ste /
NK070(thu)001:6529: bskyod chen yan lag lnga las dang ma 'go'i mig
NK070(thu)001:6530: la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga la zung lnga ya
NK070(thu)001:6531: bcu lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga h'u zung
NK070(thu)001:6532: lnga / de bzhin g.yon pa la tram'am s+w+aa rkang
NK070(thu)001:6533: pa g.yon gyi sor mo la h+r+ai 'am am g.yas
NK070(thu)001:6534: la hah rnams la ya bcu bcu'o //
NK070(thu)001:6535: lus kyis phyogs mtshams su h'u zung bcu'o //
NK070(thu)001:6536: yi ge tshogs de dag las tshom bu lnga 'i
NK070(thu)001:6537: dkyil 'khor yab yum lnga bcu dang khro bo bcu
NK070(thu)001:6538: khro mo bcu'i phreng ba rnams bskyed pa yongs su
NK070(thu)001:6539: gyur pa las / slob pa kun por gyur par
NK070(thu)001:6540: bsgom la dbang rdzas rdo rje dang dril bu gtad
NK070(thu)001:6541: gyur pa las / de / phyogs bcu dus bzhi zhes sogs kyi tshigs bcad brjod do //
NK070(thu)001:6542: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6543: dam tshig dbang gi slob dpon de la slob bu rab kyis shes rab bsgrub pa /
NK070(thu)001:6545: lus ngag tha mas zang zing gis mnyes par ma byas shing /
NK070(thu)001:6546: phan nus zab mo'i dbang rnams thob par ma byas pa zhes bya ba la sogs te go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:6547: rgyu 'bras don gyi go rim du 'khrugs sdebs dgos te /
NK070(thu)001:6550: dbu gargyan khacod pan phreng ba dang //
NK070(thu)001:6551: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK070(thu)001:6552: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK070(thu)001:6553: kasnying po lnga la dbang bskur na //
NK070(thu)001:6555: dngos su bskur ba ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:6557: khams lnga'i bcud lnga dpa' bo 'bru lngar gnas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:6558: snying po lnga'i mtshungs rgyu dang ro rkyang bde ba'i
NK070(thu)001:6559: lam gnyis g.yas g.yon nas 'phyang ba cod pan dang
NK070(thu)001:6560: // rtsa dbu ma a ba d+hu ti'i nang du
NK070(thu)001:6561: bcud thig le 'dud pa'i yungs kar gyi tshad mtshan
NK070(thu)001:6562: // dang ldan pa // phreng ba'i dad pa khyab pa go cha'i /
NK070(thu)001:6563: lus la rtsa sa ya phrag bcu gsum gyis dra ba'i rtsa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6565: dbang po rgyal mtshan gyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:6566: phung po lnga la sogs pa rtogs tshogs thams cad sku dang /
NK070(thu)001:6567: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas pa phyag rgya'i dang glad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo //
NK070(thu)001:6568: gdugs kyi dang lus nyid bum pa /
NK070(thu)001:6569: h'u gis mgrin pa na ro drug /
NK070(thu)001:6570: gam rtsa gnas su thig le h'u gi rnam pas gang la bum pa'i dang /
NK070(thu)001:6571: bde ba'i ye shes dang bcas //
NK070(thu)001:6573: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga //
NK070(thu)001:6574: ru gnas pa dbu rgyan gyi mtshungs rgyu'o //
NK070(thu)001:6575: sngags dang dbang rdzas rab gnas can dang rgyu'i dgongs
NK070(thu)001:6576: pas rgyu gang yin pa de rkyen gyis bslang ba
NK070(thu)001:6577: // kun nas dbang don ldang zhing duhkha las skyob pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:6578: sdug bsngal las grol nas rgyal ba'i rigs su nges //
NK070(thu)001:6579: zhes 'byung ba'i phyir phan pa'i dbang kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6580: dbang thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin pa'i sras //
NK070(thu)001:6582: zhes bya ba la sogs pa nas bde ba phun
NK070(thu)001:6583: sum tshogs pa zhes pa'i bar ni go sla ste
NK070(thu)001:6584: / phan pa'i dbang gi yon tan thun mong du
NK070(thu)001:6585: mtho ris kyi lha tshangs pa brgya byin lta bu
NK070(thu)001:6586: dang mir skyes na yang 'khor lo bsgyur ba'am /
NK070(thu)001:6587: dbang por te rgyal po gyur la nus pa'i dbang lnga thob na /
NK070(thu)001:6588: thar pa'i lam ston pa'i bdag por rig 'dzin du'am dge ba'i bshes gnyen mkhas par 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:6589: zab mo'i dbang gsum thob pa'i yon tan ni rigs
NK070(thu)001:6590: kyi bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa kun tu bzang
NK070(thu)001:6591: po nyid du 'gyur bar nges so //
NK070(thu)001:6593: le'u bcu pa mdog bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6595: // de nas ting nge 'dzin bzhi pa spros pa la gnas pa rnams kyi don du /
NK070(thu)001:6596: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6597: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs /
NK070(thu)001:6598: rgyal po dbang bsgyur ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6599: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bya ba le'u bzhi pa'i
NK070(thu)001:6600: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yab yum kho na la bya
NK070(thu)001:6601: ba'i phyir / 1tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs 'dir yang tshom bu lnga pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6602: yab yum bdun cu la sogs pa gsum pa la
NK070(thu)001:6603: zhe drug gcig pa la bco brgyad pa rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:6604: phyag rgya zung du 'brel pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6605: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i yang rgyal po'o //
NK070(thu)001:6606: 1de dag gi dus su tshogs kyi longs spyod lnga
NK070(thu)001:6607: po thams cad ldan pa'i phyir yang rgyal po zhes
NK070(thu)001:6608: bya'o // rnal 'byor pa 'dus pa de dag gtan tshigs rtogs pa rnam pa bzhis /
NK070(thu)001:6609: rtogs tshogs thams cad kyang 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK070(thu)001:6610: shes kho nar gsal ba'i phyir spyod yul yongs su
NK070(thu)001:6611: dag pa'i bsgyur ba zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6612: de lta bu'i don ston pa'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin mngon du snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:6613: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig ste /
NK070(thu)001:6614: snyoms par zhugs nas zhes sogs gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6615: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul /
NK070(thu)001:6616: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6617: lta ba'i gtan tshig rnam par dbye ba ston te /
NK070(thu)001:6618: rgyu 1dang rang byung ye shes rang snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6621: de dag mya ngan las 'das pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK070(thu)001:6622: 1rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang log rtog kun brtag gi rgyun las /
NK070(thu)001:6625: chos can 111de gnyis zhan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6627: gsal bas mtshon tshul gyi dbye ba tha dad kyang don la ngo bo gcig ste /
NK070(thu)001:6630: 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa dang rkyen las nyon
NK070(thu)001:6631: gnyis po nyid dper na rgyal po phru gu 'bangs
NK070(thu)001:6632: su 'khyams pa bzhin don las nor yang /
NK070(thu)001:6633: rang gi ngo bo rang ye shes las mi 'gyur bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6635: gti mug ces ni brjod pa yang //
NK070(thu)001:6636: ma rig pa'i nang tshan gyi ming gi rnam grangs te //
NK070(thu)001:6638: de yang gnyis med kyi don gcig yin par bshad //
NK070(thu)001:6641: phyin ci log nyid yang dag ste //
NK070(thu)001:6642: ma rig pa de nyid ye shes su gsal //
NK070(thu)001:6644: nyon mongs sdug bsngal de rang byang chub mchog /
NK070(thu)001:6647: log rtog nyid du snang ba de rig pa rang
NK070(thu)001:6648: snang bas na he du grub pa'i don ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:6649: rang byung gi ye shes kho na yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:6650: de'i ngo bo ni gzhal la phyogs gcig tu bstan
NK070(thu)001:6651: du med pa ni mnyam pa'i chen po dbyings su
NK070(thu)001:6652: gsal bas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi rgyu
NK070(thu)001:6654: yig 'bru'i tshul la ni yi ge gsum ste rgyu
NK070(thu)001:6655: 0nyid kyi phyir shes bya'i chos thams cad sems nyid
NK070(thu)001:6656: las / gzhan gang yang ma grub pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6657: sems de nyid yin khags cir yang ma skyes pa
NK070(thu)001:6658: ni yi ge a'i tshul ste gsung rdo rje gi
NK070(thu)001:6659: rang bzhin no // ngo bo nyid phyogs gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:6660: ma grub pa'i rig pa'i rtsal cir yang snang ba
NK070(thu)001:6661: rang bzhin no // ni / a la na ro o snang ba'i tshul ste /
NK070(thu)001:6663: de dag gi brjod byed kyis tshigs la snga phyir snang yang /
NK070(thu)001:6664: brjod bya don gcig par rtog pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lngar gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6665: yi ge gyi tshul ste thugs rdo rje kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6666: tshon dang 'dra ba'i yi ge a gcig la tshul
NK070(thu)001:6667: gsum gyi don mtshon nas ras dkar po dang 'dra
NK070(thu)001:6668: ba'i kaphung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog pa thams
NK070(thu)001:6669: cad kha dog dmar por bsgyur ba dang 'dra ba'i
NK070(thu)001:6670: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su sangs rgyas par byin
NK070(thu)001:6674: mngon sum par zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6675: spyir mngon sum la dbang po yid rnal 'byor rang rig bzhi las /
NK070(thu)001:6676: 'dir chos nyid lta bya'i yul lta byed kyi mkhan
NK070(thu)001:6677: po gnyis su med par rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK070(thu)001:6678: mo // stong bzhi po des chos thams cad sngar
NK070(thu)001:6679: bshad pa'i rjes su spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:6681: grub mtha' rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa grangs bzhi
NK070(thu)001:6682: po shes byed yin pa chos thams cad rang rig
NK070(thu)001:6683: pa'i mngon du rdzogs shing rang rig par dbang bsgyur
NK070(thu)001:6684: bas rgyal po grub mtha' gzhan med pas che ba'o
NK070(thu)001:6686: yan lag lnga dbang po lnga rnam shes lnga po kun //
NK070(thu)001:6687: rnam min du shes par bya //
NK070(thu)001:6689: 'di nas bsdus don mar spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston te /
NK070(thu)001:6690: lnga gsum po 'di dag tu rang gi rig pa
NK070(thu)001:6691: nyid du rang snang bar shes pas rtog pa phra
NK070(thu)001:6692: rags sam rab 'bring tha mar 'i rnam pa /
NK070(thu)001:6693: yin te mi snang gi thams cad rig pa bdag
NK070(thu)001:6694: nyid chen po lhun grub du gsal ba ni ye
NK070(thu)001:6695: shes lnga'i ngo bo la yi ge cha lnga du
NK070(thu)001:6696: shes par bya zhes brdar bstan to //
NK070(thu)001:6697: de la zhi khro'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi
NK070(thu)001:6698: skabs su dbang po rnam shes 'khrul pa'i snang ba
NK070(thu)001:6699: rnams lha'i ngo bor rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge
NK070(thu)001:6701: zhi khro rigs lnga bsgom pa yang mi 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6702: zhi ba 1rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:6703: zhi ba las gdam ka yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:6705: gzugs sgra dri ro reg la sogs //
NK070(thu)001:6706: rnam smin mum du shes par bya //
NK070(thu)001:6708: 'dod yon lnga'i rgyu sems nyid kyis rang snang bas
NK070(thu)001:6709: 'bras bu gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la sogs
NK070(thu)001:6710: pa yul gyi snang ba yang rig pa bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:6711: chen po las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6712: yul lnga'i rnam pa gang du yang rang rgyud du
NK070(thu)001:6713: snang ba min te med par rang gsal ba ni
NK070(thu)001:6714: / mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings te /
NK070(thu)001:6715: mtshon byed yi ge mum du shes par bya zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6716: gzhan zhi khro'i yum gyis dkyil 'khor gnyis bsgom pa ni yab dang rjes su mthun pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6717: tshogs kyi yo byad thun mong pa bzhi byin gyis brlabs cing spyad pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6718: zhi ba'i chos gos lnga dang khro bo'i stag sham
NK070(thu)001:6719: la sogs dang zhi ba'i rin po che'i rgyan brgyad
NK070(thu)001:6720: dang khro bo la sbrul dang thod rgyan bza' ba
NK070(thu)001:6721: dang btung ba dang glu tshig dang //
NK070(thu)001:6722: bro gar tshogs kyi sprin dpung las //
NK070(thu)001:6723: h'u du shes pas rab spyad na //
NK070(thu)001:6729: rigs so so'i bro gar 'du 'phro dang /
NK070(thu)001:6731: rgyas pa'i rgyud kyi don brgyad pa las bro gar rtse 'jo le'u gcig gis bstan to //
NK070(thu)001:6732: bzhi po de dag tu mang bar spyod pa'i phyir na /
NK070(thu)001:6733: tshogs kyis dang sprin dpung la zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6735: rang rig tu shes pas de rab tu spyad na
NK070(thu)001:6736: bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis spyod bzhin du ye shes
NK070(thu)001:6737: kyis tshogs kyis ma chags pa dper na chu la
NK070(thu)001:6738: nyam nga med par 1nya dang mkha' la zhan pa
NK070(thu)001:6739: med pa 11bya lta bu'i tshul gyi bag chags kyis
NK070(thu)001:6740: mi gos par slar tshogs chen po gnyis su 'byung
NK070(thu)001:6741: ba ni / ngo mtshar 'byung ba zhes bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:6742: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa /
NK070(thu)001:6745: yo byad lnga pa gsang ba a li ka li /
NK070(thu)001:6746: byin gyis brlabs pa bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:6747: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK070(thu)001:6748: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:6751: nus pa dang dngos su rang dgugs pa yang yin la /
NK070(thu)001:6752: yang na lo grangs ni lo bcu gnyis bcu drug nyi shu ma /
NK070(thu)001:6754: yang na mtshan rab 'bring tha ma gsum ngam rtsa'i
NK070(thu)001:6755: mtshan 'dab ma brgyad pa rab 'dab bzhi 'bring tha
NK070(thu)001:6757: yang 1zla ba dkar po 'dzag pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6758: nyi ma 1 dang dmar po 'dzag pa ldan 11pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6761: yang sbyor thabs kyis dbang du yum bdag nyid bde ba rigs ngan dang /
NK070(thu)001:6762: gzhan yab bde ba klu mo dang /
NK070(thu)001:6763: gnyis ka bde ba bskyed pa lha mo dang de rnams kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6764: lta bsgom gyi nus pa chung na dabye'am /
NK070(thu)001:6765: yang nus pa che na mi dbye bar /
NK070(thu)001:6767: rang gi sbyor thabs mkhas mi mkhas dang sbyar ro //
NK070(thu)001:6769: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen pa //
NK070(thu)001:6770: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK070(thu)001:6772: 'di dag spyir lam gyi bsnyen sgrub kyi /
NK070(thu)001:6774: bsnyen pa ni stong pa chen po dang snying rje
NK070(thu)001:6775: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gong ma don dam pa
NK070(thu)001:6776: kun rdzob gnyis kyi byang chub kyi sems nyams su
NK070(thu)001:6777: len pa'o // nye ba'i bsnyen pa phyag rgyar gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6778: ting nge 'dzin 'og ma phyag rgya gcig spros /
NK070(thu)001:6782: yo byad lngas tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6784: de'i dus su a li ka li'i bde ba nyams
NK070(thu)001:6785: su lon pa ste de la sbyor ba thabs kyi
NK070(thu)001:6786: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:6787: a li phyag rgya ma mtshan ldan ma snyed nas /
NK070(thu)001:6788: lus bsrung gos barje dam tshig sbyin pa'i chos gsum
NK070(thu)001:6789: gyis brtan par byas pa'am yang na chos bshad dbang
NK070(thu)001:6792: tshogs kyi yo byad bzhi dang /
NK070(thu)001:6793: gos rgyan gyis mdzes par byas /
NK070(thu)001:6796: bro glu shes pa g.yon pa bskyed la /
NK070(thu)001:6797: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos cha drug cu kyis /
NK070(thu)001:6798: bde ba rgyas par byas pa ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6799: phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par zhugs pa ni bsgrub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6800: nyi zla'i thig le rdo rje'i lces blang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6802: 1de nyid gsal bar tan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6803: rgyal ba mchod pa yum gyi pad+ma'i gsang ba dkyil 'khor du /
NK070(thu)001:6804: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:6805: stong gsum yungs 'brur zhes pa le'u dgu par rgyas par bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:6806: dngos grub blang ba bsgrub pa nyi zla'i snying po de //
NK070(thu)001:6807: dkyil 'khor rdo rje lce yis blangs //
NK070(thu)001:6809: snyoms 'jug gis bsgrub pa las 'byung ba'i phyir na bsgrub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6812: nyi zla'i thig le gnyis gcig tu 'dres ste /
NK070(thu)001:6813: yon tan thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa snying po'o //
NK070(thu)001:6815: bde ba ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6817: rlung gi stobs kyis slar rang gnas su 'dren par byed pas rdo rje nyid lce 00yin pas na /
NK070(thu)001:6818: don de la tshigs de skad ces bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6819: blang ba 'i thabs ni le'u bcu par bde chen dbang du bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:6820: tha mal te thabs kyis ma zin pa ni rlung
NK070(thu)001:6821: gi tshur bzlog ma nus pa rnams kyi dbang du
NK070(thu)001:6822: rang gi lce la rdo rje rtse lnga par bsgom
NK070(thu)001:6823: pa ni rdo rje lce ste /
NK070(thu)001:6824: des blangs nas thig le zos /
NK070(thu)001:6825: pa'i thun mong gi yon tan ni /
NK070(thu)001:6826: nam mkha' la 'phur na bya bzhin du 'gro ba
NK070(thu)001:6827: dang kha dog gsal zhing gzi brjid 'bar ba dang
NK070(thu)001:6828: tshe ring ba la sogs pa thob na zhes bya'o
NK070(thu)001:6829: // 00snga ma'i yon tan mchog gi dngos grub yon tan yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar ram /
NK070(thu)001:6830: yid la bsam pa bzhin du 'byung ste /
NK070(thu)001:6831: sprin tsam gyi bdag sogs drug pa 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:6833: tshogs bsgrubs de dag gi zhing bsgral ba thugs rjes
NK070(thu)001:6834: ni gzhan las rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa bstan
NK070(thu)001:6835: pa'i phyir / zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK070(thu)001:6836: nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor mkhas pas bzhag /
NK070(thu)001:6837: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:6838: spyir zhing gyur pa la gong ma'i yon tan 'byung zhing mchod pa'i zhing ni /
NK070(thu)001:6839: bkra shis pa dag pa'i skye ba bdun pa lta bu dang /
NK070(thu)001:6840: 'go ma la thugs rje 'byung ba'i zhing /
NK070(thu)001:6842: 'dir thugs rje'i 'byung ba zhing ste bsgral ba'i zhing bcu po'o //
NK070(thu)001:6843: de la dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK070(thu)001:6844: dam las log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:6846: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK070(thu)001:6850: ngan 'gro yin pas mchog phra na yin ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6851: bcu po de dag rnams lho phyogs e'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:6852: gru gsum gyi steng du nyi zla'i gdan bsam ste
NK070(thu)001:6853: / rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid khro bo 0ta ki'i ra tsar gsal ba /
NK070(thu)001:6854: ting nge 'dzin ma yengs pas gru gsum gyi steng du mgo lho nub rkang pa byang shar te /
NK070(thu)001:6855: 'khor ba'i ril thams cad myang 'das du bzlog par
NK070(thu)001:6856: bya ba'i phyir gan rkyal du bsgyel ba'i snying khar
NK070(thu)001:6858: mkhas pas bzhag pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6859: lugs gzhan du thabs lam ltar na na /
NK070(thu)001:6860: yab yum nyi zla gnyis kyis bsgral bya'i rnam par shes pa la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6861: yang yin pa nga rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:6862: h'u khadu gyur pas rnam par kadag /
NK070(thu)001:6863: dbyings ga su thim nas phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK070(thu)001:6865: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal ba bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:6867: sgrol ba'i ging nyid 0lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyi nga
NK070(thu)001:6868: rgyal ma nyams lag pa'i sor mo'i lnga yi ge
NK070(thu)001:6870: lnga'i 'od zer gyi 'du byed kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:6871: bsgom pas bsgral bya'i snying kha'i rigs drug gis sa
NK070(thu)001:6872: bon a n+ri sum tri pre du drug po nyid
NK070(thu)001:6874: par dag pa'i sems srog mi shigs pa'i thig le
NK070(thu)001:6875: nyid yi ge h'u dkar por drug tu gyur de
NK070(thu)001:6876: yang gcig tu gyur pa byas pa tshur drangs te
NK070(thu)001:6877: ging bdag gis shangs bug g.yon nas glad pa'i rgyas
NK070(thu)001:6878: su phyin / srog dag pa'i lam nas 'ong /
NK070(thu)001:6879: sgal tshig gi rta la brgyud gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas /
NK070(thu)001:6880: rim par brgyud de nas yum gyi mkha' la bab
NK070(thu)001:6881: pa de yab yum gyi byang chub sems kyi dbyings
NK070(thu)001:6882: su bstim nas 'od du zhu ba las phyag rgya
NK070(thu)001:6883: rdo rje 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gyur de yongs
NK070(thu)001:6884: su gyur pa las cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:6886: de nyid nyon mongs pa dug lnga ma spangs /
NK070(thu)001:6887: gnas su dag pa'i rtags su 'od zer sna lnga
NK070(thu)001:6888: rab tu 'phro ba brjid pa dad ldan pa'i spyi
NK070(thu)001:6889: bor 'i gtsug tu rigs kyi bdag po mi bskyod
NK070(thu)001:6890: pa tshon gang ba gcig bsgom pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:6891: 'khor ba las mngon par te rnam par rgyal ba'i bsgom pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:6892: don de la tshigs de skad ces bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6893: ngo mtshar khangan ka'gro thar ba'i lam //
NK070(thu)001:6895: las ngan spyad pas ngan par 'gro ba mi las gyur pa bdun /
NK070(thu)001:6897: 'bras bu ngan par song ba gsum ste bzhi bcu ril thams cad la /
NK070(thu)001:6898: rang gi bsod nams bsags pa med na yang bdag la nyes pas mi gos /
NK070(thu)001:6899: gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyod pa ngo mtshar ba'i
NK070(thu)001:6900: 'bras bu deng na song las thar pa'i thabs 'di
NK070(thu)001:6901: las lhag pa gzhan la med pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:6902: 'o na sgrol ba des don la mi bsgrib sam snyam du dgos pa la /
NK070(thu)001:6903: lta ba rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi ring gis cis kyang mi gos par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6904: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK070(thu)001:6905: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK070(thu)001:6906: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK070(thu)001:6907: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK070(thu)001:6909: sbyor sgrol lam zhing bcu de dag nyid kyi rang
NK070(thu)001:6910: bzhin gyi snang ba ni ye gdod ma nas rang
NK070(thu)001:6911: rgyud can du ma skyes pa med pa don dam
NK070(thu)001:6912: pa de nyid bzhin kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6913: don de la 'gro ba rang gi log rtog gi
NK070(thu)001:6914: ngo bor shar ba yang rgyu ma rig pa dang
NK070(thu)001:6915: / rkyen las nyon 'dus pa tsam las kun rdzob phung por snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6916: rang rgyud du ma grub pa 1sgyu ma ra snang ba lta bu'o //
NK070(thu)001:6917: 1de la ngo bo nyid rang rgyud par yod par mthong ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6918: mig gis snang ngor tho yor la mir 'du shes pa lta bu'i tshul yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:6919: de'i ngang du sbyor sgrol gyi bya ba kun byas
NK070(thu)001:6920: kyang rang rgyud pa med pa'o bden pa gnyis po
NK070(thu)001:6921: gong 'og tu 'di dag ltar shes na /
NK070(thu)001:6923: gsad pa med pa gsad bdo ba'i 'du shes mi
NK070(thu)001:6924: 'jug ste rang kha ma'i dri ma sdug bsngal cha
NK070(thu)001:6927: bden pa'i gtan tshigs de dag la sogs pa'i lta ba'i dag mnyam thun mong pa /
NK070(thu)001:6929: snod bcud rgyud rnam dag rtog cing /
NK070(thu)001:6930: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:6931: sngar le'u gsum pa'i byin rlabs kyi skabs su bshad
NK070(thu)001:6932: pa bzhin rgyu 'byung phung po rnams ye gdod ma
NK070(thu)001:6933: nyid nas / rnam par dag pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6934: de'i rgyu mtshan ni rtog pa thams cad kyang rang rig pa kho nar gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:6935: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su sha stag yin
NK070(thu)001:6936: pas snod 'byung ba lnga'i ngo bor yum lngar dag
NK070(thu)001:6937: pa dang / bcud phung po lnga rigs lngar dag pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:6938: sems rgyud rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad rnams ye
NK070(thu)001:6939: shes lngar dag pa ra rtogs pa'i don la 'khor
NK070(thu)001:6940: ba rang kha ma ngang gis med pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:6941: // mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK070(thu)001:6943: chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su don dam skye
NK070(thu)001:6944: med dang kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa'i mdo sde
NK070(thu)001:6946: dag dang yang mthun pas thun mong gi mnyam gnyis yin la /
NK070(thu)001:6947: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK070(thu)001:6948: don dam mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings dang /
NK070(thu)001:6949: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes ni le'u gsum pa'i skabs su bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:6950: rgyud 'di nyid kyi rang gzhung gi dgongs pa ni sku dang ye shes dbyer med yin pas /
NK070(thu)001:6951: dag pa'i gsum pa skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6952: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK070(thu)001:6954: gzhal bya dngos po 'di rnams la gtan tshig rtogs
NK070(thu)001:6955: pa bzhi dang dag pa gsum mnyam pa bzhi'am gnyis
NK070(thu)001:6956: dang / gtan tshig gsum gyis gzhal nas gtan la
NK070(thu)001:6957: phab pa'i dus su 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di rang
NK070(thu)001:6958: rgyud can du ma grub ste /
NK070(thu)001:6959: dag pa nyid kyi chos can dngos po rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:6960: de kho na nyid ni sku dang ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:6961: dkyil 'khor du ye nas dag par gnas pa ni
NK070(thu)001:6962: / ngo bo nyid kyis kun tu bzang po'i zhing khams zhes bya kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:6963: byed spyod tshogs chen gnyis gyur nas //
NK070(thu)001:6964: yan khalag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK070(thu)001:6965: cho ga kardzogs pa shes pa yis //
NK070(thu)001:6967: nges capar legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:6972: de'i lus ngag yid gsum gyi byed spyod ma 'gag pa bsod nams dang /
NK070(thu)001:6973: mi dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis
NK070(thu)001:6974: su gyur pa ni lta spyod ting 'dzin g+ho 'byor
NK070(thu)001:6975: cing / 'phrug pa gcig gis bsgrub par bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:6976: de yang dang por dgu pa dang bcu pa ltar dbang rim par mnos nas /
NK070(thu)001:6977: de nas lta ba'i gtan tshig gsum pa dang lnga
NK070(thu)001:6978: pa ltar dag mnyam rtogs bzhi'i gtan tshigs gsum gyi
NK070(thu)001:6979: don dngos po'i gnas lugs de kho na nyid kyi
NK070(thu)001:6981: de nas de ting kun ting phyag rgya gcig pa'i
NK070(thu)001:6982: sku gsung thugs gsum gyi cho ga gsum rdzogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:6983: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum shes pa'i don dang
NK070(thu)001:6984: ldan nas bzhi pa phyag rgya spros pa /
NK070(thu)001:6985: la sngags kyi yan lag lnga ma nyams shing /
NK070(thu)001:6986: rim par sems sbyangs te snang ba rnam par 'byed
NK070(thu)001:6987: pa 'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob pa'i rnal
NK070(thu)001:6988: 'byor pa ste de yang tshom bu lnga pa la
NK070(thu)001:6990: gsum pa la bzhi bcu rtsa drug gam /
NK070(thu)001:6991: gcig pa la bco brgyad kyi rnal 'byor pho mo 'tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis gnas /
NK070(thu)001:6992: 'khor khang sum rim du yo byad lnga dang ldan par bsogs te tshogs bsgrub na /
NK070(thu)001:6993: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras
NK070(thu)001:6994: bu tshe dbang phyag chen lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK070(thu)001:6995: 'dzin gsum dang / mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga yang 'grub zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:6996: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor rang gyi ngo bo bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:6998: gtso mo yum lnga yi dkyil 'khor zhal sbyor ba yis //
NK070(thu)001:6999: tshom bu lnga'i lha bkod nas //
NK070(thu)001:7000: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcu //
NK070(thu)001:7001: 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom //
NK070(thu)001:7002: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:7003: dkyil 'khor lha so so rnal 'byor pa so so /
NK070(thu)001:7004: thog ma 1nas mi grangs lha grangs sprad nas rang bsgom pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:7005: yang na bar skabs bsgyur te rnal 'byor phan tshun
NK070(thu)001:7006: gcig la gcig gi lha bsgom pa'i 'am yang na
NK070(thu)001:7007: tshom bu gsum lnga pa dang po mi gcig gis
NK070(thu)001:7008: kun bsgom byed mthar mi grangs sprad nas bsgom pa
NK070(thu)001:7009: / pho mo bcu yi dbus su rdo rje rigs yab yum gtso 'khor bcu dgod do //
NK070(thu)001:7010: de ltar phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi yab yum bcu'o //
NK070(thu)001:7011: ste de na tshom bu lnga pa'i lha lnga bcu bkod la bsgom pa /
NK070(thu)001:7012: de'i phyi rol du phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu la /
NK070(thu)001:7013: khro bo dang khro mo bcu /
NK070(thu)001:7015: ste lha lnga bcu bsgom pa /
NK070(thu)001:7016: tshom bu gsum pa la gtso bo rigs gsum yod pa /
NK070(thu)001:7018: shar de bzhin rigs kyis lha yab yum bcu dang /
NK070(thu)001:7020: rdo rje'i rigs kyi bcu dang /
NK070(thu)001:7021: rgyab tu pad+ma'i rigs kyi lha bcu ste de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi lha sum cu /
NK070(thu)001:7022: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:7023: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du khro bo yab yum bcu drug go //
NK070(thu)001:7024: gi tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu gsum gyi lha zhe drug gi gtso bor rnams bsgom pa'i /
NK070(thu)001:7025: tshom bu gtso bo rigs gcig pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7026: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK070(thu)001:7027: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK070(thu)001:7028: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:7029: spyir de pa'i rigs thams cad kyi bdag nyid lnga
NK070(thu)001:7030: yin la de ni rdo rje'i rigs su 'dus pas
NK070(thu)001:7031: te / rdo rje'i rigs ni tshom bu gcig pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7032: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs kyi rigs kyi gtso
NK070(thu)001:7033: te / bo kho na'o // rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i rgyud ni /
NK070(thu)001:7034: gcig dang tha dad las grol bas /
NK070(thu)001:7035: gnas skabs rigs kyi gtso bo 'gyur yang don thugs ye shes kyi ngo bo mi 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7036: spyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs thams cad ye shes lngar 'dus la /
NK070(thu)001:7037: lnga yang thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kho
NK070(thu)001:7038: nar 'dus pas de ni thams cad kyi mchog go
NK070(thu)001:7040: ste gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnyis
NK070(thu)001:7041: rigs chung gis sems dpa' yab yum brgyad dang bcu
NK070(thu)001:7042: / khro bo bzhi dang khro mo'i tshogs dang ldan pa /
NK070(thu)001:7044: de ltar tshom bu gcig pa'i lha yab yum bco brgyad kyi tshogs rnams bsgom mo //
NK070(thu)001:7047: ci bgyis la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NK070(thu)001:7048: dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK070(thu)001:7050: khro bo tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gcig pa
NK070(thu)001:7051: khro bo yab lnga dang khro mo yum lnga ste
NK070(thu)001:7052: bcu 'i tshogs chen po dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su
NK070(thu)001:7053: bkod / de bzhin rtsibs mchan dang gru chad la
NK070(thu)001:7054: rim pas pho nya gnas ma brgyad phyag brnyan yul
NK070(thu)001:7055: ma brgyad bka' brnyan sgo ma bzhi ste /
NK070(thu)001:7056: lha mo nyi shu'i tshogs dang bcas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7057: dpal chen po'i spyan sngar ci bgyis zhes las bsgrub pa'i nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK070(thu)001:7058: sogs sgras bsdu ba ni khro bo khro mo nyi shu ste /
NK070(thu)001:7059: rnal 'byor pho mo bdun bcu rtsa brgyad kyi tshogs rnams kyi bsgrub na phrin las bzhi dang /
NK070(thu)001:7061: dngos grub gnyis ka yang rdzogs par byed do //
NK070(thu)001:7063: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:7065: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7066: rnam par dbye ba ni tshogs bsgrubs kyi lta ba thams cad ye nas dbyer med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7067: spyod pa la yang thogs pa med pa gnyis kyi mgo 'brel pa ra bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7068: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i cig char 'jug pa lam dang gnyis kathun mong du ston to //
NK070(thu)001:7069: rnal 'byor ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:7073: lam gyi skor la spyi ru gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:7074: kha phyag rgya'i lha'i sku bsgom pa bskyed rim mtshan ma dang bcas pa /
NK070(thu)001:7075: rnal 'byor dang gardzogs rim mtshan ma med pa ye shes kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK070(thu)001:7076: de las rgyud 'di 'i rnal 'byor ni phyag rgya
NK070(thu)001:7077: dang ye shes kyi rnal 'byor de gnyis mi phyed
NK070(thu)001:7081: gnyis su 'dzin pa'i yid skyob pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7082: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub gnyis te /
NK070(thu)001:7083: byin gyis brlabs pa chen po'i ston pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:7085: bsgom pa rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gyis mngon sum du nyams su myong pa ni 'chang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:7086: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du lta bya lta byed gnyis su med par rtogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7089: thun mong pa gsum dang mchog gnyis ste /
NK070(thu)001:7090: mchog gi zhar la byung ba'i phyir thun mong zhes
NK070(thu)001:7091: yang na lha bsgom nyams su blang ba'i rnal 'byor
NK070(thu)001:7093: mnyam rdzogs lhun grub dang gnas shing //
NK070(thu)001:7096: gsang sngags thabs kyi theg pa'i lta ba ni //
NK070(thu)001:7097: bla med rgyu'i theg pa'i byang sems las 'phags pa //
NK070(thu)001:7098: yin te ci'i phyir zhe na don dam du ni
NK070(thu)001:7099: thams cad lhun gyis grub pas dbyings ye shes gnyis
NK070(thu)001:7100: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:7101: nor bdun gyi dpag pa yin no //
NK070(thu)001:7102: kun rdzob tu ni sku dang ye shes mnyam par rdzogs so //
NK070(thu)001:7105: rang rig pa nyid shes bya'i dngos po thams cad
NK070(thu)001:7106: du rang snang bas snang tshul yin tshul gyi dngos
NK070(thu)001:7107: po gnyis ka rang rig pa'i sku dang ye shes
NK070(thu)001:7108: su gsal bar mnyam pa la 'bras bu lhag ma
NK070(thu)001:7109: lus pa med pa ni rdzogs pa kho na 'o
NK070(thu)001:7111: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang ni skye
NK070(thu)001:7112: 'gag rtag chad gcig tha dad 'gro 'ong gi spros
NK070(thu)001:7113: pa brgyad dang bral ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7114: lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang ni 'khor 'das kyi dngos
NK070(thu)001:7115: po thams cad sems nyid kho na'i yin pa phyir
NK070(thu)001:7116: / sems nyid rig pa don dam la phyogs gcig
NK070(thu)001:7117: cir yang ma yin pa nyid la che ba'i yon
NK070(thu)001:7118: tan bkor lnga ril lhun gyis grub par gnas pa'o
NK070(thu)001:7119: / // bden gnyis dbyer med de dag ni /
NK070(thu)001:7120: rnal 'byor gsum gyi dang po rang bzhin gyi rnal 'byor te /
NK070(thu)001:7122: mtshan nyid gsum gyi dang po rgyu'i shes pa mtshan nyid lta ba yin de /
NK070(thu)001:7123: brjod bya'i don rtogs pas dgos pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7124: byang chub sems kyi shes pas /
NK070(thu)001:7126: rnal 'byor pa gang gis lta don de la ting
NK070(thu)001:7127: nge 'dzin gyi blo gnas par byar med pa'i tshul
NK070(thu)001:7128: gyis rang gsal bar gnas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7129: sngags 'chang ba la gsum gyi gnyis pa lam gyi rnal 'byor te /
NK070(thu)001:7130: gsum gyi gnyis rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:7131: spyod pas ci la'ang thog med pa //
NK070(thu)001:7133: lta bsgom de dag gi grogs byed pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7134: nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa'i dngos po nyi
NK070(thu)001:7135: shu gang yang ma bkag pa ci la'ang spyod pa
NK070(thu)001:7136: kho na ste / lta ba brtan pa klong du gyur par byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7137: ci la'ang spyod pas nyes skyon gyis mi gos pa'i phyir te /
NK070(thu)001:7138: gang yang spyod par bya ba 'i yul dang /
NK070(thu)001:7140: spyod pa byas par rang gi ngo bo yid la
NK070(thu)001:7141: byed pa de ni 'dzin pa dang ma bral ba
NK070(thu)001:7143: bya ba byed pa byas pa de gsum du mi 'dzin pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7146: byis sba bzhin du spang blang med par spyad ces bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7147: de 1dag ci'i phyir spang blang med /
NK070(thu)001:7149: thams cad ye nas dbyer med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7151: chos can gyi dngos po thams cad ni /
NK070(thu)001:7152: ye gdod ma nas sems nyid kyi ngo bor snang
NK070(thu)001:7153: stong gnyis su byar med pa kho nar gnas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7155: de ltar lta spyod gnyis su med pa dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:7156: pa ni rkyen 'jug pa 'i mtshan nyid ting nge
NK070(thu)001:7157: 'dzin nyams su len pas dgos 'brel bzhi las /
NK070(thu)001:7161: gzungs kyi rgyal mo chos nyid dang 'du 'bral med par bsgrub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7163: de nyid mngon du byas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7165: bsgrub pa chen po 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:7166: bzhi'am gsum gyi tha ma dgos pa'i yang dgos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7168: rdo rje'i rab tu thams cad dkyil //
NK070(thu)001:7169: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7170: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i thabs las /
NK070(thu)001:7171: tshigs dang po 'dis tshom bu gcig pa'i bsgrub pa'i thabs ston te /
NK070(thu)001:7172: rdo rje'i rigs su rigs bzhi po /
NK070(thu)001:7175: tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7176: spyir kun bzang bdag po'i rigs kyang ming gi bla dwags su rdo rje'i rigs su 'dogs te /
NK070(thu)001:7177: ci zhe na rigs lnga char cig du ma dang
NK070(thu)001:7178: bral ba'i tshul gyis lhun gyis grub pas dbyer mi
NK070(thu)001:7179: phyed pa'i rdo rje phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:7180: rgyu mtshan de bas na le'u dang po la sogs
NK070(thu)001:7181: pa'i le'u bsdus pa thams cad nas de pa thams
NK070(thu)001:7186: phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:7189: chags med tshul gyis btim par bya //
NK070(thu)001:7191: tshom bu gcig gi rtsa ba'i lha bco brgyad la
NK070(thu)001:7192: yan lag gi lha dgu rnams dang chas par 'od
NK070(thu)001:7193: zer 'phro ba gzi brjid 'bar ba rab tu bsgom
NK070(thu)001:7194: tshogs kyi yo byad lnga la yo byad tsam na
NK070(thu)001:7196: thogs pa med pas 'i tshul gyi spyod bya spyod
NK070(thu)001:7197: byed spyod pa'i 'du shes dang bral bas spyod pa
NK070(thu)001:7198: byas pa'i ngo bo dang gsum du 'dzin pa med
NK070(thu)001:7199: pa ni / bstim par bya ste thim pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7200: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK070(thu)001:7202: bza' btung gos rgyan glu tshig bro gar gyi yo
NK070(thu)001:7203: byad thun mong bzhi po la lta spyod gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:7204: med pas ra gyur na sku phyag rgya chen po'i
NK070(thu)001:7207: yo byad lnga pa nyi zla 'i thig le gnyis su med par gyur pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7208: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med kyi phyag rgya chen po'i kha sbyor ba'i dngos grub thob ste /
NK070(thu)001:7209: dpe na thabs kyi lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin 'grub bo //
NK070(thu)001:7211: bde 'dus ye shes thig le la //
NK070(thu)001:7212: mtha' yas ye shes rab snang ba //
NK070(thu)001:7213: ma rtsal lhun grub rig 'dzin mchog /
NK070(thu)001:7215: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK070(thu)001:7216: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7217: gcig pa la dkar bas yang na 'khor 'das kyi
NK070(thu)001:7218: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs su nyid 'dus pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7219: phyir / de rgyal ba thams cad lhag ma ma
NK070(thu)001:7220: lus pa kun gyi sku gsung thugs kyi tshom bu
NK070(thu)001:7221: gsum pa'i sgrub thabs ston te /
NK070(thu)001:7222: bsgom tshul spyod lugs ni gcig pa dang rjes su mthun no //
NK070(thu)001:7223: pa ni ting nge 'dzin gsal 'bar zhes pa nas sdug bsngal sel bar byed /
NK070(thu)001:7225: rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas //
NK070(thu)001:7227: de pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad sku gsung thugs gsum po kho nar 'dus la /
NK070(thu)001:7228: de dag dbyer mi phyed pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7229: rdo rje zhes ming gi bla dwags su brjod pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7230: sa de'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas kho na /
NK070(thu)001:7231: skyob pa dang byin brlabs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7232: sngags te de rang rig mngon sum du /
NK070(thu)001:7233: 'chang ba'i dngos grub yang dag ni //
NK070(thu)001:7234: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7235: tshom bu lnga pa'i sgrub thabs te /
NK070(thu)001:7237: gong dang 'dra rjes su mthun pa ste thabs dang
NK070(thu)001:7238: shes rab ces pa nas bstim par bya zhes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7239: bar yin no // de'i 'bras bu ni /
NK070(thu)001:7240: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:7242: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa ni dngos grub 1mchog
NK070(thu)001:7243: gi don ste de dag lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK070(thu)001:7245: bsgrub bya thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pas snying po 'grub par 'gyur /
NK070(thu)001:7247: shes rab yum kyi yab kyi de bzhin gshegs pa yab dang yum gyi lha yum du bsgom /
NK070(thu)001:7248: la 'khor yab kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' 'am
NK070(thu)001:7249: yab dang yum gyi sems ma yum nyid du bsgom
NK070(thu)001:7251: sgyu 'phrul bsdus pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:7252: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de /
NK070(thu)001:7253: kha bskangs pas lha bco brgyad do //
NK070(thu)001:7256: rigs drug po gang rung ste ma nges pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7257: gtso bo ma nges pa'i don gyis na tshigs rkang gsum po 'di ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:7258: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:7259: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:7260: bsdus pa dang gsum po kun la'ang sbyang bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7261: ste gdul bya mos pa tha dad pas dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:7262: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo bsgyur du rung ba /
NK070(thu)001:7263: so so'i gasngags dang phyag rgya khadang //
NK070(thu)001:7264: ting ka 'dzin yang dag so sor gsal //
NK070(thu)001:7266: spyir lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang yang khyad par du lha so so bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK070(thu)001:7267: bca' ba'i phyag rgya dang bzlas pa'i sngags rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:7268: rang rang ma 'dres par yang dag par gsal ba kho na'o zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7269: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK070(thu)001:7270: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK070(thu)001:7273: shin tu dben pa'i sa phyogs su 'khor khang sum
NK070(thu)001:7274: ril ni phyi ma la yo byad la bsog bar
NK070(thu)001:7279: yang pa rin po che'i rgyan gyis mdzes par spras par byas pa der /
NK070(thu)001:7280: longs spyod lnga la gnang bkag med par 'jol nyog tu spyod pa ni ci bde dang zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7281: de'i dus su rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7282: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin du 'brel pas 'i blo
NK070(thu)001:7283: ni rab tu ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo rnams
NK070(thu)001:7284: kyi / bsgrub po zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:7285: dang po ma mnos bzhin du bya //
NK070(thu)001:7287: dang por tshom bu'i bcu gsum lnga pa ci tsam bsgrub pa grangs dang /
NK070(thu)001:7288: a li'i sbyor ba spyod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7289: dam tshig ni dang por rang gis dam ci ltar
NK070(thu)001:7290: bcas shing mnos pa las mi 'da' ba bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:7293: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'dir zag med kyi 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:7294: mthar gtugs pa'i thob dgos pa phyir rtags kyi bsnyen
NK070(thu)001:7295: pa'o // la la dag bsgrub pa'i dus su zhag
NK070(thu)001:7296: grangs ci tsam khas blangs shing dam mnos pa bzhin
NK070(thu)001:7297: pa'o // du bya zhes / smra ba ni dkyus kyis don med pa ste mi grub pa /
NK070(thu)001:7299: le lo som nyi med pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:7300: the tshom med par bsgrub byas nas //
NK070(thu)001:7303: som nyi ni 'bras bu ma lus pa'i gegs kho na'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:7304: de gnyis med pa'i blo la the tshom med par
NK070(thu)001:7305: bsgrub cing nyams su len par byas na 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:7307: rdo rje gsang mchog dam pa 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:7309: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gcig gsum lnga pa
NK070(thu)001:7310: gsum gang bsgrub du rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK070(thu)001:7313: 1gcig dang du ma dang bral bas 'grub par gyur
NK070(thu)001:7314: pa de bas na rdo rje gsang mchog dgongs pa
NK070(thu)001:7315: dam pa thob pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7316: sgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni /
NK070(thu)001:7317: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK070(thu)001:7319: bsgrub pa 'grub pa'i dus zhag sum cu phrag drug la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7320: 'di nyid kyis le'u dgu par zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam zhes sogs gsungs la /
NK070(thu)001:7321: skar ma rgyal dang tshes brgyad la sogs pa bzang po la 'jug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7322: rgyud gzhan dag ste bam brgyad rngam glog kun 'dus gsungs pa bzhin du bshad pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7323: tshes ni yar gyis brgyad la rtsam //
NK070(thu)001:7324: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma la //
NK070(thu)001:7325: byang chub spyod pa cher spyod pa //
NK070(thu)001:7326: gsang mchog si ti myur pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:7327: gza' skar shis pa dang du blangs //
NK070(thu)001:7331: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:7333: phyag rgya spros pa man chad goms pa'i skye bo
NK070(thu)001:7334: 'dza' ba kun lha grangs dang mnyam par 'tshogs pa
NK070(thu)001:7335: de ni skal ldan rnal 'byor mi pho mo 'tshogs
NK070(thu)001:7337: bza' btung la sogs pa 'byor pa'i longs spyod kun tshang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:7338: 'byor ldan gyi bde ba'i longs spyod tshogs su bshad /
NK070(thu)001:7339: ye shes kyi lha dang chos skyong dam can te srung ma kun kyang 'dus /
NK070(thu)001:7341: 'dus pa chen po'i dgyes ldan lha tshogs su gsungs /
NK070(thu)001:7342: byed spyod thams cad spyod pa bsod nams kyi tshogs de la mi 'dzin pas /
NK070(thu)001:7343: ye shes kyi tshogs de ltar tshogs gnyis dus rgyun du rdzogs par byed pas /
NK070(thu)001:7345: tshogs chen po dus de rdzogs par nges par bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:7349: rdo rje sems dpa' tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dkyil nyid yin te /
NK070(thu)001:7350: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mos 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:7352: yang na shes bya rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ni don yod med kyi mthar las /
NK070(thu)001:7354: de nyid kun rdzob dag ma dag gi /
NK070(thu)001:7355: 'jig rten sna tshogs su snang ba 'khor yin no //
NK070(thu)001:7358: le'u ste bcu gcig pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7360: // de nas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor de dag yo byad
NK070(thu)001:7361: la brten te dus nye bar sgrub pa'i thabs bstan
NK070(thu)001:7362: pa'i phyir / de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK070(thu)001:7363: rol mo'i sprin rnam par spros te rgyan bkod pa /
NK070(thu)001:7365: rol mo ni dper na gzhi ma nges par thabs kyis drangs na sna tshogs su snang bas /
NK070(thu)001:7366: ltas mo ba mi thams cad kyang tshim par byed pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7367: tshogs bsgrub kyi skabs 'dir yo byad lnga la sogs
NK070(thu)001:7368: pa thams cad du rig pa rang snang ba'i dus
NK070(thu)001:7369: na / ra shes pa de la tshogs su spyod
NK070(thu)001:7370: pa nyid ye shes kyi rol pa'i sprin rnam par
NK070(thu)001:7371: snang ba sna tshogs su spros ste /
NK070(thu)001:7372: de dag 'khor ba dang mya ngan la 'das par
NK070(thu)001:7373: gnyis su med par sgrub pa'i thabs su mdzes pa
NK070(thu)001:7374: dang / gnyis su med pa'i rgyan bkod pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7375: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:7378: nges par tshogs bsgrub par 'dod pa'i 'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis /
NK070(thu)001:7379: rgyud 'di'i gzhung gi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gcig gsum
NK070(thu)001:7380: lnga pa'i rnam pa gsum po gang yang rung ba'i
NK070(thu)001:7381: lha yab yum zung du 'brel la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK070(thu)001:7382: ba ste de la blo sbyangs te /
NK070(thu)001:7383: rang rigs pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7384: tshom bu'i lha dang dkyil 'khor spros pa la brten
NK070(thu)001:7385: pa thob pa'i snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting
NK070(thu)001:7386: nge 'dzin la dbang thob pa des spyod lam la
NK070(thu)001:7387: brten te bsgrub bo zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7388: yo byad lnga la spyad pa po'i yon tan bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:7391: dang po la sgyu 'phrul la rgyas pa'i rgyud kyis
NK070(thu)001:7392: bcu gcig pa don bdun pa bzhugs gnas kyi le'u
NK070(thu)001:7393: bzhin du / gnas khang dang sa phyogs rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:7394: gzhi la rin po che'i 'phran mig gis spras par
NK070(thu)001:7395: bzhin du / byin gyis brlabs / de nas yan
NK070(thu)001:7396: lag lnga la rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor lnga bcu po
NK070(thu)001:7397: bzhin du / byin gyis brlabs / bkod pa dang
NK070(thu)001:7398: / rtog pa'i yan lag zhe gnyis kun lhar gsal
