NK070(thu)001:7399: bar byas nas lus rgyan gyis brgyan te /
NK070(thu)001:7400: rkang pa'i bro stabs dang yan lag gi gar stabs
NK070(thu)001:7401: sna tshogs dang glu tshig rgyas pa 'i don gsum
NK070(thu)001:7402: pa bro gar rtse 'jo'i le'u las 'byung ba la
NK070(thu)001:7403: sogs pa sna tshogs su blangs ba'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:7404: dbu'i dkyil 'khor rnam snang bsgul zhing bskyod pas //
NK070(thu)001:7405: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams ma lus g.yo //
NK070(thu)001:7406: lag gi 'du byed bskyod byas nas //
NK070(thu)001:7407: rig 'dzin zhing khams thams cad g.yo //
NK070(thu)001:7408: rkang pa'i stabs chen mnan mchong na //
NK070(thu)001:7409: bdud dang log 'dren thams cad gnon //
NK070(thu)001:7410: zhes bya ba la sogs pa bzhin du /
NK070(thu)001:7413: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bro gar byas pa'i yon tan ni //
NK070(thu)001:7414: ri brag 1dang sa la thogs chags med par 'dzul
NK070(thu)001:7415: zhing rkang 'og gi phyag rgya klu mo rnams la
NK070(thu)001:7417: nam mkha' la 'phur nas 'gro zhing lha dang gnod
NK070(thu)001:7418: sbyin mo rnams la longs spyod cing thams cad bran
NK070(thu)001:7419: du 'khol cing dbang du 'du bar 'gyur bar byed
NK070(thu)001:7420: do // h+aum glu tshig sgra yi phyag rgya yis //
NK070(thu)001:7421: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:7423: gong 'og gi yo byad lnga po thams cad rig
NK070(thu)001:7424: pa kho na ra snang ba yin bas ci spyad
NK070(thu)001:7425: kyang sems nyid rang snang bas sku rang bzhin med
NK070(thu)001:7426: pa gsung gnyis su med pa thugs las 'da' ba
NK070(thu)001:7427: med pa'i 'am sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs las
NK070(thu)001:7428: 'da' ba med pa phyir ngag gi glu tshig sgra'i
NK070(thu)001:7429: phyag rgya ste / des lce la n+ri bkod de yar rgyal ba la bstod pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7430: mar 'gro ba rang rang gi skad du mos pa
NK070(thu)001:7431: ltar du chos ston par bsgom pa'i rgyu'i ting nge
NK070(thu)001:7432: 'dzin kho na'i phyir 'bras bu gdul bya so so
NK070(thu)001:7433: la chos kyi 'khor lo so sor ston par 'i
NK070(thu)001:7434: dngos grub thob 'gyur zhi ba la dar gyi stod
NK070(thu)001:7435: g.yogs smad dkris / sku reg gsang gnas dbu rgyan phyag rgya phu rung ste /
NK070(thu)001:7436: rgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK070(thu)001:7439: chas gos lnga dang rin po che 'i rgyan dbu rgyan /
NK070(thu)001:7441: mgul rgyan la sogs pa sna tshogs kyi longs spyod
NK070(thu)001:7442: rdzogs pa'i sku'i cha lugs kho na ltar bya ba
NK070(thu)001:7443: dang / khro bor tshogs bsgrub na rus pa'i dbu rgyan phyag gdub /
NK070(thu)001:7446: do shal gyis rgyan lnga la sogs pa bgo ba'i
NK070(thu)001:7447: gos glang chen gyi rko rlon la sogs pa dang
NK070(thu)001:7448: ldan pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya des 'bras
NK070(thu)001:7449: bu lus shin tu gzhan las dpags pa'i gzi byin
NK070(thu)001:7450: gyis 'od 'bar ba'i rgyal po des gzhan thams cad
NK070(thu)001:7452: thub pa med pa seng ge lta bur gnas pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7453: 'grub pa bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK070(thu)001:7454: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:7455: ces bya ba ni dam rdzas lngas gzhi byas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7456: bza' ba dang btung ba rnams dang longs spyod sna
NK070(thu)001:7457: tshogs rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi lha mor byin
NK070(thu)001:7458: gyis brlab pas / rang lha'i sku gsung thugs su gsal ba'i phyag rgya yis /
NK070(thu)001:7459: mchod pa 'i 'bras bu ni yid bzhin gyi sku
NK070(thu)001:7460: rin po che tshon shel gyis spar khab du bcug
NK070(thu)001:7462: bdud rtsi'i bcud zag pa med pas 'gro ba thams
NK070(thu)001:7463: cad kyang tshim par byed par 'grub pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:7464: // +aa li k+aa li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK070(thu)001:7467: brdar bstan pa'i k+aa li ni /
NK070(thu)001:7469: +aa li ni shes rab yum kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:7470: yab yum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar gsal ba'i ngang du snyoms par 'jug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7472: bcu gcig par bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:7473: des ni phrin las bzhi po thams cad dang /
NK070(thu)001:7475: dngos grub thams cad ci 'dod pa ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:7476: bsam pa yongs su skong ba 'grub par 'gyur ba
NK070(thu)001:7477: kho na'o // shes 'jug mtshan nyid 'byor pa'i gzungs //
NK070(thu)001:7478: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK070(thu)001:7479: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK070(thu)001:7480: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags /
NK070(thu)001:7482: lta ba ting nge 'dzin 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rnam
NK070(thu)001:7483: pa gsum gyi bskyed rdzogs kyi lam rim bcu gnyis
NK070(thu)001:7484: gnyis ka'i rim pa thun mong du ston te /
NK070(thu)001:7485: bcu gcig pa'i skabs kyi rnal 'byor sngags 'chang dang sdebs te bkrol lo //
NK070(thu)001:7486: he dus rtogs pa rnam pa bzhis shes bya mnyam
NK070(thu)001:7487: rdzogs kyi don ci lta bar nyams su lon pa
NK070(thu)001:7488: ni / gnas lugs shes pa'i mtshan nyid gnas skabs
NK070(thu)001:7489: mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis kyi ngo bo bskyed
NK070(thu)001:7490: pas 'bras bu smin byed kyi nyer len gyi rgyu
NK070(thu)001:7491: ni / kho na'o // lta ba dang ldan pa de nas /
NK070(thu)001:7492: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i don lta bas rtogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7493: ngang la ting nge 'dzin gnas te spyod pas ci
NK070(thu)001:7494: la'ang thogs pa med par spyod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7495: lta spyod 'go 'byor par 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid de ting nge 'dzin /
NK070(thu)001:7496: 'bras bu khyad par bskyed pas 'bras bu smin byed
NK070(thu)001:7497: kyis lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen zhes bla dwags tsam
NK070(thu)001:7498: ste / de ni ngan song ltung ba'i 'jigs pa
NK070(thu)001:7499: las thar ba sa der mi ltung bas gzung ba
NK070(thu)001:7500: ste / kho na'o // lta bsgom spyod gsum de
NK070(thu)001:7501: la dus rgyun du goms pa'i nus pa mthu can
NK070(thu)001:7502: du gyur nas mthar lam pa lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7503: rig 'dzin 'byung ba las ma rag par gnas pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7504: tshe dbang ni lam rang gi ngo bor yongs su
NK070(thu)001:7506: de nyid mthar thug gi 'bras bu nye bar len pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7507: rgyu rkyen gnyis las 'byung bas 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid de /
NK070(thu)001:7508: de la bskyed rim lha'i sku phyag 1rgya'i rnal 'byor
NK070(thu)001:7509: pas ni lam gcig spros kyi dus na yi dam
NK070(thu)001:7511: so so'i rig 'dzin pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7512: de la yang mthong lam rnam par smin pa'i lus dang ldan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7513: de phral nas lus lha'i sku bsgom lam phyag rgya
NK070(thu)001:7514: chen po'i rigs lnga gang rung gi rig 'dzin pas
NK070(thu)001:7515: gnyis so // kri yog man chad gzhan dag gi rig 'dzin ni /
NK070(thu)001:7516: spyir phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor ram ye shes kyi rnal
NK070(thu)001:7517: 'byor ni lam pa gang ting nge 'dzin gyi rig
NK070(thu)001:7518: pa yul rkyen gyi gyis mi phrog pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7520: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i rigs mngon sum du zin pa'i pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7522: de 1dag don yid la byed pa spangs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7523: yid kyi yul du byar med gzung 'dzin med pas
NK070(thu)001:7524: theg pa chen po pa yin par brjod pa ste
NK070(thu)001:7525: / ci zhe na kun tu 1brtag pa'i blo dang /
NK070(thu)001:7526: rtog pa'i yul go ba spyi'i mtshan nyid 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:7527: rgyu rkyen gzhan gyi dbang dang gsum 111las yongs su grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:7528: don de ltar na gcig shos kyis rdzogs pa'i lam du zhugs pa yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:7529: mthong lam tshe 2la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob pa
NK070(thu)001:7530: la sogs pa phyag chen lhun grub gsum po ni
NK070(thu)001:7531: / lhag pa'i lus 'di nyid mi yangs pa sa
NK070(thu)001:7532: lhag bcas su mya ngan las 'das pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:7533: / // sngar bshad pa'i rnam smin dang kri yog
NK070(thu)001:7534: man chad gzhan gyi lugs kyi phyag rgya chen po
NK070(thu)001:7536: lam 0gzhung gi phyag rgya chen po sbyor gyi don
NK070(thu)001:7537: 'dir ma tshud pa'i lung ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:7538: las / mngon par byang chub pa'i phyag 3rgya'i chen po cha lugs kyi sku gzugs de 2sku //
NK070(thu)001:7539: mtshan so gnyis dang dpe byad brgyad cu la sogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:7540: sku'i cha lugs longs sku mngon gsum du phyung na yang //
NK070(thu)001:7541: de chos nyid zhi ba bden pa dbyer med mnyam
NK070(thu)001:7542: pa nyid kyi don de nyid rtogs shing mthong ba
NK070(thu)001:7545: 2gong ma'i rig 'dzin de dag la ni phyogs bcu'i
NK070(thu)001:7546: rgyal ba dkyil 'khor ma lus pas dbang gsum bskur
NK070(thu)001:7547: zhing sangs rgyas su lung ston pas grags pa kho
NK070(thu)001:7548: na'o // de'i skye ba'i cha byad sprul lus ci
NK070(thu)001:7549: lta bu zhe na mi khadang lha dang tshangs pa
NK070(thu)001:7550: na'o // yi // skye gaba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK070(thu)001:7551: khyad 00par sa la gnas gyur yin //
NK070(thu)001:7554: gzugs khams na spyod pa tshangs pa'i lha dang /
NK070(thu)001:7555: gling bzhi mi'i dbang po ste rgyal po dngos su grub pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7556: skye ba la rang dbang yod thob pa pas lha
NK070(thu)001:7557: mi'i skye ba rnam par dag pa de dag tu
NK070(thu)001:7558: snang ba'i lus 'dzin mod yang 'am kyang gi sgras
NK070(thu)001:7559: khyad par rgyu'i 'khor bar mi ldog pas sa dang
NK070(thu)001:7560: po la gnas pa dang tshe dbang skal pa mnyam
NK070(thu)001:7561: pa dang / mtha' mi g.yo bas brgyad pa phyag chen dang /
NK070(thu)001:7562: 'bras bu thob la ma rag pas bcu pa dag dang /
NK070(thu)001:7564: skal ba mnyam pa'i ra 'gyur ba yin gyi phyogs
NK070(thu)001:7565: kun tu mi nyams pa phyir lam chu tshe'ang dang
NK070(thu)001:7567: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog dang //
NK070(thu)001:7568: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK070(thu)001:7569: gsum pa bcu dang skal ba mnam mod //
NK070(thu)001:7570: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho khyad par 'phags //
NK070(thu)001:7573: zhes gsungs pa'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:7574: pha rol phyin pa kun tu rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:7575: thabs dang shes rab thabs kyi mchog /
NK070(thu)001:7576: shes rab mchog gi mchog gyur pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:7578: khyad par gyi gsang sngags kyi sa'i gsum thob pa phyir gsungs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7579: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom pa dang spyod pa gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:7580: rgyur shes pa'i mtshan nyid du lta spyod bsgom gsum dbyer myed cing 'go 'byor pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7581: byed spyod thams cad kyang snang la ma zhen pas
NK070(thu)001:7582: tshogs gnyis su 'gyur bas na te de'ang gnyis med
NK070(thu)001:7583: kyi don la tha dad du mi 'dzin pas sbyin
NK070(thu)001:7584: pa la sogs pa'i pha h'u rol tu phyin pa
NK070(thu)001:7585: bcu dang tshogs gnyis ril la rgyun du de'i don
NK070(thu)001:7589: mnyam pa'i ngang la gnas pa ni mnyam pa nyid
NK070(thu)001:7590: kyi dbyings las rang mtshan mthong bas sa dang po
NK070(thu)001:7591: rab tu dga' ba 1mthong lam ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:7592: snang stong phyogs re'i lta ba ngan pa dag pas
NK070(thu)001:7593: sa gnyis pa dri ma med pa la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:7594: bsgom pa'i lam sa brgyad gnyis kyang yongs su rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:7595: pa'o // gnas gang du lhun grub rig 'dzin lta sgom gyi /
NK070(thu)001:7596: 0nus pa'i mthu dang ldan pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7597: 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi dgongs pa shar ba rgyal
NK070(thu)001:7598: ba thams cad kyi rig pa'i 1lung dang rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:7600: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7602: rig 'dzin de'i 0nus pa'i mthus go phye ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:7603: mtha' bral gyi rig pa nyid thams cad du khyab pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7605: thabs zhes pa ni 'khor 'das thams cad du rig pa rang snang ba phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7606: dpe na chos nyid gang du yang ma bkag pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7607: 'khor bar snang ba'i chos ma lus pa la spyod
NK070(thu)001:7608: kyang rang bzhin med pa shes rab kyi dbang gis
NK070(thu)001:7609: skyon gyi nyes pas ma gos pa ni dper na
NK070(thu)001:7610: pad+ma 'dam gyi nang nas gnas kyang des ma gos
NK070(thu)001:7613: ni thabs kyi mchog ste kun tu 'od las khyad
NK070(thu)001:7614: par du gyur pas bcu gnyis pad+ma spyan gyis zhes
NK070(thu)001:7616: 1gang yul yul can cir yang mi dmigs pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi shes rab ni /
NK070(thu)001:7617: yul yul can thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyi 1 mchog ste /
NK070(thu)001:7618: don de nyid rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7619: rtog tshogs thabs kyang dbyer med bdag nyid chen po'i
NK070(thu)001:7620: yin pa phyir 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su
NK070(thu)001:7621: gsal bas / yul gyi zhen snang gi bye brag
NK070(thu)001:7622: tha snyad dang bral bas 'i ngang na chos can
NK070(thu)001:7623: gyi ril thams cad mkhyen pa ni mchog tu gyur
NK070(thu)001:7625: bcu gsum yi ge 1 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa zhes bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:7626: sa gsum po de dag mngon du byas pa ni 'bras bu'i mthar phyin pa mtshan nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:7627: gzhi chos nyid gcig la gnas skabs lta ba rtogs
NK070(thu)001:7628: pa ting nge 'dzin goms pa 'bras bu mngon du
NK070(thu)001:7629: byas / kyi mtshan nyid dang gsum tha snyad tsam
NK070(thu)001:7630: gyi dbye ba'i phyir 'bras bu'i ming thob pa kho
NK070(thu)001:7631: byas / na'o // gang gi lam dang 'bras bu de dag rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7632: sa'i khyad 00par byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu dang /
NK070(thu)001:7634: ni h+aum rgyu phar phyin gyi sa bcu dang /
NK070(thu)001:7635: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum gyi khyad par
NK070(thu)001:7636: thams cad lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:7639: nam mkha' dkyil dwangs pa'i kyu dbyings dang de'i ngang du nyi zla //
NK070(thu)001:7640: shar ba lta bu'i ye shes rgyal po stang ste yab dang /
NK070(thu)001:7642: pa de la rgyal ba'i rigs lnga dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pas de kun //
NK070(thu)001:7643: lhag ma lus par ni thams cad bsgom par 'a gyur //
NK070(thu)001:7645: zhes bya ba ni bsdus don rdzogs rim pa'i lam pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:7646: nye ba'i yi dam lha bsgom pa bskyed rim pa rnams kyi dbang du gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:7647: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:7648: gcig dang du mar bral ba kho na'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:7649: // yab yum du bsgom pas kun bsgom par 'gyur /
NK070(thu)001:7650: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK070(thu)001:7651: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:7653: bskyed rim gyi lam rim cig car gnyis kyis lta ba gzhi thun mong du bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7654: sku gsum gyi sangs rgyas pa zhes ming gi tha
NK070(thu)001:7655: snyad pa rnams ni theg pa 'og ma pa'i lugs
NK070(thu)001:7656: gzhan ltar sangs rgyas rnyed pa dag srid kyi mthar
NK070(thu)001:7657: thug yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga
NK070(thu)001:7658: ni / gdul bya'i dbang gis ming du gdags su
NK070(thu)001:7659: zin kyang lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas rang gi ngo
NK070(thu)001:7660: bo nyid ni phyogs gcig ga sgo nas gzhan la
NK070(thu)001:7662: dus bzhi dang phyogs bcu gang gi gnas nas lam
NK070(thu)001:7663: gyi 'bad rtsol gyis rtsal bar gyur kyang rdzogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7664: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba gcig gzhan du brtsal bas
NK070(thu)001:7665: mi rnyed de rnyed par mi 'gyur pa kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:7666: // 'o na sangs rgyas de ni gtan nas mi
NK070(thu)001:7667: rnyed par rgya chad do bar dogs pa la de'i
NK070(thu)001:7668: lan du 1sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te /
NK070(thu)001:7670: lta ba'i skabs 1rgyu nyid nas khams gsum thams cad
NK070(thu)001:7671: sems nyid du gtan la phab cing shes pa ni
NK070(thu)001:7672: / khams gsum gyi chos thams cad gang yang ma
NK070(thu)001:7673: spangs par 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su gyur
NK070(thu)001:7675: kabdag gi sems nyid las gzhan du ci yang ma dmigs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7676: rnyed pa rgyu dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang gnas pa
NK070(thu)001:7677: ye ci bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis ka ma brtsal
NK070(thu)001:7678: bar rang la lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:7679: thob pa yin te sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK070(thu)001:7680: 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad rang bzhin gyis rang la gnas pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7682: gzhan nas 'ongs pa med pas ma tshol cig ces gdams so //
NK070(thu)001:7683: de ltar med kyang sgrib byed rang rgyud kyi zhen pa log pas bdag gi zhal bdag gis mthong //
NK070(thu)001:7685: dper na sangs rgyas gzhan ma tshol cig /
NK070(thu)001:7687: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor rtog pa kun tu blos rab tu sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:7688: rang bzhin mthar phyin 'bras bu nyid kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:7689: thams cad ma brtsal bar lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:7692: bskyed rim rim gyis pa ltar na sangs rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK070(thu)001:7693: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK070(thu)001:7695: nges pa'i don bkrol na dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lngar 'dus //
NK070(thu)001:7696: pas de ltar gcig bsgom pas kun bsgom par 'gro zhes 'byung ba'i phyir yang yin la /
NK070(thu)001:7697: gcig shos te rdzogs rim cig car kyis lam pa dag gi yang phyir te /
NK070(thu)001:7698: ma ning gi rgyud rmad byung las rang bzhin gyi
NK070(thu)001:7699: dkyil 'khor rang bzhin mthar phyin 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:7700: zhes bya ba ni chos nyid byang chub sems las
NK070(thu)001:7701: ma yengs na / de nyid la dkyil 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:7702: snying po thams cad lhun gyis grub pa yin pas
NK070(thu)001:7703: na dkyil 'khor thams cad dus gcig la bsgom par
NK070(thu)001:7704: ma yengs na / 'gyur // zhes 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:7705: cho ga lhag gam ma tshang na'ang //
NK070(thu)001:7706: skyon nyid dag ste nyes pa med //
NK070(thu)001:7708: la la dag na re rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:7709: gsal ba rnams tshig gi lhag chad la gtsor mi
NK070(thu)001:7712: sngar bshad pa'i le'u dgu pa dang lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi rjes su 'jug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7715: khyad par du gyur pas lhag pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7716: thod rgal gyi phyag rgya gcig spros te ting nge
NK070(thu)001:7717: 'dzin gyis mthong lam thob pa lta bu lam gong
NK070(thu)001:7718: ma thams cad la'ang ting nge 'dzin mi dmigs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7722: ma tshang ba ni cig car pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:7723: de ting kun ting bsgom pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7724: sems dmigs pa med pa'i rim gyis pa'i 'ur du
NK070(thu)001:7725: 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin sems ting nge 'dzin rang
NK070(thu)001:7726: gi ngo bo nyid kyang mi dmigs 1na skyon nam
NK070(thu)001:7727: cho ga lnga gzhan grub pa lta ci smos pa
NK070(thu)001:7728: ste / sems sam lhag chad gang yang ma grub pas na skyon med pa kho na'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7731: lhag chad gang gis blo chung ba gang la gnod par gyur pa ni skyon nyid ste /
NK070(thu)001:7732: sngar bshad pa 'i rim gyis 'jug pa rnams kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7734: skyon de dag gis mi gnod pa ni dag pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:7735: nyes pa med pa'i steng nas slar lam nye bas na /
NK070(thu)001:7737: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:7738: rol mo'i sprin gyis mnyes par gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:7740: rol mo ni le'u stod du bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:7741: longs spyod lnga'i tshogs la spyad pa dag gis rgyu
NK070(thu)001:7742: 'bras te snang stong gnyis su med par longs spyod
NK070(thu)001:7743: pa'i rgyan chen po'i rgyan rol pa nyid du gsal
NK070(thu)001:7744: bas mchod rdzas dang mchod yul gnyis su med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7745: mchod pa 'khor gsum dag la gnas su stob pa
NK070(thu)001:7746: sa nyes par gyur to zhes kho nar bzhugs so
NK070(thu)001:7748: tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:7749: tshogs ni bcu gcig par bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:7750: bsgrub pa ni 'og pa pa'i lugs gzhan du lam
NK070(thu)001:7751: gyi rkyen gang dag gis 'bras bu gang zhig don
NK070(thu)001:7752: du gnyer ba'i rtsol ba byas pa la bsgrub pa
NK070(thu)001:7753: kho na ste / 'dir ni rang gzhung gi rgyas
NK070(thu)001:7754: pa'i rgyud las rgyu sems can 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:7755: ye nas dbyer med de nyid du snga phyi tha
NK070(thu)001:7756: dad ma yin pas na 'bras bu la lam du
NK070(thu)001:7757: byed par gyur nas rgyu 'bras dus gcig tu mnyam
NK070(thu)001:7758: kho na ste / par sbyar ro // zhes gsungs pas /
NK070(thu)001:7759: rkyen 'jug pas ting nge 'dzin gyis lam nyams su
NK070(thu)001:7760: len pa tsam la sgrub pa zhes tha snyad du
NK070(thu)001:7761: 'dogs pa'i phyir / na gzhi lam 'bras bu mtshan nyid gsum du btags pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7762: tsam du le'u ste bcu gnyis pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7764: // de na de khapa phyogs kabcu dus bzhi'i sku ga
NK070(thu)001:7765: gsung thugs rdo rje'i chadkyil nga'khor thams ca cad dus
NK070(thu)001:7768: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i rgyud dag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7769: de pa thams cad kyi sku 1gsung 1thugs 1kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:7770: 111'khor lnga gsum po ril ni chos can he dus
NK070(thu)001:7771: sems nyid rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7772: de dag 00rang rig pa kho nar mi phyed pas ming gi bla dwags su rdo rje ste /
NK070(thu)001:7774: de nyid la thams cad gcig tu 'dus pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7775: de dag gis le'u 'dir mngon sum du ston pa'i brda ste /
NK070(thu)001:7776: don de nyid bstan pa rgyal ba thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:7777: dgongs pa rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir dgyes pa chen
NK070(thu)001:7779: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK070(thu)001:7780: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK070(thu)001:7782: don de'i phyir rgyal ba mang po gcig tu 'tshogs par smra ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:7783: don med kyang rgyal ba thams cad rang rig pa
NK070(thu)001:7784: las ma g.yos pas bdag nyid chen po'i phyir gcig
NK070(thu)001:7785: tu 'dus pa zhes pa'i sgra tsam ni 'gal ba
NK070(thu)001:7786: med do // gcig tu 'dus pa'i dgongs pa de nyid nye bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7787: chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen pa chen
NK070(thu)001:7788: por lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig shin tu gsang
NK070(thu)001:7789: ba'i snying po sprin bkod pa zhes gsung te /
NK070(thu)001:7790: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK070(thu)001:7791: thams cad ye gdod ma nas dkar nyid nas dag
NK070(thu)001:7792: cing / rang rig pa kho na'i yin pa phyir
NK070(thu)001:7793: de nyid thams cad du ma 'gag pa sku yin
NK070(thu)001:7794: 1la gzhan du ma skyes par 2sar gsung bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:7795: du gsal bas 3 thugs de ltar sku 1gsung 2thugs
NK070(thu)001:7796: 3 kho na yin pa de las gzhan pa med
NK070(thu)001:7797: cing / pa ni / rdzogs pa chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:7798: rang rig pa de la ltos pa'i kun brtag pa
NK070(thu)001:7799: dang ldan pa sems tsam pa rnams kyis skad cig
NK070(thu)001:7800: ma'i rgyu rkyen gyi rnam pa brjod kyang /
NK070(thu)001:7801: yid de nyid rang byung gi ye shes nyid yin pas rgyu rkyen med par rang snang ba las /
NK070(thu)001:7802: 'da' mi srid pa'i ste mi 'da' ba phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7803: lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig ce 'o //
NK070(thu)001:7804: don de ni gzhi rang bzhin shin tu gsang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:7805: snying po nyid de ci zhe na rang byung ye
NK070(thu)001:7806: shes phal gyi blo'i spyod yul du gyur pa ma
NK070(thu)001:7807: yin pa'i phyir / rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK070(thu)001:7808: de na de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul yin te /
NK070(thu)001:7809: 'o na lam don med do zhe na rnal 'byor
NK070(thu)001:7810: pa gsang sngags kyi skyes bu rig pa'i blo rtsal
NK070(thu)001:7811: shes rab can kyi rtogs dang zhe'o //
NK070(thu)001:7812: de la 'khor 'das kyi tha snyad gnyis mtshon par byed pa'i sgo dang /
NK070(thu)001:7813: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi nyams su myong bar byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK070(thu)001:7814: don nyid mthar phyin cing 'bras bu mngon du byas
NK070(thu)001:7815: pa'i yon tan mang po nas mkha'i sprin tsam du
NK070(thu)001:7816: phyes nas ston pa'i 'am bkod pa dgongs pa ting
NK070(thu)001:7817: nge 'dzin la nye bar snang ba sa snyoms par
NK070(thu)001:7818: zhugs ste / gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:7819: gsum pa de la dang po don mtshon pa'i sgo bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7820: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK070(thu)001:7823: mu stegs dang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa gnyis ka'i
NK070(thu)001:7824: lta ba cir yang ma rtogs pa ni 'jig rten
NK070(thu)001:7826: 'khrul gzhi ni snang ba dang rang bzhin gyi snang
NK070(thu)001:7827: ba po las ni gol ba'i phyir zer ma gol
NK070(thu)001:7828: mod kyang / rang rgyud par zhen pas gol zhes bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:7829: rang bzhin gyi snang ba de la mu stegs rtag
NK070(thu)001:7830: chad gnyis ni kun rdzob don dam las log par
NK070(thu)001:7831: rtogs pa ste / de yang snang phyogs las gol ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:7833: stong phyogs las gol ba chad lta 'khor ba la
NK070(thu)001:7834: dbug 'byin pa'i ngal bso ba pa'am lam stegs kyi
NK070(thu)001:7836: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs /
NK070(thu)001:7839: rag pa gang gi bdag med nang pa'i phyogs tsam rtogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7840: rnam rig sems tsam pas ni /
NK070(thu)001:7841: snang ba'i gsal cha sems yin par phyogs gcig rig pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:7843: kun rdzob chos can gyi dngos po thams cad chos
NK070(thu)001:7844: nyid kyi de kho nyid don gyi dbyings dang ye
NK070(thu)001:7845: shes dang 'bras bu don dam pa gsum gyi ngo
NK070(thu)001:7846: bor gnas pa yin pa la de ltar kun rdzob
NK070(thu)001:7847: don dam gyi bden pa gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa
NK070(thu)001:7848: gsang sngags kyi don de nyid mngon du ma byas
NK070(thu)001:7849: te bden gnyis tha dad du 'byed pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7850: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:7851: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK070(thu)001:7852: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams ni //
NK070(thu)001:7854: nges pa'i don bden pa gnyis su med pa yin
NK070(thu)001:7855: pa yang dag par bstan mod kyi khrus dang gtsang
NK070(thu)001:7856: spra'i spyod pas lus ngag yid kyi sgo gsum 'dul
NK070(thu)001:7858: phyi lus ngag gi spyod pa bas nang gi rnal
NK070(thu)001:7859: 'byor dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtsor byed pa yo
NK070(thu)001:7860: ga pa dang / phal la med pa'i lta ba rig pa bdag nyid chen po dang /
NK070(thu)001:7861: spyod pa blang dor med pa la gnas pas na
NK070(thu)001:7862: gsang ba ste nang pa ma h+aa dang a nu
NK070(thu)001:7863: gnyis po dang / chos can gyi dngos po rnams
NK070(thu)001:7864: kyi rang bzhin chos nyid la 'bras bur sku dang
NK070(thu)001:7865: ye shes kyi ngo bo gnas kyang yul yul log
NK070(thu)001:7866: par kun tu brtag pa'i mngon par zhen pa'i rim
NK070(thu)001:7867: pa las nyon shes bya'i gzung 'dzin phra rag sna
NK070(thu)001:7868: tshogs kyis bsgrib pa gsang ba tsam du don ston
NK070(thu)001:7869: gnyis po dang / pas / a ti yo ga'o //
NK070(thu)001:7870: theg pa de rnams kyis tha snyad kyi mtshon pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7871: sgo nas ming tshig yi ge'i tshogs bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:7872: / yi ge'i sgras btags ming tshogs la //
NK070(thu)001:7873: brten pa tshig gi don rab tu mtshon te //
NK070(thu)001:7875: a'i na ta sna yig las snang yi ge thams cad ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:7876: a'i 'od zer gyi sgra'i la btags pa yi ge k+aa li sum cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:7877: a de nyid kyi sgra las gug 'greng la sogs pa brtag pa dbyangs yig a +aa /
NK070(thu)001:7884: de gnyis ka las snang ba ni ri r+ai /
NK070(thu)001:7886: ma ning gi yi ge bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:7887: sgra yig dbyangs yig de dag 'dus pa las ming byung /
NK070(thu)001:7888: ming de la brten nas byung ba'i tshig gi tshogs glegs bam rgya mtsho tsam gyi don rab tu /
NK070(thu)001:7889: mtshon nas bstan pa de gang gi theg pa brgyad
NK070(thu)001:7890: po gzhan dag snang ba ni lam rkyen yi ge'i
NK070(thu)001:7892: khong kanas gab khasbas don nga'byin pa //
NK070(thu)001:7893: ston gapa chardo rje'i thugs 2la gnas //
NK070(thu)001:7896: 1rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK070(thu)001:7897: khong 3nas ngo ma shes pas blo 'khrul pas btags
NK070(thu)001:7899: gshis las gab pa'i don ni rgyud kyi ston pas kun tu bzang mo lam gyi rgyud bshad pa /
NK070(thu)001:7900: mngon du 'byin la 'on kyang lam gyi rgyud 'khrugs
NK070(thu)001:7901: pa la sogs pa rag chod can la rgyud 'di
NK070(thu)001:7902: las sbas pa'i don rnams ni rjes 'jug gi rdo
NK070(thu)001:7903: rje slob dpon bla ma rgyud pa'i man ngag can
NK070(thu)001:7904: gyis 'byin pas sangs rgyas kyi lam rgyud kyi gzhung
NK070(thu)001:7905: gi lung yod kyang bla ma'i gdams ngag las rag
NK070(thu)001:7906: las pa mchog gi khyad par du le'u bcu gsum
NK070(thu)001:7907: pa 'di tshig rgyud don rgyud snyan rgyud gsum gyis
NK070(thu)001:7908: rgyud don gtan la phab pa'i bla ma'i man ngag
NK070(thu)001:7909: gi don la thugs gnas pa gcig la rag las
NK070(thu)001:7910: pa kho na'o // dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK070(thu)001:7911: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:7912: phyi rol du grol lam rim gyis 'jug pa bskyed
NK070(thu)001:7913: pa'i rim pa'i dbang du rim pa drug ltar bshad
NK070(thu)001:7914: pa ni / gzhi rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med
NK070(thu)001:7915: nyid kyis dkyil 'khor dang ldan pa de lta bas
NK070(thu)001:7916: gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi don de ngo shes
NK070(thu)001:7917: nas lta bas de'i blos ting nge 'dzin lnga'i dang
NK070(thu)001:7918: po stong pa nyid kyi skabs su bsgom bya don
NK070(thu)001:7919: dam chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la ni bsgom byed
NK070(thu)001:7920: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi spros bral du
NK070(thu)001:7921: pa ni / bsgom / pa ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK070(thu)001:7922: de nas gnyis pa ye shes sgyu ma'i lta bu
NK070(thu)001:7923: ting nge 'dzin gyi skabs su phyi nang gi chos
NK070(thu)001:7924: thams cad gzugs brnyan gyi tshul gyis dkyil 'khor du
NK070(thu)001:7925: snang ba rnams ma bris par gsal bar byas pa
NK070(thu)001:7926: de ni gong gi ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:7927: 'khor goms pa las gyur pa'i don ni kun tu
NK070(thu)001:7929: de nas gsung pa phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK070(thu)001:7930: skabs su khams gsum ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:7931: nyid du gsal ba de gnas kyi yi ge h'u
NK070(thu)001:7932: du bsdus te cho ga gsum gyi lhag pa ting
NK070(thu)001:7933: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du lha bsgom pa'i ni
NK070(thu)001:7934: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi mchog
NK070(thu)001:7935: ces bya'o de dus na yan lag gi thugs kar
NK070(thu)001:7936: ye shes sems dpa' bsgom pa ni bdag nyid chen
NK070(thu)001:7937: po'i lha dang thugs kyi ye shes lnga'i rtags su
NK070(thu)001:7938: dbu rgyan gyi lha rigs lngas dbang bskur ba dang
NK070(thu)001:7939: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum gyi byin khagyis brlabs
NK070(thu)001:7940: kapa ni lhag pa'i lha'o de la ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:7941: rab tu brten pa de ni rtogs dka' zhing gnyis
NK070(thu)001:7942: med du zlums pas gsang ba'i thig le de dkyil
NK070(thu)001:7943: 'khor gyi lha du ma'i 'byung gzhir gyur pas dbyings
NK070(thu)001:7944: de nas bzhi po snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7945: skabs su 'byung ba lnga ni shes rab ste cha
NK070(thu)001:7946: phra bas rigs kyi yum lngar bsgom phung po ni
NK070(thu)001:7947: thabs te rags pas rigs kyi yab lngar bsgom pa
NK070(thu)001:7948: de bzhin te / la sogs pa dbang po lnga
NK070(thu)001:7949: yul lnga dus bzhi rig pa rnam shes lnga dang
NK070(thu)001:7950: sum 'dus kyi reg pa lta ngan bzhi de rnams
NK070(thu)001:7951: kyi rtog pa ni byang chub sems dpa' sems ma
NK070(thu)001:7952: khro bo khro mo de ltar lha rtogs dbyer med
NK070(thu)001:7953: pa ni rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7954: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi lha zhe gnyis kyi
NK070(thu)001:7955: dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i gong du bshad pa'i khayan
NK070(thu)001:7956: lag gi lha dgu rnams yongs su rdzogs pas yid
NK070(thu)001:7957: kyi mos kaspyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu
NK070(thu)001:7958: bzang po dang bzang mo thub drug dang bcas par
NK070(thu)001:7959: bsgom pa'o // de nas lnga pa tshogs bsgrub pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7960: dus su a li ka li la sogs pa longs
NK070(thu)001:7961: spyod lnga ni 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyi snying po
NK070(thu)001:7962: la yul du ma chags pa'i thabs kyis rol pas
NK070(thu)001:7963: ni thig le mnyam sbyor bas zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:7964: lus la bde ba'i ye shes skyes nas tshim pa'i
NK070(thu)001:7965: rol mo yi sems dga' ba'i ye shes skyes pa
NK070(thu)001:7966: ni bdag nyid chen po dgyes pa la mchod pa
NK070(thu)001:7967: 'bul ba ste / de ltar spyod pas ci byas
NK070(thu)001:7968: kyang rang kha ma'i bag chags su mi 'gyur te
NK070(thu)001:7969: 'bul ba ste / / chos nyid zag pa med
NK070(thu)001:7970: pa'i ye shes dang bsod nams kyi tshogs gnyis kyi
NK070(thu)001:7971: rgyun la gnas pas rgyu sems can rnams ye shes
NK070(thu)001:7972: sgyu mar snang ba nyid las /
NK070(thu)001:7973: 'bras bu sangs rgyas mi gzhan par rang snang bas
NK070(thu)001:7974: na rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog ces sa
NK070(thu)001:7975: bcu gsum par yi ge 'khor lo phyin nas snang
NK070(thu)001:7976: stong gnyis su mi phyed pa'i don rtogs dka' zhing
NK070(thu)001:7977: gnyis med du zlums pas gsal ba'i thig le nyid
NK070(thu)001:7978: kyis dbyings de nyid ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos
NK070(thu)001:7979: gzhi zung 'jug gi sku thob pa'i dus na phyogs
NK070(thu)001:7980: bcu dus bzhi mngon par rdzogs pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:7981: yon tan phrin las thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK070(thu)001:7982: pa nyer lnga'i bdag nyid kyi zhal bdag gis mthong
NK070(thu)001:7983: ba'i phyir ste / thams cad rig pa bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:7984: chen po'i ngang du dbang bsgyur zhing mchog nyid dam
NK070(thu)001:7986: gzhi rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lam thabs grol gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:7987: 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor gsum /
NK070(thu)001:7988: ma lus par dus gcig tu rang snang bas na
NK070(thu)001:7989: 'og gi dkyil 'khor la gnas zhes pa'i tshig gsum
NK070(thu)001:7990: drang ngo // gdul bya gang yang mi 'dor zhes
NK070(thu)001:7991: sa'i skabs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor ba
NK070(thu)001:7992: zhes pa'i tshig lnga drang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:7995: 'bras bu zhib tu mi bcom mo //
NK070(thu)001:7996: de nas nang du grol lam ring 'jug pa zhes ye shes myur bas /
NK070(thu)001:7997: rdzogs pa'i don 'og sgo bas ye shes bul bas bskyed pa'i rim par gsang thig ltar bshad pa /
NK070(thu)001:7998: la bzhi'i dang po yid kun tu bzang po'i thig le'i man ngag bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8000: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8001: nang snying kha gi rtsa'i mdo snying po dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8002: yan lag rin po che sgrob lta bu'i na rtsa'i
NK070(thu)001:8003: khrag gi drod kyi bug gi bde ba'i 1dwangs ma
NK070(thu)001:8004: chen po ye shes kyi 'byung ba lnga dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:8005: pa rang snang ba ni yum spyan ma m+aa ma
NK070(thu)001:8006: ki gos dkar mo sgrol ma kun mo lnga ye
NK070(thu)001:8007: shes sku lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo nyid du
NK070(thu)001:8008: ldan pa de dwangs ma lnga po de dag 1
NK070(thu)001:8009: gi rten sdud smin bskyod go 'byed par byed pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8010: las mi mthun pa lnga'i lus sam rtogs pa thams
NK070(thu)001:8011: cad bde ba chen por snang bar byed pas na
NK070(thu)001:8012: sgra'i gnas brgyad ni ngo bo bya byed dgongs pa
NK070(thu)001:8013: dang / byung khungs dang ni 'brel pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8014: gnas bzhi dang ni ba dgas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8015: zhes de'i gnyis pa las kyi dbye ba'am /
NK070(thu)001:8016: yang na sgra gnas pa ka ba /
NK070(thu)001:8017: de las bzhag na ka bas te /
NK070(thu)001:8018: gdung ma 'degs pa'i byed las mtshon pa lta bu
NK070(thu)001:8019: kho nar brjod kyang lnga po de nyid bdag po
NK070(thu)001:8020: 'i rkyen dbang po'i yang na mu stegs rtag lta'i
NK070(thu)001:8021: byed pa po'i bdag po lta bu ma yin gyi
NK070(thu)001:8022: don du na rgyal ba'i sku la mdun rgyab med
NK070(thu)001:8023: pa ltar ston 'khor ram snang ngam bya ba dang
NK070(thu)001:8024: byed pa gnyis ka las ma 'das pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8025: tha snyad tsam du mtshon tshul gyis byed pa po nyid du'ang 'gal ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:8028: dwangs ma lnga po de dag nyid ye shes snying
NK070(thu)001:8029: po'i gzhugs gnas gzhal yas khang gi ngo bo dkyil
NK070(thu)001:8030: 'khor yin pa'i phyir sgra gnas pa gnas gzhi'i tshigs
NK070(thu)001:8031: la ste / shing la bya tshangs bcas bya ba lta bu'am /
NK070(thu)001:8032: yang na spyi bor yi ge gyis ye shes lnga
NK070(thu)001:8033: mtshon pa lta bu ye shes 00snying po'i thig le
NK070(thu)001:8034: de 1nyid las ma g.yos par lngar snang bas gcig
NK070(thu)001:8035: dang du mar 1bral ba'i tshul gyi thabs 1bde ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8036: ye shes dang / shes rab stong pa gnyis su med pa nyid do //
NK070(thu)001:8037: ye shes snying po'i thig le de'i ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:8038: ni kun rda'i 'od lta bu las 'od kha dog
NK070(thu)001:8039: sna tshogs kyi phyir phyogs gcig tu cir yang ma
NK070(thu)001:8040: nges pas phyogs med du cir yang snang bas blos
NK070(thu)001:8041: yul du brtag tu med pas rang snang gsal bas
NK070(thu)001:8042: sgra gnas gsum par ka ste dpe byed pa mtshon
NK070(thu)001:8043: pa'i sgra shing la s+t+wa re rgyob byas pa lta
NK070(thu)001:8044: bu'am / yang na rtsa la ba sbyar na /
NK070(thu)001:8045: thams cad kyi rtsa ba byed pa lta bu yang 'gyur te /
NK070(thu)001:8046: de ltar bsgom bya sgom byed bsgom pa rang gi dngos po gsum du gyur pa med pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8047: yul yul can med par rang gsal bas rang rig
NK070(thu)001:8048: pa'i mngon sum yin pas dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i mchog
NK070(thu)001:8049: go // 1de'i dgos pa ci zhig snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:8050: dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor las ka byung ba'i //
NK070(thu)001:8053: dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying po dang drug po
NK070(thu)001:8054: de dag ye shes lnga rang byung ye shes dang
NK070(thu)001:8056: rang snang bar ye nas gnas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8057: gzhi mi 'gyur bar yongs su grub pa shes bya'i
NK070(thu)001:8058: dkyil 'khor yin pa de las gong du 00bshad pa
NK070(thu)001:8059: ltar phyin ci ma log par shes byed du yongs
NK070(thu)001:8060: su grub pas rang rang gsal ba /
NK070(thu)001:8061: ye shes lngar ma 'dres la rang byung ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8062: su yongs su rdzogs par gsal bar byung ba ste
NK070(thu)001:8063: / ye shes drug go brten nas de'i 'od kyis
NK070(thu)001:8064: chos nyid kyi yon tan gyi rang rgyud kyi ye
NK070(thu)001:8065: shes kyi rtsa bzhi'i nang gi snying po sku +aahgasunga
NK070(thu)001:8066: h'u thugs kyi yi ge 'bras bu gsum bskul /
NK070(thu)001:8067: 1de dag gi 'od kyis 'gro drug bskyed pa'i sa bon sum tri pre du a n+ri drug dang /
NK070(thu)001:8068: sems las byung ba la drug kyog gnyid kyi rtog
NK070(thu)001:8069: pa sbyangs nas kun gyi snying yid sgo lnga'i rnam
NK070(thu)001:8070: par shes pa bag chags bzhi pa dag pas ye
NK070(thu)001:8071: shes kyi 'od ye shes kyi snying po'i thig le
NK070(thu)001:8072: la 'dus pas dwangs ma 'byung ba lnga yang rim
NK070(thu)001:8073: pa bzhin du ye shes snying po la bsdus nas
NK070(thu)001:8074: ye shes snying po'i thig le nyid kyang ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:8075: nyid cir yang ma dmigs te /
NK070(thu)001:8076: yod med kyi mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i thugs
NK070(thu)001:8077: ye shes h'u lnga'i dkyil 'khor du rang gsal ba
NK070(thu)001:8078: ni / gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir mtha' bral
NK070(thu)001:8079: gyi bde ba'i ye shes dkyil 'khor gyis mchog go
NK070(thu)001:8080: ni / // de dag sgra gnas lnga par 'byung
NK070(thu)001:8081: khung gi shing las 'bras bu 'gyur ba lta bu
NK070(thu)001:8082: tha snyad tsam du bzhag mod kyi 'bras bu ye
NK070(thu)001:8083: nas rgyu rkyen med par rang snang bas gsal byed
NK070(thu)001:8085: bskyed bya bskyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras tha dad su thal ba'am song ba med do //
NK070(thu)001:8086: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa kun mo'i thig le'i man ngag bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8087: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor thig le dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:8088: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8089: gsang ba'i lte ba'i rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:8090: dbus ni dbyings phyug ma yum lnga'i thig le a
NK070(thu)001:8091: thung gi dbyibs su gnas pa de ye shes lnga'i
NK070(thu)001:8092: dkyil 'khor du gsal ba de ni der yi ge
NK070(thu)001:8093: a'i thung ngu yod pa 1phyir ma skyes pa dang
NK070(thu)001:8094: lus sam yi ge 1thams cad kyi rgyu'i ru gyur
NK070(thu)001:8095: pa 1phyir na dbyings zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8096: 1de'i phyir na dwangs ma'i 'byung ba lnga'i cha phra ba shes rab rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK070(thu)001:8097: cha rag pa chen po lnga ni rigs kyi yab yin pas de bzhin te /
NK070(thu)001:8098: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8099: lte ba'i a de'i dwangs ma lnga'i cha phra ba cha rag pa las /
NK070(thu)001:8100: rigs 1lnga yab yum du rang snang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8101: khabyang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK070(thu)001:8102: 1dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK070(thu)001:8104: lte ba'i a de'i yan lag gi drug cu re
NK070(thu)001:8105: bzhi'i yi ge ka dang kha la sogs pa rnams
NK070(thu)001:8106: kyi mtshon pa'i rtog pa dbang po lnga yul lnga
NK070(thu)001:8107: dus bzhi rig pa rnam shes lnga'i dngos po rnams
NK070(thu)001:8108: kyi sgras sum 'dus kyi reg pa dang lta ngan
NK070(thu)001:8109: bzhi po kyang rdo rje'i skye mched de byang chub
NK070(thu)001:8110: sems dpa' dang sems ma khro bo dang khro mo'i
NK070(thu)001:8111: tshogs du gsal bar byed 1pa la 1de'i yid chos
NK070(thu)001:8112: nyon mongs pa drug po thams cad kyang lha'i sku
NK070(thu)001:8113: thub drug la sogs phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du rang
NK070(thu)001:8114: snang bar byed pas na spyod yul thams cad yongs
NK070(thu)001:8115: su dag pa'i kun tu bzang po'i ngo bor gyur
NK070(thu)001:8116: pa'i phyir / kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK070(thu)001:8118: bdag nyid chen po lhag pa yis //
NK070(thu)001:8119: thugs kyi ye shes lngas blta 00zhing //
NK070(thu)001:8121: chen po 'khor 'das kyi dngos po thams cad ngo
NK070(thu)001:8122: bo yid chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes kho
NK070(thu)001:8123: na'i yin pa phyir bdag nyid chen po zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:8124: ba ste / de yang dkyil 'khor dang por snying
NK070(thu)001:8125: kha chos kyi 'khor lo la yang bsgom pa'i khyad
NK070(thu)001:8126: par gyi cho gas rang la gnas pa de kun
NK070(thu)001:8127: tu bzang po'i man ngag gis khyad par du gsal
NK070(thu)001:8128: bar byas pa'i phyir lhag pa'i sa zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:8129: ba ste / ste / chos kyi 'khor lo de nyid ye shes h'u lngar sngar grub zin to //
NK070(thu)001:8130: de yang dkyil 'khor la zhes pa yi ge la
NK070(thu)001:8131: 0dang ye shes lnga'i zhes pa 0sa gnyis kyi sgra
NK070(thu)001:8132: gnas gsum 0 pa snying kha byed pa po'i sa
NK070(thu)001:8133: dang gnyis 0 pa lte ba bya ba las kyi
NK070(thu)001:8134: lta bur blta 0bya la lta byed 0kyi bar 'dogs
NK070(thu)001:8135: mod kyang / snying kha dang lte ba steng 'og gi 1gnas dang /
NK070(thu)001:8136: thugs kyi don ye shes lngar gsal yang mthar 'bral
NK070(thu)001:8137: du byed pa'i 1las kyi tha 11dad kyang yid rang
NK070(thu)001:8138: byung gi ye shes dang kun gzhi chos dbyings ye
NK070(thu)001:8139: shes gnyis ngo bos tha mi dad pas dbyings ye
NK070(thu)001:8140: shes gnyis med kyi don lta ba sa mthong zhing
NK070(thu)001:8141: rtog pa ni yul dbyings mthong ba med pa'i tshul
NK070(thu)001:8142: gyis rang gsal ba'i ye shes gnyis med du mthong
NK070(thu)001:8143: ba kho na'o // de ltar mngon du /
NK070(thu)001:8144: ma gyur te yul du zhen pa ni theg pa
NK070(thu)001:8145: chen po'i gsang sngags pa ting nge 'dzin las nyams
NK070(thu)001:8146: pa'o // lte ba'i kun gzhi a de nyid las
NK070(thu)001:8147: bde'i ye shes thob pa'i dus na snying kha'i tha
NK070(thu)001:8148: mal pa'i yid kyis rgyun yang bde ba'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8149: su bsdus te rang rgyud pa med lte ba'i a
NK070(thu)001:8150: thung kun gzhi rang gi ngo bo thig le nyid
NK070(thu)001:8151: kyang phyogs gcig 'di 'drar mi dmigs nas yod med
NK070(thu)001:8152: kyi mtha' thams cad dang bral bar rang gsal ba
NK070(thu)001:8153: pa'o // ni / kun gzhi de nyid kun tu
NK070(thu)001:8154: bzang mo'i ngo bo nyid nyams su myong bas don
NK070(thu)001:8156: dkyil 'khor gsum po mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8157: lo sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:8158: / snying po thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:8159: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te //
NK070(thu)001:8160: 1gong ma sprul pa'i 'khor lo las a'i sgra tsam
NK070(thu)001:8161: snang ba las kyang thig 1ler 'od dkar po byung
NK070(thu)001:8162: ngo // de dag 1gi 'od zer rtsa a ba
NK070(thu)001:8163: d+hu te nas yar gyen du song bas mgrin pa
NK070(thu)001:8164: 1longs spyod kyi snying po'i thig le la phog pa
NK070(thu)001:8165: sa thig ye 'khyag pa bzhugs te /
NK070(thu)001:8166: bzhag dkar po 'o mas gang ba ltar song ba
NK070(thu)001:8167: ni mnyam bzhag gi sbyor ba sa rtog tshogs dag
NK070(thu)001:8169: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo'i sa //
NK070(thu)001:8170: ye shes dgyes la mchod pa 'bul //
NK070(thu)001:8172: longs spyod kyi thig le de zhu zhing yongs su
NK070(thu)001:8173: gyur pas kha ba mngar ba tsha ba skyur ba
NK070(thu)001:8174: yang ba ska ba'i 0ro drug gi bde ba'i 1ye
NK070(thu)001:8175: shes drug tu gsal bas lam pa'i blo tshim par
NK070(thu)001:8176: byed pa ni rol mo'i ye shes kyis mchog ste
NK070(thu)001:8177: / bde ba'i ye shes 1de nyid yul du myong
NK070(thu)001:8178: ba med pa'i tshul gyis dgyes shing rang gsal du
NK070(thu)001:8179: myong ba la ni mchod pa gnas su stobs pas
NK070(thu)001:8181: de ltar ro drug po thams cad kyang spyod pa
NK070(thu)001:8182: la mi 'dzin par sa na spyod pa dag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8183: man ngag ces bya ba 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:8184: 'khor lo bzhi pa glad pa bde chen khyab bdal
NK070(thu)001:8185: chen po'i bsgom pa phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba
NK070(thu)001:8186: thams cad mngon gsum du rdzogs pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:8187: yon tan phrin las kyi gnas man ngag bstan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8188: phyir / zag pa med pa'i bsod nams 0kyis //
NK070(thu)001:8189: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8190: 0bshad pa nyid kyi ro drug pa la sogs thams
NK070(thu)001:8191: cad zag pa med pa'i bde ba nyams su myong
NK070(thu)001:8192: ba'i bsod nams kyis 'khor ba'i rgyu dngos 'dzin gyi
NK070(thu)001:8193: bag chags su mi 'gyur zhing dri ma dag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8194: phyir / ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba //
NK070(thu)001:8196: ye shes de nyid la ma zhen pa'i rol pa'i skad cig ma'i yin pa phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8197: sgra gnas 0gnyis par bya ba las kyis yang 'gyur la /
NK070(thu)001:8198: zhen pa med par gsal ba'i phyir na sgyu mar yang rang snang ba la ming 'dogs so //
NK070(thu)001:8199: longs spyod pa po yin pa de'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8200: mgrin pa'i ye shes 00drug po de nyid 'od zer
NK070(thu)001:8201: drug tu 'bar nas a ba d+hu ti nas yar
NK070(thu)001:8202: gyen du 'agro'o // rol mo'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas mchog /
NK070(thu)001:8204: 'od zer 00de'i bde ba chen po'i 'khor la chen po'i ham gyi thig le bzhu nas /
NK070(thu)001:8205: thig le bzhi bcu rtsa lnga la sogs pa'i rtsa
NK070(thu)001:8206: gnas thams cad du thim pas rol mo'i gzhi ma
NK070(thu)001:8207: nges pa sna tshogs su snang ba bzhin du bde
NK070(thu)001:8208: ba'i ye shes kyis tshim par byed pas phung po
NK070(thu)001:8209: la sogs pa'i rtogs pa thams cad sku dang ye
NK070(thu)001:8210: shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsam yas su snang bar byed
NK070(thu)001:8213: he du 1de ci'i phyir snang bar byed snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:8214: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:8216: ham gyi thig le de nyid bde ba chen po'i
NK070(thu)001:8217: ngo bo nyid du ye nas gnas kyang rtogs par
NK070(thu)001:8218: dka' ba sa gsang ba'i don de nyid las 'bras
NK070(thu)001:8219: bu bde ba chen po'i skye ba rgyun du 'byung
NK070(thu)001:8220: ba nyid kyi rgyur gyur pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8222: ham gyi de nyid bsgom nas snang ba 1las kyi
NK070(thu)001:8223: dang ye nas bde bar byas pa rang gi ngo
NK070(thu)001:8224: bo gnyis kas bde ba 11chen po'i 'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8225: kho na'i phyir / de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'am dngos /
NK070(thu)001:8227: thig le de nyid kyi bsgom pa'i yon tan bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:8228: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:8229: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK070(thu)001:8230: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NK070(thu)001:8232: sngar gong du bshad pa bzhin du dkyil 'khor bzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:8233: man ngag gi nyams su myong ba ni rgyab dkyil
NK070(thu)001:8234: 'khor ma lus pa nyer lnga po thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:8235: zhal mngon sum du mthong ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:8236: de yang dag nyid kyis zhal bdag gi mthong ba zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8237: phyi nang gnyis po de dag las /
NK070(thu)001:8238: thugs thig ltar rdzogs pa'i rdzogs par 'og sgo thabs kyi lam cig char du bshad pa /
NK070(thu)001:8240: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8241: gzhi rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ye nas ldan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8242: thig le nang byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:8243: bde ba'i ye shes kyi don de dkyil 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:8244: ngo bor go ba des gong gi 1dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK070(thu)001:8245: por la ni steng sgo'i ye shes kyi bde ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8246: ro bskyed pa la dkyil 'khor bsgom pa sngar dang
NK070(thu)001:8247: 'dra'o // de nas rnal 'byor pa yab yum thabs
NK070(thu)001:8248: dang shes rab lha yab yum kyis sku phyag rgya'i
NK070(thu)001:8249: dkyil 'khor gnyis su khams dang skye mched mkha' gsang
NK070(thu)001:8251: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa las byung ba'i yab kyi
NK070(thu)001:8252: zla ba'i byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gsang ba
NK070(thu)001:8253: rdo rje'i nor bu bde ba'i ro dang bcas pa
NK070(thu)001:8254: snang ba'i dus na thugs kyis ye shes lnga'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:8255: 'khor du gsal bar snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8256: sku ye shes mtha' ma bsgrib par rang bzhin gyi
NK070(thu)001:8257: 'od gsal bas dkyil 'khor gyi mchog don gsum gyis
NK070(thu)001:8258: dang po ye shes gsal ba'i thabs nyid shes 0rab
NK070(thu)001:8259: mi rtog pa'i ngang du sbyor ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:8260: sbyor ba de'i tshe yum gyi nyi ma'i byang sems
NK070(thu)001:8261: kyi gsang ba'i thig le'i dkyil 'khor la thams cad
NK070(thu)001:8262: kyi bcud thig le 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8263: 'khor 'das sam lha'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i rgyur
NK070(thu)001:8264: gyur pas na dbyings bzlog pa'i thabs mkhas pas bde
NK070(thu)001:8265: ba'i ye shes kyis zin na de la gang byung
NK070(thu)001:8266: zhe na 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum chen
NK070(thu)001:8267: mo phung po lnga la sogs pa rnams ni rigs
NK070(thu)001:8268: kyi de bzhin zhes pa nas rig pa rnams zhes
NK070(thu)001:8269: pa'i bar thams cad kyang spyod yul yongs su dag
NK070(thu)001:8270: pa kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis
NK070(thu)001:8271: grub par byin gyis brlabs par byed pa'i mthu dang
NK070(thu)001:8272: ldan pa de pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru'i rtser snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:8273: / gnyis pa shes rab mi rtog pa thabs su lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba sbyor ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:8274: yab kyi zla ba'i byang sems kyi ro ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8275: lngar gsal bas ma nyams shing bdag nyid lhag pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8276: thugs kyis ye shes lnga'i ngo bor lta zhing dmigs
NK070(thu)001:8277: pa mi 'gyur bar ting nge 'dzin brten pas snying
NK070(thu)001:8278: po thig le dus gcig tu bsres pas mnyam por
NK070(thu)001:8279: sbyor bas yod med kyi mtha' gnyis las grol ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8280: bde ba'i ye shes kyi ro thob nas steng 'og
NK070(thu)001:8281: gi rlung la sogs pa'i lus kyi 'khrul 'khor gyi
NK070(thu)001:8282: rol mo yi gar thabs chen pos bde ba skye
NK070(thu)001:8283: pa'i thig le la dga' ba bcu drug gis rim
NK070(thu)001:8284: pa slar rang gi gnas su ldog nas gzhi rang
NK070(thu)001:8285: bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor de rtogs pa lta ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8286: dkyil 'khor du gnas pa'i ye shes dgyes pa la
NK070(thu)001:8287: mchod par 'bul bas de gzhi ci bzhin nyid du
NK070(thu)001:8288: mngon sum du gyur cing gshegs pa'i tshe chos thams
NK070(thu)001:8289: cad kyang 'khrul pa zhen pa'i snang ba dang rang
NK070(thu)001:8290: bzhin snang ba gnyis su gnas pa'i 'khrul snang rtog
NK070(thu)001:8291: pa'i zag pa phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa zad nas
NK070(thu)001:8292: med pa'i bde stong gnyis med kyi don gcig po
NK070(thu)001:8293: de rang bzhin gyi snang ba las rtogs pa lta
NK070(thu)001:8294: bu'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa la sbyor ba'i thabs
NK070(thu)001:8295: lam kyi nges pa pos nges par te gsal ba
NK070(thu)001:8296: byas pas 'bras bu lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba
NK070(thu)001:8297: las bsod nams kyi tshogs mi 'dzin pas ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8298: kyi tshogs dang gnyis kyi skabs su sgrib pa byang
NK070(thu)001:8299: ba dang / 'bras bu chub pa gnyis dus gcig
NK070(thu)001:8300: tu ye shes sgyu mar rang snang bar 'gyur te
NK070(thu)001:8301: ba dang / / yab yum gyi thig le'i rtog
NK070(thu)001:8302: pa rang rang gi bde ba'i ye shes la rol
NK070(thu)001:8303: mo lta bu'i 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:8304: dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab par snang bas mtha'
NK070(thu)001:8305: yas mchog ces bya'o de yang nyi zla'i thig le
NK070(thu)001:8306: gnyis su med cing zung du 'brel pa'i don de
NK070(thu)001:8307: rtogs dka' zhing gnyis med du zlum pas gsal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8308: thig le nyid kyi dbyings kyi ro las ma 'das
NK070(thu)001:8309: ba dang / / pa'i phyir / don dam stong
NK070(thu)001:8310: pa dang kun rdzob bde ba'am gsal ba'i bden pa
NK070(thu)001:8311: gnyis su mi phyed pa'i zung 'jug gi don de
NK070(thu)001:8312: ni sangs rgyas kun kyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi sku
NK070(thu)001:8313: 'od de la lnga la sogs lhun gyis grub pa
NK070(thu)001:8314: ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon sum du rdzogs pas
NK070(thu)001:8315: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las thugs ma lus
NK070(thu)001:8316: pa rnams rang rig pa'i mngon sum du byas pa
NK070(thu)001:8317: ba dang / / pa'i phyir / ni / yul
NK070(thu)001:8318: yul can du mthong ba med pa'i tshul gyis rang
NK070(thu)001:8319: gsal bas bdag nyid kyi zhal bdag gis mthong ba
NK070(thu)001:8320: ba dang / / pa'i phyir / ni / zhes
NK070(thu)001:8321: bya'o // gong gi bskyed rdzogs kyi lam gsum po
NK070(thu)001:8322: de dag gi yon tan thun mong du bstan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8323: ba dang / / pa'i phyir / ni / zhes
NK070(thu)001:8324: bya'o // phyir / dbang bsgyur mchog nyid dam pa
NK070(thu)001:8325: ba dang / / pa'i phyir / ni / zhes bya'o // phyir / yin // zhes gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8326: gong gi phyi nang gsang gsum du rnam par bshad
NK070(thu)001:8327: pa'i rjes su 'phrin las bzhi dang dngos grub gnyis
NK070(thu)001:8328: po thams cad la rang dbang du bsgyur bar byed
NK070(thu)001:8329: pa ni / rig pa'i rgyal po rang dbang thob pas mchog nyid dam pa yin pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8331: rdzogs gapa'i dkyil kha'khor kalhun gyis grub //
NK070(thu)001:8332: cargyan du dkyil nga'khor ma lus chathogs //
NK070(thu)001:8334: phyi bskyed rim gyis lam lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi lha'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:8335: nang gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor thig
NK070(thu)001:8336: le dang bde ba'i ye shes dang gsum la blo
NK070(thu)001:8337: brten par gnas pas don gyi gzhi shes bya rang
NK070(thu)001:8338: bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gnas lugs de nyid mngon
NK070(thu)001:8339: du byas bas rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin lhun
NK070(thu)001:8340: gyis grub pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8341: du rang snang bar gyur pas na rdzogs pa zhes
NK070(thu)001:8342: bya'o // dkyil 'khor bdun gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK070(thu)001:8343: cad sku dang ye shes kyi gsal cha'i rgyan du
NK070(thu)001:8344: ma 'dres la chos nyid du yongs su rdzogs par
NK070(thu)001:8347: 'o na rgyal ba'i snang ngo na chos thams cad
NK070(thu)001:8348: sku'i dkyil 'khor du snang bas gdul bya sems can
NK070(thu)001:8349: du snang ba med pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8350: thugs rje mi skye bar 'gag par dogs pa'i 'gal
NK070(thu)001:8351: pa khong nas 'ong ba la len dkyus su 'debs
NK070(thu)001:8352: pa ni rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas //
NK070(thu)001:8355: gong du bshad kapa bzhin du gzhi rang bzhin dang /
NK070(thu)001:8356: 'bras bu rdzogs par lhun gyis grub kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8357: gnyis rang rig pa'i bdag nyid du mnyam par sbyor
NK070(thu)001:8358: bas / gdul bya 'gro ba drug po thams cad kyang rgyal ba bdag nyid rang /
NK070(thu)001:8359: las mi gzhan par gsal ba nyid thugs rje chen
NK070(thu)001:8360: por bdag nyid gcig par 'brel ba yod pa yin
NK070(thu)001:8361: pa'i phyir / gdul bya 'gro drug gi dus snga
NK070(thu)001:8362: phyi dang gnas mtho dman thams cad du sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:8363: kyi ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:8364: 'khor 1ma 'dres la ji lta ba mkhyem pa'i ye
NK070(thu)001:8365: shes kyis spros bral du yongs su 1rdzogs 11par mkhyen
NK070(thu)001:8366: cing gsal bas thams cad kyi mdzad pa gzugs sku
NK070(thu)001:8367: gnyis la sogs pa gang yang mi 'gog par yongs
NK070(thu)001:8369: de'i phyir na phyogs dus dkyil 'khor 'dul ba'i mgon //
NK070(thu)001:8371: phyogs bcu dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rgyal ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8372: dkyil 'khor longs sku sprul sku la sogs pa thams
NK070(thu)001:8373: cad du rang snang bas gdul bya dag ma dag
NK070(thu)001:8374: gang yang mi 'dor bar 'dul ba'i phyir sdug bsngal
NK070(thu)001:8375: skyob cing 'gro ba'i mgon po byed pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8378: gdul bya'i dus gnas thams cad sangs rgyas las ma
NK070(thu)001:8379: 'dres par gsal nas 'gro don mdzad na de dag
NK070(thu)001:8380: la don byed pa'i rtog pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:8381: yang na gdul byar zhen pa'i rtog pa mi mnga' 'am snyams pa /
NK070(thu)001:8382: rgol ba kho la len dkyus sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrol ba yi //
NK070(thu)001:8383: bya byed med par dkyil 'khor spyod //
NK070(thu)001:8385: dper na sgyu ma mkhan ni sgyu ma'i rdzas rgyu
NK070(thu)001:8386: rkyen gyis byas pa'i dus nyid na dang po ji
NK070(thu)001:8387: ltar yin pa'i lo rgyus shes pas sgyu ma de
NK070(thu)001:8388: dag dngos 0por mi rtogs te bden par 'dus shes
NK070(thu)001:8389: pa med pa bzhin du ston pa ye shes sgyu
NK070(thu)001:8390: ma'i dkyil 'khor gzugs sku gnyis su snang bas 'gro
NK070(thu)001:8391: ba sgrol ba'i don byed pa'i mdzad pa'am gdul byed
NK070(thu)001:8392: do // de dag kyang thams cad sems nyid rig
NK070(thu)001:8393: pa ra snang du shes pas dpe sgyu ma de
NK070(thu)001:8394: do // bzhin 0yin / pa kho na'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8395: don bya pa'i yul byed pa'i mkhan po don bya
NK070(thu)001:8396: ba'i dngos po gsum du mi rtog ste rtog pa
NK070(thu)001:8397: med par gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor gzhan don gyi mdzad
NK070(thu)001:8398: pa ril thams cad mi 'gog par don spyod pa
NK070(thu)001:8399: kho na'o // rang gzhan gyi 'bras bu de dag kyang byas pa ma yin par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8400: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK070(thu)001:8401: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8402: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras bu sangs
NK070(thu)001:8403: rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan ril lhun grub tu
NK070(thu)001:8404: rdzogs pa ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ste
NK070(thu)001:8405: rdzogs pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK070(thu)001:8406: gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas de dag rang la yod
NK070(thu)001:8407: med kyi phyin ci log tu brtag pa'i sgrib byed
NK070(thu)001:8408: gzung 'dzin gyi zhen pa ldog par dka' ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:8409: / gnyen po thos bas ma bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyi //
NK070(thu)001:8410: rang byung ye shes kyis dkyil 'khor rang rig pa'i mngon sum kun ngam lhun gyis grub /
NK070(thu)001:8412: gnyen po thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyis
NK070(thu)001:8413: gong du bshad pa'i phyi nang gsang ba'i man ngag
NK070(thu)001:8414: gsum po'i don la blo mnyam par sbyor nas gnas
NK070(thu)001:8415: pas sgrib byed kyi zhen pa mthar dag ldog pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8416: dus na gzhi rang byung ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8417: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba nyid la
NK070(thu)001:8418: 'khor 'das kyis chos kun la ngam pa ste 'bras
NK070(thu)001:8419: bu rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK070(thu)001:8420: ming 'dogs pa'i phyir 'bras bu log nas rgyu rkyen
NK070(thu)001:8421: 'dus byas pa ma yin pa ste mdor na gsal
NK070(thu)001:8422: byed kyi rgyu rkyen las byung ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8423: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK070(thu)001:8424: 'da' bar mi mdzad dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:8426: lam 'di ni med par lam gzhan gyis sangs mi rgyas pa'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:8427: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid 'di las
NK070(thu)001:8428: mi 'da' ba'i ste 'da' bar mi mdzad pa na
NK070(thu)001:8429: dam tshig mchog yin phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:8430: theg pa 'di'i che ba'i yon tan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8431: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK070(thu)001:8432: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi //
NK070(thu)001:8433: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK070(thu)001:8434: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:8435: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:8436: sdig pa'i grogs po ste log pa'i bshes gnyen ma
NK070(thu)001:8437: bstan pas blo phyin ci ma log pa'i gang zag
NK070(thu)001:8438: gang zhig dag rgyud sde zab mo 'di la mos
NK070(thu)001:8439: par gyur pa tsam gyis kyang /
NK070(thu)001:8440: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor lhag ma ma lus pas
NK070(thu)001:8441: thams cad kyi phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun tu nas
NK070(thu)001:8442: thams cad dkyil 'khor ma lus nye bar bsnyen par
NK070(thu)001:8443: byed pa'i nye ba'i thugs kyi sras su dgongs pas
NK070(thu)001:8444: ra 'gyur ba bar ma dor lam log par mi
NK070(thu)001:8445: ltung bas mi 'dor ro zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8446: skal pa chen po sprul sku'i zhing gi khams rdul phra mo snyed du //
NK070(thu)001:8447: bsil ba'i grangs dang skal ba mnyam pa'i theg pa
NK070(thu)001:8448: 'og ma shes rab blo shin tu sbyangs pa la
NK070(thu)001:8450: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yis //
NK070(thu)001:8452: zhes bya ba ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:8453: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad la mchod cing
NK070(thu)001:8454: bsnyen bsgrub byas pas 'bras bu na rang bzhin gsang
NK070(thu)001:8455: ba'i snying po bsgrub bya kun kyi mthar thug tu
NK070(thu)001:8456: gyur pas chen po 'di yin pa te de nyams
NK070(thu)001:8459: de ci lta bu yin zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:8460: gnas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i khams nang /
NK070(thu)001:8461: bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK070(thu)001:8462: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pas //
NK070(thu)001:8463: brnyes nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:8464: zhes bya ba ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:8465: dus 'das pa dang da ltar byung ba'i gnyis kyis
NK070(thu)001:8466: bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK070(thu)001:8467: ril thams cad gyi rgyu'i theg pa'i sgo nas dka'
NK070(thu)001:8468: ba mang po spyod kyang 'bras bu mthar ma phyin
NK070(thu)001:8469: pa de dag mthar thug gsang ba'i snying po'i lam
NK070(thu)001:8470: 'di rnyed nas bzod rgyal ba sku lnga yang dag
NK070(thu)001:8471: pa'i ra lhun gyis rdzogs pa sangs rgyas sa 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:8472: ba kho na'o // 'byung dang ma 'ongs thams cad kyang //
NK070(thu)001:8475: dus phyis 'byung ba dang ma 'ongs pa 'byung 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:8476: gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i rgyal ba thams cad rnams kyang
NK070(thu)001:8477: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di yi don rtog
NK070(thu)001:8478: pa la brten nas bzod sku lnga lhun gyis grub
NK070(thu)001:8480: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:8481: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa'i sa //
NK070(thu)001:8483: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di'i don nyid la
NK070(thu)001:8484: ni de lta bas rtogs pa rgyu bsgom pas de
NK070(thu)001:8485: don la blo gnas pa rkyen de mngon du byas
NK070(thu)001:8486: pas 'bras bu'am yang na gzhi lam 'bras bu'i mtshan
NK070(thu)001:8487: nyid gsum du brtag kyang don gyi ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:8488: dbyer mi phyed par gcig pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8490: de'i phyir rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa sa rnams la //
NK070(thu)001:8491: yang thugs kyi brtag bya 'di las gsang ba'i bya ba nges don gzhan med //
NK070(thu)001:8493: de las gzhan pa'i nges don gcig btsal kyang gzhan lta ci smos rgyal bas kyang mi bsnyes so //
NK070(thu)001:8495: zhes bya ba ni go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:8496: de ltar 'das pa dang da ltar gyi rgyal ba
NK070(thu)001:8497: kun gyi dgongs pa'i zhe phug yang 'di yin la
NK070(thu)001:8498: ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar 'byung bar ma nges
NK070(thu)001:8499: pa'i rgyal ba kun gyi bgrod pa'i lam kadang dgongs
NK070(thu)001:8500: pa'am mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu rang bzhin zer gnyis
NK070(thu)001:8501: ka yang gsang ba'i snying po'i don 'di las mi
NK070(thu)001:8502: bda' ba'i sa phyag rgya chen po'i mchog yin pa
NK070(thu)001:8503: phyir ro // kakun kyi phyag rgya chen po'i 1mchog /
NK070(thu)001:8505: 'di gang zag sus gzungs snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:8506: thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab gsum la rab tu sbyangs pas //
NK070(thu)001:8507: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis gzungs //
NK070(thu)001:8509: chos can gyi dngos po thams cad kyi chos nyid de kho na nyid shes pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8510: shes rab kyi mig dang ldan pa'i skyes bu rnams kyis 'di zungs shig go //
NK070(thu)001:8511: gang la sbyin pa'i snod bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8512: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la brten //
NK070(thu)001:8513: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK070(thu)001:8515: bstan pa'i don go ba shes rab dang gzhan don
NK070(thu)001:8516: gtsor byed pas snying rje dang bstan pa'i don 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:8517: nus pas nogs thub pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8518: snod kyi yon tan gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8519: gzhan gyis lus ngag la gnod pa ci byas kyang
NK070(thu)001:8520: rang gi sems rgyud mi 'khrugs pa ni ngang bzang
NK070(thu)001:8521: ba'o // skye bo tha mal pa rnams kyi spyod
NK070(thu)001:8522: pa las log pa ni dge slong gsar pa lta
NK070(thu)001:8524: blo mi 'gyur ba ni dam bca' mi 'dor te
NK070(thu)001:8525: brten zhing lus dang longs spyod chos phyir gtong phod
NK070(thu)001:8528: de las gzhan du ste snod ngan rnams la dus nam yang sbyin par mi bya //
NK070(thu)001:8531: gong ma'i yon tan rnams las bzlog pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8532: snod med de dag la ni rang gi snying 'byin
NK070(thu)001:8533: pa'i nyes pa dang bsdos te mi smra bar shin
NK070(thu)001:8535: gal te gsang mi thub pa'i nyes pa ni slob
NK070(thu)001:8536: dpon yang slob ma dpyad la blo rmongs pa mi
NK070(thu)001:8537: chos las gcom phyar che bas gal te snod med
NK070(thu)001:8538: la man ngag sbyin pa'i nyes dmigs ni tshe 'dir
NK070(thu)001:8539: yang dus min bar ni tshe srog zad nas /
NK070(thu)001:8540: 'chi bar 'gyur la shi ma thag tu /
NK070(thu)001:8541: bsreg dang tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad spreb pa grang
NK070(thu)001:8542: ba'i dmyal ba brgyad la stsogs pa sdug bsngal la
NK070(thu)001:8546: sa ma ya bkod pa las /
NK070(thu)001:8547: 1bskal pa chen po gsum du dmyal gabar gnas so //
NK070(thu)001:8548: de las thar nas bskal pa gnyis su yi dwags su ltung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8549: de nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi sgra thos par daka'o //
NK070(thu)001:8551: shin tu gsang ba man ngag gi snying po //
NK070(thu)001:8553: snod dkon zhing gsang mi thub pa'i gong ltar du
NK070(thu)001:8554: ltung ba nyes che ba'i phyir shin tu gsang dgos
NK070(thu)001:8555: la / snod dang ldan pa rnyed na tsheg chung
NK070(thu)001:8556: ngus dgos pa mtha' dag 'grub pa'i phyir man ngag
NK070(thu)001:8558: le'u bcu gsum pa'i rnam grangs su bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8560: // de nas rol mo'i glu rgyan gyi ye shes kyi dgyes pa bskyed pa'i mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8561: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen po'i glu 'di /
NK070(thu)001:8563: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yin la /
NK070(thu)001:8564: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi bstod pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8565: glu lnga spyir bsdus pa drug dang bcas par bzhi
NK070(thu)001:8566: bcu rtsa gnyis pa thams cad 'dus pa'i phyir rgyal
NK070(thu)001:8567: ba thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don glu
NK070(thu)001:8568: lnga ye shes mtshon pa ltar bzhugs pa gsal bar
NK070(thu)001:8569: de snang ba nyid dgyes pa chen po zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:8570: ste / glu drug po 'di bsnyen nas blang ngo
NK070(thu)001:8571: zhes gdul bya'i ngo na dgyes pa ltar snang ba
NK070(thu)001:8572: yin gyi rnam par rtog pa'i rkyen gyis bstod bskul
NK070(thu)001:8573: nas blang ba lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:8574: dang por rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku lnga la bstod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8575: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:8576: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8577: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'am rgyal ba sku bzhir snang ba
NK070(thu)001:8578: thams cad kyang rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8579: gcig gi ngo bo la lhun gyis grub par rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:8580: pa ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK070(thu)001:8581: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK070(thu)001:8583: thugs ye shes lnga 'i dkyil 'khor ni rnam par
NK070(thu)001:8584: mi rtog pa'i thig le ye shes chen por gsal
NK070(thu)001:8585: de nyid chos thams cad la khyab bdag chen por
NK070(thu)001:8586: gnas pa ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK070(thu)001:8587: bsod nams dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba ni 'khor ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8588: chos gang yang ma spangs pa'i la zhen pa zag
NK070(thu)001:8589: pa med pa'i bsod nams kyi gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8590: du rang snang ba ni sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:8591: pa chen po'i sku kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8592: sku'i mchog ces bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8593: gdul bya 'gro drug thams cad kyi ngo la zhing
NK070(thu)001:8594: khams dang dus thams cad kyi sku'i mchog cir yang
NK070(thu)001:8595: snang ba'i phyir sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:8596: // snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:8598: snang stong gnyis su mi phyed pa'i phyir thig le'i
NK070(thu)001:8599: ngo bo sku thams cad kun dbyer med du rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:8600: pa'i rdo rje'i sku kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8602: mjug gi ho zhes bya ba cha drug gnyis ni
NK070(thu)001:8603: +amo gyi thig le zla tshes na ro 'a chung
NK070(thu)001:8604: gi yi ge cha lnga'i sku lnga la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:8605: re re'ang lnga mtshon par glu'i mgo drang ba dang
NK070(thu)001:8606: nyer lnga dang ldan pa de ltar bstod pas mnyes
NK070(thu)001:8607: par gyur pa ni hohzhesa bya ba ste drug po
NK070(thu)001:8608: kun la mthun par shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8609: gsung lnga la bstod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8610: rdo rje zhes bya ba ni gsung gi ngo bo
NK070(thu)001:8611: grags stong dbyer mi phyed pa dang phrin las kyis
NK070(thu)001:8612: 'khor gyi sgrub pa 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:8613: bsod nams zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8614: bsod nams kyi ngo bo 'gro drug gi sgra skad
NK070(thu)001:8615: thams cad ma spangs par re re skad dang mthun
NK070(thu)001:8616: par rang snang ba'i phyir rdo rje'i tshig gis gsungs
NK070(thu)001:8619: grwa zur gyi spros pa med pa la thig le
NK070(thu)001:8620: chen po rang bzhin tshig tu brjod du med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8621: phyir na chos sku don gyi gsung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8622: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK070(thu)001:8624: tshig tu ma brjod par ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8625: kyi rig pa dang ldan pa sna tshogs kyis ni
NK070(thu)001:8626: thams cad 'khor ba gsal bar brda sprod pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:8627: mngon byang rig pa'i gsung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8628: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK070(thu)001:8630: sgra chen po gcig la yan lag mtha' yas pa
NK070(thu)001:8631: grangs mang ste sum brgya drug cu por grags pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8632: phyir tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi gsung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8633: rdo rje kha rgyal po thig kale che ho //
NK070(thu)001:8635: tshig tu brjod du med pa 'i thig le nyid
NK070(thu)001:8636: brjod pa dang 'dra bar 'khor gyi blo la gsal
NK070(thu)001:8637: ba ni / gsung gi rab bam rgyal po yin
NK070(thu)001:8638: pa'i phyir yi ge med pa'i lung sku'i gsung ngo
NK070(thu)001:8639: ba ni / // kasku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs khapa che //
NK070(thu)001:8640: yon ka tan phrin las kun khatu rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:8641: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8642: thugs lnga la bstod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8643: thugs stong kapa nyid kyi ye shes dang gsung so
NK070(thu)001:8644: sor rtogs pa dang sku me long lta bu'i dang
NK070(thu)001:8645: ye shes gsum po rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid chen po
NK070(thu)001:8646: de la yon tan mnyam pa nyid kyi dang phrin
NK070(thu)001:8647: las bya ba grub pa zhes bya ba'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:8648: lnga po nyid la 'bras bu sku kagsung thugs yon
NK070(thu)001:8649: tan lnga lnga po kun tu rdzogs la /
NK070(thu)001:8650: don ye shes lnga po de kalas rgyu rkyen gyis
NK070(thu)001:8651: ma btsal bar 'bras bu ye nas sku lnga la
NK070(thu)001:8652: sogs par nyer lnga rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8653: ye kanas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK070(thu)001:8655: 'dus pa'i rdzogs chen thig le che //
NK070(thu)001:8658: don ye shes lnga dang 'bras bu sku gsum thugs
NK070(thu)001:8659: yon tan phrin las lnga gnyis po de dag rgyu
NK070(thu)001:8660: sems nyid nas tha mi dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:8661: don dang rtags kyi gnas skabs kyis sku dang ye shes su snang ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8662: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:8663: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8664: yon tan lnga la bstod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8665: don dam par mi dmigs pa'i rig pa nyid kun
NK070(thu)001:8666: rdzob tu sgyu 'phrul te lha'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs
NK070(thu)001:8667: su snang bas na don la snang stong gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:8668: med pa mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings pa phyi 1nang
NK070(thu)001:8669: dang rgya che 1chung 11gzhal du med pa'i phyi rgyas
NK070(thu)001:8670: pa las / gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK070(thu)001:8671: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK070(thu)001:8672: zhes gzhal yas khang yon tan can ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8673: mtha' yas kun tu zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8674: rgyal ba drug pa'i longs sku zhing la mtha' yas shing /
NK070(thu)001:8675: thug pa med pa'i kun tu snang ba phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8677: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kha dog sna
NK070(thu)001:8678: tshogs pa'i 'od zer 'phro zhes bya ba ni 'od
NK070(thu)001:8680: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK070(thu)001:8682: grangs mtha' yas pa'i 'dod yon lnga po'i ril yon
NK070(thu)001:8683: tan thams cad kun nas lhun gyis grub pa nyid
NK070(thu)001:8684: myong ba rang rgyud pa med par myong tshul gyis
NK070(thu)001:8685: thim pa ni longs spyod pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8686: ste rgyan cha yon tan sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8687: ston pa la yon tan sna tshogs pa'i yon tan
NK070(thu)001:8688: stobs bcu dang mi 'jigs pa bzhi la sogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8689: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi dbang bcu phrin las bzhi po
NK070(thu)001:8690: lhun gyis grub pa de nyid rtags glang chen seng
NK070(thu)001:8691: ge'i la sogs pa'i sems can gyi khri la sogs
NK070(thu)001:8692: par mchog rma bya shang shang gi gdan thams cad
NK070(thu)001:8694: gdan de dag rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs chen po
NK070(thu)001:8695: las mi gzhan pa'i phyir gdan khri'o yon tan can
NK070(thu)001:8696: yin pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du /
NK070(thu)001:8697: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK070(thu)001:8698: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK070(thu)001:8700: phrin las la bstod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8701: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rdul phra mo snyed
NK070(thu)001:8702: 'dul ba'i zhing khams mtha' yas pa rnams ni chos
NK070(thu)001:8703: sku'i zhing khams sam dag pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK070(thu)001:8704: khams dang sprul sku'i zhing ngam ma dag pa sems
NK070(thu)001:8705: can dang / bar ma longs sku'i zhing khams rig 'dzin byang sems gsum du 'dus so //
NK070(thu)001:8706: rgyal bas 'gro ba'i don rnams mdzad pa'i phrin las
NK070(thu)001:8707: grangs mtha' yas rdul phran rnyed rnams ni zhi rgyal
NK070(thu)001:8709: phrin las de dag mdzad mkhan gyi skamsprul pa'i sku
NK070(thu)001:8710: grangs mtha' yas pa rdul phran bsam yas pa ni
NK070(thu)001:8712: cha lugs sna tshogs kyis tshul 111zhes bya bar 'dus so //
NK070(thu)001:8713: skad khacig yud la lhun gyis gagrub //
NK070(thu)001:8715: sprul pa de kamdag zhing khams de khamdag don mdzad
NK070(thu)001:8716: dus yud tsam la song ba med par zhing khams
NK070(thu)001:8717: thams cad khyab nas phrin las de dag gambya ba
NK070(thu)001:8718: gcig la zhugs nas rdzogs pa'i bar du skad cig
NK070(thu)001:8719: mas phrin las bzhi rim par ma brtsal bar dus
NK070(thu)001:8721: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK070(thu)001:8723: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK070(thu)001:8725: gong gi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las de
NK070(thu)001:8726: dag gis mtshon nas 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis
NK070(thu)001:8727: kyis bsdus pa'i chos can ril thams cad ma lus
NK070(thu)001:8728: pa yang chos nyid sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK070(thu)001:8729: las lngar ye nas gsal bar gnas pa zhes bya'o
NK070(thu)001:8730: // sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK070(thu)001:8732: gangs chen po'i mtsho lnga ste mya ngan las 'das
NK070(thu)001:8733: pa'i ye shes lnga'am yang na dus bzhi dang 'dus
NK070(thu)001:8734: ma byas pa'am brjod du med pa'i dus dang lngas
NK070(thu)001:8735: bsdus pa yang de dag sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK070(thu)001:8736: phrin las lnga'i ngo bo kho na'i bdag nyid yin
NK070(thu)001:8737: pa'i phyir ro // sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK070(thu)001:8739: gangs chen po'i mtsho lnga ste 'khor ba dug lnga'am
NK070(thu)001:8740: yang na gong ltar du lngas bsdus pa yang 'bras
NK070(thu)001:8741: bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po
NK070(thu)001:8742: de dag gis ngo bo nyid kun tu khyab pa
NK070(thu)001:8743: kho na'o // yin pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:8744: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho //
NK070(thu)001:8746: chos can 'khor ba dang chos nyid sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:8747: yon tan kyi 'bras bu lnga po de dag nyid
NK070(thu)001:8748: kyang phan tshun tha mi dad pa thig le chen
NK070(thu)001:8750: mnyes pa zhes bya ba ni gong du 1bshad zin 00to //
NK070(thu)001:8751: le'u bcu bzhi pa khong khrol du bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8753: // de nas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor 'khor rdzogs nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8754: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8755: spyir rgyud 'di la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:8762: dkyil 'khor rnam pa bdun las 'dir lhag pa'i ting
NK070(thu)001:8763: nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rnam pa
NK070(thu)001:8764: gnyis dang / tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:8765: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang bzhi
NK070(thu)001:8766: po rnams la zhi khro gnyis su bstan pa la
NK070(thu)001:8767: / de yan chad du zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi po rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:8768: bcu gcig par khro bo khro mo zhes pa khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:8769: dgu par khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te zhes
NK070(thu)001:8770: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyis dkyil 'khor zur tsam bstan
NK070(thu)001:8771: nas / 'di nas mar khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du bstan pa las /
NK070(thu)001:8772: le'u bco lnga pa 'dis khro bo rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK070(thu)001:8773: de pa thams cad kyis dkyil 'khor gyis bdag po /
NK070(thu)001:8775: de pa thams cad ni mdor rigs lngar 'dus la /
NK070(thu)001:8776: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyi bdag po ni rgyal ba drug pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8777: kun tu bzang mo sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyi /
NK070(thu)001:8778: zhes bya ba ni rgyal ba drug pa nyid zhi
NK070(thu)001:8779: khro'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor brgyad po thams cad
NK070(thu)001:8781: drug pa las ma g.yos pas /
NK070(thu)001:8782: du mar bral ba'i tshul gyi dgongs pa lhun gyis grub pas na drug pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8783: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:8784: che ba mtshan du brtags pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8785: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8786: de bas na khro bor ni sku snang ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:8787: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du snang nas mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK070(thu)001:8789: khro bo la rnam pa gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:8790: de la ngo bo nyid kyi shes rab chos nyid spros bral chen po'i khro bo ni /
NK070(thu)001:8792: yang dag pa'i chos nyid phyin ci ma log par shes rab chen po ni lta ba rtogs nas /
NK070(thu)001:8793: gzung 'dzin gyi dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa 'joms pa'i phyir na khro bo'i mchog ste zhe'o //
NK070(thu)001:8794: bya de rtogs pa'i rig pa'i ye shes chen po'i khro bo ni /
NK070(thu)001:8796: rnal 'byor pa gang gi rang rig pa'i ye shes
