NK070(thu)001:8797: chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i rgyal po 1yis
NK070(thu)001:8798: // gang bsdus na phyogs 2bcu 'jig rten gyi khams rnams sems su dbang 1du bsdus nas //
NK070(thu)001:8799: chos kun 2 kyang yul yul can du mi dmigs
NK070(thu)001:8800: pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su thim
NK070(thu)001:8801: // ste 'gyur pa de'i rang rtsal du thams cad kyang khro bo'i tshogs su gsal bar 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:8803: zhe'o sa bya dpa' chen rngam brjid phyag rgya chen
NK070(thu)001:8804: po'i khro bo nyid kyi 'khor ni don dbyings ye
NK070(thu)001:8805: shes gnyis med kyi rtags sku gsung thugs zhal phyag
NK070(thu)001:8806: tu snang ba 'og nas 'chad pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8807: gar dgu dang ldan pa'i khro bo 'di dag gdul
NK070(thu)001:8808: bya'i ru dra ngo bo la snang yang sangs rgyas
NK070(thu)001:8809: la lhun gru ba rtsol bar thal ba med do
NK070(thu)001:8812: khro bor snang ba de gtan tshigs ci'i phyir kyi
NK070(thu)001:8813: dri bas khro bor snang ba de'i dgos pa 'tshal
NK070(thu)001:8814: 00ba ni ru tra 'dul ba'i phyir du ste /
NK070(thu)001:8815: gang yin zhe na snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:8816: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:8817: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:8818: rgyu bdag tu 'dzin pa las las rgyu 'bras la
NK070(thu)001:8819: rmongs pa'i kun tu brtags pa las byung ba'i ma
NK070(thu)001:8820: rig pa las rtog pa sna tshogs su snang ba
NK070(thu)001:8821: kho na'o // brtag pa la mngon par zhen pa /
NK070(thu)001:8823: kun brtags pa'i gzung 'dzin gnyis la mngon par zhen pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8824: spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med la sgros btags
NK070(thu)001:8825: nas 'khrul pa rang gi mtshan nyid dngos po tha
NK070(thu)001:8826: dad dam yang dag tu rngos zhing du mthong ba'o
NK070(thu)001:8827: // yang dag pa'i lam dang bral ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8828: rgyal ba'i bka' lung las bla ma'i man ngag gis
NK070(thu)001:8829: zin pa'i yang dag pa'i don bskyed rdzogs gnyis kho
NK070(thu)001:8830: na ste / ru tra gang la lam de dag dang bral bas med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8832: bdud rang gi ngo ti ston pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8833: sngon gyi bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su mi
NK070(thu)001:8834: bskyod pa'am mngon byung rgyal pa'i bstan pa snga ma
NK070(thu)001:8835: las 'byung ba'i dge slong thar pa nag po'o //
NK070(thu)001:8836: de 'i rgyu ci zhig snyam pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8837: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8838: gzhi gnas lugs rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'o //
NK070(thu)001:8839: sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8840: lam rkyen gyi yi ge rgyud las byung ba'i sbas
NK070(thu)001:8841: pa'i gsang ba ta na sgrol ba g+ha na sbyor
NK070(thu)001:8842: ba la sogs pa dug lnga ma spang bdud rtsi
NK070(thu)001:8844: 'dod yon lnga spyad par gsungs pa rnams la mngon
NK070(thu)001:8845: par 'chil sgra ci bzhin par bzung nas don ma
NK070(thu)001:8846: rtogs par rang dgar dus rgyun du spyad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8847: rgyu dang 'bras bu la rmongs pas /
NK070(thu)001:8849: rgyu mi dge ba'i spyod pa 'bras bu rnam par smin pa la sdug bsngal 'byung bar ngo //
NK070(thu)001:8851: srid pa'i sa bon tsub mos zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8852: srid pa ngan song du skye ba'i sa bon ni
NK070(thu)001:8853: 'bras bu bskyed pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa'i las
NK070(thu)001:8854: ngan pa dang / nyon mongs par rang kha ma rnams kyi bag chags rtsub mos 'phang nas so //
NK070(thu)001:8855: 'tshams med pa'i zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8856: sdug bsngal lam bde ba'i skabs med pas bar mi chad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8857: rab tu tsha ba sogs tsha ba'i dmyal bar skyes so //
NK070(thu)001:8858: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:8860: shi yang bsil byed kyi rlung 'jam pos yang sos pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8861: thig nag po btab nas bshags pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8862: ra lug gi gdong pa 'dra ba gnyis kyi bar du bsdus te 'joms pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8863: lcags kyi khang pa rkyang ba rim gyi ngu 'bod dang /
NK070(thu)001:8864: lcags kyi khang pa gnyis rim gyi ngu 'bod chen po dang /
NK070(thu)001:8865: mdung rtse gcig pas tsha ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:8866: rtse gsum pas rab tu tsha ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:8867: thabs de la mnar du med pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8868: shin tu grang ba brgyad ces bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8869: lus 'gyur ba lnga chu bur can dang /
NK070(thu)001:8870: chu bur rdol pa can dang /
NK070(thu)001:8871: ngag 'gyur gsum so tham tham pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8874: ud pal ltar bzhir gas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8875: pad+ma ltar brgyad du gas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8876: pad+ma chen po ltar bcu drug tu gas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8877: de dag tu skye zhing 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing /
NK070(thu)001:8880: rten gyi khams gzhan na skad cig mas brgyud cing
NK070(thu)001:8881: 'pho ste de'ang skal pa chen po stong phrag bcu
NK070(thu)001:8882: gnyis su tsha grang gi sdug bsngal myong ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:8885: se gol gcig gis phyin par byed /
NK070(thu)001:8887: de nas rnam par smin pa de zad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8889: dmyal ba'i gnas su skyes pa de nas sems can gsad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8891: lta sgom gyi gdeng med pa'i rang kha'i phrin las dang /
NK070(thu)001:8893: gzhan dam tshig can la ngan du sems pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8894: rang nga rgyal che bas dregs pa la sogs pa'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK070(thu)001:8896: zhes pa yi dwags kyi gnas su skyes nas ldog
NK070(thu)001:8897: pa dang skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu gdung
NK070(thu)001:8899: zhes pa la sogs pa go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:8900: sdug bsngal myong bas rgyu las kyi sgrib pa'i nus pa zad pas mtshams sbyor /
NK070(thu)001:8901: 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams yid du mi 'ong ba /
NK070(thu)001:8903: phyi'i 'dod pa'i dngos po bza' btung rnams ci yang ngan skyugs su mthong ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:8904: yid du mi 'ong bas dngos po gzhan du 'gyur ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8907: gdug cing rtsub pa'i dngos po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8908: zas ci zos pa 'thung ba khro chu dang lcags tshan du 'gyur ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:8909: me lce'i 'khor lo can zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8910: yongs med par yang 'gyur zhes bya ba gnod pa
NK070(thu)001:8911: phyi yi yul la yang yod pas yang dngos po
NK070(thu)001:8912: mi snang bar 'gyur bas na phyi'i sgrib pa can
NK070(thu)001:8913: te / bza' baca'i dngos po mthong nas der bgrod
NK070(thu)001:8914: nas phyin pas yongs med yang 'gyur zhing lus shin
NK070(thu)001:8915: tu rid cing snyom pa zhes pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8916: lus dang yan lag dbang po mi 'tshams pa //
NK070(thu)001:8918: mgo lus ri bo che tsam la dang yan lag
NK070(thu)001:8919: phyir thur tsam dang zhes pa dbang po mi 'tshams
NK070(thu)001:8920: pa ste kha phra ba khab mig tsam la sogs
NK070(thu)001:8921: par gyur ba ste gnod pa nang lus la yod
NK070(thu)001:8922: pas nang gi sgrib pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:8923: gnas der skal pa chen po stong phrag drug tu skyes so //
NK070(thu)001:8924: de nas las kyi sgrib pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:8926: yi dwags su skyes pa de nas las kyi sgrib
NK070(thu)001:8927: pa rtsub mo ni nor dang zas la skam pa
NK070(thu)001:8928: dang / rang gi gtong mi phod pas 'jugs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8929: gzhan gyi zas nor la brnab sems dang /
NK070(thu)001:8930: dkon mchog mchod pa'i longs spyod la rngam pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:8931: rang gis bsog 'jog byas pa la sogs pa'i 'bras bu /
NK070(thu)001:8933: las byung ba'i las de khad kyis bsrab dang rjes /
NK070(thu)001:8934: sngon gyi srid pas mtshams sbyor nas //
NK070(thu)001:8936: sngon gyi dge slong thar pa nag po'i dus su khro bo dbu dang phyag mang po dang /
NK070(thu)001:8937: phra men ma stag dang seng ge'i zhal las la
NK070(thu)001:8938: sogs par lha rang rgyud du yid la byas nas
NK070(thu)001:8939: las spyod pa barlanga por byas pa'i srid pa'i mtshams
NK070(thu)001:8940: sbyor nas rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK070(thu)001:8941: yi dwags kyi srin por skyes pa yi dwags srin
NK070(thu)001:8942: po chen po rab tu gdug pa zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:8943: la sogs pa nas gzugs dang zhes pa'i bar ni
NK070(thu)001:8944: bdud rang gi ngo bo ste go sla ste /
NK070(thu)001:8946: lus kyi dri dang kha rlang gi zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:8947: la sogs pa 'bras bu che'i lha man chad dbang
NK070(thu)001:8948: du bsdus so zhes pa'i bar ni /
NK070(thu)001:8949: de'i las kyi sbyor bas thams cad la gnod pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8950: sngon gyi brten pa'i stobs zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8951: sngon gyi dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu bsten pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8952: stobs kyis sngags kyis theg pa chen por sems bskyed
NK070(thu)001:8954: 'i stobs kyis thub dka' dang dad 'phags gnyis dpal
NK070(thu)001:8955: chen gsang bdag tu gyur pa'i thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK070(thu)001:8956: ye shes kyis gzigs nas zhes pa thugs rjes 'dul
NK070(thu)001:8957: bar gyur te / zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8958: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las kyi dus la bab pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:8959: ra mkhyen pa zhes pa ste lhag ma can te 'og nas 'dul bar byed pa dngos dang sbrel /
NK070(thu)001:8960: 'di nas mar 'dul byed ye shes kyi khro bo
NK070(thu)001:8961: bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i
NK070(thu)001:8962: rdo rje bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul dra ba zhes bya
NK070(thu)001:8963: ba la sogs pa bdud btul ba'i gleng gzhi rang
NK070(thu)001:8964: gi ngo bo la don gsum ste /
NK070(thu)001:8965: cho 'phrul rmad du byung ba drug dang /
NK070(thu)001:8968: phrin las rmad du byung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:8969: gnyis de la gsum gyi dang po cho 'phrul rmad
NK070(thu)001:8970: du byung ba la don rnam pa drug las 'di
NK070(thu)001:8971: ni / dang po de pa kun tu bzang po
NK070(thu)001:8972: nyid che mchog tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK070(thu)001:8973: ni / cho 'phrul te / rdo rje bkod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:8974: zhi ba'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes sogs dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8975: rnams kyi nas gzi brjid bstan pa'i phyir gyi bar
NK070(thu)001:8976: zhes bya'o // de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK070(thu)001:8977: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:8978: zhes bya'o // ni / rigs kyi bdag po ste /
NK070(thu)001:8979: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po kun tu bzang po'o //
NK070(thu)001:8981: khro bo'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po //
NK070(thu)001:8983: khro bo'i rgyal ba dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rtsa
NK070(thu)001:8984: ba rigs lnga'i he ru ka'i rgyal po che mchog
NK070(thu)001:8985: gi skur snang bar byed pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:8986: gyi sprin chen po rnam par 'phro ba'i sgyu 'phrul
NK070(thu)001:8987: d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i ting nge 'dzin la de snyoms
NK070(thu)001:8988: par zhugs te zhes pa'i don la tshig skad ces
NK070(thu)001:8989: bya'o // de nas de bzhin nyid kyis dbyings nas
NK070(thu)001:8990: khro mo dbang phyug chen mo'i sku mngon du phyung
NK070(thu)001:8991: bya'o // ba ste / zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:8992: 'di nas mar dkyil 'khor rmad du byung ba la
NK070(thu)001:8993: bzhi las dang po che mchog 'di gsang ba'i longs
NK070(thu)001:8994: spyod chen po'i yum phyungs te sbyor ba mdzad pa
NK070(thu)001:8996: le'u bzhi par a ni skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK070(thu)001:8998: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings na kun mo kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:8999: de nyid las khro mor dbang phyug chen mo'i /
NK070(thu)001:9000: mngon du phyung ste rang snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9001: gzhan hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis rin chen dgyes par mdzad nas zhes pa ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:9002: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas thim nas /
NK070(thu)001:9004: slob dpon la la'i gzhung gis yab yum sku nyid
NK070(thu)001:9005: 'od du zhu zhing yongs su gyur pa'i byang chub
NK070(thu)001:9006: kyi sems kyis 'od dpung las khro bo 'chol ba
NK070(thu)001:9007: spros nas / phyis slar yang rigs bzhi khrag 'thung 'khor du snang ba yang 'chad do //
NK070(thu)001:9008: zhes pa ni gzhan dang dgongs pa bstun pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9009: 'dir ni nyi zla byang chub kyi sems gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:9010: med par 'khril pa'i dgyes pa ni thim pa zhes
NK070(thu)001:9011: bya'o // de nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi du 'char byed rgyu yin pa'i phyir na /
NK070(thu)001:9012: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi ye shes lnga sprin las char byung ba ltar ro //
NK070(thu)001:9014: h'u h'u h'u b+hi shwa badz+ra zhes sogs zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9015: khro bo 'byung ba'i bskyed sngags kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK070(thu)001:9016: zhes pa'i sngags brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK070(thu)001:9017: mtha' yas par zhes bya ba la sogs pa nas
NK070(thu)001:9018: 'thor bar gyur ces pa'i bar ni sprul pa rdzu
NK070(thu)001:9020: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad g.yos zhes
NK070(thu)001:9021: bya ba la sogs pa nas gtor ro zhes pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9022: bar ni byin gyis rlabs kyi cho 'phrul lo //
NK070(thu)001:9023: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu stong khams thams cad
NK070(thu)001:9024: na gnas pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni
NK070(thu)001:9025: sa g.yo pas chos nyid sgyu ma lta bu'i don
NK070(thu)001:9027: dbang chen zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9029: lha chen po gzi brjid che ba ni tshangs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9030: mthu che ba'i lha khyab 'jug go //
NK070(thu)001:9031: ra hu la dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa 2thams cad brgyal rab tu brgyal /
NK070(thu)001:9032: kun tu brgyal zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9033: khams 'khrugs te dran pa nyams shing brgyal /
NK070(thu)001:9034: nas lus sa la 'gyel te rab tu brgyal sems
NK070(thu)001:9035: dran pa myos shing kun tu brgyal par gyur te
NK070(thu)001:9036: zhes pa'o // la la'i ste sgyu 'phrul bla ma
NK070(thu)001:9037: gzhung gis skabs 'dir khams gsum dur khrod kyi gzhal
NK070(thu)001:9038: yas su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK070(thu)001:9039: gnas der dregs pa can thams cad gdan du mdzad par bskyed rim gyi skabs su ston to //
NK070(thu)001:9040: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po nyid
NK070(thu)001:9041: 'jigs byed chen po zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:9042: nas klong gi dkyil 'khor zhes pa'i bar ni che
NK070(thu)001:9043: mchog gi sprul pa rigs lnga'i khro bo 'chol pa
NK070(thu)001:9044: bas lhag pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK070(thu)001:9045: dbang phyug chen po dang dur khrod kyi bdag po
NK070(thu)001:9046: dregs pa khyo shugs zhes bya ba ni ru tra
NK070(thu)001:9047: pho mo'o // byi ching gi gdan la zhabs brkyang bskum du bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:9048: zhes pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin phung zhes
NK070(thu)001:9049: bya ba 'phro ba na dang po byang chub sems
NK070(thu)001:9050: ye shes lnga'i khyab pa las sprul pa 'phros pa
NK070(thu)001:9051: ste / des gdul bya dug lnga dang de las
NK070(thu)001:9052: gyur pa 'gro lnga brtul nas de dag kyang slar
NK070(thu)001:9053: yang rigs bzhin du bsdus pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9054: ste phyogs bzhir 'khod de'ang la la ni dpal khrag
NK070(thu)001:9055: 'thung chen po zhes pa nas 'khril ba'i tshul gyis
NK070(thu)001:9056: bzhugs so dang ngo mtshar bstan te zhes pa'i bar
NK070(thu)001:9057: bstan pa de nas dregs pa chen po la sogs
NK070(thu)001:9058: pa gtum pa'i sems kyis gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul bstan
NK070(thu)001:9059: nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa nas tshur rngam
NK070(thu)001:9060: zhes pa'i bar ni phrin las rmad du byung ba
NK070(thu)001:9061: gnyis las / phrin las kyi ngo bo ston te /
NK070(thu)001:9063: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dbu dgu brgya phyag bco brgyad ces bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9064: rnam shes dgu ye shes dgu'i rtags su khrag 'thung he ru ka lnga rak+sha /
NK070(thu)001:9066: yak+sha he ru ka dang dgu klong rngam pa'i zhal du gdug pa can gsol ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9067: sgrol byed kyi ging bco brgyad kyi phyag gis sgrol
NK070(thu)001:9068: ba'i ste zhabs brgyad ces pa nas khros nas zhes
NK070(thu)001:9070: h'u h'u h'u ni gdul bya dang sbyar na drag
NK070(thu)001:9071: po'i sgo gsum dbang du gnyen po dang sbyar na
NK070(thu)001:9072: sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las kyis sdud pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9073: ha ha ha ni dgyes pa'i gad mos srog dbugs dug gsum la rngam pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9074: kha kha kha hi ni sha khrag rus gsum lhag
NK070(thu)001:9075: ma ma lus par zhal du gsol ba'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:9076: // zhes brjod pas dbang phyug chen po la sogs
NK070(thu)001:9077: pa gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag gi snying
NK070(thu)001:9078: phyung ba ni sems kyi bdag 'dzin nyon yid rtsad
NK070(thu)001:9080: dbang po kun phyung ba ni dbang po skye mched kyi sgo dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9081: nang khrol drang ba ni gzugs la sogs pa'i yul
NK070(thu)001:9082: la mngon par zhen pa dag par bya ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9083: ro // yan lag kun bcad pa btub nas zhes
NK070(thu)001:9084: pa ni las ngan gyi rgyun rtsad nas bcad pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9085: ro // phyir ro // khrag kun 'thung ba ni 'dod chags zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9086: sha kun zos pa ni gti mug dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9087: rus pa kun 'chos pa ni zhe sdang dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9088: de nas h'u h'u h'u ni mo rnams kyis lus ngag yid gsum dbang du sdud pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9089: de'i sngags ni b+h+yo e a ra li dza dza /
NK070(thu)001:9090: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9091: 'khor sdud pa'i cho 'phrul la gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:9092: dang po 'khor sdud pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK070(thu)001:9093: zhes brjod pas phyogs bcu 'jig rten gyi khams nam
NK070(thu)001:9094: mkha' dang bcas pa yungs 'bru gcig tsam du chud
NK070(thu)001:9095: par bsdus so // zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9096: dregs pa rnams kyi rnam par shes pa h'u gsum du bsdus pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9097: rgyu des dregs pa'i chos thams cad sems su gcig par mthong ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9098: sa sems gnas spar ba gzhan ni bsdus pa de
NK070(thu)001:9099: nas 'byung po ma lus pa'i rgyal mo zhes pa
NK070(thu)001:9100: nas dbang du bsdus so zhes pa'i bar go sla'o
NK070(thu)001:9101: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chon po zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9102: dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga char yongs su
NK070(thu)001:9103: rdzogs pa'i ra snang ba dkyil 'khor ston te ma
NK070(thu)001:9104: mo rnams 'dul ba'i thabs kyi yang 1rigs lnga'i 'jigs
NK070(thu)001:9105: byed chen por snang bar byas nas zhes bya ba
NK070(thu)001:9106: ni / che mchog gi sku nyid ma mo dbang
NK070(thu)001:9107: mo rnams kyi ngo la rigs lngar snang ba ste
NK070(thu)001:9108: ni / / khyo dang chung ma gnyis sam yang
NK070(thu)001:9109: na gong du rigs lngar snang ba dang 'dir yang
NK070(thu)001:9110: rigs lngar snang ba gnyis kyi phyir 1yang zhes bya'o
NK070(thu)001:9111: ni / / // yang na dbu dgu pa dang rigs lnga gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:9112: de dag kun kyang dgyes par rol pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:9113: gyi sprin 'byung ba zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:9114: nas shin tu bcum par gyur te zhes pa'i bar
NK070(thu)001:9115: ni 'khor sdud pa'i cho 'phrul gyi bya ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9117: de nas dgyes te ha ha zhes brjod pas zhes
NK070(thu)001:9118: bya ba la sogs pa rigs lnga dang dbang phyug
NK070(thu)001:9119: ma'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi sprin las
NK070(thu)001:9120: ha'i tshogs spros pa ni ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:9121: 'khor ma phra nyi shu dang chas te re re'i
NK070(thu)001:9122: nyer brgyad nyer brgyad ston te /
NK070(thu)001:9123: de yang dkar mo'i tshogs dang zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9124: ke'u ri ma ni thugs rnam par dag pas zhi
NK070(thu)001:9125: ba'i 'phrin las kyis gdul bya'i don mdzad pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9126: ro // sku mdog dkar mo 'dres pa rkun mo'i
NK070(thu)001:9127: tshogs tsoo'u ri ma ni che ba'i yon tan gyis
NK070(thu)001:9128: mthus sku bas dbang gi phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9129: rmongs mo'i tshogs pra mo ha ni zhi ba'i las kyi phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9130: dgra bgegs thal bar brlag par byed pa mo'i tshogs
NK070(thu)001:9131: be ta li ni drag po'i las kyi phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:9132: // sbos mo'i tshogs puk+ka s+ai ni che ba'i yon tan gyis kang ka rgyas pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9133: gtum mo'i tshogs kasma ri drag po'i las byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9134: sme sha can gyi tshogs sme sha can ni las bzhi po gang yang 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9135: sku mdog ljang gu ma tshogs ma'i tshogs tsan+d+ha li
NK070(thu)001:9136: ni tshe dang brgyud 'phel bar byed pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:9137: // de rnams re re yang tshogs zhes pa'i sgras
NK070(thu)001:9138: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rang rang ga lag cha dang
NK070(thu)001:9139: bcas pa ni ke'u ri ban dmar byi dbyug sngo
NK070(thu)001:9140: la sogs pa ngo mtshar ba'i tshul du ma dang
NK070(thu)001:9142: gdug pa can la rngam zhing de'i 'khor la ngam pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9143: 'di dag ni dpal chen po'i yon tan gyi snang
NK070(thu)001:9144: tshul la sbyar te seng gdong ma chen mo'i tshogs
NK070(thu)001:9145: ni gdug pa can thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9146: phyir ro // stag gdong ma chen mo'i tshogs ni dpa' brtul gyi las drag po'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9147: wa gdong chen mo'i tshogs ni thabs mkhas pas phung po'i bdud dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9148: ne'u tshe che ba khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs ni
NK070(thu)001:9149: khyi rgod spyang ku ste rnam par g.yeng byed kyi
NK070(thu)001:9150: lha'i bu'i bdud 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9151: bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs ni mtsho'i nang gi spu
NK070(thu)001:9152: 'gul ba tshor bas shes bya thams cad la thogs
NK070(thu)001:9154: dur bya 'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs ni 'khor ba'i ro dang du len pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9155: kam dang kha kha'i ra ka'i 'grel pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9156: 'ug gdong chen mo'i tshogs ni mtshan mo chu nang
NK070(thu)001:9157: du skra nyag ma tshun chad mthong ba gdul bya
NK070(thu)001:9158: phra ba yang mi 'dor ba'i ra byed pa phyir
NK070(thu)001:9159: ro // dbang rtags su rdo rje rtse lnga pas
NK070(thu)001:9160: dbu brgyan cing sring 'gro ma ni rta'i gdong pa
NK070(thu)001:9161: ro // ste / lcags kyu bsnams nas 'khor ba mi gtong ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9162: rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs ni phag gi gdong pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9163: phrin las gdong tshugs su byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9164: rdo rje 'jig rten ma'i tshogs ni dred gdong ma ste /
NK070(thu)001:9165: thams cad mes bsreg par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9166: rdo rje ro langs ma'i tshogs ni spyang gdong ma ste /
NK070(thu)001:9167: khams gsum rnam par rtog pa klong du shi ba
NK070(thu)001:9168: slar 'tsho bar byed pas ro langs ma zhes bya'o
NK070(thu)001:9169: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po /
NK070(thu)001:9170: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9171: phrin las kyi 'bras bu la gnas spar ba dang dam la brtag pa gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:9172: dang po dregs pa rnams gnas stob pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9173: thugs rje chen po bdud rtsi 'byung ba ni dri chen ste /
NK070(thu)001:9174: sku gsung thugs rdo rje las byung ba ni ye
NK070(thu)001:9175: shes lnga badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa a mri ta
NK070(thu)001:9177: badz+ra rdo rje bdud rtsi a mri ta chen po ma h+aa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9178: gang ltar na bdud rtsi gcig kyang dam rdzas lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9179: ma h+aa kro ta zhes bya ba ni khro bo chen po ste /
NK070(thu)001:9180: 'og nas 'byung ba'i snoms nas phyung ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9181: mi gtsang ba zhal du gsol bas khro bo sme ba mi gtsang ba len gnyis brtsegs so //
NK070(thu)001:9182: am am am zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9183: bdud rtsi len gsum byin pas rin chen gyis dbang bskur ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9184: sku 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na /
NK070(thu)001:9187: dbu phyag mang po bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin ltar gdul byas /
NK070(thu)001:9188: mthong gi bdag nyid du ma gyur ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9189: so sor snang ba dus gcig tu btul lo zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9190: bcu bzhi pa las sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis /
NK070(thu)001:9191: dus skad cig yud la tsam lhun gyis grub ho //
NK070(thu)001:9193: gdul bya tha dad par 'i snang ngo sku tha
NK070(thu)001:9194: dad par snang bas gdul bya kun dus gcig tu
NK070(thu)001:9196: de nas de dag shin tu zhes pa nas rul bar 'chi zhes pa'i bar ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:9197: de nas de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:9198: zhes bya ba la sogs pa nas phyi rim nas
NK070(thu)001:9199: bkod do zhes pa'i bar ni phrin las rmad du
NK070(thu)001:9200: byung ba'i 'bras bu la gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:9201: 'khor dam la btags te bka'i srung ma byed pas bstan pa yun ring du gnas par byas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9202: le'u bco lnga pa'i dka' ba bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9204: // khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gi lhag pa'i ting
NK070(thu)001:9205: nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor sngags rang bstan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9206: phyir / de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9207: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po khro bo'i dkyil
NK070(thu)001:9208: 'khor gyi tshogs chen po de dag sngags kyi dam
NK070(thu)001:9209: tshig gi skur bsgrub par bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9210: gsung gi dam tshig ni sngags gsum po rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:9211: de bzhin gshegs pa'i khro bo ye shes rngam pa
NK070(thu)001:9212: zhes bya ba ni shin tu rngam pa'i nga ro
NK070(thu)001:9214: ye shes lnga ldan rtsa sngags sam 'go 'dren no //
NK070(thu)001:9215: sarba thams cad ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs
NK070(thu)001:9216: pa ma h+aa chen po sh+r+ai dpal he ru ka
NK070(thu)001:9217: khrag 'thung zhes bya ba ni nyid kyi snying po'o
NK070(thu)001:9218: // ste bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags las sngags 00ma h+aam tsan+d+ha ni gtum po chen po'o //
NK070(thu)001:9219: sarba dush+tana ni sdang ba thams cad do //
NK070(thu)001:9220: ta ka ha na ni togs shig rgyobs shig pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9221: da ha pa tsa ni choms shig /
NK070(thu)001:9223: h'u h'u h'u phata ces bya ba gdug pa can
NK070(thu)001:9224: gyi lus ngag yid gsum dbang du bsdus la sod
NK070(thu)001:9225: cig pa'o // de dag gi phyir rtsa 00ba las 00dang bcas pa'i sngags kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9226: gzhan badz+ra nas sa ma y+aa ba ti ho'i bar ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:9227: b+h+yohrnamasa ni ma mo rnams kyi rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i snying po ste /
NK070(thu)001:9228: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang bzlas pa las kyis
NK070(thu)001:9229: sngags gnyis ni rang gi ming nyid kyis ma nu
NK070(thu)001:9230: rak+sha si la sogs pa grub pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9231: le'u bco lnga par bshad pa bzhin yin la de
NK070(thu)001:9232: yang ma nu rak+sha ni srin mo chen mo mi
NK070(thu)001:9233: srin mo la sogs pa 'phral skad du gsal ba'o
NK070(thu)001:9234: // ste bskyed pa dang spyan drang ba ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9236: snyan gsan gsol ba'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:9237: e ha hi a na ya zhes bya ba ni bskul ba'i sngags so //
NK070(thu)001:9238: dzahmh'u bam hohzhesa bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9240: rim par spyan drangs nas mdun gyi nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9241: ram zhes bya ba ni dngos su ye shes dam
NK070(thu)001:9242: tshig gi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi me dpung gnyis 'dres
NK070(thu)001:9243: pa ste / shes rab kyis gnyis med du sbyor ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9244: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK070(thu)001:9245: zhes bya ba ni rig pa'i me tog dor ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:9246: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis med pa gcig par gsal ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9247: +amo ni ye shes lnga ldan dregs pa kho bo'i
NK070(thu)001:9248: gdul bya la thugs rjes khros pa'i tshul bstan pas
NK070(thu)001:9249: dregs pa can gyi gdul bya zhi bar mdzad pa
NK070(thu)001:9250: / ni thugs rje chen po gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK070(thu)001:9251: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9252: bskul ba ste bskul ba'i sa la bzhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9253: slar yang bskul ba'i sngags ni badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK070(thu)001:9254: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya hoh badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata /
NK070(thu)001:9256: dam tshig bskul bas dgyes nas /
NK070(thu)001:9257: ye shes pa'i sku gsung thugs gsum nas drag po'i
NK070(thu)001:9258: yig 'bru la phata nag po grangs mang pos spros
NK070(thu)001:9259: pa bdag dam tshig pa'i snod dag par mdzad pa'o
NK070(thu)001:9260: // de nas phyi'i mchod pa 'bul ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9261: a li u li ta la ta pa ti //
NK070(thu)001:9266: ta pa si bca' ba sna tshogs spros la 'bul ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9267: de dag gang la phul snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:9268: dam kha tah zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9269: sgra bsgyur na mche ba can te /
NK070(thu)001:9270: don rigs lnga he ru ka yab yum rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:9271: ga n+aa roo t+r+ai zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9273: khro mo gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu'o //
NK070(thu)001:9277: ma mo dbang mo nyer brgyad rnams so //
NK070(thu)001:9278: kh+aa hi zhes bya ba ni gsol gcig par bstan pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9279: de nas mnyes pa'i phyir hehzhesa bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9281: ha sa ma mo hes phra man phatahkyi sgo ma zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9282: dam tshig dkyil 'khor la ye shes pa gtso 'khor gnas gdan drang rim par thim pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9283: zhes brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad tshig rab tu tshig kun tu tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:9285: bzlas pa las kyi sngags rnams kyi mthu brten pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9286: sa rtog pa thams cad tshig ces pa la sogs pa 'bar rab tu 'bar /
NK070(thu)001:9287: kun tu 'bar zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9288: bskyed pa'i rkyen gyi sngags kyis mthu byin brlabs kyis
NK070(thu)001:9289: rtog tshogs thams cad kyang lhar gyur pas 'bar zhes
NK070(thu)001:9290: pa la sogs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9291: thams cad du 'bar ba'i ye shes pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyis gang rab tu gang /
NK070(thu)001:9292: kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:9294: spyan drangs zhing bstim pa'i sngags rnams kyis ye shes
NK070(thu)001:9295: kyi dkyil 'khor dang dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK070(thu)001:9296: su med pa'i yon tan gyis kun tu rgyas /
NK070(thu)001:9297: te gang ba la sogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9298: le'u bcu drug pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9300: // de nas lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sku dang /
NK070(thu)001:9301: thugs phyag mtshan kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9302: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs /
NK070(thu)001:9304: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9306: 'di yang ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa le'u lnga
NK070(thu)001:9307: pa dang rjes su mthun par de ting kun ting
NK070(thu)001:9308: gnyis sbyar ro // de nas rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:9309: h'u las dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang la thog
NK070(thu)001:9310: mar gdan ni chos 'byung gru gsum rlung rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:9311: gnyis sbyar ro // rgya gram ro // rak+ta'i rgya
NK070(thu)001:9312: mtsho keng rus kyi ri rab bskal pa'i me ri
NK070(thu)001:9313: gnyis sbyar ro // rgya gram ro // dang / 'byung ba lnga bskyed nas /
NK070(thu)001:9314: de'i steng du b+h+aum smug nag la dur khrod kyi
NK070(thu)001:9315: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang dbyibs 'og gi 'di ltar
NK070(thu)001:9316: dag lhar bskyed pa 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la sogs
NK070(thu)001:9317: ste go sla'o // 'bar ba'i bar 'khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK070(thu)001:9319: bshad pa'i bla ma rgyud kyi spor ma'i sa dgos so zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:9320: 'dir nang phra men ma'i gser khyams dang phyir dbang
NK070(thu)001:9321: phyug ma'i khrag mtsho'i khyams gnyis su 'gal ba med
NK070(thu)001:9322: do // dur khrod kyi rgyan khathod sprul sna tshogs kanyi mas gabrjid //
NK070(thu)001:9324: thod pa skom rlon sna tshogs kyi rtsigs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9325: de dag nyid phal kar ti las /
NK070(thu)001:9326: sprul chen gyi d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi zhags pas mgul du drangs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9327: de dag gi bar na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od zer /
NK070(thu)001:9329: 'gyed pa thams cad du snang bar byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9331: bdag po'i rkyen gyis 'bar ba'i 'phro ba mang pos 'khrugs /
NK070(thu)001:9333: gzhal yas khang gi phyi nang kun las rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK070(thu)001:9334: rnam pa me dpung 'bar ba las /
NK070(thu)001:9335: me'i khro bo mang po bsnol mar 'phro ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9337: gzhal yas khang de dag gi nang du gdan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9338: khyu mchog ni stod glang la smad seng ge zer glang gi gtso bo /
NK070(thu)001:9341: gtum po dom gyi spar kabas ni //
NK070(thu)001:9343: gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su khyu mchog 1dang /
NK070(thu)001:9347: khong 1khro dom de rnams 11111gnas su dag pa khongs
NK070(thu)001:9348: su chud nas de dag gi sgo nas phrin las
NK070(thu)001:9349: mdzad pa'i phyir / 'di rnams kyi spar bas ni 'og gi 'di dag gnon pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9350: dbang phyug lha chen ru tra pho mo la 1sogs gzung /
NK070(thu)001:9353: bco lngar dri za gshin rje srin po gnod sbyin rnams bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:9354: dregs pa rnams la phrin las nan tur du bstan
NK070(thu)001:9355: pa'i phyir kaspar bas pho'i sog phrag dang mo'i nu
NK070(thu)001:9357: bud+d+ha he ru ka smug nag badz+ra he ru ka sngo nag rat+na he ru ka ser nag dang /
NK070(thu)001:9358: pad+ma he ru ka dmar nag karma he ru ka ljang nag thams cad shin tu 'jig pa'i sku /
NK070(thu)001:9359: zhes bya ba ni sku mdog rnams bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9360: las bzhi po thams cad kyis gzhi ma drag po
NK070(thu)001:9361: kho nas 'i sgo na phrin las mdzad pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9362: / rtsa ba nag por smos pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9363: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir brkyang bskum du bsgrad //
NK070(thu)001:9365: stong pa nyid mtshan ma med pa /
NK070(thu)001:9366: smon pa med pa'i rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dgu gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:9368: ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug dang rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK070(thu)001:9369: rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su zhabs bzhi
NK070(thu)001:9370: gyad kyi dor thabs su bgrad pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9371: kharko rlon gos ni sna tshogs go gani //
NK070(thu)001:9373: thabs mkhas phrin las kyi gos dang /
NK070(thu)001:9374: khakhyab pa thugs rje'i gos dang /
NK070(thu)001:9375: phyi ga nang gsang bar sdud pa'i gos kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:9376: zhing ka gi g.yang gzhi'i sked ching khaglang po che'i rko rlon yang ba kor ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9377: stag gis pags pa'i sham thabs kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9378: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK070(thu)001:9380: gdug pa rngam pa'i sgra can gshe zhing myur bar ma rangs pa khros pa'i gad mo bzhad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9381: ste 'jigs pa'i nga ro ha ha phata phata dang
NK070(thu)001:9382: ru lu la sogs par sna tshogs par sgrogs pa
NK070(thu)001:9383: sbrul dang thod rlon nyi mar bcas //
NK070(thu)001:9385: sbrul gyi chas ni dbu rgyan /
NK070(thu)001:9395: ni snom pos dbu la brgyan /
NK070(thu)001:9396: rlon pos phreng ba do shal tsha bus dpung rgyan /
NK070(thu)001:9397: dbu'i skra ral pa'i gseb la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK070(thu)001:9398: 'od zer bye ba dang bcas pa 'gyed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9400: rdo rje dung chen gang ba dang //
NK070(thu)001:9401: ral gri dgra sta gshol la sogs //
NK070(thu)001:9402: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs bsnams //
NK070(thu)001:9403: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9404: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK070(thu)001:9405: 'di dag rgyas pa las kyang gsungs nas /
NK070(thu)001:9407: rdo rje'i rigs kyi g.yas dang pos rdo rje g.yon dang po dril bu dang //
NK070(thu)001:9408: g.yon tha ma stong gi 'jig rten 'khor yug dang bcas pa 'deg /
NK070(thu)001:9410: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi g.yas dang pos 'khor lo g.yon dang pos dgra s+t+wa dang //
NK070(thu)001:9411: g.yon tha mas kha t+aam rab tu khrol ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9412: 2nor bu ste rat+na'i g.yas dang pos 1rin chen g.yon dang pos 3rgyu zhags dang //
NK070(thu)001:9413: g.yon tha ma rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dgra s+t+wa rab tu brdeg /
NK070(thu)001:9415: chags chog ste pad+ma'i rigs kyi g.yas dang pos pad+ma chen po dang //
NK070(thu)001:9416: g.yon dang pos dril bu g.yon tha mas rnga sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9417: las kyi rigs ni g.yas dang pos ral gri g.yon dang po gshol chen dang //
NK070(thu)001:9418: g.yon tha ma 'jig rten rgyang mar 'phen pa 'i tshul ste //
NK070(thu)001:9419: rigs lnga po kun gyi g.yas bar ma rdo rje
NK070(thu)001:9420: g.yon bar mas dung chen dmar gyis bkang pa 'khrugs
NK070(thu)001:9422: kun gyi g.yas tha mas ti ra zhing gi dbyug pa chen po rab tu brdegs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9424: rang rang gi rigs kyi yab yum btsun mo 'jigs pa'i tshogs dang 'khril //
NK070(thu)001:9425: nas g.yas dril bu 'dzin cing yab la 'khyud pa g.yon dung khrag zhal du stob pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9426: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya na zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:9427: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad khrag 'thung
NK070(thu)001:9428: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bcu kun tu gang
NK070(thu)001:9429: bar gyur to // zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9430: don mtshon pa'i rtags ste gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9431: le'u bcu bdun pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9433: // de nas zhi khro de dag gi dkyil 'khor la mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9434: de nas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9435: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos lha tshogs rnams mnyes pa'i mchod pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9436: phyi rgyud man chad la rmad du byung ba'i mchod
NK070(thu)001:9437: pa chen po 'og tu 'chad pa'i zhe sdang sgrol
NK070(thu)001:9438: ba 'dod chags sbyor ba gti mug dam rdzas 'dod
NK070(thu)001:9439: yon rgyan gyi mchod pa bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:9440: de la mchod sbyin dam pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9442: de la de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la mchod pa
NK070(thu)001:9443: dang ma mo mkha' 'gro la sbyin cing de rnams
NK070(thu)001:9444: kyi thugs rgyud tshim pa'i phyir nges tshig gang zhe
NK070(thu)001:9445: na sha khrag rus pa dug gsum gyi mchod pas
NK070(thu)001:9446: dug gsum dang 'dod yon spangs pa med par ye
NK070(thu)001:9448: skyabs chen po thob pa'i phyir dam pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9449: de dag gang zhig snyam pa la /
NK070(thu)001:9450: thog khamar bdag kanyid rtog gam gabsgral //
NK070(thu)001:9451: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9452: 'dis sgrol ba po'i gang zag ston te dang por
NK070(thu)001:9453: thog ma shes bya rtogs pa rnam bzhi bcu gcig
NK070(thu)001:9454: par bshad pa bzhin du don rtogs shing khong du
NK070(thu)001:9455: chud nas ting nge 'dzin gnyis brten pa'i goms stobs
NK070(thu)001:9457: bdag 1nyid kyi bdag 'dzin dag pas bsgral ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9458: thugs rjes gzhan bsgral ba'i po lta ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9459: rtog pas bdag bsgral de nas gnyis med blo yis ni /
NK070(thu)001:9461: rnal 'byor ba gang gis gong gi lta ba'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin du grub pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9462: bsgral bya gzhan thams cad kyang rig pa bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:9463: chen po las mi gzhan ste gnyis su med par
NK070(thu)001:9464: mthong ba'i blo yis nyid bsgral bar 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:9465: bsgral bya'i yul bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9466: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK070(thu)001:9468: bsgral bya'i zhing bcu dag ni las rgyu 'bras tsam yang mi shes pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9469: blo ngan zhing shes rab chung ba kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:9470: bsgral bya'i zhing bcu de dag rang rang gi las rnams kyis dus yun ring du 'khor ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9471: dus gtan du 'jig rten pa kho na la 'khyams te /
NK070(thu)001:9472: sdug bsngal ba de dag snying rjes zin par bya ba'i zhing ngo //
NK070(thu)001:9473: yin pas snying re rje gsungs bsgral ba'i thabs dang gnas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9474: bsgral bya sgral byed yig chen gnyis su med par shes pa chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9476: thabs rgyas pa ni bcu gcig pa'i skabs su bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:9477: gong du kha 'phangs pa'i gnas ni bsgral bya'i shes
NK070(thu)001:9478: pa rdo rje sems par bskyed pa de nyi zla
NK070(thu)001:9479: steng du rlung gis 'og min du 'phang nas rdo
NK070(thu)001:9480: rje 'dzin pa yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:9481: med pa'i byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur nas sangs
NK070(thu)001:9482: rgyas su rigs nges par bsgral bar bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9484: g+ha na'i sbyor ba mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9485: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas /
NK070(thu)001:9486: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK070(thu)001:9488: yab yum thabs dang shes rab phan tshun gnyis med du 'khril ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9489: bdag gzhan chos gsum ngam rang gis nyams su myong
NK070(thu)001:9490: ba rgyal ba mnyes sems can gyi rtog pa tshim
NK070(thu)001:9493: yab yum de nyid kyi nyi zla byang chub kyi
NK070(thu)001:9494: sems gnyis dus gcig tu mnyam par sbyor ba sa
NK070(thu)001:9495: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kun bdag nyid rnal 'byor
NK070(thu)001:9496: pa yab yum bde ba chen po mnyes pas rgyal
NK070(thu)001:9497: ba thams cad kyang mnyes par bya ba kho na'o
NK070(thu)001:9498: // de dag gi bya thabs ni /
NK070(thu)001:9499: le'u dgu par gsal ldan ma'i byin rlabs las zhes
NK070(thu)001:9500: pa'i skabs dang bcu gcig par zur tsam bshad zin
NK070(thu)001:9501: to // dam rdzas lnga ni man chad las khyad
NK070(thu)001:9502: par rmad du byung ba'i mchod pa yin par bstan
NK070(thu)001:9503: to // pa'i phyir / mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen dag /
NK070(thu)001:9504: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9505: dam rdzas lnga dang rigs lnga ye shes lnga mnyam
NK070(thu)001:9506: pa ni rang bzhin chos nyid kyi mnyam pa rig
NK070(thu)001:9507: pa dang / bsgrub na der snang bas spyod pa ni las kyi mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9508: bdud rtsi lnga po de dag grub pa'i rdzas chen po bzhi dang ldan pa dag yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:9509: 1gang zhe na chos nyid rang bzhin grub pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9510: 2chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9514: phyi nang ngam dam rdzas lnga'i dngos po ma lus
NK070(thu)001:9515: pa'i rang bzhin rang gi sems nyid las mi gzhan
NK070(thu)001:9516: pa'i phyir sems de nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni yod
NK070(thu)001:9518: bral ba ye shes chos kyi dbyings /
NK070(thu)001:9519: nyid yon tan cir yang 'char bas /
NK070(thu)001:9520: khams lnga'i bcud lnga'i 2rang bzhin gyi bde ba'i ngo bo ni ye shes lnga /
NK070(thu)001:9521: ru gsal ba de rgyu rkyen byed pa po med par 1 rang snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9522: shes 3rab lta ba dang sgom pa ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa'i bden pa'i thabs dag gis /
NK070(thu)001:9523: spyad na nad lnga sel ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9524: sman lnga grub pa'i nus mthu sa mchog thun mong gnyis nges par 'byung bar 'gyur /
NK070(thu)001:9526: dam rdzas dang du len pa 'di 4lta'i bu lam la rnal 'byor pa gang gnas pa /
NK070(thu)001:9528: phyogs bcu dus gsum po kun nas rgyal ba sras dang bcas pas byin gyis barlobasa /
NK070(thu)001:9530: zhor la ma mo mkha' 'gro byin gyi brlabs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9531: zhes 'byung ba kho na'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9532: mchod pa'i gnas sam zhing bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9533: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK070(thu)001:9535: 'bul mkhan gyi rnal 'byor pa bdag gang dang 'bul
NK070(thu)001:9536: yul lha gang dag 'bul rgyu'i mchod pa de dag
NK070(thu)001:9537: sems nyid du mnyam pa'i ngang du lha tshogs la
NK070(thu)001:9538: 'bul ba ni zhing mkhan mchod pa'i dngos po 'khor
NK070(thu)001:9539: gsum yongs su dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9540: mchod pa gnas su stob pa'i mchod pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9541: 'dod pa'i longs spyod rgyan gyi mchod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9542: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK070(thu)001:9543: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9544: 'di dag tshogs kyi le'ura bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:9545: mchod pa de dag gi spyi'i yon tan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9546: mchog gi dngos grub ni phyogs bcur bzhugs shing dus bzhir bdag don du yang dag pa'i sa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9547: gzhan don du thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don du gshegs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:9548: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:9549: yon tan phrin las gzhan las khyad par du gyur
NK070(thu)001:9551: de nyid ye nas rang la lhun gyis grub pa
NK070(thu)001:9552: ma gtogs pa de gzhan nas yod pa gcig bdag
NK070(thu)001:9553: gi drung tu 'ong ba ma yin par grub nas
NK070(thu)001:9554: thob pa te // gzhan thun mong pa lha srin
NK070(thu)001:9555: la sogs pa dbang du 'du ba lta smos kyang
NK070(thu)001:9556: thob pa te // ci dgos // zhes gsungs pa ni go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:9557: mchod bya mchod byed mchod pa gang yang sems su
NK070(thu)001:9558: dbyer med pas rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ra
NK070(thu)001:9559: gcig par rtogs pa gnas su stob pa'i mchod par
NK070(thu)001:9561: rnal 'byor bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin las spyod lam
NK070(thu)001:9562: rnam bzhir mi 'da' zhing las su rung ba'i gang
NK070(thu)001:9563: zag rnams kyis / lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po
NK070(thu)001:9564: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs par
NK070(thu)001:9565: zag rnams kyis / gyur cing / sku gsung thugs
NK070(thu)001:9566: kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'i tshad yul rkyen gyis mi
NK070(thu)001:9567: phrog par brtan pa thob nas 'grub mi 'gyur gyi
NK070(thu)001:9568: zag rnams kyis / gyur cing / / yid gnyis dang the tshom med pas na /
NK070(thu)001:9569: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'bar bar 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:9571: gdod nas gnas pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:9572: bskyed pa ting nge 'dzin lha'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK070(thu)001:9573: spyan drangs ba ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsum po
NK070(thu)001:9574: ril thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9576: dkyil 'khor chen po zhes bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:9577: mchod pa'i zhing dang rdzas mkhan po des na thams
NK070(thu)001:9578: cad rig pa'i rgyal po rang dbang du bsgyur ba'i
NK070(thu)001:9579: sa na 'bar bar 'gyur ba phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9580: bdag nyid chen po'i mchod par 'gyur le'u bco brgyad pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9581: mchod pa de'i rjes su dam tshig bstan pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9582: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos sngags
NK070(thu)001:9583: 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9585: sngags 'chang rnams bcu gcig par rnal 'byor sngags 'chang zhes pa'i skabs su bshad zin to //
NK070(thu)001:9586: theg pa chen po'i gsang sngags pa dam tshig ni dgos pa /
NK070(thu)001:9587: gnas skabs su len pa'i cha nas lam gyi dang mthar thug mngon du gyur pa'i cha nas /
NK070(thu)001:9588: yang dgos 'bras bu'i dam tshig dang /
NK070(thu)001:9590: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:9591: spyir thun mong gi theg pa'i 'bras bu lha mi'i lus la gzhi brten nas /
NK070(thu)001:9592: rgyud kyis yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po
NK070(thu)001:9593: bdun po rnams dus nye bar bsgrub pa'i phyir na
NK070(thu)001:9594: / dgongs 'dus las gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba sa gzhi gshin pa ltar /
NK070(thu)001:9595: bslab pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9596: dam tshig chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9597: sngags theg pa chen po'i lugs kyi dam tshig ni /
NK070(thu)001:9599: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis kyis dpag pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9600: dang po dam tshig che ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9601: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK070(thu)001:9602: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9603: theg khapa 'di'i lta sgom spyod gsum gyi kalam 'di
NK070(thu)001:9604: dang 'bras bu gnyis ka'i gong gana gzhan med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9605: phyir bla na med pa'i theg pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9606: de'i gzhung gis dam tshig rtsa ba lnga /
NK070(thu)001:9607: yan lag bcu ste bco lnga nyams su rab tu
NK070(thu)001:9608: lon te rtogs pa ni lta ba'i gdengs dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:9610: nyon mongs pa lnga 'dod yon lnga kun spyad kyang //
NK070(thu)001:9611: las byas la bag chags mi sogs par slar tshogs gnyis su gyur te //
NK070(thu)001:9614: don gyis mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK070(thu)001:9615: 'tshams med pa lnga nye ba lnga lci ba bzhi log pa brgyad la sogs pa kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:9616: de dag la spyad kyang rig pa rang snang du
NK070(thu)001:9617: spyod pa byas bzhin bsod nams dang ye shes kyi
NK070(thu)001:9618: tshogs te de ltar tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa ste dngos
NK070(thu)001:9619: zhen gyis mi 'dzin pa kho na'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9620: bde zhes pa der ma zad /
NK070(thu)001:9621: khatshul khrims kasdom pa phun gasum tshogs //
NK070(thu)001:9623: byang sems kyi sdom pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9624: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims rnams kyis srog gcod pa
NK070(thu)001:9625: la sogs pa rtsa ba bzhi dang sngags kyi rgyud
NK070(thu)001:9626: kyi dam tshig de rnams ni ched du bsrung ba
NK070(thu)001:9628: 'dir yon tan yar ldan du rtsa ba'i dam tshig thams cad pa rdzogs la /
NK070(thu)001:9629: yan lag bcu po thams cad mdor bsdus na ni
NK070(thu)001:9630: rnam pa ni nyes spyod spangs ba mi dge sdom
NK070(thu)001:9631: pa'i dang dge ba'i tshogs bsgrub pa chos sdud dang
NK070(thu)001:9632: / rang gis brtan pa thob nas /
NK070(thu)001:9633: dang po dang brgyud pa'i sgo nas gzhan don byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9635: de dag 'dir ni dam tshig lta ba 'di dag la gnas pa'i dus na /
NK070(thu)001:9636: sgo gsum las mi dge ba bcu la sogs pa
NK070(thu)001:9637: dang nyon mongs pa lnga'i ril thams cad la spyad
NK070(thu)001:9639: don gyi ngo bo la cir yang byas pa med
NK070(thu)001:9640: pa sa ltung bar mi 'gyur ba de ni mi
NK070(thu)001:9641: dge ba sdom pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK070(thu)001:9642: gzhan gyi don du gyur nas srog gcod pa la
NK070(thu)001:9643: sogs pa rtsa ba bzhi po gang yang mi 'dor
NK070(thu)001:9644: bar byed pa ni sems can gyi don byed pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9645: tshul khrims so // gang ltar spyad kyang sgo gsum
NK070(thu)001:9646: lha'i sku gsung thugs phyag rgya chen po las mi
NK070(thu)001:9647: nyams pa ni dge ba bcu la sogs pa der
NK070(thu)001:9648: 'dus pas chos su sdud pa zhes bya ba'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9649: tshul khrims so // / lam dang 'bras bu'i bla
NK070(thu)001:9650: na med pa gsang sngags theg pa mchog gi dam
NK070(thu)001:9652: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis gsungs pa'i nyos kyi tshul khrims dang //
NK070(thu)001:9653: ci snyed 2byang sems dang kyi sdom 1pa bsam yas pa //
NK070(thu)001:9654: lhag ma lus pa kun kyang bla med theg par
NK070(thu)001:9655: 'dus pas 'di bsrung ba'i ngang du rnam par dag
NK070(thu)001:9657: yod med dbu ma mi dmigs shing //
NK070(thu)001:9658: zhes bya ba la sogs pa bla med kyi theg
NK070(thu)001:9659: pa 'di dag rgyu nyos kyi tshul khrims dang byang
NK070(thu)001:9660: sems kyi sdom pa'i rtsa ba bzhi 'dir thams cad
NK070(thu)001:9661: la spyad kyang 'og ma'i nyes pas mi gos pas
NK070(thu)001:9662: ngo bo yar ldan du rdzogs tshogs gnyis su 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:9663: bas yon tan yar ldan du 'dus shing /
NK070(thu)001:9665: dam tshig gi spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig tu yang 'gyur la /
NK070(thu)001:9666: bdag gzhan gnyis ka sems nyid du gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9667: de nyid yod med dbus kyi mtha' dang gsum la
NK070(thu)001:9668: mi dmigs shing blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i phyir
NK070(thu)001:9669: rang gzhan gnyis kar don dam par mnyam pa kho
NK070(thu)001:9672: kun rdzob tsam tu log rtog gi rgyu rkyen 'dus
NK070(thu)001:9673: pa tsam nyid du rang gzhag gnyis su snang ba
NK070(thu)001:9674: de la rang rgyud du grub par blo kun tu
NK070(thu)001:9675: brtags pa de dag dper na sgyu ma 'am mig
NK070(thu)001:9676: gi snang ngor tho yor gyi snang ba la mi
NK070(thu)001:9677: ma grub pa lta bu phung po rang rgyud can
NK070(thu)001:9678: du ma grub par shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9679: kun rdzob tu bcad bya srog kyang gcod byed kyi
NK070(thu)001:9680: skyes bu'i ra snang ba 'di ni med pa la
NK070(thu)001:9681: yod par 'dzin pa log rtog rten 'brel gyi snang
NK070(thu)001:9683: de ltar rig pa ni srog bcad bya 'i yul
NK070(thu)001:9684: gcod byed kyi mkhan po gnyis su med par ka
NK070(thu)001:9685: nas dag pa'i phyir ci bcad kyang gcod pa'i 'du
NK070(thu)001:9686: shes med pas don gyi ngo bo la srog bcad
NK070(thu)001:9688: srog gi gcod pa spang ba'i sdom pa yar ldan du 'dul la dag pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:9689: srog med pas srog kyang bcad du med //
NK070(thu)001:9691: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK070(thu)001:9692: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni ma byin par len pa 'dus la dag par ston te /
NK070(thu)001:9693: kun rdzob dang don dam bden pa gnyis ka sems
NK070(thu)001:9694: nyid kyi ngo bo la bdag gzhan gnyis mi phyed
NK070(thu)001:9695: pa ste / dbyer med lugs 'bru ni bshad pa sngar grub bo //
NK070(thu)001:9696: dper na 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad min //
NK070(thu)001:9698: 'phrul dag'i lha rnams ni 'tsho ba'i longs spyod rang las sprul cing rang rigs /
NK070(thu)001:9700: tshul de bzhin du don rang rig pa de nyid
NK070(thu)001:9701: bdag gzhan nam 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad du
NK070(thu)001:9702: rang snang bas snang yang don gyi ngo bo la
NK070(thu)001:9703: gnyis su ma grub ste tha dad pa med par
NK070(thu)001:9704: rang rig pa la ma byin pa blang rgyu'i gzhan
NK070(thu)001:9705: rdzas dang de'i bdag po ma byin par len mkhan
NK070(thu)001:9706: gnyis ka bdag kanyid chen po las mi gzhan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9707: ste dmigs su med pa phyir kun rdzob tu ci
NK070(thu)001:9708: galtar blangs kyang blang ba'i 'du shes med de thams
NK070(thu)001:9709: cad bdag nyid chen po las 'das pa med pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9710: don gyi sa na dbyings zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9711: gzhan kadang ma byin med khapa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:9712: blang gamed thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:9714: ma byin par len pa'i sdom pa yon tan yar ldan du 'dus pa la dag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9715: rdzun du smra ba spangs pa'i don gyi sdom pa la 'dus la dag par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:9716: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu dang //
NK070(thu)001:9717: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9718: phyi yul dang nang sems gi dngos po gnyis kyis
NK070(thu)001:9719: bsdus pa'i chos rnams log rtog gi rgyu rkyen 'dus
NK070(thu)001:9720: pa tsam kho na'i nga ba phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9721: snang dus bden dngos kyis stong pa sgyu ma lta
NK070(thu)001:9722: bu yang dag par ngo bo nyid med bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:9723: dngos po yod par brtags pa'i zhan blo rang gi
NK070(thu)001:9724: ngo bo nyid du snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9725: rang rgyud du mi bden pa ngo bo nyid kyi rdzun zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9726: ming dang tshig tu brtags pa rdzun //
NK070(thu)001:9728: dngos po med bzhin du blo 'khrul ba'i zhen pa
NK070(thu)001:9729: de nyid du snang ba de dag la ming dang
NK070(thu)001:9730: tshig sna tshogs su brtags nas ming tshig tsam la
NK070(thu)001:9731: bden par 'dzin cing spyod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9732: ngo bo nyid kyi rjes su sbyod pa'i rdzun gnyis pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9733: rjes su spyod pa de dag las kyang 'gal ba'i dngos po yod las med /
NK070(thu)001:9735: yang na mi chos bla ma'i rdzun shes bzhin du
NK070(thu)001:9736: byed pa ni gsum pa log pa'i rdzun zhes bya'o
NK070(thu)001:9737: // de dag gsum ka la ni bden pa'i yul gyi gzhi ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9738: de ltar rang rgyud can du ma grub pas rdzun
NK070(thu)001:9739: nyid yin pa la ni rdzun spyod pas bden par
NK070(thu)001:9741: des na rdzun zhes ming du brtags pa tsam yang dmigs su yod pa ma yin //
NK070(thu)001:9744: de ltar du rtogs shing shes na bdag gzhan chos
NK070(thu)001:9745: gsum gyi don du smras kyang nyes pas mi gos
NK070(thu)001:9746: pa ni / rdzun gyi sdom pa yon tan yar ldan du sdom pa 'dus la dag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9747: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:9749: ngo bo rang gi cha na dngos po thams cad
NK070(thu)001:9750: sems nyid du rang snang bas yul sems gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:9751: med par rang gsal ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9752: ma chags pa'i ye shes nyid kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9753: de la gzung 'dzin nam pho mo gnyis su zhen pa'i chags pa ni log pa'i 'dod chags te /
NK070(thu)001:9754: de'i ltar spyod pa kadus nyid na lta bas sems nyid du shes pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9755: ting nge 'dzin de las mi 'da' ba dang spyod
NK070(thu)001:9756: pa thabs kyis zin pa'i chags pa 'gag med du
NK070(thu)001:9757: spyod pa'i ro de nyid ye shes su gsal bas
NK070(thu)001:9758: na chags pa rang kha ma de'i nyes pa gol
NK070(thu)001:9759: ba'i dri ma med pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9760: kachags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK070(thu)001:9762: de ni tshangs par sbyod pa'i mchog bde ba'i ye
NK070(thu)001:9763: shes su dbang bsgyur bas tshangs spyod kyi rgyal po
NK070(thu)001:9765: shin tu kachags pa chen po yin //
NK070(thu)001:9767: shin tu chags pa chen po spang gnyen ro gcig
NK070(thu)001:9768: tu gyur pa de ni de pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo
NK070(thu)001:9769: bo nyid de la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK070(thu)001:9770: kyang dbyer med pa'i yin pa phyir mi tshangs par
NK070(thu)001:9771: spyod pa'i sdom pa yon tan yar ldan du 'dus
NK070(thu)001:9772: la dag pa'o // bla med mi spangs bla ma bkur //
NK070(thu)001:9773: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9774: rnam par dbye ba'i dam tshig gi rnam grangs la /
NK070(thu)001:9775: mdo dang rgyas pa gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:9776: 'di na mar dang po mdor bstan pa ston te /
NK070(thu)001:9777: bla na med pa'i byang chub sems kyi dam tshig te /
NK070(thu)001:9778: de'i ngo bo ni theg pa chen po'i gsang sngags
NK070(thu)001:9779: kyi gzhung gi yi dam gyi lha sku phyag rgya
NK070(thu)001:9780: chen por ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba
NK070(thu)001:9781: kun rdzob byang chub dang rang bzhin med par stong
NK070(thu)001:9782: pa don dam byang chub sems te gnyis su med
NK070(thu)001:9783: pa de ni mi spangs pa kho na ste 'bras
NK070(thu)001:9785: tshig don de'i lam gong nas lhag ma gzhan med pa'i phyir bla na med par ro //
NK070(thu)001:9786: 'di la lta spyod lhas mi khrel ba gcig dgos
NK070(thu)001:9787: bla ma ni rdo rje theg pa'i slob dpon te
NK070(thu)001:9788: de la rnam pa'i grangs lnga ste /
NK070(thu)001:9789: dang por chos sgor 'jug pa'i 'go 'dren pa dang
NK070(thu)001:9790: dkyil 'khor du bcugs nas rtsa ba yan lag gi
NK070(thu)001:9791: dam tshig dbog shing phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur
NK070(thu)001:9792: ba dang / bdag gi dam tshig nyams chag skongs pa'i dpang po byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9793: rang gi shes pa'i rgyud ma shes pas bcings pa las grol ba'i rgyud sde gsungs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9794: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i man ngag dang lung dbog pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9795: bskur ba'i tshul ni spangs bya'i bslab bya la rang gis sgo gsum zol dang sgyu med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9796: dang du blang bya'i bslab bya la bla ma mnyes
NK070(thu)001:9797: pa'i thabs lus ngag yid kyis rtsal 'byung ba kho
NK070(thu)001:9798: na'o // ste srid zhu slob dpon gyis mi khrel
NK070(thu)001:9799: ba gcig dgos pa sngags ni rtsa ba bskyed las
NK070(thu)001:9800: na'o // gsum mo // phyag rgya ni dam tshig las chos rgya chen bzhi'o //
NK070(thu)001:9801: rgyun ni brtson 1pa rab 'bring dang goms pa che
NK070(thu)001:9802: 2chung 2gis dus kyi thun rgyun nyin gsum mtshan gsum
NK070(thu)001:9803: nyin gcig mtshan gcig nyin zhag gcig la thang cig
NK070(thu)001:9804: gsum dang yang na yang rab kyis skad cig ma'i
NK070(thu)001:9806: chu rgyun bzhin du yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK070(thu)001:9808: yang dag pa thabs shes rab bskyed rdzogs rnam pa
NK070(thu)001:9809: gnyis la kyi lam mthun pa zhugs pa rnams ni
NK070(thu)001:9811: de la ma h+aa la zhugs shing lta spyod mthun pa nye ba 2dang /
NK070(thu)001:9812: sngags la zhugs pa tsam ring 1ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9813: bla ma gcig la gdams ngag gcig tu 'dres 3pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9814: mchod de dag la sgo gsum gyis phan pa'i rtsal /
NK070(thu)001:9816: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK070(thu)001:9819: de'ang lta thabs spyod pa barlanga po dang lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams /
NK070(thu)001:9820: spyir gsang bzhi bsgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas /
NK070(thu)001:9821: zhes bar gsang bzhi mdor bsdu na mthong bya dang
NK070(thu)001:9822: mthong byed rnams gsang bar 'os pa slob dpon dang
NK070(thu)001:9823: mched kyis gdams pas gsang bar gnyer gtad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9824: gsang ba bcu po de dag gi don dgos pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9825: gdul bya blo chung ba'am gzhan gyi don dang /
NK070(thu)001:9826: chos gsang sngags kyi don dang /
NK070(thu)001:9827: mched lcam grogs po'i don dang bzhi po kho nar 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9828: gang la gsang na dam med pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9829: yod kyang dam nyams pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9830: rang dang dam tshig gcig tu ma 'dres pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9831: rang dang dam tshig 'dres pa dag la'ang gnas skabs kyi sgrub rog mi na gsang ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:9832: tshul ji ltar na tshig ngag gi smra bar mi
NK070(thu)001:9833: bya ba dang spyod lam thams cad kyis sbas pa
NK070(thu)001:9834: kho na'o // 'di la g.yo sgyu rang sems kyis mi khrel ba gcig dgos so //
NK070(thu)001:9835: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te /
NK070(thu)001:9837: lnga po de dag rnams ni gnas skabs sam mthar
NK070(thu)001:9838: thug 'bras bu'i yon tan ril gyi gzhir gyur pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9839: phyir ro // bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK070(thu)001:9842: gsung gi dam tshig gnyis ni bsgrub cing nyams su len pa'i dam tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:9843: slob dpon dang mched thugs kyi dam tshig gsum ni sgo gsum gyis bsrung ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:9844: yan lag gi dam tshig bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9845: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK070(thu)001:9846: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK070(thu)001:9847: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9848: spyir yang dag dug lnga 'i lta spyod phyin ci
NK070(thu)001:9849: ma log pa dang btag pa ba gang zag dam
NK070(thu)001:9850: pa'i rgyud la mnga' ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9851: log pa'i ni pho rog rang kha ma dug mtshan
NK070(thu)001:9852: nyid pa so so skye bo'i rgyud la yod pa
NK070(thu)001:9853: dang / gnyis su rgyas pa'i rgyud don gcig pa dang gsum pa las gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:9854: de las log pa'i dug lnga nyid /
NK070(thu)001:9855: ma 'dres pa rang gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK070(thu)001:9856: gti mug sems blun zhing mi 'byed pa la sogs pa'i 'dod chags dang /
NK070(thu)001:9858: nga rgyal phrag dog rnams dang /
NK070(thu)001:9859: yongs su rdzogs pa spyi'i mtshan nyid lta ba dag
NK070(thu)001:9860: mnyam rtogs bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis nyon mongs thams cad
NK070(thu)001:9861: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid yin pa la blos
NK070(thu)001:9862: nyams su lon na dug lnga'i 'char sgo ma 'gag
NK070(thu)001:9863: par sku rang bzhin ma skyes pa gsung gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:9864: med pa thugs kho na nyid yin pa las spang
NK070(thu)001:9865: bya'i rdzas gang yang mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9867: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK070(thu)001:9868: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK070(thu)001:9869: rnam par byang pa'i lam du 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:9871: yang dag pa'i lta spyod kyi dug lnga ni gsal
NK070(thu)001:9872: bkra ltar gnyis char la gnas pa ni theg pa
NK070(thu)001:9873: chen po'i lta spyod gnyis la dam tshig gi ril
NK070(thu)001:9874: thams cad rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9875: gsang sngags gi dug lnga mi spang ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:9876: dkar rtsi ni byang sems dmar rtsi ni rak+ta dri chen dang dri chu sha chen //
NK070(thu)001:9877: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK070(thu)001:9879: gang dang du blang na dam rdzas lnga po 'di
NK070(thu)001:9880: nyid ci'i phyir dang du blang na sngar bco brgyad
NK070(thu)001:9881: par bshad pa'i grub pa bzhi po dag gis brgyan
NK070(thu)001:9882: pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i snod bcud 'di dag dang
NK070(thu)001:9884: des dgos ched la gzhan sel rtsang smee'i rtog pa sbyang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9885: don gnyer la'ang thun mong gi yon tan nad lnga sel ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:9886: dri chen tshe ring ba la sogs gnyis gnyis kyi yang 'byung ba'i phyir te /
NK070(thu)001:9887: dam rdzas de dag rgyun du spyad par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9889: yan lag la mi spang ba lnga mi dor ba lnga dang bcu'i dam tshig ste /
NK070(thu)001:9891: rnal 'byor rtsa ba'i 'di dam tshig lnga dag ma nyams pa las /
NK070(thu)001:9892: yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag 1'byung zhing snang
NK070(thu)001:9893: ba des bsgrub pa'i grogs cher 1byed 11pa'i phyir ro
NK070(thu)001:9894: // ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyad //
NK070(thu)001:9896: dug lnga dam rdzas lnga'i dngos po thams cad ye
NK070(thu)001:9897: gdod ma nas dag pa gsum dang mnyam pa bzhi'i
NK070(thu)001:9898: ngo bor gnas pa'i sku ye shes de dag rang
NK070(thu)001:9899: snang du rtogs pas dug lnga spyad pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:9900: rtogs par 'dod pas dam rdzas la spyad pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9901: de ltar de dag go rim bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:9902: bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam tshig lnga //
NK070(thu)001:9903: rtsa ba yin te rigs med 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:9904: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9905: rtsa ba dang yan lag gnyis su phye ba'i dam tshig gi nges tshig bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9906: bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam tshig rtsa ba lnga po
NK070(thu)001:9907: ni lam 'bras thams cad kyi gazhi'am rtsa ba yin
NK070(thu)001:9908: te / nyams na gnas skabs su mi dang lha'i rigs kyang med par 'gyur na /
NK070(thu)001:9909: mthar thug theg pa chen po'i rigs lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK070(thu)001:9910: mkhar rmings 'gram nas zhig pa ltar chos kyis rmings 'gram nas med par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9911: nyams na mi dang lha'i rigs kyang med par 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:9912: na de ltar theg pa chen po'i rig mi spangs
NK070(thu)001:9913: pa lnga dang / mi 'dor lnga tshan gnyis ni /
NK070(thu)001:9914: yan lag gi dam tshig yin na yang /
NK070(thu)001:9917: de yang log pa'i dug lnga gnyen pos spangs ba ni nyos lta bur gyur pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9918: lam nor bas lta ba'i mnyam pa nyid dgag bsgrub med pa klong las nyams pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:9919: yang dag pa'i dug lnga le lo byed nas spang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9920: rang gzhan gyi don gnyis ma 'grub pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9921: rang gi rgyud la lta spyod gnyis med pas byin brlabs med par 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:9922: dam rdzas lnga sme bar byed nas /
NK070(thu)001:9923: spangs ba ni kri ya ltar gyur pas /
NK070(thu)001:9925: spyod pa gnyis su med par ma 'brel ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:9926: bla med kyi theg pa 'dir mi chud pa'i skyon kho na'i yod pa phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:9927: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba'i /
NK070(thu)001:9928: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK070(thu)001:9929: mnyam rdzogs chen por thob par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:9931: rnam grangs kyi skabs su rtsa ba las gnyis su
NK070(thu)001:9932: phye ba rtsa ba chen po med do mnyam pa
NK070(thu)001:9934: dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin gzhi don dam
NK070(thu)001:9935: kun rdzob dbyer med kyi bden pa gsum gyis mnyam
NK070(thu)001:9936: pa la / mnyam pa ltar shes rab lta ba
NK070(thu)001:9937: dang sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyis mnyam par sbyor
NK070(thu)001:9938: pa la / ba'i dus na / phyi nang gi
NK070(thu)001:9939: chos gang yang rig pa bdag nyid chen po mnyam
NK070(thu)001:9940: pa'i don las mi 'da' ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9941: mnyam pa nyid kyi dam tshig kho na'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9943: rtsa ba dang yan lag gam /
NK070(thu)001:9944: yang na gal che bas dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba /
NK070(thu)001:9945: gud na te log yod pa ma yin te /
NK070(thu)001:9946: 'o na gang zhe na rang gi lta ba rtogs pa'i don la mi 'da' ba dam tshig no /
NK070(thu)001:9949: 'di'i don de la gnas na de'i 'bras bu ni /
NK070(thu)001:9950: mnyam rdzogs chen po gang yang ma spang par kun
NK070(thu)001:9951: tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa thob ste
NK070(thu)001:9953: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK070(thu)001:9955: 'di nyid ma rtogs shing nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9956: de bzhin gshegs pa yang mnyam pa'i dam tshig 'di'i ngo bo las mi 'da' bar bzhugs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9957: gang zhig bdag nyid chen po mnyam pa'i dam tshig
NK070(thu)001:9958: las 'das shing nyams na de la gzhan par ma
NK070(thu)001:9959: nyams pa mthong ba dang spyod pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9960: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid las nyams
NK070(thu)001:9961: pa ste 'bras bu thob pa ma yin pa kho
NK070(thu)001:9962: na'o // rtsa ba nyams pa'i phyag 'tshal dag /
NK070(thu)001:9963: gso la nye bar mi brtson na //
NK070(thu)001:9965: gong gi rtsa ba lnga po kun nyams pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9967: phyag 'tshal ba dag pa zhes bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:9968: rtsa ba lnga po de dag kun kyang bsdu na kasku dang /
NK070(thu)001:9971: de yang sku ka slob dpon dang mched lcam spun
NK070(thu)001:9972: la dam tshig nyams na gsal bkra ltar zas nor
NK070(thu)001:9973: 'byor pa lnga la sogs pas gang la nyams pa'i
NK070(thu)001:9974: gnas su gaso'o // khabla na med pa byang sems
NK070(thu)001:9975: dang gsum sngags dang phyag rgya'i dam tshig nyams pa
NK070(thu)001:9976: bsgrub pa chen po yang yang lan gsum gyis bshags
NK070(thu)001:9977: nas bzlas pa'ang ba ldab re sob kyis gaso'o //
NK070(thu)001:9978: gagsang ba thugs ni dam tshig nyams na shes rab lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyis gaso'o //
NK070(thu)001:9979: de ltar myur du gso ba'i cho ga la nye bar mi brtson nas mi gso ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:9980: 'o ma rul ba dang rta rngo can dang spal
NK070(thu)001:9981: rma can 'dra bas dam tshig can rnams kyis zla
NK070(thu)001:9982: nyams kyis bar chad 'gyur bas tha na lung pa
NK070(thu)001:9983: gcig gi chu la mi btung ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:9984: dus skad cig gis yud tsam du yang smra bar
NK070(thu)001:9985: ma byed cig dam tshig nyams pa can dang 'grog
NK070(thu)001:9986: par gyur pa'i nyes pa brjod kyi mi lang ngo
NK070(thu)001:9987: zhes gsungs so // rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK070(thu)001:9988: bsgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:9989: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:9990: nyams pa'i skyon rnams bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:9991: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po nyams par gyur na
NK070(thu)001:9992: tshe 'dir yang bsgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur
NK070(thu)001:9993: te bzang po'i las ci brtsam pa'i ril la nus
NK070(thu)001:9994: mthu med cing bar chad mang bas gang yang don
NK070(thu)001:9996: tshe phyi mar yang yid du mi 'ong ba'i sdug
NK070(thu)001:9997: bsngal sna tshogs pa'i 'bras bu ngan song gsum mi
NK070(thu)001:9998: 'dod bzhin du rang dbang med par 'du bar 'byung
NK070(thu)001:9999: ngo // yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK070(thu)001:10000: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK070(thu)001:10002: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spangs mi 'dor ba gnyis nyams na ni /
NK070(thu)001:10003: nyon mongs pa spangs pas nyos dang rdzas la blang
NK070(thu)001:10004: dor byed pas kri ya ltar gol bar 'gyur bas
NK070(thu)001:10005: na / gsang sngags bla med kyi gzhung gis bstan
NK070(thu)001:10006: pa'i thun mong ni nad lnga med cing tshe ring
NK070(thu)001:10008: 1mchog gi 11sku gsung thugs 'bras bu med cing de
NK070(thu)001:10009: la mi spangs mi dor de dag dag mnyam rtogs
NK070(thu)001:10010: bzhi'i lung man ngag rigs pa'i gtan tshig gsum dang
NK070(thu)001:10011: / bdag gzhan chos kyi dgos ched gsum gyi sgo
NK070(thu)001:10012: nas mi spyod par rang kha mar log par spyad
NK070(thu)001:10013: pas dam tshig nyams pa can rnams ngan song gsum
NK070(thu)001:10014: du ltung bar 'gyur ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10015: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK070(thu)001:10016: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK070(thu)001:10018: dam tshig rang bzhin bstan pa ste //
NK070(thu)001:10019: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:10020: rang bzhin ni lta spyod gnyis su mi phyed pa
NK070(thu)001:10024: 'bras bu gsum yang dbyer med par mi phyed pa'i phyir rdo rje che zhes bya ste /
NK070(thu)001:10025: de dag ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi gshegs shul gyi lam dang /
NK070(thu)001:10026: dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin pa kho na'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10027: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni /
NK070(thu)001:10028: de gcig la'ang shes rab lta ba dang thabs ma
NK070(thu)001:10029: 'gags par spyod pa gnyis su dbye zhing byed pa
NK070(thu)001:10030: dang / de la dbye ba bcu phrag gsum /
NK070(thu)001:10031: ste rtsa ba lnga po re re la'ang sum cu rtsa gnyis pa tsho lnga ste brgya drug cu'o //
NK070(thu)001:10032: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spang mi 'dor ba lnga gnyis ste bcu la /
NK070(thu)001:10033: de gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su phye /
NK070(thu)001:10034: bas nyi shu po tsho bcu ste gnyis brgya dang kun dril bas sum brgya drug cu /
NK070(thu)001:10035: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni rnam grangs la
NK070(thu)001:10036: mdor rgyas bshad gnyis las 'dir rgyas par bstan pa
NK070(thu)001:10037: ste / spyir dam tshig rgyas pa 'bring po bsdus
NK070(thu)001:10038: pa rnam pa gsum las de re re yang rgyas
NK070(thu)001:10040: de yang rgyas pa'i gsum ni grangs med gsum ste stong rtsa brgyad do //
NK070(thu)001:10042: lnga brgya sum brgya drug cu /
NK070(thu)001:10044: bsdus pa'i gsum ni nyer brgyad /
NK070(thu)001:10045: bco lnga mdo mnyam pa nyid kyi dam tshig dang dgur dbye ba las /
NK070(thu)001:10047: sum brgya drug cur dbye ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:10048: de gang zhe na tshig mang du 'dogs pas mi lang ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10049: 'phra rgyas 'byed pa las gsal bas mi dgos phyir 'dir ma bris so //
NK070(thu)001:10050: rgyas pa grangs med pa yang zung tsam bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10051: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK070(thu)001:10052: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10053: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi dam tshig 'di rnams ni /
NK070(thu)001:10054: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i khrims ni 'dul thabs shin tu mang ba'am /
NK070(thu)001:10055: nyams na bskang du gtub pa dang 'dra ste /
NK070(thu)001:10056: gdul bya'i dbang gis rnam grangs rgya chad pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10058: de nyid nye bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10059: gnas 'jig rten dug gi phyogs bcu'i zhing khams grangs
NK070(thu)001:10060: med pa na gdul bya srid pa gsum gyis bsdus
NK070(thu)001:10062: rnal 'byor rtog pa 0'dul ba'i gnyen por dam tshig de snyed spro //
NK070(thu)001:10065: gnyen pos spong 'gog gi 'dul ba nyan rang dang /
NK070(thu)001:10067: stong nyid du sbyangs pas 'dul ba dang byang sems /
NK070(thu)001:10068: ltar bsgyur bas 'dul ba phyi rgyud dang /
NK070(thu)001:10069: ma spang bar rang dag pas 'dul ba nang pa gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:10070: chos thams cad rang sa na ngo shes pas 'dul ba a ti la sogs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10071: gdul bya dang 'dul thabs de dag gi don bya
NK070(thu)001:10072: ba'i phyir dam tshig yang rnam grangs ma nges pa
NK070(thu)001:10073: bsam gyis mi khyab pa de snyed cig spros pa
NK070(thu)001:10074: kho na'o // gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun nam gis //
NK070(thu)001:10075: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni bsrung ba'i yon tan bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10076: gong du bshad pa'i mnyam rdzogs kyi dam tshig yon tan las gzhan par gyur pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10078: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig bco lnga
NK070(thu)001:10079: ma nyams pa ra bsrung ba la ni 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:10081: rigs kyi bdag po ni rgyal ba'i mchog ste /
NK070(thu)001:10083: 1de'i ngo bo nyid ci lta bu zhe na /
NK070(thu)001:10084: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yi //
NK070(thu)001:10085: bsgrub med dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK070(thu)001:10087: 'khor 'das kyi ngo bo nyid kyis bsdus pa ril
NK070(thu)001:10088: thams cad ma lus pa'i snang ba 1sku grags pa
NK070(thu)001:10089: gsungs dran rtog 1thugs kyi 1phyag 11rgya ra yi ngo
NK070(thu)001:10090: bo ye nas lhun gyis grub pas de'i ngang du
NK070(thu)001:10091: rtog pa'am skyon spang pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10092: yon tan dang du blang ba med pa ni bsgrub tu med pa 'bras bu'i mchog dam pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10093: kun tu bzang po'i yon tan gyi ril ma lus pa 'grub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10094: de'i la sogs pa yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab
NK070(thu)001:10095: pa'i ngag tu brjod las 'das pa'i mtha' yas pa
NK070(thu)001:10097: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK070(thu)001:10099: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa ste //
NK070(thu)001:10100: zhes bya ba la sogs pa yon tan nye bar mdor bsdus te bstan pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10101: dam tshig 'di dag lta spyod tshang bar mgo 'byor pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10102: dang po lta ba rtogs pa sar chud pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK070(thu)001:10103: lta don de la ting nge 'dzin dus rgyun du gnas pa ni gnyis pa sa la gnas pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10105: lta sgom de nus pa'i stobs su gyur nas 'bras
NK070(thu)001:10106: bu thob pa ni gsum pa sa yongs su smin
NK070(thu)001:10107: pa'i rig 'dzin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10109: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK070(thu)001:10110: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis barlobasa //
NK070(thu)001:10112: dam tshig bsrung zhing sgrub pa po de la 'jig
NK070(thu)001:10113: rten gyis gtso bo lha ma srin sde brgyad 'khor
NK070(thu)001:10114: g.yog dang bcas pas rnams kyis de'i dgongs pa bsgrub
NK070(thu)001:10115: cing bkur sti byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10116: dam pa mchog sangs rgyas dang /
NK070(thu)001:10117: dam pa rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' ril thams
NK070(thu)001:10118: cad gyis sras dang spun du dgongs shing byin gyis
NK070(thu)001:10119: barlobasa par gyur pa dang zhor la ma mo mkha'
NK070(thu)001:10120: 'gro rnams kyis ming por dgongs shing sdong grogs byed
NK070(thu)001:10121: pa / dam can chos skyong rnams kyis rje dpon du dgongs nas phrin las bsgrub pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10122: bde bar gshegs nyid kyis yul la zhugs /
NK070(thu)001:10124: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig bco lnga po
NK070(thu)001:10125: de nyid de pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi
NK070(thu)001:10127: sangs rgyas dang spyod yul gcig pa la zhugs zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10128: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK070(thu)001:10130: bde bar gshegs kyi yul la zhugs pa de phan
NK070(thu)001:10131: chad sgo gsum gyi las ci spyad kyang ltung ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10133: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i kun tu bzang po'i sbyor ba phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10134: ci bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK070(thu)001:10136: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid ci bzhin pa de
NK070(thu)001:10137: nyid mngon du byed pa'i mnyam pa dam tshig chen
NK070(thu)001:10139: 'dul ba'i thabs bco lnga pa la sogs pa sum
NK070(thu)001:10140: brgya drug cu rnam grangs mtha' yas thams cad ma
NK070(thu)001:10141: brtsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10142: nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims ji snyed pa dang byang
NK070(thu)001:10143: sems kyi sdom pa dang gsang sngags phyi rgyud kyi
NK070(thu)001:10144: dam tshig mtha' yas pa de rnams lhag ma ma
NK070(thu)001:10145: lus pa'i dgag bya thams cad rnam par dag cing
NK070(thu)001:10146: yon tan thams cad yar ldan du lhun gyis grub
NK070(thu)001:10149: nyams na bskang bas rdzogs pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:10150: de la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa mchog /
NK070(thu)001:10153: spyir dam tshig rnams las rkyen ngan pa'i dbang gis lan cig nyams na /
NK070(thu)001:10154: log na de nas nyams pa bskangs bas zhing gso kyang /
NK070(thu)001:10155: nyams chags dag nas yon tan yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur na /
NK070(thu)001:10158: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la 'dul bar gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:10160: dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kun gyi bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:10161: rgyal ba de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyang 'di dag las mi 'da' nas 'dul bar gyur pa na /
NK070(thu)001:10162: gzhan lam pa lta ci smos zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK070(thu)001:10163: le'u bcu dgu pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10165: // dam tshig dang ldan pa de nas phrin las bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10166: lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig byin gyis brlabs pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10167: byang chub kyi sems nyid la 'og gi don sems ltar gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa zhi ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10169: 'khor 'das gnyis med dbang du 'du ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10170: rtog pa'i mtshan ma las grol ba drag po ste /
NK070(thu)001:10171: phrin las rnam bzhi rang bzhin gyi lhun gyis grub
NK070(thu)001:10172: par gnas pa de de las mi 'da' bas dam
NK070(thu)001:10173: tshig de nyid phrin las cho ga bzhis rang gnas
NK070(thu)001:10174: bskul bas de'i don mngon sum du snang bar byed
NK070(thu)001:10175: pa ni byin gyis brlabs pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10176: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK070(thu)001:10177: ces bya ba la sogs pa 'di dag kyang /
NK070(thu)001:10178: rgyud kyi rim pa man ngag gis 'khrugs bsdebs te /
NK070(thu)001:10180: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK070(thu)001:10181: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK070(thu)001:10182: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i don gyis bsgrub bya dgra bgegs dang /
NK070(thu)001:10184: 'dus pa dang zhi rgyas kyi gdul bya la sogs pa'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'am /
NK070(thu)001:10188: til dang sbrang la sogs pa zas lnga so //
