NK070(thu)001:10189: rnam pa rgyu bag zan la bag re bsre zhing
NK070(thu)001:10190: de la ling ga pho mo gang yin gyi mtshan
NK070(thu)001:10192: gzhi shog gu'am gro ba la dpral bar ming snying
NK070(thu)001:10193: khar rus dang bcas pa bris par bya la de'ang
NK070(thu)001:10194: 'dams su las gzhi gang byed kyi sngags /
NK070(thu)001:10198: yan lag bzhi la dzahmh'u bam hohbrisa la /
NK070(thu)001:10200: thod pa'i nang du brub khung tsher ma can du mgo lho nub tu bstan nas /
NK070(thu)001:10202: de nas sngags mkhan gyis phrin las rnam bzhi rang
NK070(thu)001:10203: gi phyogs su zhi ba la shar la sogs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10204: gdul bya gang byed du kha bltas la chas gos
NK070(thu)001:10205: bzhi so sor gyon nas e yi tshogs kyi dkyil
NK070(thu)001:10206: 'khor mchog / ces pa la sogs pa'i nas ya'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK070(thu)001:10209: las bzhi so so'i lha drag po la badz+ra he
NK070(thu)001:10210: ru ka dkyil 'khor gsal bar bskyed de gsum po
NK070(thu)001:10211: des 'dres so // ba hu bi tas lha rnams nges par las bzhi gang byed la btsud nas /
NK070(thu)001:10212: bden pa bdar sprul pa spro de nas /
NK070(thu)001:10213: bkug nas rdo rje phur pas gdab //
NK070(thu)001:10214: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10215: sprul pa'i pho nya rnams kyis bkug nas ling ga la bstim ste /
NK070(thu)001:10216: am gu sha dza la sogs pa'i phyag rgya bzhis
NK070(thu)001:10217: bcing nas dmigs bya gang yin pa mngon du byas
NK070(thu)001:10218: la bzhag go // de la lcags la sogs pa phur pa'i rgyu bzhi dang /
NK070(thu)001:10219: nag po la sogs pa'i dbyibs bzhi las bzhi so
NK070(thu)001:10220: so'i phur pa gsum lnga bzhi drug rnams thugs kyi
NK070(thu)001:10221: rigs la sogs pa rigs bzhi so so'i k+ai la
NK070(thu)001:10227: gsang gnas rkang lag la gnyis dang /
NK070(thu)001:10229: rdo rje phur pa btab te gdab la gzir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10230: tshe lung khrus lung gnyen po rang las byung bas bsgral /
NK070(thu)001:10231: yungs kar gyis thugs dam bskul /
NK070(thu)001:10233: rdul du byas nas tshogs su 'bul //
NK070(thu)001:10234: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i don gyis /
NK070(thu)001:10235: las bzhi'i bsam pa bzhi dang chas par hri ti'i sngags kyis pho'i rkang pa g.yas /
NK070(thu)001:10237: ral gris gtub la ling ga rnams rdul phran bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10238: du byas nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs pa 'bul
NK070(thu)001:10239: lo // gang la 'bul zhe na khrag 'thung 'bar
NK070(thu)001:10240: ba drag po gtum chen rngams pa'i tshogs rnams la
NK070(thu)001:10241: lo // / khros pa'i yid kyis ye shes kyi lha la mchod /
NK070(thu)001:10242: ma dang mkha' 'gro ma la sbyin pa'i las bya /
NK070(thu)001:10243: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i don gyis /
NK070(thu)001:10244: 'bar ba gzi brjid lhun chen la /
NK070(thu)001:10246: gsal ba'i gzi byin mtshar ba la //
NK070(thu)001:10247: ces pa rigs bzhi so so'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas
NK070(thu)001:10248: pa mngon sum du dmigs nas dug gsum gyi mchod
NK070(thu)001:10249: pa 'bul bas / rtod cing zos par 'bul lo //
NK070(thu)001:10250: de nas gdul sems khos pa'i yid kyis brlag pa drag po dang /
NK070(thu)001:10251: chags pa'i yid kyis dbang du 'dus pa dang dga' ba'i yid kyis rgyas pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10252: dwangs pa'i yid kyi zhi ba la sogs pa'i gdung
NK070(thu)001:10253: sems kyi bsam pas phye nas mchod sbyin phul bar
NK070(thu)001:10254: byas na zhi drag gis rang la mi gnod cing
NK070(thu)001:10255: / dbang rgyas kyi rang la 'dod pa bzhin du 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK070(thu)001:10256: de dag gi dang po lhag pa'i sgo nas rdzas kyi las /
NK070(thu)001:10258: gnyis rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi las bzhi bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10259: bro ra'i dbyibs gru gsum zla gam gru bzhi zlum
NK070(thu)001:10260: po byas pa'i sgrub pa po yab yum rnams lag
NK070(thu)001:10261: pa'i srin lag lu gu rgyud du sbrel ba'i ra
NK070(thu)001:10262: bsdam nas de dbus su ling ga bzhag la /
NK070(thu)001:10263: khadrag po'i e karam bam garam gyis dbang gi ma
NK070(thu)001:10264: ram gyis rgyas pa'i ya ram gyis zhi ba'i zhes
NK070(thu)001:10265: bya ba'i sngags kyis las bzhi so so'i gzhal yas
NK070(thu)001:10266: me dpung dang chas par bsam /
NK070(thu)001:10267: zhing bsgom de'i nang du lha tshogs kyi las bzhi
NK070(thu)001:10268: so so'i dkyil 'khor du rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid
NK070(thu)001:10270: de nas rgyas pa'i rgyud le'u nga bdun pa nas
NK070(thu)001:10271: drug cu'i bar las 'byung ba ltar h'u h'u zhe
NK070(thu)001:10273: zhes sogs kyi tshigs su bcad pas bskul la khro
NK070(thu)001:10274: bo'i stangs stabs sum b+ha ni sngags kyis sprul pa
NK070(thu)001:10275: rnams 'phros pas khams gsum ras bal rlung gis bskyod
NK070(thu)001:10276: pa ltar sprugs nas dmigs pa'i srung ba'i lha dang
NK070(thu)001:10277: phral te / bkugs nas ling ga la mngon du
NK070(thu)001:10278: bstim nas gnas pa la bdag lhar gsal ba'i gnas
NK070(thu)001:10279: gsum nas 'od zer kha dog bzhi byung bas ling
NK070(thu)001:10280: ga la thim nas las bzhi'i bsam yas dbang bsgyur
NK070(thu)001:10281: phral te / nas / las bzhi'i dngos grub ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du 'grub pa yin ste /
NK070(thu)001:10282: drag pos ni sangs rgyas rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK070(thu)001:10283: las byung ba'i gzugs kyi sku yang 'jigs pa dang
NK070(thu)001:10284: / sems myos nas lus gas te snying 'tshig par
NK070(thu)001:10285: 'gyur na bsgrub bya dgra bgegs gzhan lta ci smos
NK070(thu)001:10288: dbang gi yon tan ni rdo rje'i gsung pad+ma dbang
NK070(thu)001:10289: gi rgyal po pad+ma gar dbang yang dbang du 'du
NK070(thu)001:10290: bar 'gyur ba dang bsgrub bya 'gug par 'gyur ba
NK070(thu)001:10291: ci smos mthu stobs kyi bdag nyid phyag na rdo
NK070(thu)001:10292: rje 'ang khyi la zan byin pa bzhin phyi bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10293: du 'brang zhing rang gi ci 'dod pa de bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10295: bsgrub bya mi mos mi 'dod pa gzhan lta ci smos /
NK070(thu)001:10298: yon tan tshad las 'das pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang
NK070(thu)001:10299: mnyam pa thob pa dang 'dod dgu kun 'byung ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10300: yid bzhin gyis nam mkha' yang khengs zhing gang par
NK070(thu)001:10302: zhi bas 'i las kyi yon tan ni gtum chen
NK070(thu)001:10303: rngam pa khro bo'i las kyi sbyor ba'ang zhi nas
NK070(thu)001:10305: zhe sdang gis kun nas bslangs pa'i phyi nang gi
NK070(thu)001:10306: gdug rtsub thams cad kyi g.yo ba med par byed
NK070(thu)001:10307: do // 'bru ni go sla bas so sor ma bshad do //
NK070(thu)001:10308: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK070(thu)001:10309: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni las bzhi de
NK070(thu)001:10310: dag gi dus su 'khor dbang mo rnams bskul bas
NK070(thu)001:10311: las la mngag pa ste go sla'o //
NK070(thu)001:10312: khro bo bsgrub pa'i las kyi gtso bo 'di yin no zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10313: khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dus su
NK070(thu)001:10314: phrin las bzhi bya ba'i rnams kyi gtso bo mchog
NK070(thu)001:10315: ni bro gar glu tshig 'di yis 'grub par bya
NK070(thu)001:10316: ba'o // yon tan no zhes pa khrag 'thung chen po la sogs pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:10317: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10318: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi las la sogs pa'i dus su /
NK070(thu)001:10319: bdag cag khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga yab yum
NK070(thu)001:10320: la sogs pa'i lha ru byin gyis brlabs la khams
NK070(thu)001:10321: gsum gyi ril yang de las mi gzhan par byas
NK070(thu)001:10322: te / rkang pa'i bro stabs dang /
NK070(thu)001:10323: lag pa'ang gar thabs su g.yeng ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10324: ngag tu sum b+ha ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa /
NK070(thu)001:10325: glu tshig gi nga ro chen po dam chas par byas pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10326: las thams cad dngos grub thams cad ci 'dod par //
NK070(thu)001:10327: thams cad thams cad 'grub pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:10329: las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad ci 'dod par 'grub par 'gyur /
NK070(thu)001:10334: ke'u ri la sogs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10335: tsoo ri phra mo ha bee ta li rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:10336: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar
NK070(thu)001:10338: bro gar glu tshig chen mo ni /
NK070(thu)001:10339: dbang la 'du bar 'dod na dbang du 'du bar byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10340: tshe bsod nams ci rgyas shing 'phel bar 'dod pa rgyas zhing 'phel bar byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10341: sbos mo chen mo ni puk+ka si la sogs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10342: kasma hri sma she ni tsan+da li rnams kyi ting
NK070(thu)001:10343: nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa sngar bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10344: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK070(thu)001:10345: zhi ba'i las kyi lhan ner 'dod na lhan ner byed pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10347: mngon spyod kyi las kyi smug par 'dod na ni rmug par byed pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10348: gzhan seng gdong chen mo ma tshogs pa'i tshigs bcu gnyis ni /
NK070(thu)001:10350: ljon pa dang ni lcug phran tshal //
NK070(thu)001:10351: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10352: phrin las rnam bzhi'i yum ste /
NK070(thu)001:10354: zhi ba'i gzungs la shing ljon pa dang chos mthun
NK070(thu)001:10355: pa'i dung can ma ni kha dog dkar mo lus
NK070(thu)001:10356: bu chung la skad gdang che ba //
NK070(thu)001:10358: yan lag dang nying lag phra ba 'jam pa skad gsal zhing //
NK070(thu)001:10359: rlung khar te phyi nang gi byed spyod dang /
NK070(thu)001:10360: bsrung sdom thams cad la lci bas gsang thub pa ni zhi ba'i yum du shes par bya //
NK070(thu)001:10362: rgyas pa'i yum ni lcug phran gyi tshal dang chos
NK070(thu)001:10363: mthun pa'i ba glang can spun zla dang yan lag
NK070(thu)001:10365: lus sam mkha'i dbyings 'phra zhing bshan la gzangs su ring //
NK070(thu)001:10366: bzhin dang lus kyi kha dog ser zhing dbyibs gru bzhir gnas //
NK070(thu)001:10368: rna ba 'phyang ba sha 0 dang nu 0ma rgyas //
NK070(thu)001:10370: 'phel ba'i rgyas pa dus su yum 'di dag gzungs //
NK070(thu)001:10372: shing sdong gcig dang chos mthun pa'i pad+ma can ni
NK070(thu)001:10373: bzhin gyi mdog pad ma 'dra ba dbyibs sog ka
NK070(thu)001:10374: 'dra ba la // smin ma'i dkyus ring la lus kyi stod smad phyed //
NK070(thu)001:10375: lus dang rngul chu dang mkha'i rlung la dri zhim zhing //
NK070(thu)001:10376: bde ba bskyed pa dang ldan zhing yan lag bu tsha med //
NK070(thu)001:10378: yum 'di ni dbang du sdud pa'i mchog tu 'gyur //
NK070(thu)001:10379: drag po'i yum ni shing mes reg pa dang chos
NK070(thu)001:10380: mthun pa'i ri mo can ni kha dog nag mo
NK070(thu)001:10381: bzhin gyi dbyibs gru gsum skra nag la rtsub pa
NK070(thu)001:10382: rtsid mgo ma // khro gnyer dang gal bag chags pas byis sba'i lus dang ldan zhing //
NK070(thu)001:10383: ro tshad gtum zhing ngag barlanga po'i tshig tu smra zhes 'dzem bag med //
NK070(thu)001:10385: gtsang sme'i rtog pa dang bral ba gsod par drag po'i yum yin pa bshad //
NK070(thu)001:10387: dwangs bas dga' bas chags pa dang //
NK070(thu)001:10388: khros pas ka li rab tu bya //
NK070(thu)001:10390: phrin las rnam bzhi'i bsam pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10391: don sems mtshungs ldan rgyud la gnas tshul yin te /
NK070(thu)001:10392: de'ang zhi ba'i don sems ni 'khor ba'i chos 1thams cad dang /
NK070(thu)001:10393: gnas skabs yid du mi 'ong ba'i dngos po 1rnams
NK070(thu)001:10394: sems la 11rang bzhin gyis mi gnas pa ste dwangs
NK070(thu)001:10395: pa dang gdung sems ni gdug pa zhi bar 'dod
NK070(thu)001:10396: pa'i las kyi sbyor bas de'i grogs byed pa'i bsam
NK070(thu)001:10397: pa ste las kyi kun slong gi bsam pa dwangs
NK070(thu)001:10399: rgyas pa'i don sems ni che ba'i yon tan don
NK070(thu)001:10400: gyi dngos po rnams rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i dga'
NK070(thu)001:10403: ra bsam pa dbang gi don sems ni bsgrub bya
NK070(thu)001:10404: sems gang yin pa rang gi sems nyid las mi
NK070(thu)001:10405: gzhan par chags pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10406: gdung sems ni mngon du zhen pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10407: 'i sgo nas bsgrub bya dbang du 'du bar bsam pa /
NK070(thu)001:10409: dngos po'i rang bzhin med du 'jig pa'am yang na /
NK070(thu)001:10411: khros pa'i ka li gdung sems ni /
NK070(thu)001:10412: 'jigs shing brlag par mos pa'i sems kyis las la rab tu sbyor ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10413: ra bya de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi sbyor bar gyur to //
NK070(thu)001:10414: zhes bya ba ni che ba'i tshad du'ang 'gyur la /
NK070(thu)001:10415: gdul bya dus phyi ma gnyis kyi ma 'ongs pa
NK070(thu)001:10416: dang 'byung bar ma nges pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK070(thu)001:10417: nyid de sems can rnams la gnyen po snga ma
NK070(thu)001:10418: 'das pa dang / da lta ba gnyis kyi de
NK070(thu)001:10419: bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad pa phrin las kyi rgyud dag
NK070(thu)001:10422: le'u nyi shu pa khong bkrol ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10424: // de nas mthar phyin khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang lhag
NK070(thu)001:10425: pa'i ting nge 'dzin sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK070(thu)001:10426: la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las spyir bstod
NK070(thu)001:10428: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis shin tu rngams pa'i gdangs kyis glu 'di blangs so //
NK070(thu)001:10430: rab tu mang ba'i tshogs khro bo rang bzhin gyis
NK070(thu)001:10431: dkyil 'khor de dag rnams kyis zhal khro tshul ldan
NK070(thu)001:10432: pa'i shin tu thugs rje che bas 'dzum pa dang
NK070(thu)001:10433: bcas pa ni / rngam pa'i mdangs kyis zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10434: glu nga ro dang bcas pas bstod pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10435: 'i 'di dag blangs so zhes pa dang po sku la bstod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10436: h'u gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK070(thu)001:10437: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10438: ye shes lnga po re re yang ye shes lnga
NK070(thu)001:10439: ka'i bdag nyid du mtshon pa'i h'u ni glu nyid
NK070(thu)001:10441: nam rol pa'i phyir glu'i 'go drang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10442: 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi khro bo de dag kun
NK070(thu)001:10443: kyang rngams pa'i tshems mche ba gtsigs pas gtum pa
NK070(thu)001:10444: dang / 'bar ba'i sku 'jigs pa'i cha byad gtum pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10445: phrin las drag shul mdzad pa'i phyag 'jigs pa'i mtshon
NK070(thu)001:10446: cha sna tshogs bsnams nas gtum pa'i ste gnod sbyin
NK070(thu)001:10447: la sogs pa'i 'gran zla med pa phyir chen po
NK070(thu)001:10448: ste / khro bo de lta bu'i sku las bzod
NK070(thu)001:10449: par dka' ba'i me dpung ste spyir me la bzhi
NK070(thu)001:10450: ste / las / bskal pa'i 'jig pa'i dus mtha'
NK070(thu)001:10451: me ltar 'khrugs shing 'bar ba'i nang na bzhugs pa'o
NK070(thu)001:10452: ste / las / // 'od zer nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi //
NK070(thu)001:10454: mun pa sel ba'i 'od zer ni ngo bo gsal ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10455: thabs la mkhas pa'i 'od zer ni kha dog sna tshogs pa mang po dang /
NK070(thu)001:10456: thugs rje chen po'i 'od zer gyis thams cad du khyab pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10457: de dag dper na nyi ma 'bum tsho gcig dus
NK070(thu)001:10458: gcig tu shar ba'i 'od ltar gzhan gyis ril thams
NK070(thu)001:10460: 'i gzi brjid che ba khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK070(thu)001:10462: thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i khro gnyer ni dpral ba'i smin mtshams su bsdus pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10463: zil gyis gnon pa'i khro gnyer ni gyen du bzhi 'greng ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10464: thabs la mkhas pa'i khro gnyer ni 'phred du gsum gsum ste drug /
NK070(thu)001:10465: sna tshogs su g.yo ba de dag dper na glog stong dus gcig 'gyu ba ltar 'khyug pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10466: mche ba zangs yag za byed che ho //
NK070(thu)001:10468: skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i mche ba ni rtse mo dkar ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10469: gdug pa can za byed kyis mche ba ni rtsa ba dmar ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10470: rngam pa'i mche ba ni rab tu rno ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10471: rnams zangs yag 'bar ba ltar gdug pa ga can
NK070(thu)001:10472: za bar byed pa 'gran pa'i zla med par che
NK070(thu)001:10473: ba gsung rngam par sgrogs pa'i nga ro drag po'i
NK070(thu)001:10475: 'brug stong dus gcig tu ldir ba tsam du thugs chem ri rab 'bum snyil skad /
NK070(thu)001:10477: spyan drangs pa'i tshe lha gshegs pa'i thugs chem che ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10478: bdud brtul ba'i tshe phrin las mdzad pa'i thugs chem drag po dang /
NK070(thu)001:10479: gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshe sprul pa 'khrugs pa'i thugs chem /
NK070(thu)001:10480: mnga' ba'o de dag ni dper na ris 'bum dus gcig tu snyil ba'i skad grags pa tsam mo //
NK070(thu)001:10481: a a ha he gad rgyang che /
NK070(thu)001:10483: gdug pa can la rngam pa'i gad mo ni a a /
NK070(thu)001:10484: gtum pa'i gad mo ni ha ha /
NK070(thu)001:10485: dgyes pa'i gad mo ni he he'o //
NK070(thu)001:10486: gsum ni rgyangs nas sgra rab tu che ba /
NK070(thu)001:10487: phyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che //
NK070(thu)001:10489: 'khor sdud pa'i dbyug pa ni 'phra la snyan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10490: gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyug pa ni drag po dang /
NK070(thu)001:10491: byin pheb pa'i dbyug pa ni 'tshor zhing ring la che ba ste /
NK070(thu)001:10492: de dag las 'thor rlung chen po 'byung bas khams gsum g.yeng bar byed do //
NK070(thu)001:10493: pas che la 'gran zla med thugs la bstod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10494: h'u khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK070(thu)001:10496: shes rab ye shes phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo
NK070(thu)001:10497: dang gsum ni 'dir khro bo nyid shes rab kyi
NK070(thu)001:10498: ngo bo ste / ci zhe na ltas ngan gyi
NK070(thu)001:10499: ril mi dmigs par te phyogs re ba'i mtha' dang
NK070(thu)001:10500: bral byed pa'i phyir de cis kyang ma bsgrib par
NK070(thu)001:10501: gsal bas na 'od po che ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10502: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK070(thu)001:10504: shes byed thugs ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor shes bya
NK070(thu)001:10505: ma lus par kun dus gcig tu yul med pa
NK070(thu)001:10506: rang la mkhyen pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10507: de la 'bar ba rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:10508: kyi ngo bo snang ba thams cad kyang nyid las
NK070(thu)001:10509: mi gzhan par sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10510: lta ngan thams cad kun du 'joms pas na /
NK070(thu)001:10513: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK070(thu)001:10515: sna tshogs ye shes chen po bco brgyad ni kun 'dus le'u dang po nas /
NK070(thu)001:10522: cir yang mdzad pa'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10523: me long lta bu ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10524: nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10525: sgyu ma lta bu'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10526: rin cen lta bu'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10527: nyi ma lta bu'i ye shes /
NK070(thu)001:10533: mi rtogs pa'i ye shes so //
NK070(thu)001:10534: yang na nang pa'i ye shes lnga /
NK070(thu)001:10538: thams cad mkhyen pa dang dgu /
NK070(thu)001:10540: mdo sde'i ye shes bzhi dang bco brgyad /
NK070(thu)001:10541: la sogs pa rtsis la 'das pa rnams tha dad
NK070(thu)001:10542: du gsal ba kun gyi mi gnas pa'i ye shes
NK070(thu)001:10543: chen por gcig par bstod pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10544: shes pas na thig le che zhes h'u khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK070(thu)001:10546: zhes bya ba ni yon tan la bstod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10547: khro bo'i rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor 'di dag gi yon tan gyi tshogs rab tu mang po /
NK070(thu)001:10548: sprin chen po lta bur 'khrigs pa las /
NK070(thu)001:10549: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor so so'i sprul pa dang bcas
NK070(thu)001:10550: pa bsam yas pa gdul bya tha dad la dgos
NK070(thu)001:10553: de dag mi zad pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10554: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag kyang yid bzhin gyi
NK070(thu)001:10555: nor bu las dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i tshul du mi
NK070(thu)001:10556: zad pa'i gter gyi gdul bya so so'i re ba
NK070(thu)001:10559: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che /
NK070(thu)001:10561: yon tan sna tshogs dang bcas pa'i khros pa'i tshul
NK070(thu)001:10562: ston pa khro bo rnams ye shes chen po'i khro
NK070(thu)001:10564: pa ni thig le zhes bya /
NK070(thu)001:10565: phrin las la bstod pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10566: h'u bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK070(thu)001:10567: bdud kyi bdud ste bdun rnams 'joms zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10568: phung po la sogs pa bdud bzhi po ma lus
NK070(thu)001:10569: pa spangs pa med par dbang du byed pa ni
NK070(thu)001:10570: bdag nyid chen po badz+ra he ru ka ste /
NK070(thu)001:10572: bdud ru tra sde dang bcas pa rnams kyi yang
NK070(thu)001:10573: bdud ltar du snang ba yin te pho rnams kyi
NK070(thu)001:10574: phung po bsgral zhing gnas spar nas /
NK070(thu)001:10575: phyi rol gzhan snang du pham par snang ba ni bdud rnams bcom pa ste 'joms pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10577: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che ho //
NK070(thu)001:10579: de'i phyir 'jigs pa'i tshogs ru tra sde dang bcas pa thams cad kyang /
NK070(thu)001:10580: bsdigs nas 'jigs par byed pa'i tshul du snang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10581: 'jigs byed khro bo chen po'i mdzad pa ril thams
NK070(thu)001:10582: cad ye shes kyi mdzad pa nyid las ma g.yos
NK070(thu)001:10583: par rang snang ba'i sa na thig le che zhes
NK070(thu)001:10584: pa phyir ro // don rnams par mi rtog pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10585: ye shes de mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pas mi
NK070(thu)001:10586: shigs pa'i rtags su khro bo rnams kyi sku ni
NK070(thu)001:10587: dper na rdo rje brag chen sra ba po /
NK070(thu)001:10589: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po /
NK070(thu)001:10591: don 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du stud cing /
NK070(thu)001:10592: ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rje chags pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10593: rtags su khrag gi rgya mtsho zhal du rngub cing
NK070(thu)001:10594: gsol ba'o // rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che /
NK070(thu)001:10596: don ye shes kyi me des mtshan ma'i bag chags
NK070(thu)001:10597: thams cad mi gnas pa'i bsregs pa'i rtags su me
NK070(thu)001:10598: dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10599: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho /
NK070(thu)001:10601: don ye shes kyi rlung gis rnam par rtog pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10602: rlung skyed byed kyi dbyings su 'thor bar byed pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10603: rtags su zhal dang shangs nas shugs rlung drag po
NK070(thu)001:10605: de dag gi mjug bsdus nas bstod pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10606: khro bo rnams kyi ni ngo bo'am rang bzhin mi sa phyed chupa medang /
NK070(thu)001:10607: phrin las kyi gzhan bdud bzhi rlung'jams pa'i phyir rdo rje bzhi kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:10608: gnyis po de dag gi phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10609: yang na khro bo de dag gi gnyis med kyi
NK070(thu)001:10610: ye shes su 'degs pas sa gnyis med du sdud
NK070(thu)001:10611: pa / rtog pa'i bag chags bsregs pas me tog pa 'thor bas rlung dang /
NK070(thu)001:10612: dpe bzhi lta bur snang ba'o //
NK070(thu)001:10613: de las gzhan yang rnam gcig tu dur khrod kyi 'byung ba bzhi po la sbyar te /
NK070(thu)001:10614: de yang keng rus kyis ri rab rak+ta'i rgya mtsho /
NK070(thu)001:10615: bskal pa'i me dang rlung dang de yang sems ye shes rdo rje'i ngo bor bstod pa yang /
NK070(thu)001:10617: le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa mdor bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10619: // de nas brjod bya rjod byed kyi rgyud gnyis sdud pa po la yongs su gtad cing /
NK070(thu)001:10620: rnal 'byor pa la mi nub par bzung bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10621: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes po chen pos de
NK070(thu)001:10622: pa nyid la sngar gyi rgyal por brtan par bzung
NK070(thu)001:10624: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10625: gang gis na bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos
NK070(thu)001:10626: gang la na 'khor thams cad de'ang go phye ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10627: 'khor ni rang bzhin la dgongs nas /
NK070(thu)001:10628: nyid las mi gzhan pa nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:10629: lhan cig pa'i 'khor la yongs su rdzogs par dgongs pa thugs su chud pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10630: 'khor gnyis po gang la yang de pa nyid la zer ba 'gal ba med pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10631: gsang sngags kyi rgyud rang bzhin dang lam gyi rgyud /
NK070(thu)001:10632: gnyis ni theg pa'i ngo bo dang yon tan le'u
NK070(thu)001:10633: bcu gsum pa dang bcu gnyis bar bshad pa rnams
NK070(thu)001:10634: kyi don gyis na rgyal po kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:10635: dgos ched ci'i phyir na rgyud de dag rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10636: gyi rgyud gzhan du mi 'gyur bar brten par bya
NK070(thu)001:10637: ba dang / lam gyi lha gzung bas mi nus pa ni brtan pa zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10638: yongs su gtad pa la gdams pa dang gtad pa gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:10639: dang po rang bzhin gyi rgyud mi 'gyur bar gdams pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10641: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK070(thu)001:10642: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK070(thu)001:10644: 'khor thams cad ni ston pa nyid las rang bzhin dbang du mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10645: kye kye zhes gus pas bos pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10646: gang la bos na sdud pa po lhan cig pa'am /
NK070(thu)001:10648: go phye ba gang zag chos kyi ming can nam ma 'ongs 1pa'i de bzhin gshegs 11pa gnyis so //
NK070(thu)001:10650: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i tha snyad gnyis kyi bsdus
NK070(thu)001:10651: pa'i 'khor 'das ril gyi chos kyi rang bzhin gyi
NK070(thu)001:10652: chos nyid ni / 0bud+d+ha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sku gsung thugs gsum dang /
NK070(thu)001:10653: rtsa lnga'i sku dang ye shes su ye gdod ma
NK070(thu)001:10654: nas gnas pa'i 'i ni de dgongs pa rang bzhin
NK070(thu)001:10655: gsang ba'i snying po'i ngo bo nyid /
NK070(thu)001:10657: don ni nges pa'i lung kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10658: de ni sems can thams cad la rang bzhin gyis gnas pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10659: dus gsum du mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10660: 'o na lam la dgos pa med pa 'gyur ro
NK070(thu)001:10661: snyam na da ni lam gyi rgyud yongs su gtad
NK070(thu)001:10662: pa bstan te / lam gyi rgyud de dag gi bshad pa'i dgongs pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10664: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK070(thu)001:10665: zhes bya ba ni 0yin de ltar yin mod kyi /
NK070(thu)001:10666: de ltar ma rtogs te ma rig pa'i bdag tu
NK070(thu)001:10667: 'dzin pa las byung ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi kun brtags
NK070(thu)001:10668: gnyis kyis spros pa la 'khor ba thog ma med
NK070(thu)001:10669: pa'i dus nas mngon par 'chal goms pa'am mthus rnam
NK070(thu)001:10670: par rtog pa'i zhags pas 'gro drug gi gnas so
NK070(thu)001:10671: sor 'dzin pas bcings pa'i 'gro ba dag gi bdag
NK070(thu)001:10672: nyid ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa ngo mi shes
NK070(thu)001:10673: pa dag / gzung 'dzin kun brtags kyis zhen pa
NK070(thu)001:10674: bkrol ba nyid kyis rgyal ba dang dus mnyam du
NK070(thu)001:10676: lam rkyen gyi rgyud rnams gsungs pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10677: 'o na nye lam khyad par lam gsang ba'i snying
NK070(thu)001:10678: po gcig bus chog pas thun mong gi lam du
NK070(thu)001:10679: ma nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi gsungs pa dgos
NK070(thu)001:10680: pa med do bar zhes dogs pa la theg pa
NK070(thu)001:10681: 'og ma'i sa dang lam rnams kyi mtho dman gyi
NK070(thu)001:10682: khyad par bkod pa de yang /
NK070(thu)001:10683: mthar thug gsang ba'i snying por de 'gro ba'i lam /
NK070(thu)001:10684: steg gi dgos ched yin no //
NK070(thu)001:10685: des na mthar phyin pa'i ye shes ngo mtshar can
NK070(thu)001:10686: rab 'byams dpag tu med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi 'gro
NK070(thu)001:10687: ba'i don du mi 'gyur ba'i lam ni yongs ma
NK070(thu)001:10690: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni shin tu rtogs dka' shing /
NK070(thu)001:10691: zab pas gang zag phal gyi blo'i spyod yul ma
NK070(thu)001:10692: yin pa de yang thun mong gi lam la blo
NK070(thu)001:10693: rim par sbyangs pa rnams kyis don rtogs shing myong
NK070(thu)001:10694: du rung ba'i phyir des na thun mong gi sa
NK070(thu)001:10695: dang / lam mtha' yas pa yang gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud /
NK070(thu)001:10696: 'di nyid kyi byin brlabs kyi khyad par las bkod cing snang bar byas pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10698: yongs su gtad pa dngos la rnam pa gnyis las /
NK070(thu)001:10699: sdud pa po la dang po rgyud kyi mtshan nyid
NK070(thu)001:10700: brjod nas yongs su gtad pa bstan pa'i phyir de
NK070(thu)001:10702: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' /
NK070(thu)001:10703: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10704: de bzhin gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:10705: dgongs pa phyin ci ma log par mngon du bstan
NK070(thu)001:10706: pa la rang bzhin gyi rgyud gsang ba'i snying po
NK070(thu)001:10707: 'di yin phyir las ma rtogs pa de nas gzhan
NK070(thu)001:10708: mi mnga' pa'i sgro bskur pa zhi ba'i /
NK070(thu)001:10709: gsang 00 ba'i snying po de kho na /
NK070(thu)001:10710: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyungs //
NK070(thu)001:10712: de lta bu'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i ngo bo nyid 'di 'dra bar sgro 'dogs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10713: skur pa 'debs pa gnyis ka med par zhi ba'i don phyin ci ma log par ston pa ni /
NK070(thu)001:10714: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid de nges pa'i don zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10715: lam gyi rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'di kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:10716: shes bya'i rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi ming gsang ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10717: snying po ni shes byed lam gyi rgyud las btags
NK070(thu)001:10718: pa'i phyir ro // des nas rang bzhin gyi rgyud
NK070(thu)001:10719: gsang snying ni gcig shos lam gyi rgyud ril gyi
NK070(thu)001:10720: 'byung khungs su gyur pa'i dbyings de las lam rkyen
NK070(thu)001:10721: yi ge'i rgyud 'di nyid mngon du snang ba ni
NK070(thu)001:10723: nges pa'i lung las byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10724: mngon du phyung ba'i lung ngo //
NK070(thu)001:10726: lung 'di bka' sdud pa po phyag rdor la khyod kyi lung 'di zungs shig par gtad /
NK070(thu)001:10728: sgrub pa po la mi nub par gzung bar gtad pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10729: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK070(thu)001:10730: phyag rgya gsang chen 'di yin te //
NK070(thu)001:10731: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK070(thu)001:10732: rgyud 'di'i rigs don ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK070(thu)001:10733: cad kyi bdag po'i drug pa kun tu bzang po
NK070(thu)001:10735: gsung gi chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10736: gsang chen snying po 'di lam gyi rgyud 'di rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi don 1mtshan pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10737: 'dis rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ngo bo nyid dang /
NK070(thu)001:10738: gcig par 'di las 11mi 'da' ba'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10739: phyag rgya rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK070(thu)001:10740: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK070(thu)001:10743: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK070(thu)001:10744: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:10745: zhes bshad 00 pa nyid kyi phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10746: rgyud 'di rang gi phyin ci ma log par rtogs shing nyams su lon nas /
NK070(thu)001:10747: mi nub par bya ba'i phyir snod dang ldan pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10748: gdul bya rnams la blo dang 'tshams par smra zhing
NK070(thu)001:10749: / sgrogs pa ra gang byed pa de nyid ni
NK070(thu)001:10750: ston pa kun bzang nga nyid dang khyad par med
NK070(thu)001:10752: phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang lnga yang yongs su
NK070(thu)001:10753: rdzogs pas dbang gi nus pa chen po dang ldan
NK070(thu)001:10754: pa zhes bya'o // de ni nges par lung bstan te /
NK070(thu)001:10755: sras ni thugs la skyes pa yin //
NK070(thu)001:10757: de lta bu'i gang zag ni sa la gnas pa'i byang sems du nges par lung bstan te /
NK070(thu)001:10759: de ni kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK070(thu)001:10760: rang rig pa las phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK070(thu)001:10761: pa'i phyir ro // skyes pa yin zhes pa rgyu
NK070(thu)001:10762: 'bras kyi sa la byas pa'i byang sems du lung
NK070(thu)001:10763: bstan pa gang yin snyam pa la rgyu'i theg pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10764: sa las mchog tu gyur pa'i rab rig pa 'dzin
NK070(thu)001:10769: rang rig pa'i ye shes ni rgyud kyi don yin pa'i phyir //
NK070(thu)001:10770: yul med par rang snang ba'i rig pa yis mngon du byas pas //
NK070(thu)001:10771: rig 'dzin gsum gyi mchog de lhun gyis 'grub pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10772: ma bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi nus pa'i mthu stobs med kyang //
NK070(thu)001:10773: sa rim bar sbyangs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bskyed ste 'dren du med //
NK070(thu)001:10774: bde bar gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK070(thu)001:10776: rig pa'i skyes bu zhes bya ba'i lung thob pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10778: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dbyer med par dgyes nas /
NK070(thu)001:10780: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba de pa'i ril thams cad
NK070(thu)001:10781: yang dgongs pa bde ba chen por ro gcig par
NK070(thu)001:10782: dgongs pa dbyer med par snang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10783: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dgyes nas zhes pa zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10784: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings //
NK070(thu)001:10785: sku gsung thugs kyi lhun stug po bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:10787: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi bsdus pa'i chos ril thams
NK070(thu)001:10788: cad rang rig pa nyid kho na las gzhan med
NK070(thu)001:10789: cing / rang rig par mnyam pa'i dbyings de nyid
NK070(thu)001:10790: kyi ngo bo gsung rang rgyud du ma grub kapar
NK070(thu)001:10791: chos thams cad du ma 'gag par rang snang ba
NK070(thu)001:10793: 0 snang stong gnyis su mi phyed pas thugs de
NK070(thu)001:10794: nyid logs su ma rtsal ba'i sku gsung thugs lhun
NK070(thu)001:10796: de dag gi ngo bo nyid ni tshig tu'am phyogs
NK070(thu)001:10797: gcig tu 'di 'drar brjod pa las 'das pas don
NK070(thu)001:10798: de nyid grangs mtha' yas pa'i sku dang ye 00shes
NK070(thu)001:10799: kyi phyag rgya stug po bkod bar gsal ba ste
NK070(thu)001:10800: / de las gzhan pa'i sel med par sku ye shes sha stag gis yongs su gang ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10801: dper na til gyi gang bu ltar chos kyi dbyings
NK070(thu)001:10802: kyis mtha' yas par sku dang ye shes kyis bdal
NK070(thu)001:10803: pa ste / de dag kyang shin tu stug po bkod pa'i rgyan gyis mdzes pa'i phyir dang /
NK070(thu)001:10804: don gyi ngo bo nyid tshig tu brjod par dka'
NK070(thu)001:10805: bas na bltas pas mi ngom pa dang chos thams
NK070(thu)001:10807: rang rig pa'i rgyan nyid du kho na ste /
NK070(thu)001:10808: phan tshun rgyan dang rgyan can tha dad med par ring thung spangs pa kho na'o //
NK070(thu)001:10809: rgyal pa thams cad dgongs pa de lta bu'i ngo
NK070(thu)001:10810: bor gnas pa'i yul med pa'i tshul du rang gsal
NK070(thu)001:10811: bar gnas pa ni bzhugs pa ste /
NK070(thu)001:10812: rgyal ba 'di dag gi rang gi ngo bo nyid
NK070(thu)001:10813: dang thugs kyi dgongs pa de las ni bzhengs pa'i
NK070(thu)001:10814: rjes thob dang bzhugs pa'i mnyam bzhag gnyis dus nam
NK070(thu)001:10815: du yang mi dmigs pas na spyir rtags la ngo
NK070(thu)001:10819: rnam pa gsum las 'dir ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10821: ngo bo nyid rtag rdo rje sku /
NK070(thu)001:10822: ther zug rgyun la rang grol ba /
NK070(thu)001:10823: zhes bka' lung du ma las bzhugs so //
NK070(thu)001:10824: 'phags pa bzhi rtogs pa lnga'i rgyal po zhes bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10825: shes bya lta ba dbyer med de bden pa tha dad du 'dod pa las 'phags pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10826: thabs spyod pa nyon mongs pa la spyod kyang mi
NK070(thu)001:10827: 'ching bar grol bas spang sbyang 'dod pa las 'phags
NK070(thu)001:10828: pa dang / dus tshe gcig la 'bras bu thob
NK070(thu)001:10829: pas bskal pa grangs med gsum la sogs pa las
NK070(thu)001:10830: pa dang / 'phags pa dang / 'bras bu mthar
NK070(thu)001:10831: thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga lhun grub thob pas
NK070(thu)001:10832: kun tu 'od las 'phags pa la sogs pa'i 'khor
NK070(thu)001:10833: du lta spyod ting nge 'dzin dam tshig la sogs
NK070(thu)001:10834: phyi rgyud man chad kyi lugs gzhan las /
NK070(thu)001:10836: ngo bo nyid kyis togs pa ni chos nyid du zhen pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10837: so so'i skye bo 'khrul pa'i rtogs pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10838: mu steg rtag chad log pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10839: sems dang sems byung yul gyi snang ba'i rnam par rtog pa dang /
NK070(thu)001:10840: yang dag pa'i rtogs pa la sogs pa las /
NK070(thu)001:10841: lam gsang ba'i snying po'i sgra /
NK070(thu)001:10842: spyir snang ba rtog pa chos spyir dang rang gi
NK070(thu)001:10843: mtshan nyid mngon par 'byed pa'i rtogs pa 'di dag
NK070(thu)001:10844: ni / mtshon bya yang dag pa'i don la blos nges par nges par ma nor 'byed pa'i phyir /
NK070(thu)001:10845: na yang dag pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10846: de'i phyir rtogs pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK070(thu)001:10848: 'khor lo bskor ba de dag gi 'bras bu'i mchog ces bya ba ni /
NK070(thu)001:10849: bud+d+ha'i bstan pa rnams ni dang po 'khor la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10850: ston pa'i dgongs pa 'khor gyi blo la 'char nas 'khor ba dang /
NK070(thu)001:10853: bstan pa dang theg pa mang por spros pa ste
NK070(thu)001:10854: bskor ba de dag gi mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK070(thu)001:10856: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu rnams las kyang /
NK070(thu)001:10857: 'di'i 'bras bur lam bzo dang bgrod dgos pa'i phyir na mchog go //
NK070(thu)001:10858: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa mnyes
NK070(thu)001:10859: kha pa dang yongs kabzung ba zhes bya ba ni
NK070(thu)001:10860: / rang bzhin gyi mdzad kapa yongs su bzung ba rdzogs pas /
NK070(thu)001:10861: ston 'khor khathams cad kyang dbyer med par dgyes pas na mnyes pa'i phyir ro //
NK070(thu)001:10862: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa man ngag rim pa 'khrugs sdebs nas bshad pa'o //
NK070(thu)001:10864: // dper na stong 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po bsod
NK070(thu)001:10865: nams kyis tshogs dang ldan yang rgyal srid sna bdun
NK070(thu)001:10866: la sogs pa de bzhin du don sems nyid ni
NK070(thu)001:10867: chos thams cad du rang snang du shar ba rang
NK070(thu)001:10868: byung gis ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa'i don
NK070(thu)001:10869: nyid rang snang na yang gdul bya las dang po
NK070(thu)001:10870: ba rnams ma rtogs pa de nyid mngon du snang
NK070(thu)001:10871: bar byed pa'i rkyen dgos pa dang ldan pa ni
NK070(thu)001:10872: dper na nor bu rin po che lta bu ste
NK070(thu)001:10873: rgyud don mtshon par byed pa'i 'grel pa 'di sgro
NK070(thu)001:10874: skur dang bral bar bshad rgyud la sogs pa'i lung
NK070(thu)001:10875: gi don mngon du gsal bar 'byin pa /
NK070(thu)001:10876: 'i don gang yin pa de snod ngan pa gzhan
NK070(thu)001:10877: la brda' tshigs sbas nas bzhag ste blo rmongs pa
NK070(thu)001:10878: rang gis ma rtogs pa'i sgrib pa gnyis kyi rdul
NK070(thu)001:10879: dang 'dra bas g.yogs nas ma rtogs te rang gi
NK070(thu)001:10880: blo ngan pa'i rtog pa can de rigs ngan yin
NK070(thu)001:10881: pas de'i blo la rgyud kyi don mi gsal ba
NK070(thu)001:10882: / ste mi shes pa gang yin pa de gsal
NK070(thu)001:10883: bar byed pa dper na don de mtshon byed la
NK070(thu)001:10884: rin po che kha dog sna tshogs shel gyi spar
NK070(thu)001:10886: bla ma gcig nas gcig gi rna bar brgyud pa'i man ngag dang /
NK070(thu)001:10887: rang gi blo yi nyams kyis bkrol pa'i 'grel pa
NK070(thu)001:10888: rang la bltas nas rgyud kyi don kun gsal ba
NK070(thu)001:10889: de ltar sems can kun gyis kyang rtogs par shog
NK070(thu)001:10891: 'phags pa dpal gsang ba'i snying po zhes bya ba'i
NK070(thu)001:10892: 'grel pa dpe la mtshan du btags pa rin po
NK070(thu)001:10893: che spar bkab zhes bya ba rgya gar gyi slob
NK070(thu)001:10894: dpon chen po sgeg pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs
NK070(thu)001:10895: so // rgyud rgyal snying po sgeg pa'i rdo rje yi //
NK070(thu)001:10896: rin chen spar khab rgya chen 'grel na yang //
NK070(thu)001:10897: de la nyi zer phog na ches gsal ltar //
NK070(thu)001:10898: de phyir rgyud 'grel bsdebs pas mchan du gnyer //
NK070(thu)001:10899: ji ltar rgyal rigs gang zag gsum brgyud pa'i //
NK070(thu)001:10900: bshad 'grel du ma'i gsung sgros rjes 'brang nas //
NK070(thu)001:10901: klog pa tsam gyis nyan bshad go chod pas //
NK070(thu)001:10902: rgyud don bde blag tu ni chud phyir bris //
NK070(thu)001:10903: 'di la nongs pa gang dang gang mchis pa //
NK070(thu)001:10904: chos kyi spyan chen mnga' ba'i spyan ldan rnams //
NK070(thu)001:10905: rang bzhin dgongs nas bzod mdzod rjes bzung rigs //
NK070(thu)001:10906: dge ba mkha' mnyam sems can don du bsngo //
NK070(thu)001:10907: rgyud 'grel zung du bsdebs pa'i mchan bu nyi ma'i
NK070(thu)001:10908: 'od zer zhes bya ba 'di ni rje ga ga
NK070(thu)001:10909: ke tu'i 'bangs kyi tha mar pa nam mkha' dpal
NK070(thu)001:10910: gyis kahthoga ri khrod chos gling yang dgon du sbyar
